#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:822-5
msgid ""
"You are currently reading the <b>English</b> (main) version of the "
"<b>KOReader User Guide</b>. Also volunteers are translating this guide to "
"other languages. We have many translations in progress, as you can see in "
"the <b>overall translation status</b> below. But we only link to the "
"languages which are translated <b>above 50%</b> for usability reasons."
msgstr ""
"Tá tú ag léamh an leagan <b>Béarla</b> (príomhleagan) de <b>Treoir Úsáideora "
"KOReader</b> faoi láthair. Chomh maith leis sin, tá oibrithe deonacha ag "
"aistriú an treoir seo go teangacha eile. Tá go leor aistriúcháin ar siúl "
"againn, mar is féidir leat a fheiceáil sa <b>stádas foriomlán aistriúcháin</"
"b> thíos. Ach ní nascann muid ach leis na teangacha atá aistrithe <b>os "
"cionn 50%</b> ar chúiseanna inúsáidteachta."

