#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:879-5
msgid ""
"This guide is primarily designed for color screens. If you are using it for "
"the first time, we highly recommend reading this on a computer, tablet or "
"mobile. Because seeing user interface elements highlighted in color will "
"make your life easier while learning how to use KOReader. Of course you can "
"read this on your e-ink device too, but the experience will not be optimal."
msgstr ""
"Tá an treoir seo deartha go príomha do scáileáin datha. Más é seo an chéad "
"uair atá tú á úsáid, molaimid go mór duit é seo a léamh ar ríomhaire, "
"taibléad nó fón póca. Mar má fheictear eilimintí comhéadain úsáideora atá "
"aibhsithe i ndath, beidh sé níos fusa duit agus tú ag foghlaim conas "
"KOReader a úsáid. Ar ndóigh, is féidir leat é seo a léamh ar do ghléas dúigh "
"leictreonach freisin, ach ní bheidh an taithí is fearr."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:881-5
msgid ""
"You can use the search function of your browser to find a specific topic or "
"keyword (generally <b>Ctrl + F</b>). If you have a suggestion or question "
"related to this user guide, you can write to this <a href=\"https://"
"github.com/koreader/koreader/issues/11147\">GitHub discussion thread</a>."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat feidhm chuardaigh do bhrabhsálaí a úsáid chun topaic nó "
"eochairfhocal ar leith a aimsiú (de ghnáth <b>Ctrl + F</b>). Má tá moladh nó "
"ceist agat a bhaineann leis an treoir úsáideora seo, is féidir leat scríobh "
"chuig an <a href=\"https://github.com/koreader/koreader/issues/"
"11147\">snáithe plé GitHub</a> seo."

