#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1075-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L1-whatcanyoudo"
msgid "WHAT CAN YOU DO WITH KOREADER ?"
msgstr "CAD IS FÉIDIR LEAT A DHÉANAMH LE KOREADER?"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1077-2
msgid ""
"Despite its minimalistic looks, KOReader is a very powerful and customizable "
"application. This section is like a table of contents which is how-to "
"oriented. So if you are a new user, this is the best place to start. Here "
"you can read what KOReader can do and learn how to do it by following these "
"<a href=\"#L1-whatcanyoudo\" class=\"internalink\"></a> links to go to the "
"mentioned sections."
msgstr ""
"In ainneoin a chuma íostach, is feidhmchlár an-chumhachtach agus "
"inoiriúnaithe é KOReader. Tá an chuid seo cosúil le clár ábhair atá dírithe "
"ar conas a dhéanamh. Mar sin, más úsáideoir nua thú, seo an áit is fearr le "
"tosú. Anseo is féidir leat léamh faoi na rudaí is féidir le KOReader a "
"dhéanamh agus foghlaim conas é a dhéanamh trí na naisc <a href=\"#L1-"
"whatcanyoudo\" class=\"internalink\"></a> seo a leanúint chun dul chuig na "
"rannóga a luaitear."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1079-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">INFO</span> Name of KOReader comes from the "
"beginnings of the project: <b>K</b>indle/<b>K</b>obo <b>O</b>pen Reader. Of "
"course the reader grew so much over the years, now an accurate abbreviation "
"would be something like <b>KKPRCSALMOReader</b> (Kindle Kobo Pocketbook "
"Remarkable Cervantes Sony Android Linux MacOS Open reader) but this is not "
"that nice to pronounce, so we choose to keep it simple :)"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">EOLAS</span> Tagann ainm KOReader ó thús an "
"tionscadail: <b>K</b>indle/<b>K</b>obo <b>O</b>Pen Reader. Ar ndóigh, d'fhás "
"an léitheoir go mór thar na blianta, anois bheadh giorrúchán cruinn cosúil "
"le <b>KKPRCSALMOReader</b> (Kindle Kobo Pocketbook Remarkable Cervantes Sony "
"Android Linux MacOS Open reader) ach níl sé seo chomh deas sin le fuaimniú, "
"mar sin roghnaíomar é a choinneáil simplí :)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1081-1
msgid "Transfer your reading materials in different ways"
msgstr "Aistrigh d’ábhair léitheoireachta ar bhealaí éagsúla"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1084-9
msgid ""
"<b>USB mass storage</b> mode for supporting devices <a href=\"#L2-"
"transferring\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Mód <b>stórála maise USB</b> le haghaidh gléasanna tacaíochta <a href=\"#L2-"
"transferring\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1086-9
msgid ""
"<b>Cloud storage</b> (<span class=\"external\">Dropbox</span>/FTP/Webdav) "
"with suitable accounts <a href=\"#L2-transferring\" class=\"internalink\"></"
"a>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Stóráil scamall</b> (<span class=\"external\">Dropbox</span>/FTP/Webdav) "
"le cuntais oiriúnacha <a href=\"#L2-transferring\" class=\"internalink\"></"
"a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1088-9
msgid ""
"KOReader can act as an <b>SSH server</b>, so you can use an SFTP application "
"or your file manager to directly transfer files <a href=\"#L2-pluginslist\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le KOReader gníomhú mar <b>fhreastalaí SSH</b>, mar sin is féidir "
"leat feidhmchlár SFTP nó do bhainisteoir comhad a úsáid chun comhaid a "
"aistriú go díreach <a href=\"#L2-pluginslist\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1090-9
msgid ""
"With the <span class=\"external\">Calibre</span> plugin you can send books "
"from your Calibre Library directly to your KOReader devices over wifi <a "
"href=\"#L2-transferring\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Leis an mbreiseán <span class=\"external\">Calibre</span> is féidir leat "
"leabhair a sheoladh ó do Leabharlann Calibre go díreach chuig do ghléasanna "
"KOReader thar wifi <a href=\"#L2-transferring\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1092-9
msgid ""
"With the <b>News downloader plugin</b> you can download RSS and Atom news "
"entries to your device as HTML files <a href=\"#L2-pluginslist\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Leis an <b>breiseán íoslódála nuachta</b> is féidir leat iontrálacha nuachta "
"RSS agus Atom a íoslódáil chuig do ghléas mar chomhaid HTML <a href=\"#L2-"
"pluginslist\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1094-9
msgid ""
"With the Wallabag plugin you can retrieve articles from your Wallabag "
"account (a server based read-it-later service like <span "
"class=\"external\">Pocket</span>) <a href=\"#L2-transferring\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Leis an mbreiseán Wallabag is féidir leat ailt a aisghabháil ó do chuntas "
"Wallabag (seirbhís léigh-é-níos-níos-déanta bunaithe ar fhreastalaí cosúil "
"le <span class=\"external\">Pocket</span>) <a href=\"#L2-transferring\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1097-1
msgid "Adjust the appearance of text as you wish"
msgstr "Coigeartaigh cuma an téacs mar is mian leat"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1099-9
msgid ""
"Change fonts (including your own), font size, contrast, boldness, kerning, "
"word spacing, word expansion, text alignment, line spacing, column layout, "
"margins... <a href=\"#L1-customizingappearance\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Athraigh clónna (lena n-áirítear do chuid féin), méid an chló, codarsnacht, "
"trom, cornáil, spásáil focal, leathnú focal, ailíniú téacs, spásáil líne, "
"leagan amach colún, corrlaigh... <a href=\"#L1-customizingappearance\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1101-9
msgid ""
"Use the included powerful <span class=\"ui\">style tweaks</span> or write "
"your own ones to change how your books are rendered precisely <a href=\"#L2-"
"styletweaks\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Bain úsáid as na <span class=\"ui\">coigeartuithe stíl</span> cumhachtacha "
"atá san áireamh nó scríobh do chuid féin chun an chaoi a ndéantar do "
"leabhair a rindreáil go beacht a athrú <a href=\"#L2-styletweaks\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1103-9
msgid ""
"Invert screen colors for <span class=\"ui\">night mode</span> manually or "
"automatically <a href=\"#L2-autowarmth\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Inbhéartaigh dathanna an scáileáin le haghaidh <span class=\"ui\">mód oíche</"
"span> de láimh nó go huathoibríoch <a href=\"#L2-autowarmth\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1105-9
msgid ""
"Adjust your frontlight color warmth automatically <a href=\"#L2-autowarmth\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Coigeartaigh teas dath do shoilse tosaigh go huathoibríoch <a href=\"#L2-"
"autowarmth\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1108-1
msgid "Take notes and make highlights while reading"
msgstr "Glac nótaí agus déan airdlínse agus tú ag léamh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1110-9
msgid ""
"Highlight text with different styles and colors, place bookmarks <a "
"href=\"#L1-bookmarks\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Aibhsigh téacs le stíleanna agus dathanna éagsúla, cuir leabharmharcanna <a "
"href=\"#L1-bookmarks\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1112-9
msgid ""
"Two-tap mode for academic/longer highlights <a href=\"#L2-howtohighlight\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Mód dhá sconna le haghaidh buaicphointí acadúla/níos faide <a href=\"#L2-"
"howtohighlight\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1114-9
msgid ""
"Add notes using a customizable keyboard including diacritic modifiers <a "
"href=\"#L2-keyboard\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Cuir nótaí leis ag baint úsáide as méarchlár saincheaptha lena n-áirítear "
"modhnóirí diaicriteacha <a href=\"#L2-keyboard\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1116-9
msgid ""
"Take screenshots <a href=\"#L2-predefinedgestures\" class=\"internalink\"></"
"a>"
msgstr ""
"Glac scáileáin <a href=\"#L2-predefinedgestures\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1118-9
msgid ""
"Track your reading statistics including <b>reading progress</b>, <b>time "
"range</b> and <b>calendar views</b>"
msgstr ""
"Rianaigh do staitisticí léitheoireachta lena n-áirítear <b>dul chun cinn "
"léitheoireachta</b>, <b>raon ama</b> agus <b>radhairc féilire</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1121-1
msgid "Export your notes and highlights flexibly"
msgstr "Easpórtáil do nótaí agus buaicphointí go solúbtha"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1123-9
msgid ""
"Export your notes and highlights to your device as text, markdown, HTML, "
"JSON or Kindle clippings format <a href=\"#L2-exportinghighlights\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Easpórtáil do nótaí agus buaicphointí chuig do ghléas mar théacs, marcáil "
"síos, HTML, JSON nó gearrthóga Kindle <a href=\"#L2-exportinghighlights\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1125-9
msgid ""
"Synchronize to online services like <span class=\"external\">Joplin</span>, "
"<span class=\"external\">Readwise</span>, <span class=\"external\">Memos</"
"span>, <span class=\"external\">Flomo</span> and <span "
"class=\"external\">XMNote</span> <a href=\"#L2-exportinghighlights\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Sioncrónaigh le seirbhísí ar líne ar nós <span class=\"external\">Joplin</"
"span>, <span class=\"external\">Readwise</span>, <span "
"class=\"external\">Memos</span>, <span class=\"external\">Flomo</span> agus "
"<span class=\"external\">XMNote</span> <a href=\"#L2-exportinghighlights\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1128-1
msgid "Arrange and browse your library easily"
msgstr "Socraigh agus brabhsáil do leabharlann go héasca"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1130-9
msgid ""
"Powerful <b>File Browser</b> where you can copy, move, rename, create, "
"delete files and folders and perform bulk operations <a href=\"#L2-"
"filebrowser\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Brabhsálaí Comhad</b> cumhachtach inar féidir leat comhaid agus fillteáin "
"a chóipeáil, a bhogadh, a athainmniú, a chruthú, a scriosadh agus "
"oibríochtaí mórchóir a dhéanamh <a href=\"#L2-filebrowser\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1132-9
msgid ""
"See your library as you like with many detailed and mosaic views <a "
"href=\"#L2-filebrowser\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Féach ar do leabharlann mar is mian leat le go leor radharcanna "
"mionsonraithe agus mósáice <a href=\"#L2-filebrowser\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1134-9
msgid ""
"Add your books to your <span class=\"ui\">Favorites</span> for quick access "
"or create your own <span class=\"ui\">Collections</span> with sorting and "
"filtering <a href=\"#L2-collections\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Cuir do leabhair le do <span class=\"ui\">Roghanna is Fearr leat</span> le "
"haghaidh rochtana tapa nó cruthaigh do <span class=\"ui\">Bailiúcháin</span> "
"féin le sórtáil agus scagadh <a href=\"#L2-collections\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1137-1
msgid "Fly through your book with powerful tools"
msgstr "Eitil trí do leabhar le huirlisí cumhachtacha"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1139-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Skim widget</span> to quickly jump between pages, "
"chapters, bookmarks <a href=\"#L2-skimwidget\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Giuirléid scimeála</span> chun léim go tapa idir "
"leathanaigh, caibidlí, leabharmharcanna <a href=\"#L2-skimwidget\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1141-9
msgid ""
"Unique <span class=\"ui\">Book map</span> to see a bird’s eye map of your "
"book including all your notes and highlights <a href=\"#L2-bookmap\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Léarscáil Leabhar</span> uathúil chun léarscáil súl éin "
"de do leabhar a fheiceáil, lena n-áirítear do nótaí agus buaicphointí go "
"léir <a href=\"#L2-bookmap\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1143-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Page browser</span> to move through pages like a film "
"reel <a href=\"#L2-pagebrowser\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí leathanaigh</span> chun bogadh trí leathanaigh "
"cosúil le ríl scannáin <a href=\"#L2-pagebrowser\" class=\"internalink\"></"
"a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1145-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Bookmarks browser</span> to browse your highlights and "
"notes easily <a href=\"#L1-bookmarks\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Leabharmharcanna</span> chun do bhuaicphointí "
"agus nótaí a bhrabhsáil go héasca <a href=\"#L1-bookmarks\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1147-9
msgid ""
"Create an alternative table of contents automatically or manually if you "
"don't like the one that comes with your book <a href=\"#L2-toctools\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Cruthaigh clár ábhair malartach go huathoibríoch nó de láimh mura dtaitníonn "
"an ceann a thagann le do leabhar leat <a href=\"#L2-toctools\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1149-9
msgid ""
"Hide and exclude certain parts of your book like <b>Appendix, Index, "
"References</b> etc. for more accurate page counts <a href=\"#L2-"
"hiddenflows\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Folaigh agus eisiaigh codanna áirithe de do leabhar ar nós <b>Aguisín, "
"Innéacs, Tagairtí</b> srl. le haghaidh comhaireamh leathanach níos cruinne "
"<a href=\"#L2-hiddenflows\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1152-1
msgid "Control KOReader like a virtuoso"
msgstr "Rialú KOReader mar dhuine fíorúil"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1154-9
msgid ""
"Powerful <b>gesture system</b> with 200+ actions allows you to control every "
"aspect of KOReader with a tap or swipe <a href=\"#L2-gesturecategories\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Ligeann córas <b>gothaí</b> cumhachtach le breis is 200 gníomh duit gach gné "
"de KOReader a rialú le sconna nó svaidhpeáil <a href=\"#L2-"
"gesturecategories\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1156-9
msgid ""
"If you have a keyboard (internal, wired or bluetooth) you can also assign "
"keyboard shortcuts to these actions <a href=\"#L2-keyboardshortcuts\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Má tá méarchlár agat (inmheánach, sreangaithe nó bluetooth) is féidir leat "
"aicearraí méarchláir a shannadh do na gníomhartha seo freisin <a href=\"#L2-"
"keyboardshortcuts\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1158-9
msgid ""
"Or create your own menus with your favorite actions with <span "
"class=\"ui\">Quick Menu</span> and access them with a tap or swipe <a "
"href=\"#L2-quickmenu\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Nó cruthaigh do bhiachláir féin le do ghníomhartha is fearr leat le <span "
"class=\"ui\">Roghchlár Tapa</span> agus rochtain a fháil orthu le sconna nó "
"svaidhpeáil <a href=\"#L2-quickmenu\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1160-9
msgid ""
"Create <b>Profiles</b> to control every aspect of KOReader and automate "
"actions <a href=\"#L2-profiles\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Cruthaigh <b>Próifílí</b> chun gach gné de KOReader a rialú agus gníomhartha "
"a uathoibriú <a href=\"#L2-profiles\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1163-1
msgid "Search, Lookup and Translation tools"
msgstr "Uirlisí Cuardaigh, Cuardaigh agus Aistriúcháin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1165-9
msgid ""
"Search the document by selecting or entering text (including <b>regular "
"expressions</b>)"
msgstr ""
"Cuardaigh an doiciméad trí théacs a roghnú nó a iontráil (lena n-áirítear "
"<b>nathanna rialta</b>)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1166-9
msgid "Search in your bookmarks, highlights and notes"
msgstr "Cuardaigh i do leabharmharcanna, buaicphointí agus nótaí"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1167-9
msgid ""
"Lookup text in <span class=\"external\">Wikipedia</span> or in installed "
"dictionaries and translate it by a long-tap"
msgstr ""
"Cuardaigh téacs i <span class=\"external\">Vicipéid</span> nó i bhfoclóirí "
"suiteáilte agus aistrigh é le tapáil fhada"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1168-9
msgid "Translate whole page at once between more than 130 languages"
msgstr "Aistrigh leathanach iomlán ag an am céanna idir níos mó ná 130 teanga"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1169-9
msgid ""
"With our poweful plugin system, you can even discuss the text with <span "
"class=\"external\">ChatGPT</span> (after installing the plugin) <a "
"href=\"#L2-plugintypes\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Leis an gcóras breiseán cumhachtach atá againn, is féidir leat an téacs a "
"phlé le <span class=\"external\">ChatGPT</span> (tar éis an breiseán a "
"shuiteáil) <a href=\"#L2-plugin types\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1172-1
msgid "KOReader can control your device"
msgstr "Is féidir le KOReader do ghléas a rialú"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1174-9
msgid ""
"KOReader can update itself <a href=\"#L2-devicetips\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le KOReader é féin a nuashonrú <a href=\"#L2-devicetips\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1175-9
msgid "Dim or turn off your <b>screen light</b> after a set interval"
msgstr "Laghdaigh nó múch solas do <b>scáileáin</b> tar éis eatramh socraithe"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1176-9
msgid ""
"Set your page refresh intervals for different reading conditions <a "
"href=\"#L2-mangarefresh\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Socraigh eatraimh athnuachana leathanaigh do choinníollacha léitheoireachta "
"éagsúla <a href=\"#L2-mangarefresh\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1177-9
msgid ""
"Set your own <b>screensaver</b> from many options like random images, book "
"cover, reading, progress etc."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh do <b>scáileánspaillín</b> féin ó go leor roghanna cosúil le "
"híomhánna randamacha, clúdach leabhair, léitheoireacht, dul chun cinn srl."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1178-9
msgid ""
"Set battery <b>charge limit alarms</b> to prevent deep discharge/over charge "
"<a href=\"#L2-devicetips\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Socraigh <b>aláraim teorann luchtaithe</b> ceallraí chun cosc a chur ar "
"dhíluchtú domhain/ró-mhuirearú <a href=\"#L2-devicetips\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1179-9
msgid ""
"Set a memory usage alert (useful for devices for smaller memory) and "
"optionally restart KOReader upon reaching this limit <a href=\"#L2-"
"devicetips\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Socraigh foláireamh úsáide cuimhne (úsáideach do ghléasanna le cuimhne níos "
"lú) agus roghnach atosú KOReader nuair a shroicheann tú an teorainn seo <a "
"href=\"#L2-devicetips\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1183-1
msgid "PDF documents are easier to read on e-ink with KOReader"
msgstr "Tá sé níos fusa doiciméid PDF a léamh ar r-dúch le KOReader"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1185-9
msgid "Crop margins automatically or manually"
msgstr "Bearr imeall go huathoibríoch nó de láimh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1187-9
msgid ""
"<b>Reflow</b> documents to extract text and read easier on a small screen"
msgstr ""
"<b>Athshreabhadh</b> doiciméid chun téacs a bhaint amach agus iad a léamh "
"níos éasca ar scáileán beag"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1189-9
msgid ""
"Apply <b>OCR</b> to documents without text layers, like scanned old books <a "
"href=\"#L2-ocr\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Cuir <b>OCR</b> i bhfeidhm ar dhoiciméid gan sraitheanna téacs, amhail "
"seanleabhair scanta <a href=\"#L2-ocr\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1191-9
msgid ""
"Different zoom types and page flow directions to read <b>multi-column "
"documents</b> like scientific articles easily <a href=\"#L2-readingpdfs\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Cineálacha súmála agus treoracha sreafa leathanaigh éagsúla chun "
"<b>doiciméid ilcholúnacha</b> cosúil le hailt eolaíochta a léamh go héasca "
"<a href=\"#L2-readingpdfs\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1193-9
msgid ""
"Auto straighten tilted documents, like scanned old books <a href=\"#L2-"
"pdfbottom\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Doiciméid chlaonta a dhíriú go huathoibríoch, cosúil le seanleabhair scanta "
"<a href=\"#L2-pdfbottom\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1195-9
msgid ""
"Save your highlights directly into PDFs which allows you to see them without "
"KOReader <a href=\"#L2-pdfhighlights\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Sábháil do bhuaicphointí go díreach i gcomhaid PDF rud a ligeann duit iad a "
"fheiceáil gan KOReader <a href=\"#L2-pdhighlights\" class=\"internalink\"></"
"a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1197-9
msgid ""
"Special <b>Panel zoom</b> feature for reading mangas <a href=\"#L2-"
"panelzoom\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Gné speisialta <b>Zúmáil Painéil</b> le haghaidh léamh manga <a href=\"#L2-"
"panelzoom\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1199-9
msgid ""
"Adjustable screen refresh settings for perfectly balancing between ghosting "
"and speed <a href=\"#L2-mangarefresh\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Socruithe athnuachana scáileáin inchoigeartaithe chun cothromaíocht fhoirfe "
"a bhaint amach idir taibhsí agus luas <a href=\"#L2-mangarefresh\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1202-1
msgid "Advanced features for power users"
msgstr "Gnéithe ardleibhéil d'úsáideoirí cumhachtacha"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1204-9
msgid ""
"Add your own <b>CSS style tweaks</b> for books <a href=\"#L2-styletweaks\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Cuir do <b>choigeartuithe stíl CSS</b> féin le haghaidh leabhar <a "
"href=\"#L2-styletweaks\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1206-9
msgid ""
"<b>User patches</b> system which allows you to change the core behaviors of "
"KOReader <a href=\"#L2-userpatches\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Córas <b>paistí úsáideora</b> a ligeann duit príomhiompraíochtaí KOReader a "
"athrú <a href=\"#L2-userpatches\" class=\"internalink\"></a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1208-9
msgid ""
"Create a <b>QR code</b> from your clipboard to share text and links to other "
"devices"
msgstr ""
"Cruthaigh <b>cód QR</b> ó do ghearrthaisce chun téacs agus naisc a roinnt le "
"gléasanna eile"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1210-9
msgid "View HTML source of an EPUB document"
msgstr "Féach ar fhoinse HTML doiciméid EPUB"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1212-9
msgid "Create and edit text files on your device"
msgstr "Cruthaigh agus cuir comhaid téacs in eagar ar do ghléas"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1214-9
msgid "Open a terminal emulator and run commands on your device"
msgstr "Oscail aithriseoir críochfoirt agus rith orduithe ar do ghléas"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1216-9
msgid "See your CPU, memory and battery usage stats"
msgstr "Féach ar staitisticí úsáide do LAP, cuimhne agus ceallraí"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1223-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L1-basicreading"
msgid "BASIC USAGE INFORMATION"
msgstr "EOLAS ÚSÁIDE BUNÚSÁIDE"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1227-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-transferring"
msgid "Transferring books to your reader"
msgstr "Leabhair a aistriú chuig do léitheoir"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1229-5
msgid ""
"KOReader supports <b>PDF, EPUB, DJVU, MOBI, CBZ, CBT, DOCX, RTF, HTML, TXT, "
"XPS, FB2, PDB, CHM and MD</b> files. It can also open <b>ZIP</b> archives "
"and show image files."
msgstr ""
"Tacaíonn KOReader le comhaid <b>PDF, EPUB, DJVU, MOBI, CBZ, CBT, DOCX, RTF, "
"HTML, TXT, XPS, FB2, PDB, CHM agus MD</b>. Is féidir leis cartlanna <b>ZIP</"
"b> a oscailt agus comhaid íomhá a thaispeáint freisin."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1231-5
msgid ""
"There are many ways to transfer your documents to your device. Note that you "
"may need to restart KOReader to index the transferred documents (or refresh "
"directory if you have Pocketbook/Android)."
msgstr ""
"Tá go leor bealaí ann chun do dhoiciméid a aistriú chuig do ghléas. Tabhair "
"faoi deara go mb’fhéidir go mbeidh ort KOReader a atosú chun na doiciméid "
"aistrithe a innéacsú (nó an t-eolaire a athnuachan má tá Pocketbook/Android "
"agat)."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1233-5
msgid ""
"In addition to transferring files the same way you would with the built-in "
"reader application, other options are available depending on your device:"
msgstr ""
"Chomh maith le comhaid a aistriú ar an mbealach céanna a dhéanfá leis an "
"bhfeidhmchlár léitheoireachta ionsuite, tá roghanna eile ar fáil ag brath ar "
"do ghléas:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1236-9
msgid ""
"<b>USB mass storage mode within KOReader:</b> This mode is available for "
"KOBO and some CERVANTES devices."
msgstr ""
"<b>Mód stórála maise USB laistigh de KOReader:</b> Tá an modh seo ar fáil do "
"KOBO agus do roinnt gléasanna CERVANTES."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1238-9
msgid ""
"<b>Cloud storage (<span class=\"external\">Dropbox</span>/FTP/Webdav):</b> "
"To use this function you have to add accounts for a cloud storage server via "
"menu shown below. Process is explained via <span class=\"ui\">info</span> "
"buttons in the menu while adding accounts:"
msgstr ""
"<b>Stóráil scamall (<span class=\"external\">Dropbox</span>/FTP/Webdav):</b> "
"Chun an fheidhm seo a úsáid ní mór duit cuntais a chur leis le haghaidh "
"freastalaí stórála scamall tríd an roghchlár a thaispeántar thíos. Mínítear "
"an próiseas trí chnaipí <span class=\"ui\">info</span> sa roghchlár agus "
"cuntais á gcur leis:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li.div:1240-9
msgid ""
"TOP MENU (in File Browser) / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/"
"top_tools.svg\" style=\"width:22px;\"> / Cloud storage"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR (sa Bhrabhsálaí Comhad) / <img class=\"img_inline\" "
"src=\"pictures/top_tools.svg\" style=\"width:22px;\"> / Stóráil scamall"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1243-9
msgid ""
"<b>SSH/SFTP access:</b> KOReader can act like an <b>SSH server</b>, which "
"you can access from a computer to transfer files (available on Kobo, Kindle, "
"Cervantes). You can use an SFTP application (like <span "
"class=\"external\">Filezilla</span>) or access via your file manager if your "
"operating system supports. Check our <a href=\"https://github.com/koreader/"
"koreader/wiki/SSH\">wiki</a> for how-to and also see the warning box below."
msgstr ""
"<b>Rochtain SSH/SFTP:</b> Is féidir le KOReader gníomhú mar <b>fhreastalaí "
"SSH</b>, ar féidir leat rochtain a fháil air ó ríomhaire chun comhaid a "
"aistriú (ar fáil ar Kobo, Kindle, Cervantes). Is féidir leat feidhmchlár "
"SFTP (cosúil le <span class=\"external\">Filezilla</span>) a úsáid nó "
"rochtain a fháil air trí do bhainisteoir comhad má thacaíonn do chóras "
"oibriúcháin leis. Seiceáil ár <a href=\"https://github.com/koreader/koreader/"
"wiki/SSH\">vicí</a> le haghaidh treoracha agus féach an bosca rabhaidh thíos "
"freisin."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1245-9
msgid ""
"<b>Calibre transfer:</b> With the <span class=\"external\">Calibre plugin</"
"span> you can send documents from your Calibre Library directly to your "
"KOReader devices via a wifi connection. Check our <a href=\"https://"
"github.com/koreader/koreader/wiki/calibre\">wiki</a> for how-to."
msgstr ""
"<b>Aistriú Calibre:</b> Leis an mbreiseán <span class=\"external\">Calibre</"
"span> is féidir leat doiciméid a sheoladh ó do Leabharlann Calibre go "
"díreach chuig do ghléasanna KOReader trí nasc wifi. Féach ar ár <a "
"href=\"https://github.com/koreader/koreader/wiki/calibre\">vicí</a> le "
"haghaidh treoracha."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1247-9
msgid ""
"<b>News downloader:</b> With this plugin you can download <b>RSS and Atom</"
"b> news entries as HTML files. Check <a href=\"https://github.com/koreader/"
"koreader/wiki/News-downloader\">wiki</a> for how-to."
msgstr ""
"<b>Íoslódálaí nuachta:</b> Leis an mbreiseán seo is féidir leat iontrálacha "
"nuachta <b>RSS agus Atom</b> a íoslódáil mar chomhaid HTML. Féach ar an <a "
"href=\"https://github.com/koreader/koreader/wiki/News-downloader\">wiki</a> "
"le haghaidh treoracha."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1249-9
msgid ""
"<b>Wallabag:</b> With this plugin you can retrieve articles from <span "
"class=\"external\">Wallabag</span>, a server based read-it-later service "
"like Pocket. Check <a href=\"https://github.com/koreader/koreader/wiki/"
"Wallabag\">wiki</a> page for more info."
msgstr ""
"<b>Wallabag:</b> Leis an mbreiseán seo is féidir leat ailt a aisghabháil ó "
"<span class=\"external\">Wallabag</span>, seirbhís léigh-é-níos-níos-déanta "
"atá bunaithe ar fhreastalaí cosúil le Pocket. Féach ar an leathanach <a "
"href=\"https://github.com/koreader/koreader/wiki/Wallabag\">wiki</a> le "
"haghaidh tuilleadh eolais."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.p:1252-24
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_red\">WARNING</span> Be careful if you decide to use the "
"SSH feature without a password, because this allows open access to your "
"device. But if you are using a local wifi and turn on your device wifi for a "
"short time, this risk is negligible."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_red\">RABHADH</span> Bí cúramach má shocraíonn tú an "
"ghné SSH a úsáid gan pasfhocal, mar go gceadaíonn sé seo rochtain oscailte "
"ar do ghléas. Ach má tá tú ag úsáid wifi áitiúil agus má chasann tú wifi do "
"ghléis ar siúl ar feadh tamaill ghairid, is beag an riosca seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1256-1
msgid "Accessing your books"
msgstr "Rochtain ar do leabhair"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1258-5
msgid "Following methods are available for accessing your books:"
msgstr ""
"Tá na modhanna seo a leanas ar fáil chun rochtain a fháil ar do leabhair:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1260-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">File Browser</span> - Dedicated section is here: <a "
"href=\"#L2-filebrowser\">File Browser usage</a>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span> - Tá cuid tiomnaithe anseo: <a "
"href=\"#L2-filebrowser\">Úsáid an Bhrabhsálaí Comhad</a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1261-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Favorites</span> - A list which you can add your books by "
"long pressing on them in the <span class=\"ui\">File Browser</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Ceanáin</span> - Liosta ar féidir leat do leabhair a chur "
"leis trí bhrú fada orthu sa <span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1262-5
msgid "<span class=\"ui\">History</span> - List of books you opened"
msgstr "<span class=\"ui\">Stair</span> - Liosta leabhar a d'oscail tú"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1263-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Collections</span> - Personalized book lists you created. "
"Dedicated section is here: <a href=\"#L2-collections\">Collections</a>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Bailiúcháin</span> - Liostaí leabhar pearsantaithe a "
"chruthaigh tú féin. Tá an chuid tiomnaithe anseo: <a href=\"#L2-"
"collections\">Bailiúcháin</a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1266-5
msgid "You can change how these screens look from:"
msgstr "Is féidir leat cuma na scáileáin seo a athrú ó:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1268-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU (in File Browser) / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/"
"top_cabinet.svg\" style=\"width:22px;\"> / Display mode"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR (sa Bhrabhsálaí Comhad) / <img class=\"img_inline\" "
"src=\"pictures/top_cabinet.svg\" style=\"width:22px;\"> / Mód taispeána"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1270-5
msgid ""
"If you want to change how many items are visible on these screens, look here:"
msgstr ""
"Más mian leat líon na míreanna atá le feiceáil ar na scáileáin seo a athrú, "
"féach anseo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1272-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU (in File Browser) / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/"
"top_cabinet.svg\" style=\"width:22px;\"> / Settings / Mosaic and detailed "
"list settings"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR (sa Bhrabhsálaí Comhad) / <img class=\"img_inline\" "
"src=\"pictures/top_cabinet.svg\" style=\"width:22px;\"> / Socruithe / "
"Socruithe mósáice agus liosta mionsonraithe"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1274-5
msgid ""
"You can assign gestures for each of these dialogs. For example while reading "
"a book, you can access your <span class=\"ui\">History</span> or <span "
"class=\"ui\">Favorites</span> with a gesture and open another book without "
"going through the <span class=\"ui\">File Browser</span>."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat gothaí a shannadh do gach ceann de na dialóga seo. Mar "
"shampla, agus leabhar á léamh agat, is féidir leat rochtain a fháil ar do "
"<span class=\"ui\">Stair</span> nó ar do <span class=\"ui\">Ceanáin</span> "
"le gotha agus leabhar eile a oscailt gan dul tríd an <span "
"class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1275-5
msgid ""
"You can search a book in the <span class=\"ui\">History</span> screen by "
"<b>filename</b> or <b>book metadata</b> from the upper left hamburger menu "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat leabhar a chuardach sa scáileán <span class=\"ui\">Stair</"
"span> de réir <b>ainm comhaid</b> nó <b>meiteashonraí leabhair</b> ón "
"gcnaipe roghchláir barr ar chlé."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1276-5
msgid ""
"You can also set KOReader to start with <span class=\"ui\">Favorites</span> "
"or <span class=\"ui\">History</span> screen instead of <span "
"class=\"ui\">File Browser</span> via:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat KOReader a shocrú freisin chun tosú le scáileán <span "
"class=\"ui\">Ceanáin</span> nó <span class=\"ui\">Stair</span> in ionad "
"<span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span> trí:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1279-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU (in File Browser) / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/"
"top_cabinet.svg\" style=\"width:22px;\"> / Start with"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR (sa Bhrabhsálaí Comhad) / <img class=\"img_inline\" "
"src=\"pictures/top_cabinet.svg\" style=\"width:22px;\"> / Tosaigh le"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1285-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-tapzones"
msgid "Tap zones"
msgstr "Criosanna sconna"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1289-5
msgid ""
"In the image above, you can see the positions of the default tap zones of "
"KOReader. To show the <span class=\"ui\">top menu</span> or <span "
"class=\"ui\">bottom menu</span> you can tap the indicated zones. You can "
"also swipe down the upper zone to show the <span class=\"ui\">top menu</"
"span>. On non-touch devices like Kindle 4 you can open the <span "
"class=\"ui\">bottom menu</span> by pressing the button that corresponds to "
"the <b>ENTER/OK</b> action."
msgstr ""
"San íomhá thuas, is féidir leat suíomhanna na gcriosanna tapála "
"réamhshocraithe de KOReader a fheiceáil. Chun an <span "
"class=\"ui\">roghchlár barr</span> nó an <span class=\"ui\">roghchlár bun</"
"span> a thaispeáint, is féidir leat na criosanna léirithe a thapáil. Is "
"féidir leat svaidhpeáil síos an crios uachtarach freisin chun an <span "
"class=\"ui\">roghchlár barr</span> a thaispeáint. Ar fheistí neamh-"
"theagmhála cosúil le Kindle 4, is féidir leat an <span "
"class=\"ui\">roghchlár bun</span> a oscailt tríd an gcnaipe a fhreagraíonn "
"don ghníomh <b>IONTRÁIL/Ceart go leor</b> a bhrú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1291-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">TIP</span> As indicated in the image above, "
"<span class=\"ui\">top menu</span> opening zone is divided into 3 areas. If "
"you swipe down the first 1/3 of the top edge, <span class=\"ui\">top menu</"
"span> opens with the <b>first menu tab</b>. Second 1/3 area opens the "
"<b>most recently used menu tab</b>. And last area opens the <b>last menu "
"tab</b>."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">LEID</span> Mar a léirítear san íomhá thuas, tá "
"crios oscailte an <span class=\"ui\">roghchláir</span> roinnte ina 3 "
"limistéar. Má shvaipeálann tú síos an chéad 1/3 den imeall uachtarach, "
"osclaítear an <span class=\"ui\">roghchlár</span> leis an <b>chéad chluaisín "
"roghchláir</b>. Osclaítear an dara 1/3 limistéar an <b>chluaisín roghchláir "
"is déanaí a úsáideadh</b>. Agus osclaítear an <b>chluaisín roghchláir "
"deireanach</b> sa limistéar deireanach."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1293-5
msgid ""
"If you want top open both menus at the same time, you can set <span "
"class=\"ui\">top menu</span> zone to open both the <span class=\"ui\">top</"
"span> and <span class=\"ui\">bottom menu</span> at the same time via this "
"menu:"
msgstr ""
"Más mian leat an dá roghchlár a oscailt ag an am céanna, is féidir leat "
"crios <span class=\"ui\">an roghchláir barr</span> a shocrú chun an "
"roghchlár <span class=\"ui\">barr</span> agus an roghchlár <span "
"class=\"ui\">bun</span> araon a oscailt ag an am céanna tríd an roghchlár "
"seo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1295-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Taps and Gestures / Activate Menu"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Tapálacha agus Gothaí / Gníomhachtaigh an Roghchlár"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1298-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Corner tap zones</span> can be used for many different "
"type of gestures including <b>TAP, DOUBLE TAP, TWO FINGER TAP</b> and <b>TAP "
"and HOLD</b>."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir <span class=\"ui\">criosanna tapála cúinne</span> a úsáid le "
"haghaidh go leor cineálacha éagsúla gothaí lena n-áirítear <b>TAPÁIL, TAPÁIL "
"DHÚBAILTE, TAPÁIL LE DÁ MHÉAR</b> agus <b>TAPÁIL AGUS COINNIGH</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1300-5
msgid ""
"<b>PREVIOUS PAGE</b> and <b>NEXT PAGE</b> zones can also be used for "
"<b>DOUBLE TAP</b> gestures at the same time."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir criosanna <b>LEATHANACH ROIMHE</b> agus <b>LEATHANACH EILE</b> a "
"úsáid le haghaidh gothaí <b>SCNÁIL DHÚBAILTE</b> ag an am céanna freisin."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1302-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Status bar</span> zone can be tapped to cycle between the "
"<span class=\"ui\">status bar</span> items if only one item is visible. If "
"all items are visible, tapping will show and hide the <span "
"class=\"ui\">status bar</span>."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir tapáil ar an gcrios <span class=\"ui\">barra stádais</span> chun "
"rothlú idir míreanna an <span class=\"ui\">bharra stádais</span> mura bhfuil "
"ach mír amháin le feiceáil. Má tá na míreanna uile le feiceáil, taispeánfar "
"agus folófar an <span class=\"ui\">barra stádais</span> trí thapáil."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1306-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-textappearance"
msgid "Changing text appearance"
msgstr "Athrú cuma an téacs"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1309-5
msgid "<b>Changing the font*</b>:"
msgstr "<b>An cló a athrú*</b>:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li.div:1309-35
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Font"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Cló"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1310-5
msgid "Make the font bigger"
msgstr "Déan an cló níos mó"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li.div:1310-36
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ul.li.div:1310-36"
msgid "BOTTOM MENU /"
msgstr "AN ROGHCHLÁR BUNA /"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1311-5
msgid "Make the font bolder"
msgstr "Déan an cló níos troime"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li.div:1311-36
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ul.li.div:1311-36"
msgid "BOTTOM MENU /"
msgstr "AN ROGHCHLÁR BUNA /"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1312-5
msgid "Invert the colors on screen (white on black)"
msgstr "Inbhéartaigh na dathanna ar an scáileán (bán ar dhubh)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li.div:1312-60
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Night Mode"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Mód Oíche"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1315-5
msgid ""
"You can also change other formatting options from the <span "
"class=\"ui\">BOTTOM MENU</span> to fine tune the appearance of your text. "
"These are just quick tips to get you started of course. We have a full "
"section dedicated to <a href=\"#L1-customizingappearance\">CUSTOMIZING TEXT "
"APPEARANCE</a>"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat roghanna formáidithe eile a athrú ón <span "
"class=\"ui\">ROGHCHLÁR BUN</span> chun cuma do théacs a choigeartú go "
"beacht. Níl iontu seo ach leideanna gasta chun tú a chur ar an mbóthar ceart "
"ar ndóigh. Tá cuid iomlán againn atá tiomnaithe do <a href=\"#L1-"
"customizingappearance\">CUMHAÍOCHT AN TÉACS A SAINCHEISTIÚ</a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1317-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">INFO</span> *Font selection is available only on "
"reflowable documents (EPUB, HTML, DOCX, RTF, TXT…). Fixed-layout documents "
"like PDF/DJVU are not supported."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">EOLAS</span> *Níl rogha cló ar fáil ach amháin ar "
"dhoiciméid in-athshreabhta (EPUB, HTML, DOCX, RTF, TXT…). Ní thacaítear le "
"doiciméid leagan amach seasta cosúil le PDF/DJVU."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1322-1
msgid "Controlling the backlight / frontlight"
msgstr "Rialú an chúlsholais / an tsolais tosaigh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1324-5
msgid ""
"You can control your screen light via this menu. If you have warm lighting "
"(normal white LEDs+orange ones) you can control them separately from this "
"dialog. You can also define a gesture for this dialog:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat solas do scáileáin a rialú tríd an roghchlár seo. Má tá "
"soilsiú te agat (soilse LED bána gnáth + cinn oráiste) is féidir leat iad a "
"rialú ar leithligh ón dialóg seo. Is féidir leat gotha a shainiú don dialóg "
"seo freisin:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1326-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Frontlight"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Solas Tosaigh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1330-1
msgid "Changing the screen displayed while sleeping"
msgstr "Athrú an scáileáin a thaispeántar agus tú i do chodladh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1332-2
msgid ""
"You can choose a book cover or a custom image as screensaver via this menu:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat clúdach leabhair nó íomhá saincheaptha a roghnú mar "
"spárálaíscáileáin tríd an roghchlár seo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1334-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Screen / Screensaver"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Scáileán / Sábhálaí Scáileáin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1336-5
msgid ""
"You can use JPG/PNG files as screensaver (properly dithered grayscale images "
"look best). Transfer the files from your computer into any folder on your "
"device. And choose this folder as your screensaver folder via this menu:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat comhaid JPG/PNG a úsáid mar spárálaíscáileáin (is fearr "
"breathnú ar íomhánna liathscála atá díthithe i gceart). Aistrigh na comhaid "
"ó do ríomhaire go dtí aon fhillteán ar do ghléas. Agus roghnaigh an fillteán "
"seo mar do fhillteán spárálaíscáileáin tríd an roghchlár seo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1338-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Screen / Screensaver / Settings"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Scáileán / Sábhálaí Scáileáin / Socruithe"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1340-5
msgid ""
"Please refer to this <a href=\"https://www.mobileread.com/forums/"
"showpost.php?p=3728291&postcount=17\">Mobileread forum post</a> for advanced "
"information about preparing screensaver images."
msgstr ""
"Féach ar an <a href=\"https://www.mobileread.com/forums/showpost.php?"
"p=3728291&postcount=17\">post fóram Mobileread</a> seo le haghaidh faisnéise "
"ardleibhéil faoi íomhánna spárálaíscáileáin a ullmhú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1344-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-keyboard"
msgid "Keyboard Usage And Tips"
msgstr "Úsáid agus Leideanna Méarchláir"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1346-5
msgid ""
"If you are looking for information about <span class=\"ui\">keyboard "
"shortcuts</span>, click <a href=\"#L2-keyboardshortcuts\">here</a> to go "
"that section. This heading only explains the keyboard usage."
msgstr ""
"Más mian leat eolas a fháil faoi <span class=\"ui\">aicearraí méarchláir</"
"span>, cliceáil <a href=\"#L2-keyboard shortcuts\">anseo</a> chun dul chuig "
"an rannóg sin. Ní mhíníonn an ceannteideal seo ach úsáid an mhéarchláir."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1349-3
msgid ""
"Tap outside the input field to close the keyboard, tap the input field to "
"show the keyboard again"
msgstr ""
"Tapáil lasmuigh den réimse ionchuir chun an méarchlár a dhúnadh, tapáil an "
"réimse ionchuir chun an méarchlár a thaispeáint arís"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1350-3
msgid ""
"<b>Swipe up</b> keys to enter uppercase version of that letter (or lowercase "
"if you are already in <b>shift</b> mode)"
msgstr ""
"<b>Svaip suas</b> na heochracha chun leagan mór den litir sin a iontráil (nó "
"an litir bheag má tá tú i mód <b>shift</b> cheana féin)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1351-3
msgid "You can change the appearance of the keyboard:"
msgstr "Is féidir leat cuma an mhéarchláir a athrú:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li.div:1352-4
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Device / Keyboard / Keyboard settings"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Gléas / Méarchlár / Socruithe méarchláir"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1353-3
msgid "You can select more than one layout:"
msgstr "Is féidir leat níos mó ná leagan amach amháin a roghnú:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li.div:1354-4
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Device / Keyboard / Keyboard layout"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Gléas / Méarchlár / Leagan Amach an Mhéarchláir"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1355-3
msgid ""
"You can change between your selected layouts by tapping the <img "
"loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/keyboard_world.png\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> icon on the keyboard"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat athrú idir na leagan amach roghnaithe agat tríd an deilbhín "
"<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/"
"keyboard_world.png\" style=\"width:22px;\"> ar an méarchlár a thapáil"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1360-1
msgid "Entering extra characters"
msgstr "Carachtair bhreise á gcur isteach"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1362-5
msgid ""
"Koreader keyboard allows entering extra characters when you tap and hold a "
"key. Most frequently used extra characters are shown below. You can tap and "
"hold the key in the <b>gray box</b> to get the surrounding characters:"
msgstr ""
"Le méarchlár Koreader, is féidir leat carachtair bhreise a iontráil nuair a "
"thapaíonn tú agus a choinníonn tú cnaipe. Taispeántar na carachtair bhreise "
"is minice a úsáidtear thíos. Is féidir leat an cnaipe a thapáil agus a "
"choinnigh sa <b>bhosca liath</b> chun na carachtair máguaird a fháil:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1366-5
msgid ""
"In addition to the long-press popup, you can also enter these extra "
"characters by swiping on a key. In the example below, you can swipe up on "
"the <b>a</b> key to enter an <b>uppercase A</b> or swipe other directions to "
"enter the characters shown. Note that the example shown includes the full "
"popup for demonstration. You don’t need to open this popup, you can directly "
"swipe on the keys. Once you get used to the locations of the extra "
"characters, you can enter them much quicker this way."
msgstr ""
"Chomh maith leis an bhfuinneog aníos le brú fada, is féidir leat na "
"carachtair bhreise seo a iontráil trí shlaipeadh ar eochair. Sa sampla "
"thíos, is féidir leat svaipeadh suas ar an eochair <b>a</b> chun <b>A mór</"
"b> a iontráil nó svaipeadh i dtreonna eile chun na carachtair a thaispeántar "
"a iontráil. Tabhair faoi deara go n-áirítear an fhuinneog aníos iomlán san "
"sampla a thaispeántar le haghaidh taispeántais. Ní gá duit an fhuinneog "
"aníos seo a oscailt, is féidir leat svaipeadh go díreach ar na heochracha. "
"Nuair a bheidh tú cleachtaithe le suíomhanna na gcarachtar breise, is féidir "
"leat iad a iontráil i bhfad níos tapúla ar an mbealach seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1370-5
msgid ""
"If this feature interferes with your usage, you can disable it by unchecking:"
msgstr ""
"Má chuireann an ghné seo isteach ar d’úsáid, is féidir leat í a dhíchumasú "
"trí dhíthiceáil a dhéanamh ar:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1372-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\">/ Device / Keyboard / Swipe to input additional "
"characters"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\">/ Gléas / Méarchlár / Svaidhpeáil chun carachtair "
"bhreise a ionchur"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1374-5
msgid ""
"Additionally there are some shortcuts for easier text manipulation. You can "
"<b>tap and hold</b> these keys for extra actions:"
msgstr ""
"Ina theannta sin, tá roinnt aicearraí ann le haghaidh ionramháil téacs níos "
"éasca. Is féidir leat na heochracha seo a <b>thapáil agus a shealbhú</b> le "
"haghaidh gníomhartha breise:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1376-9
msgid "<b>Left Arrow</b> - Moves the cursor to the beginning of the line"
msgstr "<b>Saighead Chlé</b> - Bogann sé an cúrsóir go dtí tús na líne"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1377-9
msgid "<b>Right Arrow</b> - Moves the cursor to the end of the line"
msgstr ""
"<b>Saighead ar Dheis</b> - Bogann sé an cúrsóir go dtí deireadh na líne"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1380-5
msgid ""
"Also <span class=\"ui\">backspace</span> key behaves different when you make "
"swipe gestures on it:"
msgstr ""
"Chomh maith leis sin, iompraíonn an eochair <span class=\"ui\">cúlspás</"
"span> ar bhealach difriúil nuair a dhéanann tú gothaí svaidhpeála uirthi:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1383-9
msgid "<b>Tap:</b> Delete a character"
msgstr "<b>Tapáil:</b> Scrios carachtar"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1384-9
msgid "<b>Long-press:</b> Delete the whole line"
msgstr "<b>Brúigh go mall:</b> Scrios an líne iomlán"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1385-9
msgid "<b>Swipe left:</b> Delete part of the word left of the cursor"
msgstr "<b>Svaip ar chlé:</b> Scrios cuid den fhocal ar chlé den chúrsóir"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1386-9
msgid "<b>Swipe up:</b> Delete the whole word"
msgstr "<b>Svaip suas:</b> Scrios an focal ar fad"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1389-2
msgid ""
"For more information, you can check the <a href=\"https://github.com/"
"koreader/koreader/wiki/Virtual-keyboard\">related wiki page</a>."
msgstr ""
"Chun tuilleadh eolais a fháil, is féidir leat an <a href=\"https://"
"github.com/koreader/koreader/wiki/Virtual-keyboard\">leathanach vicí "
"gaolmhar</a> a sheiceáil."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1391-5
msgid ""
"KOReader also integrates the Chinese stroke keyboard for inputting "
"simplified and traditional Chinese characters. You can find more info about "
"it in our <a href=\"https://github.com/koreader/koreader/wiki/Chinese-"
"keyboard\">wiki</a>."
msgstr ""
"Comhtháthaíonn KOReader an méarchlár stróc Síneach chun carachtair "
"shimplithe agus thraidisiúnta na Síne a ionchur freisin. Is féidir leat "
"tuilleadh eolais a fháil faoi inár <a href=\"https://github.com/koreader/"
"koreader/wiki/Chinese-keyboard\">vicí</a>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1395-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-autowarmth"
msgid "Auto Warmth And Night Mode"
msgstr "Mód Teasa agus Oíche Uathoibríoch"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1397-5
msgid ""
"This plugin allows you to adjust frontlight warmth in devices with "
"<b>natural (yellow/orange) light</b> and set <span class=\"ui\">night mode</"
"span> (inverted screen colors – <b>white text on black background</b>) "
"automatically according to a schedule. It can control them both or you can "
"choose <span class=\"ui\">only warmth control</span> or <span "
"class=\"ui\">only night mode control</span> mode, so you can adjust the "
"other one manually."
msgstr ""
"Ligeann an breiseán seo duit teas an tsolais tosaigh a choigeartú i "
"ngléasanna le <b>solas (buí/oráiste) nádúrtha</b> agus <span "
"class=\"ui\">mód oíche</span> (dathanna scáileáin inbhéartaithe – <b>téacs "
"bán ar chúlra dubh</b>) a shocrú go huathoibríoch de réir sceidil. Is féidir "
"leis an dá cheann a rialú nó is féidir leat <span class=\"ui\">rialú teasa "
"amháin</span> nó <span class=\"ui\">rialú mód oíche amháin</span> a roghnú, "
"ionas gur féidir leat an ceann eile a choigeartú de láimh."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1399-5
msgid ""
"This plugin comes enabled as default when you install KOReader. If for some "
"reason it is not in the menu, you can enable it here:"
msgstr ""
"Tagann an breiseán seo cumasaithe mar réamhshocrú nuair a shuiteálann tú "
"KOReader. Mura bhfuil sé sa roghchlár ar chúis éigin, is féidir leat é a "
"chumasú anseo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1401-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_tools.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / More tools / Auto Warmth and Night Mode"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_tools.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Tuilleadh uirlisí / Mód Teasa Uathoibríoch agus "
"Oíche"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1403-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">INFO</span> If you have a PocketBook device and "
"frontlight or warmth slider is not working in KOReader, please be sure that "
"in the PocketBook reader (which comes with your device) <b>SmartLight-Auto</"
"b> option is set to <b>Disabled</b>."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">EOLAS</span> Má tá gléas PocketBook agat agus "
"mura bhfuil an solas tosaigh nó an sleamhnán teasa ag obair i KOReader, déan "
"cinnte go bhfuil an rogha <b>SmartLight-Auto</b> socraithe go "
"<b>Díchumasaithe</b> sa léitheoir PocketBook (a thagann le do ghléas)."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1406-5
msgid ""
"You can adjust the warmth of your screen frontlight automatically in two "
"different ways:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat teas sholas tosaigh do scáileáin a choigeartú go "
"huathoibríoch ar dhá bhealach éagsúla:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1408-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Fixed schedule:</span> In this mode your frontlight "
"warmth changes according to the daily schedule you entered. This mode is "
"<b>static</b>, it doesn’t account for daylight length. The schedule stays "
"the same all around the year."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Sceideal seasta:</span> Sa mhodh seo athraíonn teas do "
"shoilse tosaigh de réir an sceidil laethúil a chuir tú isteach. Tá an modh "
"seo <b>statach</b>, ní chuireann sé fad sholas an lae san áireamh. Fanann an "
"sceideal mar a chéile ar feadh na bliana."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1410-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Sun's position:</span> This option calculates Sun’s "
"position in your location according to <b>coordinates</b> and <b>altitude</"
"b> information you entered. Frontlight warmth is adjusted gradually "
"according to this calculated Sun position data. This mode is <b>dynamic</b>. "
"As the length of daylight changes around the year, plugin adjusts the "
"schedule accordingly."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Suíomh na Gréine:</span> Ríomhann an rogha seo suíomh na "
"Gréine i do shuíomh de réir na <b>comhordanáidí</b> agus na faisnéise "
"<b>airde</b> a chuir tú isteach. Déantar teas an tsolais tosaigh a "
"choigeartú de réir a chéile de réir na sonraí suíomh Gréine seo a ríomhadh. "
"Tá an modh seo <b>dinimiciúil</b>. De réir mar a athraíonn fad an lae i rith "
"na bliana, déanann an breiseán an sceideal a choigeartú dá réir."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1412-5
msgid ""
"First have a look at this image to familiarize yourself with the terms used "
"in the plugin:"
msgstr ""
"Féach ar an íomhá seo ar dtús chun tú féin a chur ar an eolas faoi na "
"téarmaí a úsáidtear sa bhreiseán:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1416-5
msgid "Fixed Schedule Mode"
msgstr "Mód Sceidil Sheasta"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1419-3
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ol.li:1419-3"
msgid "Go to the plugin menu:"
msgstr "Téigh go dtí roghchlár an bhreiseáin:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li.div:1419-30
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ol.li.div:1419-30"
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Screen / Auto Warmth and Night Mode"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Scáileán / Teas Uathoibríoch agus Mód Oíche"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1421-3
msgid ""
"Tap Activate menu item and then tap <span class=\"ui\">According to the "
"fixed schedule</span>"
msgstr ""
"Beartaíonn ar an mír roghchláir Gníomhachtaigh agus ansin beartaíonn <span "
"class=\"ui\">De réir an sceidil sheasta</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1423-3
msgid ""
"Go back to previous menu and tap <span class=\"ui\">Fixed schedule settings</"
"span> menu item"
msgstr ""
"Téigh ar ais go dtí an roghchlár roimhe seo agus tapáil mír roghchláir <span "
"class=\"ui\">Socruithe sceideal seasta</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1425-3
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ol.li:1425-3"
msgid ""
"Set your warmth transition schedule by setting times for various items here. "
"Refer to the image above for an explanation of items."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh do sceideal aistrithe teasa trí amanna a shocrú do mhíreanna "
"éagsúla anseo. Féach ar an íomhá thuas le haghaidh míniú ar na míreanna."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1430-1
msgid "Sun’s Position Mode"
msgstr "Mód Seasamh na Gréine"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1433-13
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ol.li:1433-13"
msgid "Go to the plugin menu:"
msgstr "Téigh go dtí roghchlár an bhreiseáin:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li.div:1434-17
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ol.li.div:1434-17"
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Screen / Auto Warmth and Night Mode"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Scáileán / Teas Uathoibríoch agus Mód Oíche"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1436-13
msgid ""
"Tap <span class=\"ui\">Activate</span> menu item and then tap <span "
"class=\"ui\">According to the sun's position</span>"
msgstr ""
"Beartaíonn an mhír roghchláir <span class=\"ui\">Gníomhachtaigh</span> agus "
"ansin beartaíonn <span class=\"ui\">De réir shuíomh na gréine</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1438-13
msgid ""
"Go back to previous menu and tap <span class=\"ui\">Location settings</span> "
"menu item. Set your <b>coordinates</b> (necessary) and <b>altitude</b> "
"(optional) correctly and give a <b>name</b> to your location."
msgstr ""
"Téigh ar ais go dtí an roghchlár roimhe seo agus tapáil mír roghchláir <span "
"class=\"ui\">Socruithe Suímh</span>. Socraigh do <b>chomhordanáidí</b> "
"(riachtanach) agus <b>airde</b> (roghnach) i gceart agus tabhair <b>ainm</b> "
"chuig do shuíomh."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1440-13
msgid ""
"Go back to previous menu and tap <span class=\"ui\">Warmth and night mode "
"settings</span> menu item"
msgstr ""
"Téigh ar ais go dtí an roghchlár roimhe seo agus tapáil mír roghchláir <span "
"class=\"ui\">Socruithe mód teasa agus oíche</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1442-13
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ol.li:1442-13"
msgid ""
"Set your warmth transition schedule by setting times for various items here. "
"Refer to the image above for an explanation of items."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh do sceideal aistrithe teasa trí amanna a shocrú do mhíreanna "
"éagsúla anseo. Féach ar an íomhá thuas le haghaidh míniú ar na míreanna."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1445-5
msgid ""
"You can see your current schedule via <span class=\"ui\">Currently active "
"parameters</span> menu option."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat do sceideal reatha a fheiceáil tríd an rogha roghchláir <span "
"class=\"ui\">Paraiméadair atá gníomhach faoi láthair</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1450-1
msgid "Night Mode"
msgstr "Mód Oíche"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1452-5
msgid ""
"While setting the warm light percentages for different intervals, you can "
"also set that interval to <span class=\"ui\">Night Mode</span>, which "
"inverts the screen colors when that interval starts. If your minimum "
"frontlight is still too bright or if you prefer a dark page background, you "
"can activate this feature. To enable this, in the dialog below, tap the "
"<span class=\"ui\">Night mode</span> checkbox and tap <span "
"class=\"ui\">Set</span>."
msgstr ""
"Agus céatadáin an tsolais the á socrú agat le haghaidh eatraimh éagsúla, is "
"féidir leat an t-eatramh sin a shocrú go <span class=\"ui\">Mód Oíche</span> "
"freisin, rud a athraíonn dathanna an scáileáin nuair a thosaíonn an t-"
"eatramh sin. Má tá do sholas tosaigh íosta ró-gheal fós nó más fearr leat "
"cúlra leathanaigh dorcha, is féidir leat an ghné seo a ghníomhachtú. Chun "
"seo a chumasú, sa dialóg thíos, tapáil an bosca seiceála <span "
"class=\"ui\">Mód Oíche</span> agus tapáil <span class=\"ui\">Socraigh</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1454-5
msgid ""
"When you do this, a <b>moon icon</b> will appear in the menu next to this "
"interval. To disable night mode, just disable the <span class=\"ui\">Night "
"mode</span> checkbox in that interval."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a dhéanann tú é seo, beidh <b>deilbhín gealaí</b> le feiceáil sa "
"roghchlár in aice leis an eatramh seo. Chun mód oíche a dhíchumasú, níl le "
"déanamh ach an bosca seiceála <span class=\"ui\">Mód oíche</span> a "
"dhíchumasú san eatramh sin."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1460-1
msgid "Frontlight auto on/off"
msgstr "Soilse tosaigh uathoibríoch ar siúl/as"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1462-5
msgid ""
"This feature turns your frontlight on at sunset and turns it off at sunrise "
"according to your <span class=\"ui\">Currently active parameters</span> in "
"this plugin. You can override this change by manually turning your "
"frontlight on/off. On the next sunrise/sunset, <span "
"class=\"ui\">AutoWarmth</span> will toggle it again if it is necessary. You "
"can activate it by selecting <span class=\"ui\">Frontlight off during the "
"day</span> menu item in this plugin."
msgstr ""
"Casann an ghné seo do sholas tosaigh air ag luí na gréine agus múchann sé é "
"ag éirí na gréine de réir do <span class=\"ui\">paraiméadair atá gníomhach "
"faoi láthair</span> sa bhreiseán seo. Is féidir leat an t-athrú seo a shárú "
"trí do sholas tosaigh a chasadh air/as de láimh. Ag an gcéad éirí gréine/luí "
"gréine eile, déanfaidh <span class=\"ui\">AutoWarmth</span> é a lascadh arís "
"más gá. Is féidir leat é a ghníomhachtú tríd an mír roghchláir <span "
"class=\"ui\">Solas tosaigh múchta i rith an lae</span> a roghnú sa bhreiseán "
"seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1466-1
msgid "Faster warmth transitions"
msgstr "Aistrithe teasa níos tapúla"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1468-5
msgid ""
"If you want your frontlight warmth to change quickly instead of a more "
"gradual change:"
msgstr ""
"Más mian leat go n-athródh teas do shoilse tosaigh go tapa seachas athrú "
"níos de réir a chéile:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1470-9
msgid "Set the mode to <b>Fixed schedule</b> following the instructions above"
msgstr ""
"Socraigh an modh go <b>Sceideal seasta</b> ag leanúint na dtreoracha thuas"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1471-9
msgid "And adjust the settings similar to the image below:"
msgstr "Agus coigeartaigh na socruithe cosúil leis an íomhá thíos:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1476-5
msgid ""
"As you can see in these settings above, there is only a one minute "
"difference between day-night transition. So the screen warmth goes from <b>0 "
"to 100 (or reverse) in only one minute</b>. You can increase this time "
"separation to make the transition duration longer."
msgstr ""
"Mar is féidir leat a fheiceáil sna socruithe seo thuas, níl ach nóiméad "
"amháin difríochta idir an t-aistriú ó lá go hoíche. Mar sin téann teas an "
"scáileáin ó <b>0 go 100 (nó droim ar ais) i nóiméad amháin</b>. Is féidir "
"leat an scaradh ama seo a mhéadú chun fad an aistrithe a dhéanamh níos faide."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1484-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L1-userinterface"
msgid "LEARNING THE USER INTERFACE"
msgstr "AG FOGHLAIM AN CHOMHDÉANAÍ ÚSÁIDEORA"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1486-5
msgid ""
"KOReader has a simple, mainly black and white user interface because "
"gradients and different shades of gray can cause flashing and ghosting on e-"
"ink screens which can degrade reading experience."
msgstr ""
"Tá comhéadan úsáideora simplí, dubh agus bán den chuid is mó, ag KOReader "
"mar is féidir le grádáin agus scáthanna éagsúla liath splancadh agus taibhsí "
"a chur faoi deara ar scáileáin dúigh leictreonacha rud a d’fhéadfadh an "
"taithí léitheoireachta a lagú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1488-5
msgid ""
"KOReader has 2 main interfaces: <span class=\"ui\">reading screen</span> and "
"<span class=\"ui\">file browser</span>. We will explain <span "
"class=\"ui\">reading screen</span> here. <span class=\"ui\">File browser</"
"span> is explained under <a href=\"#L2-filebrowser\">this section</a> of the "
"guide."
msgstr ""
"Tá 2 phríomh-chomhéadan ag KOReader: <span class=\"ui\">scáileán "
"léitheoireachta</span> agus <span class=\"ui\">brabhsálaí comhad</span>. "
"Mínímid <span class=\"ui\">scáileán léitheoireachta</span> anseo. Mínítear "
"<span class=\"ui\">brabhsálaí comhad</span> faoin <a href=\"#L2-"
"filebrowser\">roinn seo</a> den treoir."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1491-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-readingscreen"
msgid "Reading Screen"
msgstr "Scáileán Léitheoireachta"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1493-5
msgid "<b>READING SCREEN</b> has two menus:"
msgstr "Tá dhá roghchlár ag an <b>SCÁILEÁN LÉITHEOIREACHTA</b>:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1496-3
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">TOP MENU</span> includes menu items related to the "
"general usage of KOReader. You will access your books, KOReader preferences, "
"plugins etc. here."
msgstr ""
"Áirítear sa <span class=\"ui\">ROGHCHLÁR BARR</span> míreanna roghchláir a "
"bhaineann le húsáid ghinearálta KOReader. Gheobhaidh tú rochtain ar do "
"leabhair, do chuid sainroghanna KOReader, breiseáin srl. anseo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1497-3
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">BOTTOM MENU</span> is focused on options for <b>document "
"formatting</b> like font weight/size, line spacing etc. While adjusting your "
"text appearance, you will mostly interact with the <span class=\"ui\">BOTTOM "
"MENU</span>."
msgstr ""
"Díríonn an <span class=\"ui\">ROGHCHLÁR BUN</span> ar roghanna le haghaidh "
"<b>formáidiú doiciméad</b> amhail meáchan/méid cló, spásáil líne srl. Agus "
"cuma do théacs á coigeartú agat, is leis an <span class=\"ui\">ROGHCHLÁR "
"BUN</span> a bheidh tú ag idirghníomhú den chuid is mó."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1505-5
msgid ""
"Image above shows the elements you can see on your reader screen when "
"reading a book:"
msgstr ""
"Taispeánann an íomhá thuas na heilimintí is féidir leat a fheiceáil ar "
"scáileán do léitheora agus leabhar á léamh agat:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1507-9
msgid ""
"<b>Indicator icons:</b> These icons inform you about certain ongoing "
"processes and states. You will see them at the top left corner of your "
"screen during certain operations. Normally they are smaller but here we show "
"them bigger for clarity. Next heading explains these indicator icons in "
"detail: <a href=\"#L2-indicators\">Indicator icons</a>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Deilbhíní táscaire:</b> Cuireann na deilbhíní seo ar an eolas thú faoi "
"phróisis agus stáit áirithe atá ar siúl. Feicfidh tú iad sa chúinne "
"uachtarach ar chlé de do scáileán le linn oibríochtaí áirithe. De ghnáth "
"bíonn siad níos lú ach taispeánaimid iad níos mó anseo ar mhaithe le "
"soiléireacht. Mínítear na deilbhíní táscaire seo go mion sa chéad "
"cheannteideal eile: <a href=\"#L2-indicators\">Deilbhíní táscaire</a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1508-9
msgid ""
"<b>Status bar:</b>This is a highly configurable area where you can see "
"various information about your book and KOReader. Click here to go to the "
"section: <a href=\"#L2-statusbar\">Status bar</a>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Barra stádais:</b>Is limistéar an-inchumraithe é seo inar féidir leat "
"faisnéis éagsúil faoi do leabhar agus KOReader a fheiceáil. Cliceáil anseo "
"chun dul go dtí an chuid: <a href=\"#L2-statusbar\">Barra stádais</a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1509-9
msgid ""
"<b>Alternate Status bar:</b> In addition to the default <span "
"class=\"ui\">Status bar</span>, we have an <span class=\"ui\">Alt status "
"bar</span> which appears at the top of the page if you enable it. Click here "
"for details: <a href=\"#L2-statusbar\">Status bar</a>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Barra Stádais Malartach:</b> Chomh maith leis an <span class=\"ui\">barra "
"stádais</span> réamhshocraithe, tá <span class=\"ui\">barra stádais "
"malartach</span> againn a fheictear ag barr an leathanaigh má chumasaíonn tú "
"é. Cliceáil anseo le haghaidh sonraí: <a href=\"#L2-statusbar\">Barra "
"Stádais</a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1510-9
msgid ""
"<b>Reference page numbers:</b> If the publisher of your book included the "
"page numbers from the paper printed version of the book, you will see them "
"like this. Click here for more info: <a href=\"#L3-referencepages\">Page "
"numbering and reference page numbers</a>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Uimhreacha leathanach tagartha:</b> Má chuir foilsitheoir do leabhair na "
"huimhreacha leathanach ón leagan clóite páipéir den leabhar san áireamh, "
"feicfidh tú iad mar seo. Cliceáil anseo le haghaidh tuilleadh eolais: <a "
"href=\"#L3-referencepages\">Uimhriú leathanach agus uimhreacha leathanach "
"tagartha</a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1511-9
msgid ""
"<b>Highlight types:</b> You can see the different highlight types here. Also "
"you can make colored highlights if your device has a suitable screen. Click "
"here to go to the section: <a href=\"#L1-bookmarks\">Bookmarks, Highlighting "
"and Notes</a>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Cineálacha aibhsithe:</b> Is féidir leat na cineálacha aibhsithe éagsúla "
"a fheiceáil anseo. Chomh maith leis sin, is féidir leat aibhsithe daite a "
"dhéanamh má tá scáileán oiriúnach ar do ghléas. Cliceáil anseo chun dul go "
"dtí an chuid: <a href=\"#L1-bookmarks\">Leabharmharcanna, Aibhsithe agus "
"Nótaí</a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1512-9
msgid ""
"<b>Note marker:</b> Note marker icon shows up when you add a note to a "
"highlight. We have different types of note markers. Click here for more "
"info: <a href=\"#L1-bookmarks\">Bookmarks, Highlighting and Notes</a>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Marcóir nóta:</b> Taispeántar deilbhín marcóra nóta nuair a chuireann tú "
"nóta le buaicphointe. Tá cineálacha éagsúla marcóirí nóta againn. Cliceáil "
"anseo le haghaidh tuilleadh eolais: <a href=\"#L1-"
"bookmarks\">Leabharmharcanna, Aibhsiú agus Nótaí</a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1516-1
msgid "Indicator icons"
msgstr "Deilbhíní táscaire"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1518-5
msgid ""
"KOReader has some indicators to inform you about certain ongoing processes "
"and states as you can see in the image above. You will see them at the top "
"left corner of your screen during certain operations."
msgstr ""
"Tá roinnt táscairí ag KOReader chun tú a chur ar an eolas faoi phróisis agus "
"stáit áirithe atá ar siúl mar is féidir leat a fheiceáil san íomhá thuas. "
"Feicfidh tú iad sa chúinne uachtarach ar chlé de do scáileán le linn "
"oibríochtaí áirithe."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1524-17
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_orange\">Partial rendering icons</span> This group of "
"icons belong to the partial rendering procedure and probably you will see "
"these icons more frequently than the others. You see these icons when you "
"change the settings on the <span class=\"ui\">bottom menu</span>."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_orange\">Deilbhíní rindreála páirteach</span> Baineann "
"an grúpa deilbhíní seo leis an nós imeachta rindreála páirteach agus is "
"dócha go bhfeicfidh tú na deilbhíní seo níos minice ná na cinn eile. "
"Feiceann tú na deilbhíní seo nuair a athraíonn tú na socruithe ar an <span "
"class=\"ui\">roghchlár bun</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1526-13
msgid ""
"This feature, allows you to preview the text appearance adjustments much "
"quicker by only rendering the current chapter instead of the whole book. "
"Also rotating your screen orientation is now much faster thanks to this "
"feature. This feature is <b>ENABLED</b> by default. If necessary, it can be "
"disabled per book (with a tap), or globally (with a long-tap) on:"
msgstr ""
"Leis an ngné seo, is féidir leat réamhamharc a dhéanamh ar choigeartuithe "
"cuma an téacs i bhfad níos tapúla tríd an gcaibidil reatha amháin a "
"rindreáil seachas an leabhar ar fad. Chomh maith leis sin, tá rothlú "
"treoshuíomh an scáileáin i bhfad níos tapúla anois a bhuíochas leis an ngné "
"seo. Tá an ghné seo <b>CUMASÚITHE</b> de réir réamhshocraithe. Más gá, is "
"féidir í a dhíchumasú in aghaidh an leabhair (le sconna), nó go domhanda (le "
"sconna fada) ar:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.div:1528-13
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:24px;\"> / Document / Enable partial renderings"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:24px;\"> / Doiciméad / Cumasaigh rindreálacha páirteacha"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1530-13
msgid ""
"After confirming your changes whole book has to be re-rendered so this is a "
"multi-step procedure. These icons shows the stage of rendering as explained "
"below:"
msgstr ""
"Tar éis duit do chuid athruithe a dheimhniú, ní mór an leabhar ar fad a ath-"
"rindreáil, mar sin is nós imeachta ilchéime é seo. Taispeánann na deilbhíní "
"seo céim an rindreála mar a mhínítear thíos:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1540-17
msgid ""
"In this stage, document is <b>partially</b> rendered. Page count, footer "
"info and many things are <b>innacurate</b>. You can see how the new settings "
"look and adjust further. You can also turn pages, jump links in this state."
msgstr ""
"Sa chéim seo, déantar an doiciméad a rindreáil <b>go páirteach</b>. Tá líon "
"na leathanach, faisnéis faoin mbunleathanach agus go leor rudaí "
"<b>míchruinn</b>. Is féidir leat a fheiceáil cén chuma atá ar na socruithe "
"nua agus iad a choigeartú tuilleadh. Is féidir leat leathanaigh a chasadh, "
"naisc a léim sa staid seo freisin."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1544-17
msgid ""
"A full rendering is happening in the <b>background</b>. You can still turn "
"pages, jump links, change settings."
msgstr ""
"Tá rindreáil iomlán ar siúl sa <b>chúlra</b>. Is féidir leat leathanaigh a "
"chasadh, naisc a léim, agus socruithe a athrú fós."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1548-17
msgid ""
"Full rendering is done, but <b>not yet applied</b> because KOReader is "
"waiting for you to be <b>idle</b> to reload the rest of the book (idle=not "
"interacting with the device). You can still turn pages, jump links, change "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"Tá an rindreáil iomlán déanta, ach <b>níl sé curtha i bhfeidhm fós</b> mar "
"go bhfuil KOReader ag fanacht leat a bheith <b>díomhaoin</b> chun an chuid "
"eile den leabhar a athlódáil (díomhaoin = gan idirghníomhú leis an "
"bhfeiste). Is féidir leat leathanaigh a chasadh, naisc a léim, agus "
"socruithe a athrú fós."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1553-17
msgid ""
"You've been idle for a while so KOReader is now reloading the whole "
"document. At this step KOReader is <b>blocked</b> to prevent interaction."
msgstr ""
"Bhí tú díomhaoin ar feadh tamaill agus mar sin tá KOReader ag athlódáil an "
"doiciméid ar fad anois. Ag an gcéim seo tá KOReader <b>blocáilte</b> chun "
"idirghníomhaíocht a chosc."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1557-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">INFO</span> Partial rendering is only possible if "
"your EPUB is composed of multiple fragments. EPUB files are basically .zip "
"archives that contain .html files. Some books can be a single .html file "
"while others may be composed of multiple .html files like each chapter of "
"the book is a separate .html file. <b>If your book is only a single .html "
"file, partial rendering can not work, because for each change KOReader still "
"has to calculate the whole book.</b>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">EOLAS</span> Ní féidir rindreáil pháirteach a "
"dhéanamh ach amháin má tá do EPUB comhdhéanta de bhlúirí iolracha. Is "
"cartlanna .zip iad comhaid EPUB go bunúsach ina bhfuil comhaid .html. Is "
"féidir le roinnt leabhar a bheith ina gcomhad .html aonair agus is féidir le "
"cinn eile a bheith comhdhéanta de chomhaid .html iolracha amhail is dá mba "
"chomhad .html ar leithligh gach caibidil den leabhar. <b>Mura bhfuil i do "
"leabhar ach comhad .html aonair, ní féidir le rindreáil pháirteach oibriú, "
"mar go gcaithfidh KOReader an leabhar iomlán a ríomh i gcás gach athraithe.</"
"b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1565-13
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_orange\">Highlighting icon</span> This icon shows up "
"when you are in the <span class=\"ui\">Select and highlight mode</span>. "
"KOReader has an additional highlight mode which allows you to start a "
"highlight and turn pages to make long highlights which can span multiple "
"pages. You can read about this in the <a href=\"#bookmarks\">BOOKMARKS, "
"HIGHLIGHTING AND NOTES</a> section of this guide. When you start a highlight "
"in this mode, this icon is shown at the corner to remind you that you are "
"still in the highlighting mode. It disappears when you finish your highlight "
"by <b>selecting the end of the passage</b> or when you <b>cancel the "
"highlight</b> (by tapping again on the beginning of your highlight or on "
"this <span class=\"ui\">highlighting icon</span>)."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_orange\">Deilbhín aibhsithe</span> Feictear an deilbhín "
"seo nuair atá tú sa mhodh <span class=\"ui\">Roghnaigh agus aibhsigh</span>. "
"Tá modh aibhsithe breise ag KOReader a ligeann duit aibhsiú a thosú agus "
"leathanaigh a chasadh chun aibhsithe fada a dhéanamh ar féidir leo dul thar "
"illeathanaigh. Is féidir leat léamh faoi seo sa chuid <a "
"href=\"#bookmarks\">LEABHARMHARCANNA, AIRDSHIÚ AGUS NÓTAÍ</a> den treoir "
"seo. Nuair a thosaíonn tú aibhsiú sa mhodh seo, taispeántar an deilbhín seo "
"sa chúinne chun a mheabhrú duit go bhfuil tú fós sa mhodh aibhsithe. Imíonn "
"sé nuair a chríochnaíonn tú d’aibhsiú trí <b>dheireadh an sliocht a roghnú</"
"b> nó nuair <b>chealaíonn tú an aibhsiú</b> (trí thapáil arís ar thús "
"d’aibhsithe nó ar an <span class=\"ui\">deilbhín aibhsithe</span> seo)."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1572-13
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_orange\">Pokemon ball icon</span> This icon shows up "
"when you press for a long time on a word (intentionally or accidentally). "
"KOReader has a normal <b>long press</b> menu. And an additional <b>very long "
"press</b> menu when you hold your finger longer than 3 seconds. This icon "
"means that you activated this very long press menu."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_orange\">Deilbhín liathróide Pokémon</span> Feictear an "
"deilbhín seo nuair a bhrúnn tú ar fhocal ar feadh i bhfad (d'aon ghnó nó de "
"thaisme). Tá gnáth-roghchlár <b>brúigh fhada</b> ag KOReader. Agus roghchlár "
"<b>brúigh an-fhada</b> breise nuair a choinníonn tú do mhéar ar feadh níos "
"mó ná 3 soicind. Ciallaíonn an deilbhín seo gur ghníomhaigh tú an roghchlár "
"brúigh an-fhada seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1579-13
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_orange\">Flip mode icon</span> This icon shows up when "
"you tap the top left corner if:"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_orange\">Deilbhín mód smeach</span> Feictear an deilbhín "
"seo nuair a thapálann tú ar an gcúinne uachtarach ar chlé má:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.ul.li:1581-17
msgid "You are reading a PDF document"
msgstr "Tá tú ag léamh doiciméad PDF"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.ul.li:1582-17
msgid ""
"And you are in a zoomed in view other than 100% (column, row or manual) or "
"in the <span class=\"ui\">reflow mode</span>"
msgstr ""
"Agus tá tú i radharc súmáilte isteach seachas 100% (colún, sraith nó "
"lámhleabhar) nó sa <span class=\"ui\">mód athshreafa</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1585-13
msgid ""
"This mode temporarily displays the full page without cropping, scaled to fit "
"your screen. You can turn the pages in this mode. To exit this mode, tap on "
"this icon."
msgstr ""
"Taispeántar an leathanach iomlán go sealadach sa mhodh seo gan é a "
"bhearradh, scálaithe chun freastal ar do scáileán. Is féidir leat na "
"leathanaigh a chasadh sa mhodh seo. Chun an modh seo a fhágáil, tapáil ar an "
"deilbhín seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1592-1
msgid "Page numbering and reference page numbers"
msgstr "Uimhriú leathanach agus uimhreacha leathanach tagartha"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1594-5
msgid ""
"Document types like <b>epub, mobi, html</b> naturally don't have fixed page "
"numbers because they are reflowable documents. Which means, these documents "
"can be adjusted according to the screen size and orientation of the device "
"(unlike <b>pdfs</b> or <b>djvu</b> files for example, which have a fixed "
"page size)."
msgstr ""
"Ar ndóigh, ní bhíonn uimhreacha leathanaigh sheasta ag cineálacha doiciméad "
"cosúil le <b>epub, mobi, html</b> toisc gur doiciméid in-athshreabhta iad. "
"Ciallaíonn sé sin gur féidir na doiciméid seo a choigeartú de réir mhéid an "
"scáileáin agus treoshuíomh an ghléis (murab ionann agus comhaid <b>pdfs</b> "
"nó <b>djvu</b> mar shampla, a bhfuil méid leathanaigh seasta acu)."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1596-5
msgid ""
"If you increase the font size of a reflowable document, your page count will "
"increase too, because now less text will fit on a single page. This "
"sometimes causes a problem because a highlight which you made on <b>page 38</"
"b> might be on <b>page 42</b> after the font adjustment."
msgstr ""
"Má mhéadaíonn tú méid cló doiciméid in-athshreabhta, méadóidh líon na "
"leathanach freisin, mar anois ní bheidh níos lú téacs oiriúnach ar "
"leathanach amháin. Uaireanta bíonn fadhb mar gheall ar seo mar d'fhéadfadh "
"aibhsiú a rinne tú ar <b>leathanach 38</b> a bheith ar <b>leathanach 42</b> "
"tar éis an choigeartaithe cló."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1598-5
msgid ""
"KOReader supports <b>Reference page numbers</b> feature which allows "
"publishers to embed page numbers from printed books directly to the e-book "
"version. When you enable this feature, KOReader doesn't calculate the page "
"numbers itself. Instead, it shows you the <b>embedded page numbers</b> from "
"the publisher. This means, the page number you see in your <span "
"class=\"ui\">Status bar</span> matches the print version of the book."
msgstr ""
"Tacaíonn KOReader leis an ngné <b>Uimhreacha leathanach tagartha</b> a "
"ligeann d’fhoilsitheoirí uimhreacha leathanach ó leabhair chlóite a leabú go "
"díreach isteach sa leagan ríomhleabhair. Nuair a chuireann tú an ghné seo ar "
"siúl, ní ríomhann KOReader na huimhreacha leathanach féin. Ina áit sin, "
"taispeánann sé na <b>uimhreacha leathanach leabaithe</b> ón bhfoilsitheoir "
"duit. Ciallaíonn sé seo, go bhfuil an uimhir leathanaigh a fheiceann tú i do "
"<span class=\"ui\">bharra stádais</span> ag teacht leis an leagan clóite den "
"leabhar."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1600-5
msgid "Benefits of reference page numbers:"
msgstr "Buntáistí a bhaineann le huimhreacha leathanach tagartha:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1602-9
msgid ""
"Reference page numbers enable accurate citations by matching the page "
"numbers found in the printed versions."
msgstr ""
"Cuireann uimhreacha leathanach tagartha ar chumas luanna cruinne trí na "
"huimhreacha leathanach atá sna leaganacha clóite a mheaitseáil."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1603-9
msgid ""
"Reference page numbers can aid in navigation, especially for readers who are "
"familiar with the print version of a book. It can help you find specific "
"passages or quotes more easily in the digital version."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le huimhreacha leathanach tagartha cabhrú le nascleanúint, go "
"háirithe do léitheoirí atá eolach ar leagan clóite leabhair. Is féidir leo "
"cabhrú leat pasáistí nó Sleachta sonracha a aimsiú níos éasca sa leagan "
"digiteach."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1604-9
msgid ""
"Since digital books can be read on various devices and platforms, each with "
"its own font size and display settings, shown page numbers can vary "
"significantly. Reference page numbers provide a consistent point of "
"reference when reading the same book on different devices like e-reader and "
"phone at the same time."
msgstr ""
"Ós rud é gur féidir leabhair dhigiteacha a léamh ar ghléasanna agus ardáin "
"éagsúla, agus a mhéid cló agus a shocruithe taispeána féin ag gach ceann "
"acu, is féidir le huimhreacha leathanach a thaispeántar a bheith an-éagsúil. "
"Soláthraíonn uimhreacha leathanach tagartha pointe tagartha comhsheasmhach "
"agus an leabhar céanna á léamh ar ghléasanna éagsúla cosúil le léitheoir "
"leictreonach agus fón ag an am céanna."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1607-5
msgid "You can enable this feature from:"
msgstr "Is féidir leat an ghné seo a chumasú ó:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1609-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Reference pages / Use reference page numbers"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Leathanaigh thagartha / Úsáid uimhreacha leathanach "
"tagartha"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1611-5
msgid ""
"If you also check the <span class=\"ui\">Show reference page labels in "
"margin</span> option from the same menu, this page numbers will be shown "
"next to the text in a small font."
msgstr ""
"Má dhéanann tú tic sa rogha <span class=\"ui\">Taispeáin lipéid leathanaigh "
"tagartha san imeall</span> ón roghchlár céanna freisin, taispeánfar na "
"huimhreacha leathanaigh seo in aice leis an téacs i gcló beag."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1613-5
msgid ""
"Please note that this menu appears only if there are embedded <b>Reference "
"page numbers</b> in your book."
msgstr ""
"Tabhair faoi deara nach bhfuil an roghchlár seo le feiceáil ach amháin má tá "
"<b>uimhreacha leathanaigh tagartha</b> leabaithe i do leabhar."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1617-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-statusbar"
msgid "Status bar"
msgstr "Barra stádais"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1619-5
msgid ""
"KOReader have two status bars, a <span class=\"ui\">Bottom status bar</span> "
"which is enabled by default. And we have an <span class=\"ui\">Alt status "
"bar</span> which appears at the top of the page if you enable it. This <span "
"class=\"ui\">Alt status bar</span> is available only in reflowable documents "
"(epub, html, docx, rtf, txt…)."
msgstr ""
"Tá dhá bharra stádais ag KOReader, <span class=\"ui\">barra stádais bun</"
"span> atá cumasaithe de réir réamhshocraithe. Agus tá <span "
"class=\"ui\">barra stádais Alt</span> againn a thaispeántar ag barr an "
"leathanaigh má chumasaíonn tú é. Níl an <span class=\"ui\">barra stádais "
"Alt</span> seo ar fáil ach i ndoiciméid in-athshreabhta (epub, html, docx, "
"rtf, txt…)."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1621-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Bottom status bar</span> is the newer one which is "
"actively maintained. <span class=\"ui\">Alt status bar</span> is a remnant "
"from earlier versions of KOReader so we are not adding new features to it. "
"But you can still enable this <span class=\"ui\">Alt status bar</span> if "
"you find it useful. You can enable it from:"
msgstr ""
"Is é an <span class=\"ui\">barra stádais bun</span> an ceann is nuaí atá á "
"chothabháil go gníomhach. Is iarsma ó leaganacha níos luaithe de KOReader an "
"<span class=\"ui\">barra stádais alt</span> agus mar sin nílimid ag cur "
"gnéithe nua leis. Ach is féidir leat an <span class=\"ui\">barra stádais "
"alt</span> seo a chumasú fós má cheapann tú go bhfuil sé úsáideach. Is "
"féidir leat é a chumasú ó:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1623-5
msgid ""
"BOTTOM MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Alt Status Bar"
msgstr ""
"AN ROCHLÁR BUNA / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Barra Stádais Alt"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1625-5
msgid ""
"You can configure the <span class=\"ui\">Alt status bar</span> from this "
"menu:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat an <span class=\"ui\">barra stádais Alt</span> a chumrú ón "
"roghchlár seo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1627-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.div:1627-5"
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Status Bar / Alt status bar"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Barra Stádais / Barra stádais Alt"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1629-5
msgid ""
"Instructions in the rest of this section are for the <span "
"class=\"ui\">Bottom status bar</span>."
msgstr ""
"Is don <span class=\"ui\">bharra stádais bun</span> atá na treoracha sa "
"chuid eile den alt seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1631-1
msgid "Configuring the status bar"
msgstr "Cumrú an bharra stádais"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1633-2
msgid ""
"You can configure the bottom status bar from this menu. Feel free to explore "
"the <span class=\"ui\">SETTINGS</span> sub-menu to customize your status bar "
"as you like."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat an barra stádais bun a chumrú ón roghchlár seo. Ná bíodh "
"drogall ort an fo-roghchlár <span class=\"ui\">SOCRÚCHÁIN</span> a iniúchadh "
"chun do bharra stádais a shaincheapadh de réir mar is mian leat."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1635-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Status Bar"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Barra Stádais"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1639-5
msgid ""
"There are many items you can show on the status bar. But by default, only "
"one is shown at a time and you have to tap on the status bar to cycle "
"between them. If you want to show all items at once, enable it from here:"
msgstr ""
"Tá go leor míreanna ann ar féidir leat a thaispeáint ar an mbarra stádais. "
"Ach de réir réamhshocraithe, ní thaispeántar ach ceann amháin ag an am agus "
"caithfidh tú tapáil ar an mbarra stádais chun rothlú eatarthu. Más mian leat "
"na míreanna go léir a thaispeáint ag an am céanna, cumasaigh é as seo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1641-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Status Bar / Configure items / Show all selected "
"items at once"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Barra Stádais / Cumraigh míreanna / Taispeáin na "
"míreanna roghnaithe go léir ag an am céanna"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1645-5
msgid ""
"If you enabled the option above, you can't hide the status bar by tapping on "
"it. If you want to hide it, you should assign a gesture here for toggling "
"the status bar:"
msgstr ""
"Mura bhfuil an rogha thuas cumasaithe agat, ní féidir leat an barra stádais "
"a cheilt trí thapáil air. Más mian leat é a cheilt, ba chóir duit gotha a "
"shannadh anseo chun an barra stádais a athrú:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1647-5
msgid "Gesture selection menu / Reader / Toggle status bar"
msgstr "Roghchlár roghnúcháin gothaí / Léitheoir / Barra stádais a scoránaigh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1649-5
msgid "Sorting the status bar items:"
msgstr "Sórtáil míreanna an bharra stádais:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1651-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Status Bar / Configure items / Arrange items in "
"status bar"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Barra Stádais / Cumraigh míreanna / Socraigh "
"míreanna sa bharra stádais"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1655-1
msgid "Using \"Custom Text\" item for status bar alignment"
msgstr ""
"Ag baint úsáide as an mír \"Téacs Saincheaptha\" le haghaidh ailíniú barra "
"stádais"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1656-5
msgid ""
"There is a special status bar item named <span class=\"ui\">Custom text</"
"span>. This item can show your chosen text in the status bar. You can also "
"use this feature to create a separator between the status bar items as you "
"can see in the example below:"
msgstr ""
"Tá mír speisialta sa bharra stádais darb ainm <span class=\"ui\">Téacs "
"saincheaptha</span>. Is féidir leis an mír seo an téacs roghnaithe agat a "
"thaispeáint sa bharra stádais. Is féidir leat an ghné seo a úsáid freisin "
"chun deighilteoir a chruthú idir na míreanna sa bharra stádais mar is féidir "
"leat a fheiceáil san sampla thíos:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1661-9
msgid "First enable this option with a short press on it from this menu"
msgstr "Cumasaigh an rogha seo ar dtús le brúigh ghearr air ón roghchlár seo"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li.div:1663-13
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Status Bar / Custom text: ‘KOReader’"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Barra Stádais / Téacs saincheaptha: ‘KOReader’"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1666-9
msgid ""
"Then long-press on it again to open its settings. Enter a <b>\"space\"</b> "
"character in the first box and enter the number of repetitions in the second "
"box, which will determine how wide your separator will be."
msgstr ""
"Ansin brúigh air arís chun a shocruithe a oscailt. Cuir isteach carachtar "
"<b>\"spás\"</b> sa chéad bhosca agus cuir isteach líon na n-athrá sa dara "
"bosca, rud a chinnfidh cé chomh leathan is a bheidh do dheighilteoir."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1669-5
msgid ""
"You can choose another character as a separator. You can also move this item "
"like other status bar items to change its order to adjust your groups."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat carachtar eile a roghnú mar dheighilteoir. Is féidir leat an "
"mhír seo a bhogadh freisin cosúil le míreanna eile sa bharra stádais chun a "
"hord a athrú chun do ghrúpaí a choigeartú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1671-1
msgid "Chapter progress bar"
msgstr "Barra dul chun cinn na caibidle"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1673-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Progress bar</span> in the <span class=\"ui\">status bar</"
"span> normally shows your progress for the whole book. But it can also show "
"your progress for the <b>current chapter</b> instead. This can be useful for "
"example, if a book has lots of short chapters. In this case it might be hard "
"to see your progress in the current chapter so <span class=\"ui\">chapter "
"status bar</span> can be more informative here. You can enable the feature "
"from this menu:"
msgstr ""
"De ghnáth, taispeánann an <span class=\"ui\">barra dul chun cinn</span> sa "
"<span class=\"ui\">bharra stádais</span> do dhul chun cinn don leabhar ar "
"fad. Ach is féidir leis do dhul chun cinn don <b>chaibidil reatha</b> a "
"thaispeáint freisin. Is féidir leis seo a bheith úsáideach mar shampla, má "
"tá go leor caibidlí gearra i leabhar. Sa chás seo, d'fhéadfadh sé a bheith "
"deacair do dhul chun cinn sa chaibidil reatha a fheiceáil, mar sin is féidir "
"le <span class=\"ui\">barra stádais na caibidle</span> a bheith níos "
"faisnéiseach anseo. Is féidir leat an ghné a chumasú ón roghchlár seo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1675-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Status Bar / Progress Bar / Show chapter-progress "
"bar instead"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Barra Stádais / Barra Dul Chun Cinn / Taispeáin "
"barra dul chun cinn na caibidle ina ionad"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1677-5
msgid ""
"Also you can assign a gesture to switch between normal and chapter progress "
"bars. You can find this action under:"
msgstr ""
"Chomh maith leis sin, is féidir leat gotha a shannadh chun aistriú idir "
"barraí dul chun cinn gnáth agus barraí dul chun cinn caibidle. Is féidir "
"leat an gníomh seo a fháil faoi:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1679-5
msgid "Gesture selection menu / Reader / Toggle chapter progress bar"
msgstr ""
"Roghchlár roghnúcháin gotha / Léitheoir / Barra dul chun cinn caibidle a "
"scoránaigh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1685-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-topexplained"
msgid "Top Menu Items"
msgstr "Míreanna Barr-Roghchláir"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1687-5
msgid ""
"Here we will only give an overview of the items in the <span "
"class=\"ui\">top menu</span> structure to make you familiar with the menu. "
"Detailed information is available under the related sections of this guide."
msgstr ""
"Anseo ní thabharfaimid ach forbhreathnú ar na míreanna i struchtúr an <span "
"class=\"ui\">roghchláir uachtaraigh</span> chun tú a chur ar an eolas faoin "
"roghchlár. Tá faisnéis mhionsonraithe ar fáil faoi na codanna gaolmhara den "
"treoir seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1692-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">NAVIGATION:</span> This menu contains items that allows "
"you to navigate the book you are currently reading. <b>Table of contents, "
"bookmarks, book map...</b>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">LOINGSEOIREACHT:</span> Tá míreanna sa roghchlár seo a "
"ligeann duit nascleanúint a dhéanamh tríd an leabhar atá á léamh agat faoi "
"láthair. <b>Clár ábhair, leabharmharcanna, léarscáil leabhar...</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1694-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">TYPESETTING:</span> This menu contains items that allows "
"you to change the appearance of your book. <b>Font settings, style tweaks..."
"</b>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">SOCRÚ CLÓ:</span> Tá míreanna sa roghchlár seo a ligeann "
"duit cuma do leabhair a athrú. <b>Socruithe cló, coigeartuithe stíl...</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1696-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">SETTINGS:</span> This menu contains settings for KOReader "
"and your device. <b>E-ink, light, gesture settings...</b>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">SOCRÚCHÁIN:</span> Tá socruithe do KOReader agus do "
"ghléas sa roghchlár seo. <b>Socruithe dúigh leictreonach, solais, gothaí...</"
"b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1698-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">TOOLS:</span> This menu contains plugins that can expand "
"the functionality of KOReader."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">UIRLISÍ:</span> Tá breiseáin sa roghchlár seo ar féidir "
"leo feidhmiúlacht KOReader a leathnú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1700-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">SEARCH:</span> This menu contains items related to search "
"and lookup. <b>Text search, dictionary, translation, Wikipedia...</b>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">CUARDAIGH:</span> Tá míreanna a bhaineann le cuardach "
"agus cuardach sa roghchlár seo. <b>Cuardach téacs, foclóir, aistriúchán, "
"Vicipéid...</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1702-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">FILE BROWSER:</span> This button opens the <span "
"class=\"ui\">file browser</span> which is the interface for managing your "
"library."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">BRAISEÁN COMHAD:</span> Osclaíonn an cnaipe seo an <span "
"class=\"ui\">brabhsálaí comhad</span> arb é an comhéadan é chun do "
"leabharlann a bhainistiú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1704-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">MAIN:</span> This menu contains tools for accessing your "
"books like <b>history, favorites, collections</b>. Also <b>book information</"
"b>, <b>update</b> and <b>exit</b> items are under this menu."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">PRÍOMH:</span> Tá uirlisí sa roghchlár seo chun rochtain "
"a fháil ar do leabhair ar nós <b>stair, rogha pearsanta, bailiúcháin</b>. "
"Chomh maith leis sin, tá <b>eolas leabhar</b>, <b>nuashonrú</b> agus "
"míreanna <b>scoir</b> faoin roghchlár seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1711-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-bottomexplained"
msgid "Bottom Menu Items"
msgstr "Míreanna Bun an Roghchláir"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1713-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">TIP</span> If you long tap on their names, you "
"can see an explanation of these items"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">LEID</span> Má thapaíonn tú ar a n-ainmneacha ar "
"feadh tamaill, feicfidh tú míniú ar na míreanna seo"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1718-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">View mode:</span> If you change to <span "
"class=\"ui\">continuous</span> mode you can scroll the document like a web "
"page. This mode is more suitable for non e-ink screen types (LCD, OLED). In "
"continuous mode <b>you lose top and bottom margins</b> so text may be cut on "
"the first and last line of screen. To solve this problem you can enable "
"<span class=\"ui\">Page overlap</span>:"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Mód radhairc:</span> Má athraíonn tú go mód <span "
"class=\"ui\">leanúnach</span> is féidir leat an doiciméad a scrollú cosúil "
"le leathanach gréasáin. Tá an mód seo níos oiriúnaí do chineálacha scáileáin "
"nach n-e-dúch iad (LCD, OLED). Sa mhodh leanúnach <b>caillfidh tú corrlaigh "
"uachtaracha agus íochtaracha</b> agus mar sin d'fhéadfadh téacs a bheith "
"gearrtha ar an gcéad líne agus ar an líne dheireanach den scáileán. Chun an "
"fhadhb seo a réiteach is féidir leat <span class=\"ui\">forluí leathanaigh</"
"span> a chumasú:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1720-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Page Overlap"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Forluí Leathanaigh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1722-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Render mode:</span> This option determines how your "
"document is rendered by KOReader. Default is <span class=\"ui\">WEB</span> "
"and generally you don’t need to change this setting. When a book (or saved "
"web page) is very complicated (specified widths or margins, negative "
"margins, floats etc.) and layout looks bad or overflow the screen, you can "
"try other rendering modes."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Mód rindreála:</span> Cinneann an rogha seo conas a "
"rindreálann KOReader do dhoiciméad. Is é <span class=\"ui\">GRÉASÁN</span> "
"an rogha réamhshocraithe agus de ghnáth ní gá duit an socrú seo a athrú. "
"Nuair a bhíonn leabhar (nó leathanach gréasáin sábháilte) an-chasta "
"(leithead nó corrlaigh shonraithe, corrlaigh dhiúltacha, snámháin srl.) agus "
"nuair a bhíonn cuma dona ar an leagan amach nó go bhfuil sé rófhada ar an "
"scáileán, is féidir leat modhanna rindreála eile a thriail."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1724-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Zoom (dpi):</span> This setting can be thought of as a "
"<b>general zoom factor</b> for the document (except font size). At 96 dpi "
"(which is the default setting), images in the document are rendered at their "
"original dimensions. Basically you will use this setting if you want to "
"<b>make images bigger without making the text bigger</b>."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Zúmáil (dpi):</span> Is féidir an socrú seo a mheas mar "
"<b>fhachtóir súmála ginearálta</b> don doiciméad (seachas méid an chló). Ag "
"96 dpi (arb é an socrú réamhshocraithe é), déantar íomhánna sa doiciméad a "
"rindreáil ag a dtoisí bunaidh. Go bunúsach úsáidfidh tú an socrú seo más "
"mian leat <b>íomhánna a dhéanamh níos mó gan an téacs a dhéanamh níos mó</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1730-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Word spacing and Word expansion</span> settings are "
"related and they determine how your text will look when it is justified. "
"When you justify text, space is added between words so that both edges of "
"each line are aligned with both margins. Since word counts of lines are not "
"equal all the time, in justified alignment, text has to be compressed or "
"expanded to fill the line."
msgstr ""
"Tá socruithe <span class=\"ui\">Spásáil focal agus leathnú focal</span> "
"gaolmhar agus is iad sin a chinneann cén chuma a bheidh ar do théacs nuair a "
"bheidh sé comhlíonta. Nuair a chomhlíontar téacs, cuirtear spás idir focail "
"ionas go mbeidh imeall gach líne ailínithe leis an dá imeall. Ós rud é nach "
"mbíonn comhaireamh focal na línte cothrom an t-am ar fad, i ailíniú "
"comhlíonta, caithfear téacs a chomhbhrú nó a leathnú chun an líne a líonadh."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1732-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Word spacing:</span> How much the <b>space</b> characters "
"in a line of text can be compressed to fit more words. This setting doesn’t "
"affect words, it only changes the space between them."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Spásáil focal:</span> Cé mhéad is féidir na carachtair "
"<b>spáis</b> i líne téacs a chomhbhrú chun níos mó focal a fheistiú. Ní "
"dhéanann an socrú seo difear do na focail, ní athraíonn sé ach an spás "
"eatarthu."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1734-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Word expansion:</span> If you have too much white space "
"in a line, how much of that can be distributed into the words by expanding "
"them. This setting affects the appearance of words. If you don’t want your "
"words to expand, set this to <span class=\"ui\">none</span>."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Leathnú focal:</span> Má tá an iomarca spáis bhán i líne, "
"cé mhéad de sin is féidir a dháileadh sna focail trí iad a leathnú. Bíonn "
"tionchar ag an socrú seo ar chuma na bhfocal. Mura dteastaíonn uait go "
"leathnóidh do chuid focal, socraigh é seo go <span class=\"ui\">níl</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1736-5
msgid ""
"You can experiment with different settings until the text looks pleasing to "
"you, then set them as defaults via their respective dialogs."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat triail a bhaint as socruithe éagsúla go dtí go mbeidh an "
"téacs taitneamhach duit, agus ansin iad a shocrú mar réamhshocruithe trína "
"ndialóga faoi seach."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1743-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Contrast</span> and <span class=\"ui\">Font weight</span> "
"are two options that you can use to make your text bolder (or lighter). You "
"can achieve the same appearance with either of these options but they use "
"different methods to achieve it. Of course you can use them both at the same "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Is dhá rogha iad <span class=\"ui\">Codarsnacht</span> agus <span "
"class=\"ui\">Meáchan cló</span> ar féidir leat a úsáid chun do théacs a "
"dhéanamh níos troime (nó níos éadroime). Is féidir leat an chuma chéanna a "
"bhaint amach le ceachtar den dá rogha seo ach úsáideann siad modhanna "
"difriúla chun é sin a bhaint amach. Ar ndóigh, is féidir leat an dá cheann a "
"úsáid ag an am céanna."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1745-5
msgid "The differences between them can be summarized as:"
msgstr "Is féidir na difríochtaí eatarthu a achoimriú mar seo a leanas:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div:1748-9
msgid "CONTRAST"
msgstr "CODRASACHT"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div.p:1750-13
msgid "<b>+</b> Doesn’t change font width, book length stays the same"
msgstr ""
"<b>+</b> Ní athraíonn sé leithead an chló, fanann fad an leabhair mar a "
"chéile"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div.p:1751-13
msgid "<b>+</b> Doesn’t need to re-render document, faster"
msgstr "<b>+</b> Ní gá an doiciméad a ath-rindreáil, níos tapúla"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div.p:1752-13
msgid "<b>-</b> Might look bad on LCD or low DPI screens"
msgstr ""
"<b>-</b> D’fhéadfadh cuma dhona a bheith air ar scáileáin LCD nó ar "
"scáileáin íseal-DPI"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div:1754-9
msgid "FONT WEIGHT"
msgstr "MEÁCHAN CLÓ"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div.p:1756-13
msgid "<b>+</b> Will use proper weighted fonts if you have them installed"
msgstr "<b>+</b> Úsáidfear clónna ualaithe cuí má tá siad suiteáilte agat"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div.p:1757-13
msgid "<b>+</b> Looks better on LCD or low DPI screens"
msgstr ""
"<b>+</b> Breathnaíonn sé níos fearr ar scáileáin LCD nó scáileáin íseal-DPI"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div.p:1758-13
msgid "<b>-</b> Has to re-render fonts, slower"
msgstr "<b>-</b> Caithfidh sé clónna a ath-rindreáil, níos moille"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1763-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Font hinting</span> adjusts your text for maximum "
"readability according to your screen’s pixel grid. <span "
"class=\"ui\">native</span> uses font’s internal hinting instructions, <span "
"class=\"ui\">auto</span> uses FreeType’s hinting algorithm. <span "
"class=\"ui\">auto</span> is a safer choice because font files that you "
"installed may have problematic hinting instructions. Also <span "
"class=\"ui\">auto</span> handles <b>CJK</b> text better. You can try "
"different settings to see which one looks better on your device."
msgstr ""
"Déanann <span class=\"ui\">Leideanna cló</span> do théacs a choigeartú le "
"haghaidh inléiteachta uasta de réir eangach picteilín do scáileáin. "
"Úsáideann <span class=\"ui\">dúchasach</span> treoracha leideanna "
"inmheánacha an chló, úsáideann <span class=\"ui\">uathoibríoch</span> "
"algartam leideanna FreeType. Is rogha níos sábháilte é <span "
"class=\"ui\">uathoibríoch</span> mar d'fhéadfadh treoracha leideanna "
"fadhbacha a bheith i gcomhaid chló a shuiteáil tú. Chomh maith leis sin, "
"láimhseálann <span class=\"ui\">uathoibríoch</span> téacs <b>CJK</b> níos "
"fearr. Is féidir leat socruithe éagsúla a thriail chun a fheiceáil cé acu "
"ceann is fearr a fhéachann ar do ghléas."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1765-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Font kerning</span> adjusts the spacing between letters "
"to achieve a visually pleasing result. Default is <span class=\"ui\">best</"
"span> option, which might be <b>slower</b> when opening files (depending on "
"your device) but <b>has better support for ligatures</b> (see picture below "
"for an example), joined <b>Arabic</b> glyphs and some other scripts. If your "
"device is slow, you can try <span class=\"ui\">good</span> which is faster "
"and may still look correct with western latin-script text."
msgstr ""
"Coigeartaíonn <span class=\"ui\">Cló-chéarnú</span> an spásáil idir "
"litreacha chun toradh taitneamhach ó thaobh amhairc de a bhaint amach. Is é "
"an rogha <span class=\"ui\">is fearr</span> an rogha réamhshocraithe, a "
"d'fhéadfadh a bheith <b>níos moille</b> agus comhaid á n-oscailt (ag brath "
"ar do ghléas) ach <b>tacaíonn sé níos fearr le ligatúir</b> (féach an "
"pictiúr thíos le haghaidh sampla), glifí <b>Araibis</b> ceangailte agus "
"roinnt scripteanna eile. Más mall do ghléas, is féidir leat triail a bhaint "
"as <span class=\"ui\">good</span> atá níos tapúla agus a d'fhéadfadh "
"breathnú ceart fós le téacs Laidineach an iarthair."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1774-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Alt status bar</span> enables an alternative status bar "
"which is available only in reflowable documents (EPUB, HTML, DOCX, RTF, "
"TXT…). After enabling it here, you can configure <span class=\"ui\">alt "
"status bar</span> via:"
msgstr ""
"Cumasaíonn <span class=\"ui\">barra stádais alt</span> barra stádais "
"malartach nach bhfuil ar fáil ach i ndoiciméid in-athshreabhta (EPUB, HTML, "
"DOCX, RTF, TXT…). Tar éis é a chumasú anseo, is féidir leat <span "
"class=\"ui\">barra stádais alt</span> a chumrú trí:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1776-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.div:1776-5"
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Status Bar / Alt status bar"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Barra Stádais / Barra stádais Alt"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1778-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Embedded style</span> and <span class=\"ui\">embedded "
"fonts</span> determine if publisher’s styles and fonts embedded in the "
"document will be used (or ignored) to render the document. These are general "
"on/off switches. You can achieve more fine tuned tweaks for your document "
"via:"
msgstr ""
"Cinneann <span class=\"ui\">Stíl leabaithe</span> agus <span "
"class=\"ui\">clónna leabaithe</span> an n-úsáidfear (nó an ndéanfar "
"neamhaird de) stíleanna agus clónna an fhoilsitheora atá leabaithe sa "
"doiciméad chun an doiciméad a rindreáil. Is lasca ginearálta ar siúl/as iad "
"seo. Is féidir leat níos mó coigeartuithe míne a dhéanamh ar do dhoiciméad "
"trí:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1780-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Style Tweaks"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Coigeartuithe Stíle"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1782-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Image scaling</span> determines how images in your "
"document are rendered. <span class=\"ui\">Best</span> looks more pleasing "
"but it is slower."
msgstr ""
"Cinneann <span class=\"ui\">Scálú íomhá</span> conas a rindreáiltear "
"íomhánna i do dhoiciméad. Breathnaíonn <span class=\"ui\">Is Fearr</span> "
"níos taitneamhaí ach tá sé níos moille."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1791-1
msgid "User Interface Tips"
msgstr "Leideanna maidir le Comhéadan Úsáideora"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1793-5
msgid ""
"KOReader’s user interface and options can change depending on the file type "
"you open. There are two main categories of documents:"
msgstr ""
"Féadfaidh comhéadan úsáideora agus roghanna KOReader athrú ag brath ar an "
"gcineál comhaid a osclaíonn tú. Tá dhá phríomhchatagóir doiciméad ann:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1795-4
msgid "<b>Fixed layout documents</b> (pdf, djvu, image files...)"
msgstr "<b>Doiciméid leagan amach seasta</b> (pdf, djvu, comhaid íomhá...)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1796-4
msgid "<b>Reflowable documents</b> (epub, html, docx, rtf, txt…)."
msgstr "<b>Doiciméid in-athshreabhta</b> (epub, html, docx, rtf, txt…)."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1799-5
msgid ""
"KOReader has lots of features so its menu system reflects this complexity. "
"We have a <span class=\"ui\">Menu Search</span> feature for finding menu "
"items quickly. If you remember the name of a menu item but don't remember "
"where it is, you can use this feature:"
msgstr ""
"Tá neart gnéithe ag KOReader agus mar sin léiríonn a chóras roghchláir an "
"chastacht seo. Tá gné <span class=\"ui\">Cuardaigh Roghchláir</span> againn "
"chun míreanna roghchláir a aimsiú go tapa. Má chuimhin leat ainm míre "
"roghchláir ach mura gcuimhin leat cá bhfuil sí, is féidir leat an ghné seo a "
"úsáid:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1801-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_hamburger.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Help / Menu search"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/"
"top_hamburger.svg\" style=\"width:22px;\"> / Cabhair / Cuardach roghchláir"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1803-5
msgid ""
"Also you can assign this feature to a gesture or add it to your <a "
"href=\"#L2-quickmenu\">Quick Menu</a> for faster access."
msgstr ""
"Chomh maith leis sin, is féidir leat an ghné seo a shannadh do ghluaisne nó "
"í a chur le do <a href=\"#L2-quickmenu\">Roghchlár Tapa</a> le haghaidh "
"rochtain níos tapúla."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1808-13
msgid ""
"On the <span class=\"ui\">bottom menu</span> if you tap and hold an option’s "
"name, you can see its explanation."
msgstr ""
"Ar an <span class=\"ui\">roghchlár bun</span> má thapaíonn tú agus má "
"choinníonn tú síos ainm rogha, is féidir leat a mhíniú a fheiceáil."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1812-13
msgid "You can change the interface language via:"
msgstr "Is féidir leat teanga an chomhéadain a athrú trí:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p.div:1812-59
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Language"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Teanga"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1818-13
msgid ""
"If you want to change the size of user interface, there is a <span "
"class=\"ui\">DPI</span> setting for that:"
msgstr ""
"Más mian leat méid an chomhéadain úsáideora a athrú, tá socrú <span "
"class=\"ui\">DPI</span> ann chuige sin:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.div:1820-13
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Screen / Screen DPI"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Scáileán / DPI an Scáileáin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1822-13
msgid ""
"You can choose a value from the menu or select <span class=\"ui\">Custom "
"dpi</span> to enter a value for fine tuning: <b>Higher DPI = Bigger "
"Interface</b>. Note that there is also a <span class=\"ui\">Zoom (dpi)</"
"span> setting in the bottom bar. That one is related to the documents only. "
"You can find the explanation in the next section."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat luach a roghnú ón roghchlár nó <span class=\"ui\">dpi "
"saincheaptha</span> a roghnú chun luach a iontráil le haghaidh "
"mionchoigeartú: <b>DPI Níos Airde = Comhéadan Níos Mó</b>. Tabhair faoi "
"deara go bhfuil socrú <span class=\"ui\">Zúmáil (dpi)</span> sa bharra bun "
"freisin. Baineann an ceann sin leis na doiciméid amháin. Is féidir leat an "
"míniú a fháil sa chéad chuid eile."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1826-13
msgid ""
"If you tap and hold an <b>option</b> or <b>menu item</b> (font weight, line "
"spacing etc.), you can set its value as <span class=\"ui\">DEFAULT</span>. "
"The new value will only be applied to books opened from now on. Previously "
"opened books will keep their settings. You can identify default values as a "
"<span class=\"ui\">star</span> (★) in the menu or as a <span "
"class=\"ui\">black border</span> around the indicators as seen below:"
msgstr ""
"Má thapaíonn tú agus má choinníonn tú <b>rogha</b> nó <b>mír roghchláir</b> "
"(meáchan cló, spásáil líne srl.), is féidir leat a luach a shocrú mar <span "
"class=\"ui\">RÉAMHSHOCRAITHE</span>. Ní chuirfear an luach nua i bhfeidhm "
"ach ar leabhair a osclaítear feasta. Coinneoidh leabhair a osclaíodh roimhe "
"seo a socruithe. Is féidir leat luachanna réamhshocraithe a aithint mar "
"<span class=\"ui\">réalta</span> (★) sa roghchlár nó mar <span "
"class=\"ui\">imreán dubh</span> timpeall na dtáscairí mar a fheictear thíos:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1833-13
msgid ""
"You can <b>close</b> full screen dialogs (<span class=\"ui\">History, Table "
"of Contents, Reading Statistics</span> etc.) by <b>swiping down</b>. (Except "
"<span class=\"ui\">Bookmarks</span> window. You can use any multi swipe "
"gesture to close this one)"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat dialóga lánscáileáin (<span class=\"ui\">Stair, Clár Ábhair, "
"Staitisticí Léitheoireachta</span> srl.) a <b>dhúnadh</b> trí <b>shvaipeáil "
"síos</b>. (Seachas fuinneog <span class=\"ui\">Leabharmharcanna</span>; is "
"féidir leat aon ghluaiseacht ilshvaipeála a úsáid chun í seo a dhúnadh)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1836-13
msgid ""
"You can take a <span class=\"ui\">screenshot</span> by making a <b>long "
"diagonal swipe</b> with your finger. Also <b>touching opposing diagonal "
"corners</b> will take a screenshot. You can use this second gesture for "
"example when viewing an image. Also if your device has a keyboard, you can "
"take a screenshot with the <span class=\"ui\">Alt + Shift + G</span> "
"shortcut."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat <span class=\"ui\">seat scáileáin</span> a thógáil trí "
"<b>shwipeáil fhada trasnánach</b> a dhéanamh le do mhéar. Chomh maith leis "
"sin, <b>teagmháil le coirnéil trasnánacha os coinne a chéile</b>, tógfar "
"seat scáileáin. Is féidir leat an dara gotha seo a úsáid mar shampla agus "
"íomhá á breathnú agat. Chomh maith leis sin, má tá méarchlár ar do ghléas, "
"is féidir leat seat scáileáin a thógáil leis an aicearra <span "
"class=\"ui\">Alt + Shift + G</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1839-13
msgid ""
"If you want to open a random page of a book, we have a <b>Jump to a random "
"page</b> action which you can assign to any gesture. It is in the <b>Reader</"
"b> category of the <span class=\"ui\">Gesture Manager</span>."
msgstr ""
"Más mian leat leathanach randamach de leabhar a oscailt, tá gníomh <b>Léim "
"go leathanach randamach</b> againn ar féidir leat a shannadh d'aon "
"ghluaiseacht. Tá sé i gcatagóir <b>Léitheoir</b> an <span "
"class=\"ui\">Bainisteoir Gluaiseachta</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1843-9
msgid ""
"In dialogs containing adjustment arrow buttons like the one above, you can "
"<b>tap and hold</b> on arrow buttons to change the value in bigger "
"increments."
msgstr ""
"I ndialóga ina bhfuil cnaipí saigheada coigeartaithe cosúil leis an gceann "
"thuas, is féidir leat <b>tapáil agus coinneáil</b> ar na cnaipí saigheada "
"chun an luach a athrú i méaduithe níos mó."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1844-9
msgid ""
"You can <b>close</b> this type of dialog (non-full screen) by tapping "
"outside of its window."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat an cineál seo dialóige (nach lánscáileán é) a <b>dhúnadh</b> "
"trí thapáil lasmuigh dá fhuinneog."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1845-9
msgid ""
"You can <b>move</b> this type of dialog by holding its window title and "
"dragging."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat an cineál seo dialóige a <b>bhogadh</b> trí theideal a "
"fhuinneoige a shealbhú agus a tharraingt."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1846-9
msgid ""
"You can make this type of dialog <b>semi-transparent</b> by tapping and "
"holding the <b>window title</b> (when you want to see the text under it "
"while adjusting a value)."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat an cineál seo dialóige a dhéanamh <b>leaththrédhearcach</b> "
"trí <b>theideal na fuinneoige</b> a thapáil agus a shealbhú (nuair is mian "
"leat an téacs faoi a fheiceáil agus luach á choigeartú agat)."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1850-13
msgid ""
"<b>Creating new folders - </b>In situations when you need to choose a "
"location (cloud storage, move to archive plugin, exporter plugin), KOReader "
"presents you a screen that looks like our <span class=\"ui\">File Browser</"
"span>. If you want to create a new folder while choosing:"
msgstr ""
"<b>Fillteáin nua a chruthú - </b>I gcásanna ina mbíonn ort suíomh a roghnú "
"(stóráil scamall, breiseán bogtha chuig cartlann, breiseán onnmhairithe), "
"cuireann KOReader scáileán i láthair duit atá cosúil lenár <span "
"class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span>. Más mian leat fillteán nua a chruthú "
"agus tú ag roghnú:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p.ol.li:1852-17
msgid ""
"First navigate to the folder from the <span class=\"ui\">Folder chooser "
"screen</span>"
msgstr ""
"Ar dtús, nascleanúint chuig an bhfillteán ón scáileán <span "
"class=\"ui\">roghnóir fillteán</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p.ol.li:1853-17
msgid ""
"Then <b>long-press</b> the <span class=\"ui\">Home icon</span> shown at the "
"upper-left corner of this screen"
msgstr ""
"Ansin <b>brúigh go fada</b> ar an deilbhín <span class=\"ui\">Baile</span> "
"atá le feiceáil sa chúinne uachtarach ar chlé den scáileán seo"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1859-13
msgid ""
"KOReader supports <b>dictionary lookup</b> in EPUB and scanned PDF/DJVU "
"documents. To see the dictionary definition or translation, just tap and "
"hold a word."
msgstr ""
"Tacaíonn KOReader le <b>cuardach foclóra</b> i ndoiciméid EPUB agus PDF/DJVU "
"scanta. Chun sainmhíniú nó aistriúchán an fhoclóra a fheiceáil, níl le "
"déanamh ach focal a thapáil agus a shealbhú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1860-9
msgid ""
"Pressing and holding a word brings up a dialog where you can also search the "
"selection in the document for more occurrences or look it up on Wikipedia."
msgstr ""
"Trí bhrú agus coinneáil síos focal, taispeánfar dialóg inar féidir leat an "
"rogha sa doiciméad a chuardach le haghaidh tuilleadh samplaí nó é a "
"chuardach ar Vicipéid."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:1863-13
msgid ""
"If you want to check the current date you can tap on the clock in the <span "
"class=\"ui\">TOP MENU</span>."
msgstr ""
"Más mian leat an dáta reatha a sheiceáil is féidir leat tapáil ar an gclog "
"sa <span class=\"ui\">ROGHCHLÁR BARR</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1867-1
msgid "Scrolling types"
msgstr "Cineálacha scrollaigh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1869-5
msgid "KOReader has three types of touch scrolling. You can access this from:"
msgstr ""
"Tá trí chineál scrollaigh tadhaill ag KOReader. Is féidir leat rochtain a "
"fháil air seo ó:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1871-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Taps and Gestures / Scrolling"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Tapálacha agus Gothaí / Scrollaigh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1873-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">INFO</span> You have to enable <span "
"class=\"ui\">Continuous mode</span> from the <span class=\"ui\">Bottom menu</"
"span> to be able to use scrolling."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">EOLAS</span> Caithfidh tú <span class=\"ui\">Mód "
"leanúnach</span> a chumasú ón <span class=\"ui\">roghchlár bun</span> le "
"bheith in ann scrollú a úsáid."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1876-9
msgid ""
"<b>Classic scrolling:</b> This mode works exactly like your phone/tablet "
"scrolling."
msgstr ""
"<b>Scrolláil chlasaiceach:</b> Oibríonn an modh seo díreach mar a oibríonn "
"scrollú do ghutháin/táibléid."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1878-9
msgid ""
"<b>Turbo scrolling:</b> This mode allows you to scroll faster than <span "
"class=\"ui\">classic scrolling</span>. Also you can scroll several pages "
"without lifting your finger. Scrolling amount is proportional to the "
"distance you move your finger after you initiated scrolling."
msgstr ""
"<b>Scrolla turbo:</b> Ligeann an modh seo duit scrollú níos tapúla ná <span "
"class=\"ui\">scrolllú clasaiceach</span>. Chomh maith leis sin, is féidir "
"leat roinnt leathanach a scrollú gan do mhéar a ardú. Tá an méid scrollú "
"comhréireach leis an achar a bhogann tú do mhéar tar éis duit tosú ag "
"scrollú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1880-9
msgid ""
"<b>On-release scrolling:</b> This scrolling type is more suitable for e-ink "
"screens. Because unlike other scrolling types, this mode doesn’t refresh "
"your page continuously while scrolling. It works like <span "
"class=\"ui\">classic scrolling</span> but intermediate steps are not shown. "
"So when you scroll with your finger and then release, page jumps to that "
"position. This is especially useful <b>to reposition and adjust the view</b> "
"if your book contains pictures or tables and you want to see all of it."
msgstr ""
"<b>Scrolláil ar scaoileadh:</b> Tá an cineál scrollála seo níos oiriúnaí do "
"scáileáin dúigh leictreonacha. Mar murab ionann agus cineálacha scrollála "
"eile, ní athnuachanann an modh seo do leathanach go leanúnach agus tú ag "
"scrolláil. Oibríonn sé cosúil le <span class=\"ui\">scrolláil clasaiceach</"
"span> ach ní thaispeántar céimeanna idirmheánacha. Mar sin nuair a "
"scrollaíonn tú le do mhéar agus ansin scaoileann tú é, léimeann an "
"leathanach go dtí an suíomh sin. Tá sé seo thar a bheith úsáideach <b>chun "
"an radharc a athshuíomh agus a choigeartú</b> má tá pictiúir nó táblaí i do "
"leabhar agus más mian leat iad go léir a fheiceáil."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1885-1
msgid "Go back to previous location"
msgstr "Téigh ar ais go dtí an suíomh roimhe seo"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1887-5
msgid ""
"This useful feature works like the <b>Back</b> button in your browser. When "
"you jump to some other part of the book using <span class=\"ui\">Skim "
"widget, Bookmarks list, Book map</span> etc. KOReader remembers your "
"previous location. This is useful for example if you follow an internal link "
"or reference. With one tap you can go back to where you come from. You can "
"access this feature from:"
msgstr ""
"Oibríonn an ghné úsáideach seo cosúil leis an gcnaipe <b>Ar Ais</b> i do "
"bhrabhsálaí. Nuair a léimeann tú go dtí cuid eile den leabhar ag baint "
"úsáide as <span class=\"ui\">gadget skim, liosta leabharmharcanna, léarscáil "
"leabhar</span> etc., cuimhníonn KOReader ar do shuíomh roimhe seo. Tá sé seo "
"úsáideach mar shampla má leanann tú nasc nó tagairt inmheánach. Le sconna "
"amháin is féidir leat filleadh ar an áit as ar tháinig tú. Is féidir leat "
"rochtain a fháil ar an ngné seo ó:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1889-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Go back to previous location"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Téigh ar ais go dtí an suíomh roimhe seo"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1891-5
msgid ""
"Also you can go forward too, from the same menu. This feature is assigned to "
"<span style=\"font-family: microns;\"></span> multiswipe gesture. You can "
"assign this to another gesture if you want (like tapping a corner) or add it "
"to your <span class=\"ui\">Quick Menu</span>."
msgstr ""
"Chomh maith leis sin, is féidir leat dul ar aghaidh, ón roghchlár céanna. Tá "
"an ghné seo sannta do ghluaiseacht il-shlaipe <span style=\"font-family: "
"microns;\"></span>. Is féidir leat é seo a shannadh do ghluaiseacht eile "
"más mian leat (cosúil le cúinne a thapáil) nó é a chur le do <span "
"class=\"ui\">Roghchlár Tapa</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1895-1
msgid "Prevent flashing on pages with images and in the menu"
msgstr "Cosc a chur ar splancadh ar leathanaigh le híomhánna agus sa roghchlár"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1897-5
msgid ""
"KOReader normally perform a full refresh on pages containing images (which "
"you can observe as a black flash). The reason is to get rid of the residue "
"and ghosting from the previous page. But this might not be necessary "
"depending on your device and personal preferences. You can disable this auto-"
"refresh behavior here:"
msgstr ""
"De ghnáth déanann KOReader athnuachan iomlán ar leathanaigh ina bhfuil "
"íomhánna (rud a fheiceann tú mar splanc dubh). Is é an chúis atá leis ná "
"fáil réidh leis an iarmhar agus leis an taibhse ón leathanach roimhe sin. "
"Ach b'fhéidir nach mbeidh gá leis seo ag brath ar do ghléas agus ar do chuid "
"roghanna pearsanta. Is féidir leat an t-iompar athnuachana uathoibríoch seo "
"a dhíchumasú anseo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1899-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:24px;\"> / Screen / E-ink Settings / Full refresh rate / "
"Always flash on pages with images"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:24px;\"> / Scáileán / Socruithe Ríomh-Dhúigh / Ráta "
"athnuachana iomlán / Splanc i gcónaí ar leathanaigh le híomhánna"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1901-5
msgid ""
"Also you can disable black flashing of user interface from here if it "
"disturbs you:"
msgstr ""
"Chomh maith leis sin, is féidir leat splancadh dubh an chomhéadain úsáideora "
"a dhíchumasú anseo má chuireann sé isteach ort:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p.div:1903-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Screen / E-ink Settings"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Scáileán / Socruithe Ríomhdhúigh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1912-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L1-moving"
msgid "MOVING THROUGH YOUR BOOK"
msgstr "AG BOGADH TRÍ DO LEABHAR"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1914-5
msgid ""
"There are different ways of moving through your document in KOReader with "
"their own strengths. You can use the:"
msgstr ""
"Tá bealaí éagsúla ann chun bogadh trí do dhoiciméad i KOReader agus a "
"láidreachtaí féin acu. Is féidir leat úsáid a bhaint as:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1917-3
msgid "Skim Widget"
msgstr "Giuirléid Scimála"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1918-3
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ul.li:1918-3"
msgid "Book Map"
msgstr "Léarscáil Leabhar"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1919-3
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ul.li:1919-3"
msgid "Page Browser"
msgstr "Brabhsálaí Leathanaigh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1922-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-skimwidget"
msgid "Skim Widget"
msgstr "Giuirléid Scimála"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1924-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Skim Widget</span> is a very functional navigation tool. "
"You can use it to:"
msgstr ""
"Is uirlis nascleanúna an-fheidhmiúil í an <span class=\"ui\">Giuirléid "
"Scimála</span>. Is féidir leat í a úsáid chun:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1926-13
msgid ""
"Jump to any part of your book by directly tapping on the <span "
"class=\"ui\">progress bar</span> or entering the page number"
msgstr ""
"Léim go dtí aon chuid de do leabhar trí thapáil go díreach ar an <span "
"class=\"ui\">barra dul chun cinn</span> nó uimhir an leathanaigh a iontráil"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1927-13
msgid "Navigate between chapters"
msgstr "Nascleanúint idir caibidlí"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1928-13
msgid "Navigate between bookmarks"
msgstr "Nascleanúint idir leabharmharcanna"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1932-5
msgid "How to open the Skim Widget:"
msgstr "Conas an Giuirléid Skim a oscailt:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1934-17
msgid ""
"With a long-tap on the <span class=\"ui\">Status Bar</span> area at the "
"bottom of your screen"
msgstr ""
"Le tapáil fhada ar an limistéar <span class=\"ui\">Barra Stádais</span> ag "
"bun do scáileáin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1935-17
msgid "From this menu:"
msgstr "Ón roghchlár seo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li.div:1935-37
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Skim document"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Scimáil an cháipéis"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1936-17
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ul.li:1936-17"
msgid "You can assign a gesture to it"
msgstr "Is féidir leat gotha a shannadh dó"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1937-17
msgid "You can add it to your <span class=\"ui\">Quick Menu</span>"
msgstr "Is féidir leat é a chur le do <span class=\"ui\">Roghchlár Tapa</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1942-1
msgid "Using the Skim Widget"
msgstr "Ag Úsáid an Ghiuirléid Skim"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1944-5
msgid ""
"First let's have a quick look at the diagram below. You will see that we "
"have two different <span class=\"ui\">Skim Widget</span>s. They have the "
"same functions, only their size is different:"
msgstr ""
"Ar dtús, féachfaimid go gasta ar an léaráid thíos. Feicfidh tú go bhfuil dhá "
"<span class=\"ui\">Ghiuirléid Scimála</span> éagsúla againn. Tá na "
"feidhmeanna céanna acu, ach níl mórán difríochta eatarthu:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1947-9
msgid ""
"<b>FULL-SIZE SKIM WIDGET:</b> This is the default <span class=\"ui\">skim "
"widget</span> you will see when you install KOReader. It is bigger than the "
"<span class=\"ui\">compact skim widget</span> so buttons are more "
"comfortable to press. This widget opens at the <b>center of the screen</b>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Giuirléid LÁN-MHÉIDE:</b> Seo an <span class=\"ui\">giuirléid léargaithe</"
"span> réamhshocraithe a fheicfidh tú nuair a shuiteálann tú KOReader. Tá sé "
"níos mó ná an <span class=\"ui\">giuirléid léargaithe dlúth</span> agus mar "
"sin tá sé níos compordaí na cnaipí a bhrú. Osclaítear an giuirléid seo i "
"<b>lár an scáileáin</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1949-9
msgid ""
"<b>COMPACT SKIM WIDGET:</b> This is the slimmer version of the default <span "
"class=\"ui\">skim widget</span>. It can be more useful if you are making "
"highlights for example. Since this widget is smaller and opens at the <b>top "
"or bottom of the screen</b>, it doesn't obstruct the page as much as the "
"default widget."
msgstr ""
"<b>Giuirléid Léirithe Dlúth:</b> Seo an leagan níos caol den <span "
"class=\"ui\">ghiuirléid léirithe</span> réamhshocraithe. Is féidir go mbeadh "
"sé níos úsáidí má tá tú ag déanamh aibhsithe mar shampla. Ós rud é go bhfuil "
"an giuirléid seo níos lú agus go n-osclaítear é ag <b>barr nó bun an "
"scáileáin</b>, ní chuireann sé bac ar an leathanach chomh mór leis an "
"ngiuirléid réamhshocraithe."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1956-9
msgid ""
"If you want to use the <span class=\"ui\">compact skim widget</span>, you "
"can do this by choosing <span class=\"ui\">Top</span> or <span "
"class=\"ui\">Bottom</span> from this menu:"
msgstr ""
"Más mian leat an <span class=\"ui\">giuirléid scimeála dlúth</span> a úsáid, "
"is féidir leat é seo a dhéanamh trí <span class=\"ui\">Barr</span> nó <span "
"class=\"ui\">Bun</span> a roghnú ón roghchlár seo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1958-9
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Navigation / Skim dialog position:"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Nascleanúint / Scimáil suíomh an dialóige:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.p:1960-24
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">TIP</span> Both skim widgets are movable. You "
"can move them by pressing on an empty area of the widget and dragging. Also "
"you can make these dialogs semi-transparent by long-pressing on an empty "
"area on the widget. But semi-transparency is triggered only in its initial "
"position. Once moved, long-pressing moves it back to the initial position."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">LEID</span> Tá an dá ghiuirléid scime "
"soghluaiste. Is féidir leat iad a bhogadh trí bhrú ar limistéar folamh den "
"ghiuirléid agus iad a tharraingt. Chomh maith leis sin, is féidir leat na "
"dialóga seo a dhéanamh leath-thrédhearcach trí bhrú fada ar limistéar folamh "
"ar an ngiuirléid. Ach ní spreagtar leath-thrédhearcacht ach amháin ina "
"seasamh tosaigh. Nuair a bhogtar é, bogann brú fada ar ais é go dtí an "
"seasamh tosaigh."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1962-5
msgid ""
"Now back to the diagram. You can see that on some buttons, there are two "
"descriptions in different colors:<b> blue and orange</b>. It means that this "
"button has two functions: a <b>normal press</b> action and a <b>long-press</"
"b> action. If you press normally, it will perform the <span "
"class=\"label_blue\">BLUE</span> function. If you press longer, it will "
"perform the <span class=\"label_orange\">ORANGE</span> function."
msgstr ""
"Ar ais anois go dtí an léaráid. Is féidir leat a fheiceáil go bhfuil dhá "
"chur síos i ndathanna difriúla ar roinnt cnaipí: <b>gorm agus oráiste</b>. "
"Ciallaíonn sé sin go bhfuil dhá fheidhm ag an gcnaipe seo: gníomh<b>brú "
"gnáth</b> agus gníomh<b>brú fada</b>. Má bhrúnn tú go gnáth, feidhmeoidh sé "
"an fheidhm<span class=\"label_blue\">GORM</span>. Má bhrúnn tú níos faide, "
"feidhmeoidh sé an fheidhm<span class=\"label_orange\">ORÁISTE</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1966-5
msgid "Explanations of the numbered items (long-press action in bold):"
msgstr "Mínithe ar na míreanna uimhrithe (gníomh brúigh fhada i gcló trom):"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1969-9
msgid ""
"Jump to the beginning of the previous chapter / <b>Jump to the first page of "
"the book</b>"
msgstr ""
"Léim go dtí tús na caibidle roimhe seo / <b>Léim go dtí an chéad leathanach "
"den leabhar</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1970-9
msgid ""
"Jump to the previous bookmark / <b>Jump to the first bookmark in the book</b>"
msgstr ""
"Léim go dtí an leabharmharc roimhe seo / <b>Léim go dtí an chéad "
"leabharmharc sa leabhar</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1971-9
msgid "Bookmark current page / <b>Open bookmarks dialog</b>"
msgstr ""
"Leabharmharcáil an leathanaigh reatha / <b>Oscail an dialóg "
"leabharmharcanna</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1972-9
msgid ""
"Jump to the next bookmark / <b>Jump to the last bookmark in the book</b>"
msgstr ""
"Léim go dtí an chéad leabharmharc eile / <b>Léim go dtí an leabharmharc "
"deireanach sa leabhar</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1973-9
msgid ""
"Jump to the beginning of the next chapter / <b>Jump to the last page of the "
"book</b>"
msgstr ""
"Léim go dtí tús an chéad chaibidil eile / <b>Léim go dtí an leathanach "
"deireanach den leabhar</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1974-9
msgid "Jump backward (-) or forward (+) this many pages"
msgstr "Léim siar (-) nó ar aghaidh (+) an líon leathanach seo"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1975-9
msgid ""
"This number shows the current page number. If you tap on it, a dialog opens "
"which allows you to enter a page number or percentage to jump directly. "
"<b>If you long-press, it takes you back to the page where you opened the "
"<span class=\"ui\">skim widget</span>.</b> This is useful for example if you "
"want to check some other part of the book quickly and return to your reading "
"where you left."
msgstr ""
"Taispeánann an uimhir seo uimhir an leathanaigh reatha. Má thapaíonn tú air, "
"osclaítear dialóg a ligeann duit uimhir leathanaigh nó céatadán a iontráil "
"chun léim go díreach. <b>Má bhrúnn tú ar feadh tamaill, tabharfaidh sé ar "
"ais chuig an leathanach thú inar oscail tú an <span class=\"ui\">giuirléid "
"scimeála</span>.</b> Tá sé seo úsáideach mar shampla más mian leat cuid eile "
"den leabhar a sheiceáil go tapa agus filleadh ar do léitheoireacht san áit "
"ar fhág tú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1976-9
msgid ""
"This is the <span class=\"ui\">progress bar</span>. Thin lines are the "
"chapter marks which shows the beginning of the chapters. You can tap on this "
"<span class=\"ui\">progress bar</span> to jump to that part of the book. "
"Little arrows are <span class=\"ui\">session start arrows</span> which marks "
"the place where you started reading this book in the current session. This "
"arrows reset when you switch between books."
msgstr ""
"Seo é an <span class=\"ui\">barra dul chun cinn</span>. Is iad na línte "
"tanaí na marcanna caibidle a thaispeánann tús na gcaibidlí. Is féidir leat "
"tapáil ar an <span class=\"ui\">barra dul chun cinn</span> seo chun léim go "
"dtí an chuid sin den leabhar. Is iad na saigheada beaga <span "
"class=\"ui\">saigheada tosaigh seisiúin</span> a mharcálann an áit ar "
"thosaigh tú ag léamh an leabhair seo sa seisiún reatha. Athshocraítear na "
"saigheada seo nuair a athraíonn tú idir leabhair."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:1977-9
msgid ""
"This button in the <span class=\"ui\">compact skim widget</span> works same "
"as the long-press function of the item <b>number 7</b>. It takes you back to "
"the page where you opened the <span class=\"ui\">skim widget</span>. This is "
"useful for example if you want to check some other part of the book quickly "
"and return to your reading where you left."
msgstr ""
"Oibríonn an cnaipe seo sa <span class=\"ui\">ghiuirléid scimeála dlúth</"
"span> ar an gcaoi chéanna le feidhm bhrú fada mhír <b>uimhir 7</b>. Tugann "
"sé ar ais chuig an leathanach thú inar oscail tú an <span "
"class=\"ui\">ghiuirléid scimeála</span>. Tá sé seo úsáideach mar shampla más "
"mian leat cuid eile den leabhar a sheiceáil go tapa agus filleadh ar do "
"léitheoireacht san áit ar fhág tú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.p:1980-20
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">TIP</span> If you want to open a random page of "
"a book, we have a <b>Jump to a random page</b> action which you can assign "
"to any gesture. It is in the <b>Reader</b> category of the <span "
"class=\"ui\">Gesture Manager</span>."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">LEID</span> Más mian leat leathanach randamach "
"de leabhar a oscailt, tá gníomh <b>Léim go leathanach randamach</b> againn "
"ar féidir leat a shannadh d'aon ghluaiseacht. Tá sé i gcatagóir "
"<b>Léitheoir</b> an <span class=\"ui\">Bainisteoir Gluaiseachta</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1984-1
msgid "Chapter Marks"
msgstr "Marcanna Caibidle"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1986-5
msgid ""
"KOReader can show chapter boundaries from your documents on the <span "
"class=\"ui\">SKIM WIDGET</span> and <span class=\"ui\">PROGRESS BAR</span>."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le KOReader teorainneacha caibidle ó do dhoiciméid a thaispeáint "
"ar an <span class=\"ui\">GIARR SCIM</span> agus ar an <span "
"class=\"ui\">BARRA DUL CHUN CINN</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1990-5
msgid ""
"If your document has too many heading levels, your chapter marks can look "
"crowded like the example above. You can change the depth of visible ToC mark "
"levels via:"
msgstr ""
"Má tá an iomarca leibhéil ceannteidil i do dhoiciméad, is féidir go mbeidh "
"cuma phlódaithe ar do mharcanna caibidle cosúil leis an sampla thuas. Is "
"féidir leat doimhneacht leibhéil na marc ToC infheicthe a athrú trí:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:1992-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Settings / Progress Bars"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Socruithe / Barraí Dul Chun Cinn"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:1996-5
msgid "You can also use this reduced ToC for:"
msgstr "Is féidir leat an ToC laghdaithe seo a úsáid freisin le haghaidh:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1998-9
msgid "chapter titles (if it is shown on <span class=\"ui\">Status Bar</span>)"
msgstr ""
"teidil chaibidle (más léirítear é ar <span class=\"ui\">Barra Stádais</span>)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1999-9
msgid "chapter navigation"
msgstr "nascleanúint caibidle"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2000-9
msgid "reading time left estimates"
msgstr "meastacháin ama léitheoireachta atá fágtha"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2002-5
msgid "These options are in the same menu."
msgstr "Tá na roghanna seo sa roghchlár céanna."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2003-5
msgid ""
"If your document doesn’t have a Table of Contents, you can enable <span "
"class=\"ui\">ALTERNATIVE TABLE OF CONTENTS</span>. When this setting is "
"enabled, KOReader will build a ToC from document headings (if available) or "
"from individual HTML files in the EPUB. Long press on this menu item for "
"extra info:"
msgstr ""
"Mura bhfuil Clár Ábhair i do dhoiciméad, is féidir leat <span "
"class=\"ui\">CLÁR ÁBHAIR MALARTACH</span> a chumasú. Nuair a bhíonn an socrú "
"seo cumasaithe, tógfaidh KOReader Clár Ábhair ó cheannteidil doiciméad (más "
"ann dóibh) nó ó chomhaid HTML aonair san EPUB. Brúigh fada ar an mír "
"roghchláir seo le haghaidh tuilleadh eolais:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2006-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.div:2006-5"
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Settings / Alternative table of contents"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Socruithe / Clár ábhair malartach"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2008-5
msgid ""
"You can find more info about the <b>table of contents</b> tools available in "
"KOReader in this relevant section of the guide: <a href=\"#toctools\">TABLE "
"OF CONTENTS TOOLS</a>"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat tuilleadh eolais a fháil faoi na huirlisí <b>clár ábhair</b> "
"atá ar fáil i KOReader sa chuid ábhartha seo den treoir: <a "
"href=\"#toctools\">CLÁR ÁBHAIR UIRLISÍ</a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2012-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-bookmap"
msgid "Book Map"
msgstr "Léarscáil Leabhar"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2014-5
msgid ""
"Book map is a powerful and unique feature of KOReader which can be very "
"useful for getting an overview of a book. For example if you are reading a "
"book non-linearly by skipping some parts to read them later, it would be "
"hard to track your progress. Book Map can show you which parts of the book "
"you have already read, at a glance."
msgstr ""
"Is gné chumhachtach agus uathúil de chuid KOReader í an léarscáil leabhar a "
"d’fhéadfadh a bheith an-úsáideach chun forbhreathnú a fháil ar leabhar. Mar "
"shampla, má tá tú ag léamh leabhair go neamhlíneach trí roinnt codanna a "
"scipeáil le léamh níos déanaí, bheadh sé deacair do dhul chun cinn a rianú. "
"Is féidir le Léarscáil Leabhar a thaispeáint duit cé na codanna den leabhar "
"atá léite agat cheana féin, ar an toirt."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2016-5
msgid "Additionally you can:"
msgstr "Ina theannta sin is féidir leat:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2018-9
msgid ""
"See how much time you have spent on each page (if <span class=\"ui\">Reading "
"Statistics</span> plugin is enabled)"
msgstr ""
"Féach cé mhéad ama atá caite agat ar gach leathanach (má tá an breiseán "
"<span class=\"ui\">Staitisticí Léitheoireachta</span> cumasaithe)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2019-9
msgid "Check which pages have bookmark, highlights and notes"
msgstr ""
"Seiceáil cé na leathanaigh a bhfuil leabharmharcanna, buaicphointí agus "
"nótaí orthu"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2020-9
msgid ""
"Navigate directly to any part of the book like the <span class=\"ui\">SKIM "
"WIDGET</span>"
msgstr ""
"Nascleanúint dhíreach chuig aon chuid den leabhar cosúil leis an <span "
"class=\"ui\">Giuirléid Léim</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2023-5
msgid ""
"You can access Book Map via menu and you can also assign a gesture for "
"quicker access:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat rochtain a fháil ar Léarscáil Leabhar tríd an roghchlár agus "
"is féidir leat gotha a shannadh freisin le haghaidh rochtain níos tapúla:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2025-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Book map"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Léarscáil leabhar"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2029-1
msgid "Book map controls"
msgstr "Rialuithe léarscáile leabhar"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2030-5
msgid ""
"When you open the <span class=\"ui\">Book Map</span> first time while "
"reading a book, it will be in <span class=\"ui\">Grid View</span> mode, "
"fitting all chapters on a single screen to give the best initial overview of "
"the book’s content. To get a detailed information about usage, tap the info "
"icon at the upper left corner. You can close the Book Map by tapping <span "
"class=\"ui\">X</span> on the upper right corner or with any multiswipe "
"gesture (<b>UP-DOWN, LEFT-RIGHT</b> etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a osclaíonn tú an <span class=\"ui\">Léarscáil Leabhar</span> den "
"chéad uair agus leabhar á léamh agat, beidh sé i mód <span "
"class=\"ui\">Radharc Eangaí</span>, ag cur na gcaibidlí go léir ar scáileán "
"amháin chun an forbhreathnú tosaigh is fearr a thabhairt ar ábhar an "
"leabhair. Chun faisnéis mhionsonraithe a fháil faoi úsáid, tapáil an "
"deilbhín eolais sa chúinne uachtarach ar chlé. Is féidir leat an Léarscáil "
"Leabhar a dhúnadh trí thapáil <span class=\"ui\">X</span> sa chúinne "
"uachtarach ar dheis nó le haon ghluaiseacht il-shlaipe (<b>SUAS-SÍOS, CLÉ-"
"DEAS</b> etc.)."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2036-13
msgid "Chapter boundaries"
msgstr "Teorainneacha caibidle"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2037-13
msgid ""
"Black bars indicate read pages. Higher bars means more time spent in page."
msgstr ""
"Léiríonn barraí dubha leathanaigh léite. Ciallaíonn barraí níos airde níos "
"mó ama a chaitear ar an leathanach."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2038-13
msgid "Bookmark icon shows bookmarked pages as the name says."
msgstr ""
"Taispeánann deilbhín leabharmharcanna leathanaigh atá marcáilte mar a deir "
"an t-ainm."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2039-13
msgid "Striped square icon shows pages with highlights."
msgstr ""
"Taispeánann deilbhín cearnach stríocach leathanaigh a bhfuil aird orthu."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2040-13
msgid "Pencil icon shows pages with notes."
msgstr "Taispeánann deilbhín peann luaidhe leathanaigh le nótaí."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2041-13
msgid ""
"Numbers in a circle shows your previous locations. When you choose <span "
"class=\"ui\">Go back to previous location</span> from the menu, you will "
"jump back here in order."
msgstr ""
"Léiríonn uimhreacha i gciorcal do shuíomhanna roimhe seo. Nuair a roghnaíonn "
"tú <span class=\"ui\">Téigh ar ais go dtí an suíomh roimhe seo</span> ón "
"roghchlár, léimfidh tú ar ais anseo in ord."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2042-13
msgid "Triangle shows your current page."
msgstr "Taispeánann triantán do leathanach reatha."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2043-13
msgid "Vertical scrollbar shows your current view level."
msgstr ""
"Taispeánann an barra scrollaithe ingearach do leibhéal radhairc reatha."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2044-13
msgid "Vertical scrollbar shows your current page width level."
msgstr ""
"Taispeánann an barra scrollaithe ingearach leibhéal leithead do leathanaigh "
"reatha."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2048-5
msgid ""
"You can customize <span class=\"ui\">Book Map</span> by changing these "
"options:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat <span class=\"ui\">Léarscáil Leabhar</span> a shaincheapadh "
"trí na roghanna seo a athrú:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2049-5
msgid ""
"- First try swiping <span class=\"ui\">LEFT</span> and <span "
"class=\"ui\">RIGHT</span> along the bottom edge of the screen to change "
"width of columns indicating pages and observe how it changes the scale of "
"the map."
msgstr ""
"- Ar dtús bain triail as svaidhpeáil <span class=\"ui\">AR CHLÉ</span> agus "
"<span class=\"ui\">AR DHEAS</span> feadh imeall bun an scáileáin chun "
"leithead na gcolún a léiríonn leathanaigh a athrú agus féach conas a "
"athraíonn sé scála an léarscáil."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2051-5
msgid ""
"- Then try swiping <span class=\"ui\">UP</span> and <span class=\"ui\">DOWN</"
"span> along the left edge of the screen to change chapter title depth and "
"switch to the <span class=\"ui\">Flat View</span>. See examples below."
msgstr ""
"- Ansin déan iarracht svaidhpeáil <span class=\"ui\">SUAS</span> agus <span "
"class=\"ui\">SÍOS</span> feadh imeall clé an scáileáin chun doimhneacht "
"teidil na caibidle a athrú agus aistriú go dtí an <span class=\"ui\">Radharc "
"Cothrom</span>. Féach na samplaí thíos."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2053-5
msgid ""
"In addition to default <span class=\"ui\">Grid View</span> above, here you "
"can see the <span class=\"ui\">Flat View</span> on the left and Grid View "
"without chapter titles on the right. Note the changing left vertical "
"scrollbar between views. If you want to switch back to the default view, you "
"can long-press the info icon at the upper left corner."
msgstr ""
"Chomh maith leis an <span class=\"ui\">Radharc Eangaí</span> réamhshocraithe "
"thuas, anseo is féidir leat an <span class=\"ui\">Radharc Cothrom</span> a "
"fheiceáil ar chlé agus an Radharc Eangaí gan teidil chaibidle ar dheis. "
"Tabhair faoi deara an barra scrollaithe ingearach ar chlé atá ag athrú idir "
"radhairc. Más mian leat filleadh ar an radharc réamhshocraithe, is féidir "
"leat brúigh fhada a chur ar an deilbhín eolais sa chúinne uachtarach ar chlé."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2062-1
msgid "Book map options"
msgstr "Roghanna léarscáile leabhar"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2066-5
msgid ""
"When you tap the menu icon on the <b>Book map</b> screen you are presented "
"with the menu above. Menu options are explained below:"
msgstr ""
"Nuair a thapálann tú ar dheilbhín an roghchláir ar an scáileán <b>Léarscáil "
"Leabhar</b>, cuirtear an roghchlár thuas i láthair duit. Mínítear roghanna "
"an roghchláir thíos:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2069-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">About book map:</span> Short explanation of Book map "
"usage and icon descriptions."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Maidir le léarscáil leabhar:</span> Míniú gairid ar úsáid "
"Léarscáil Leabhar agus cur síos ar dheilbhíní."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2070-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Available gestures:</span> Gestures you can use to change "
"the settings of Book map instead of using this menu."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Gluaiseachtaí atá ar fáil:</span> Gluaiseachtaí is féidir "
"leat a úsáid chun socruithe léarscáil an Leabhar a athrú in ionad an "
"roghchlár seo a úsáid."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2071-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Page browser on tap:</span> If this is checked, when you "
"tap on a page in Book map, <span class=\"ui\">Page browser</span> opens. "
"This shows you an overview of the area you selected. If you disable this "
"option, a tap in Book map directly takes you to that page. But remember, "
"depending on factors like your screen size, touch screen sensitivity, tap "
"accuracy etc. you might end up in adjacent pages."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí leathanaigh ar sconna:</span> Má tá tic sa "
"rogha seo, nuair a sconnaíonn tú ar leathanach i léarscáil an Leabhar, "
"osclaítear <span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí leathanaigh</span>. Taispeánann sé "
"seo forbhreathnú duit ar an limistéar a roghnaigh tú. Má dhíchumasaíonn tú "
"an rogha seo, tabharfaidh sconna i léarscáil an Leabhar go díreach chuig an "
"leathanach sin thú. Ach cuimhnigh, ag brath ar fhachtóirí cosúil le méid do "
"scáileáin, íogaireacht an scáileáin tadhaill, cruinneas an sconna srl., "
"d'fhéadfá críochnú i leathanaigh in aice láimhe."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2072-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Switch current/initial views:</span> If you customized "
"your Book map view, tapping this switches between the <b>default view</b> "
"and your <b>customized view</b>."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Athraigh radharcanna reatha/tosaigh:</span> Má shaincheap "
"tú radharc léarscáile do Leabhair, athraíonn tapáil air seo idir an "
"<b>radharc réamhshocraithe</b> agus do <b>radharc saincheaptha</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2073-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Switch grid/flat views:</span> Switch between separate "
"chapters or continuous chapters views."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Athraigh radhairc ghreille/chomhréidhe:</span> Athraigh "
"idir caibidlí ar leithligh nó radhairc chaibidlí leanúnacha."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2074-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Chapter levels:</span> Change the depth of chapter/sub "
"chapter levels."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Leibhéil chaibidle:</span> Athraigh doimhneacht leibhéil "
"chaibidle/fho-chaibidle."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2075-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Page slot width:</span> Make each page slot wider or "
"narrower."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Leithead sliotán leathanaigh:</span> Déan gach sliotán "
"leathanaigh níos leithne nó níos cúinge."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2076-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">10-page markers:</span> As you increase this value, first "
"it will add markers to every <b>10<sup>th</sup> page</b>, then it will make "
"them bigger and eventually it will add markers to every <b>5<sup>th</sup> "
"page</b>."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Marcóirí 10 leathanach:</span> De réir mar a mhéadaíonn "
"tú an luach seo, cuirfear marcóirí le gach <b>10<sup>ú</sup> leathanach</b> "
"ar dtús, ansin méadófar iad agus sa deireadh cuirfear marcóirí le gach "
"<b>5<sup>ú</sup> leathanach</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2080-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-pagebrowser"
msgid "Page Browser"
msgstr "Brabhsálaí Leathanaigh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2081-5
msgid ""
"Page Browser can be used to navigate between pages like in a photo album by "
"showing thumbnails of the pages as a grid. You can open <span "
"class=\"ui\">Page Browser</span> by tapping on the <span class=\"ui\">Book "
"Map</span> or from the menu. You can also assign a gesture for easier access."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir Brabhsálaí Leathanaigh a úsáid chun nascleanúint a dhéanamh idir "
"leathanaigh cosúil le halbam grianghraf trí mhioníomhánna de na leathanaigh "
"a thaispeáint mar eangach. Is féidir leat <span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí "
"Leathanaigh</span> a oscailt trí thapáil ar an <span class=\"ui\">Léarscáil "
"Leabhar</span> nó ón roghchlár. Is féidir leat gotha a shannadh freisin le "
"haghaidh rochtain níos éasca."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2084-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.div:2084-5"
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Page browser"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Brabhsálaí leathanaigh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2088-9
msgid ""
"Usage of <span class=\"ui\">Page Browser</span> is explained below. You can "
"also tap on the <span class=\"ui\"> top left corner hamburger menu button</"
"span> on this screen to see these explanations. A long-press on the same "
"button adds/removes chapter titles from the bottom strip."
msgstr ""
"Mínítear úsáid <span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Leathanaigh</span> thíos. Is "
"féidir leat tapáil freisin ar an gcnaipe roghchláir <span "
"class=\"ui\">cúinne uachtarach na láimhe clé</span> ar an scáileán seo chun "
"na mínithe seo a fheiceáil. Má bhrúnn tú ar an gcnaipe céanna ar feadh "
"tamaill, cuirtear teidil chaibidle leis/baintear iad ón stiall bun."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2091-9
msgid ""
"Swipe <b>left / right</b> over this top edge to increase / decrease the "
"number of the <b>columns</b>."
msgstr ""
"Svaidhpeáil <b>ar chlé / ar dheis</b> thar an imeall uachtarach seo chun "
"líon na <b>gcolún</b> a mhéadú / a laghdú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2092-9
msgid ""
"Swipe <b>up / down</b> over this left edge to increase / decrease the number "
"of the <b>rows</b>."
msgstr ""
"Svaidhpeáil <b>suas / síos</b> thar an imeall clé seo chun líon na "
"<b>sraitheanna</b> a mhéadú / a laghdú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2093-9
msgid ""
"Swipe the pages area to move the viewed pages. <b>Up / down</b> to scroll "
"one row (2 pages in the example), <b>left / right</b> to scroll one screen "
"(4 pages in the example)."
msgstr ""
"Svaidhpeáil limistéar na leathanach chun na leathanaigh atá feicthe a "
"bhogadh. <b>Suas / síos</b> chun ró amháin a scrollú (2 leathanach san "
"sampla), <b>ar chlé / ar dheis</b> chun scáileán amháin a scrollú (4 "
"leathanach san sampla)."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2094-9
msgid "Tap any page to open that page in reading view."
msgstr ""
"Tapáil aon leathanach chun an leathanach sin a oscailt i radharc "
"léitheoireachta."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2095-9
msgid ""
"On the bottom area, tapping on a page focuses the thumbnail view on that "
"page. Swiping <b>left / right</b> will jump one stripe width."
msgstr ""
"Ag an mbun, má thapaíonn tú ar leathanach, dírítear ar an radharc "
"mionsamhail ar an leathanach sin. Léimfidh tú leithead stríoca amháin trí "
"shlaodadh <b>ar chlé / ar dheis</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2096-9
msgid ""
"Icons on the bottom area are same as the ones used in <span "
"class=\"ui\">Book Map</span> and explained under that section."
msgstr ""
"Tá na deilbhíní ar an mbuncheantar mar an gcéanna leis na cinn a úsáidtear i "
"<span class=\"ui\">Léarscáil Leabhar</span> agus a mhínítear faoin alt sin."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2100-1
msgid "Alternative theme for Book map and Page Browser"
msgstr "Téama malartach do Léarscáil Leabhar agus Brabhsálaí Leathanaigh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2102-5
msgid ""
"Book map and page browser has an <b>Alternative theme</b> with a different "
"shading scheme which you can activate from their hamburger menus. This theme "
"uses alternating colors for the chapter headings so chapter boundaries is "
"more visible in the <span class=\"ui\">Book map</span> and <span "
"class=\"ui\">Page browser</span>. But the usage of gray color in this theme "
"requires flashing to black so it might be distracting for some users. You "
"can try both and use the one you like."
msgstr ""
"Tá <b>téama malartach</b> ag an léarscáil leabhar agus an brabhsálaí "
"leathanaigh le scéim scáthaithe dhifriúil ar féidir leat a ghníomhachtú óna "
"roghchláir hamburger. Úsáideann an téama seo dathanna malartacha do "
"cheannteidil na gcaibidlí ionas go mbeidh teorainneacha na gcaibidlí níos "
"infheicthe sa <span class=\"ui\">léarscáil leabhar</span> agus sa <span "
"class=\"ui\">bhrabhsálaí leathanaigh</span>. Ach éilíonn úsáid an datha "
"liath sa téama seo splancadh go dubh agus mar sin d'fhéadfadh sé a bheith "
"ina ábhar mearbhaill do roinnt úsáideoirí. Is féidir leat an dá cheann a "
"thriail agus an ceann is fearr leat a úsáid."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2106-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-toctools"
msgid "Table of Contents Tools"
msgstr "Clár Ábhair Uirlisí"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2107-5
msgid ""
"Some of the digital books you come across might not have a proper table of "
"contents (<b>ToC</b>). Depending on the preparation of the book, you can "
"experience these ToC problems:"
msgstr ""
"B’fhéidir nach mbeadh clár ábhair (<b>ToC</b>) ceart ag cuid de na leabhair "
"dhigiteacha a dtagann tú trasna orthu. Ag brath ar ullmhúchán an leabhair, "
"d’fhéadfadh na fadhbanna seo a leanas a bheith agat leis na ToCanna:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2110-9
msgid ""
"No ToC in the book, so you can’t jump between the chapters or see the "
"remaining reading times"
msgstr ""
"Gan aon ToC sa leabhar, mar sin ní féidir leat léim idir na caibidlí ná na "
"hamanna léitheoireachta atá fágtha a fheiceáil"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2111-9
msgid ""
"There is a ToC but it is not very useful because it has wrong or missing "
"chapter titles"
msgstr ""
"Tá ToC ann ach níl sé an-úsáideach mar go bhfuil teidil chaibidlí míchearta "
"nó ar iarraidh ann"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2114-5
msgid ""
"KOReader has some features that you can use when reading books with a "
"problematic table of contents section."
msgstr ""
"Tá roinnt gnéithe ag KOReader ar féidir leat a úsáid agus tú ag léamh "
"leabhar a bhfuil clár ábhair fadhbach iontu."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2116-5
msgid ""
"Note that <span class=\"ui\">Alternative table of contents</span> is not "
"available on <b>fixed layout documents</b> like PDF, DJVU etc. because it "
"requires HTML tags to create a ToC. <span class=\"ui\">Custom table of "
"contents</span> and <span class=\"ui\">Custom hidden flows</span> features "
"are available on all file types."
msgstr ""
"Tabhair faoi deara nach bhfuil <span class=\"ui\">clár ábhair malartach</"
"span> ar fáil ar <b>dhoiciméid leagan amach seasta</b> cosúil le PDF, DJVU "
"etc. toisc go dteastaíonn clibeanna HTML chun ToC a chruthú. Tá gnéithe "
"<span class=\"ui\">clár ábhair saincheaptha</span> agus <span "
"class=\"ui\">sreabhadh folaithe saincheaptha</span> ar fáil ar gach cineál "
"comhaid."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2119-1
msgid ""
"Automatically creating a table of contents: ALTERNATIVE TABLE OF CONTENTS"
msgstr "Clár ábhair a chruthú go huathoibríoch: CLÁR ÁBHAIR MALARTACH"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2121-5
msgid ""
"First feature is the <span class=\"ui\">Alternative table of contents</span> "
"which you can find in:"
msgstr ""
"Is é an chéad ghné an <span class=\"ui\">Clár ábhair malartach</span> atá le "
"fáil i:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2124-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.div:2124-5"
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Settings / Alternative table of contents"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Socruithe / Clár ábhair malartach"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2126-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">INFO</span> An EPUB document is basically a ZIP "
"file containing one or more HTML files. Your book might be one big HTML file "
"for the whole book or it might contain separate chapters as individual HTML "
"files (which is a better structure)."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">EOLAS</span> Is comhad ZIP é doiciméad EPUB ina "
"bhfuil comhad HTML amháin nó níos mó. D’fhéadfadh do leabhar a bheith ina "
"chomhad HTML mór amháin don leabhar ar fad nó d’fhéadfadh caibidlí ar "
"leithligh a bheith ann mar chomhaid HTML aonair (rud atá ina struchtúr níos "
"fearr)."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2128-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Alternative table of contents</span> tries to create a "
"ToC from the headings in your book (<b>H1</b> to <b>H6</b> tags in the HTML "
"files in your EPUB). If your book doesn’t contain any headings, it will try "
"to build a ToC from the document fragments (individual HTML files in your "
"EPUB book) which will point to the beginning of each file."
msgstr ""
"Déanann <span class=\"ui\">Clár ábhair malartach</span> iarracht ToC a "
"chruthú ó na ceannteidil i do leabhar (clibeanna <b>H1</b> go <b>H6</b> sna "
"comhaid HTML i do EPUB). Mura bhfuil aon cheannteidil i do leabhar, "
"déanfaidh sé iarracht ToC a thógáil ó na blúirí doiciméad (comhaid HTML "
"aonair i do leabhar EPUB) a dhíreoidh ar thús gach comhaid."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2130-5
msgid ""
"You can choose which heading levels to include (or ignore) in your ToC from "
"this menu:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat a roghnú cé na leibhéil ceannteidil le cur san áireamh (nó "
"neamhaird a dhéanamh orthu) i do ToC ón roghchlár seo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2132-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Style tweaks / Miscellaneous / Alternative ToC hints"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Feabhsuithe stíle / Ilghnéitheach / Leideanna "
"malartacha maidir le Téarmaí Úsáide"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2136-1
msgid "Manually creating a table of contents: CUSTOM TABLE OF CONTENTS"
msgstr "Clár ábhair a chruthú de láimh: CLÁR ÁBHAIR SAINCHEAPTA"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2138-5
msgid ""
"Custom table of contents feature allows you to create your own ToC from the "
"selected parts of your book. This ToC can contain only one level so you "
"can’t have sub-chapters while using this feature. To create your own ToC, "
"first enable:"
msgstr ""
"Leis an ngné clár ábhair saincheaptha, is féidir leat do Thoic féin a "
"chruthú ó na codanna roghnaithe de do leabhar. Ní féidir ach leibhéal amháin "
"a bheith sa Thoic seo agus mar sin ní féidir leat fo-chaibidlí a bheith agat "
"agus an ghné seo in úsáid agat. Chun do Thoic féin a chruthú, cumasaigh ar "
"dtús:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2141-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Settings / Custom table of contents"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Socruithe / Clár ábhair saincheaptha"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2143-5
msgid ""
"Once you enable this feature, new menu items will be added to the user "
"interface which allows you to select your chapters. You can add a chapter to "
"your ToC from two places:"
msgstr ""
"Nuair a bheidh an ghné seo cumasaithe agat, cuirfear míreanna roghchláir nua "
"leis an gcomhéadan úsáideora a ligfidh duit do chaibidlí a roghnú. Is féidir "
"leat caibidil a chur le do ToC ó dhá áit:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2146-9
msgid ""
"<b>From a highlight:</b> While reading a book, select a text like you are "
"highlighting it or long press on a word. In the popup menu you will see the "
"<span class=\"ui\">Start TOC chapter</span> item. When you press on it, you "
"will see a dialog asking you to enter your chapter title. The text you "
"selected will be already entered in the dialog. Edit your title if necessary "
"and press create."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ó airdmharc:</b> Agus leabhar á léamh agat, roghnaigh téacs amhail is dá "
"mba rud é go bhfuil tú á airdmharc nó brúigh ar fhocal ar feadh tamaill. Sa "
"roghchlár aníos feicfidh tú an mhír <span class=\"ui\">Tosaigh caibidil TOC</"
"span>. Nuair a bhrúnn tú air, feicfidh tú dialóg ag iarraidh ort teideal do "
"chaibidle a iontráil. Beidh an téacs a roghnaigh tú curtha isteach sa dialóg "
"cheana féin. Cuir do theideal in eagar más gá agus brúigh cruthaigh."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2147-9
msgid "<b>From the Page browser:</b> Open the Page browser via"
msgstr ""
"<b>Ón mbrabhsálaí leathanaigh:</b> Oscail an brabhsálaí leathanaigh trí"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2151-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.div:2151-5"
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Page browser"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Brabhsálaí leathanaigh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2153-5
msgid ""
"Long press on the page thumbnail that you want to be the beginning of your "
"chapter and select <span class=\"ui\">Start TOC chapter</span> item from the "
"popup menu. You will see a dialog asking you to enter your chapter title."
msgstr ""
"Brúigh go fada ar mhionsamhail an leathanaigh ar mhaith leat a bheith mar "
"thús do chaibidle agus roghnaigh an mhír <span class=\"ui\">Tosaigh TOC "
"caibidle</span> ón roghchlár aníos. Feicfidh tú dialóg ag iarraidh ort "
"teideal do chaibidle a iontráil."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2155-5
msgid ""
"When you are done creating your ToC and don’t want to see these extra "
"buttons, you can disable them by unchecking:"
msgstr ""
"Nuair a bheidh tú críochnaithe le do ToC a chruthú agus mura dteastaíonn "
"uait na cnaipí breise seo a fheiceáil, is féidir leat iad a dhíchumasú tríd "
"an rogha seo a dhíthiceáil:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2157-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Settings / Custom layout features / Edit mode"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Socruithe / Gnéithe leagan amach saincheaptha / Mód "
"eagarthóireachta"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2159-5
msgid ""
"Creating this ToC will not alter your original ToC which comes with your "
"book. You can clear your <b>Custom table of contents</b> from this same menu "
"(in case you want to create a new one). And you can disable this feature "
"completely in the same way you enabled it, if you want to return to the "
"original ToC. Note that if you disable this feature after creating a custom "
"ToC to return to the original one, your custom ToC will not be deleted. You "
"can still switch between the original and your custom ToC."
msgstr ""
"Ní athróidh cruthú an Téarma Ábhair seo do Téarma Ábhair bhunaidh a thagann "
"le do leabhar. Is féidir leat do <b>Chlár Ábhair Saincheaptha</b> a ghlanadh "
"ón roghchlár céanna seo (más mian leat ceann nua a chruthú). Agus is féidir "
"leat an ghné seo a dhíchumasú go hiomlán ar an mbealach céanna ar chuir tú "
"ar chumas é, más mian leat filleadh ar an Téarma Ábhair bhunaidh. Tabhair "
"faoi deara, mura ndíchumasaíonn tú an ghné seo tar éis Téarma Ábhair "
"saincheaptha a chruthú chun filleadh ar an gceann bunaidh, nach scriosfar do "
"Téarma Ábhair saincheaptha. Is féidir leat aistriú idir an bunchlár agus do "
"Téarma Ábhair saincheaptha fós."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2163-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-hiddenflows"
msgid "Excluding sections: Custom hidden flows"
msgstr "Gan rannóga a áireamh: Sreafaí folaithe saincheaptha"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2165-5
msgid ""
"Some books or documents might contain long footnotes or bibliography "
"sections. Like a scientific book which is 250 pages long but last 50 pages "
"are Appendices, Index and References. Normally these pages are included in "
"the progress bar and reading time calculations since they are part of the "
"book. But generally these sections exist as a reference and they are not "
"read completely so you might want to exclude them to make your remaining "
"page count and time estimates more accurate. Or maybe you have an anthology "
"book which contain some stories you have already read. <span "
"class=\"ui\">Custom hidden flows</span> feature of KOReader allows you to "
"exclude these kind of parts of your book."
msgstr ""
"D’fhéadfadh nótaí fada nó rannóga leabharliosta a bheith i roinnt leabhar nó "
"doiciméad. Mar shampla leabhar eolaíochta atá 250 leathanach ar fhad ach ina "
"bhfuil Aguisíní, Innéacs agus Tagairtí sna 50 leathanach deiridh. De ghnáth, "
"cuirtear na leathanaigh seo san áireamh sa bharra dul chun cinn agus sna "
"ríomhanna ama léitheoireachta ós rud é gur cuid den leabhar iad. Ach go "
"ginearálta bíonn na rannóga seo ann mar thagairt agus ní léitear iad go "
"hiomlán, mar sin b’fhéidir gur mhaith leat iad a eisiamh chun do "
"chomhaireamh leathanach atá fágtha agus meastacháin ama a dhéanamh níos "
"cruinne. Nó b’fhéidir go bhfuil leabhar díolaime agat ina bhfuil roinnt "
"scéalta atá léite agat cheana féin. Ligeann gné <span class=\"ui\">Sreabhadh "
"folaithe saincheaptha</span> de KOReader duit na codanna seo de do leabhar a "
"eisiamh."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2167-5
msgid ""
"Have a look at the image for an overview of the process. Steps will be "
"explained after the image:"
msgstr ""
"Féach ar an íomhá le haghaidh forbhreathnú ar an bpróiseas. Míneofar na "
"céimeanna i ndiaidh na híomhá:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2173-5
msgid "How to exclude a section by creating a hidden flow:"
msgstr "Conas alt a eisiamh trí shreabhadh i bhfolach a chruthú:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2176-9
msgid "Go to the first page of the section you want to exclude"
msgstr "Téigh go dtí an chéad leathanach den chuid is mian leat a eisiamh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2177-9
msgid "Open the <span class=\"ui\">Page browser</span> via:"
msgstr "Oscail an <span class=\"ui\">brabhsálaí leathanaigh</span> trí:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li.div:2179-13
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ol.li.div:2179-13"
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Page browser"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Brabhsálaí leathanaigh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2181-9
msgid ""
"Long press on the page thumbnail that you want to be the beginning of your "
"excluded section and select <span class=\"ui\">Start hidden flow here</span> "
"item from the popup menu."
msgstr ""
"Brúigh go fada ar mhionsamhail an leathanaigh ar mhaith leat a bheith mar "
"thús don chuid eisiata agus roghnaigh an mhír <span class=\"ui\">Tosaigh "
"sreabhadh folaithe anseo</span> ón roghchlár aníos."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2182-9
msgid ""
"You will see that the pages starting from your selection now have a gray "
"hatched background."
msgstr ""
"Feicfidh tú go bhfuil cúlra liath-ghréasta anois ar na leathanaigh a "
"thosaigh ó do rogha."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2183-9
msgid ""
"Now go to the last page of your excluded section. You can navigate there "
"from the <span class=\"ui\">Page browser</span> or using other ways like "
"<span class=\"ui\">Book map, Skim widget</span> etc."
msgstr ""
"Anois, téigh go dtí an leathanach deireanach den rannán atá eisiata agat. Is "
"féidir leat nascleanúint a dhéanamh ann ón <span class=\"ui\">bhrabhsálaí "
"leathanaigh</span> nó trí bhealaí eile a úsáid cosúil le <span "
"class=\"ui\">léarscáil leabhar, giuirléid scimeála</span> srl."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2184-9
msgid ""
"Once you are at the last page of your excluded section, open the <span "
"class=\"ui\">Page browser</span> again (if you are not already in it)."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a bheidh tú ar an leathanach deireanach den rannán eisiata, oscail an "
"<span class=\"ui\">brabhsálaí leathanaigh</span> arís (mura bhfuil tú ann "
"cheana féin)."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2185-9
msgid ""
"Find the last page of your hidden section and long press on the <b>next "
"page</b>. Choose <span class=\"ui\">Restart regular flow here</span> from "
"the popup menu. You will see that the background of the remaining pages will "
"return to normal color, indicating the end of hidden flow and the beginning "
"of regular flow."
msgstr ""
"Aimsigh an leathanach deireanach de do chuid i bhfolach agus brúigh ar an "
"<b>gcéad leathanach eile</b>. Roghnaigh <span class=\"ui\">Atosaigh an "
"sreabhadh rialta anseo</span> ón roghchlár aníos. Feicfidh tú go bhfillfidh "
"cúlra na leathanach atá fágtha ar a dhath gnáth, rud a léiríonn deireadh an "
"tsreafa i bhfolach agus tús an tsreafa rialta."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2190-5
msgid "Working with the hidden sections:"
msgstr "Ag obair leis na rannóga i bhfolach:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2192-5
msgid ""
"When you create a hidden flow section as described above, KOReader’s "
"behavior will be similar to the situation as if you removed a section of a "
"paper book by cutting it out:"
msgstr ""
"Nuair a chruthaíonn tú rannóg shreafa i bhfolach mar a thuairiscítear thuas, "
"beidh iompar KOReader cosúil leis an gcás amhail is dá mbainfeá rannóg as "
"leabhar páipéir trína ghearradh amach:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2195-9
msgid ""
"These hidden flow sections will be skipped when turning pages. For example "
"assume that you created a hidden flow for <b>Chapter 10</b>. Now you are on "
"the last page of <b>Chapter 9</b>. When you turn the page, you will see "
"<b>Chapter 11</b>."
msgstr ""
"Déanfar na codanna sreabhadh folaithe seo a scipeáil agus leathanaigh á "
"gcasadh. Mar shampla, glac leis gur chruthaigh tú sreabhadh folaithe do "
"<b>Chaibidil 10</b>. Anois tá tú ar an leathanach deireanach de <b>Chaibidil "
"9</b>. Nuair a chasann tú an leathanach, feicfidh tú <b>Caibidil 11</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2196-9
msgid ""
"Page numbering will continue as if these hidden flow sections <b>do not "
"exist</b>."
msgstr ""
"Leanfaidh uimhriú leathanach ar aghaidh amhail is dá mba <b>nach mbeadh na "
"rannóga sreafa folaithe seo ann</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2197-9
msgid ""
"These hidden sections will not be shown in your <span class=\"ui\">Progress "
"bar</span> (but read the explanation below) and will not be considered in "
"<b>time to read</b> calculations. But they will still be visible in the "
"<span class=\"ui\">Skim widget</span>."
msgstr ""
"Ní thaispeánfar na codanna folaithe seo i do <span class=\"ui\">bharra Dul "
"Chun Cinn</span> (ach léigh an míniú thíos) agus ní chuirfear san áireamh "
"iad i ríomhanna <b>am le léamh</b>. Ach beidh siad fós le feiceáil sa <span "
"class=\"ui\">ghiuirléid Skim</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2198-9
msgid ""
"Following direct links to the pages included in these hidden flow sections "
"will still work. Also you can still reach these sections from the <span "
"class=\"ui\">Table of contents, Book map, Page browser, Skim widget</span>."
msgstr ""
"Oibreoidh sé fós má leanann tú naisc dhíreacha chuig na leathanaigh atá sna "
"rannóga sreafa folaithe seo. Chomh maith leis sin, is féidir leat teacht ar "
"na rannóga seo ón <span class=\"ui\">Clár Ábhair, Léarscáil Leabhar, "
"Brabhsálaí Leathanaigh, agus Giuirléid Scimithe</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2201-5
msgid ""
"As we said above, your hidden flows will be excluded from your <span "
"class=\"ui\">Progress bar</span>. But if you jump to one of your hidden "
"sections using any of the methods mentioned above, your Progress bar "
"temporarily becomes this hidden section’s progress bar. You can imagine this "
"as the progress bar is zooming into that hidden flow section. If you exit "
"out of this hidden section by turning the page at the end of it, or using "
"other navigation tools, your Progress bar will go back to showing the whole "
"book again (with your custom hidden flows again not visible)."
msgstr ""
"Mar a dúirt muid thuas, eisiófar do shreabhadh folaithe ó do <span "
"class=\"ui\">bharra Dul Chun Cinn</span>. Ach má léimeann tú chuig ceann de "
"do chuid rannóga folaithe ag baint úsáide as aon cheann de na modhanna a "
"luadh thuas, bíonn do bharra Dul Chun Cinn ina bharra dul chun cinn don "
"chuid fholaithe seo go sealadach. Is féidir leat é seo a shamhlú mar go "
"bhfuil an barra dul chun cinn ag zúmáil isteach sa chuid shreabhadh folaithe "
"sin. Má fhágann tú an chuid fholaithe seo tríd an leathanach a chasadh ag a "
"dheireadh, nó trí uirlisí nascleanúna eile a úsáid, rachaidh do bharra Dul "
"Chun Cinn ar ais chun an leabhar iomlán a thaispeáint arís (agus do "
"shreabhadh folaithe saincheaptha gan a bheith le feiceáil arís)."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2204-5
msgid "Removing and cleaning up hidden sections:"
msgstr "Baineadh agus glanadh codanna i bhfolach:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2205-5
msgid ""
"You can remove individual hidden flow sections from the <span "
"class=\"ui\">Page browser</span> in the same way you created them. You can "
"also clear all of them at once with the menu item:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat rannóga sreabhadh i bhfolach aonair a bhaint as an <span "
"class=\"ui\">bhrabhsálaí leathanaigh</span> ar an mbealach céanna ar "
"chruthaigh tú iad. Is féidir leat iad uile a ghlanadh ag an am céanna leis "
"an mír roghchláir:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2207-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Settings / Custom layout features / Clear all "
"marked pages"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Socruithe / Gnéithe leagan amach saincheaptha / "
"Glan na leathanaigh mharcáilte go léir"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2209-5
msgid ""
"As you work on creating hidden flows by tagging pages as <span "
"class=\"ui\">Start hidden flow</span> or <span class=\"ui\">Restart regular "
"flow</span>, some of the previously made ones may stop having an effect. For "
"example in the case that you make <span class=\"ui\">Start hidden flow</"
"span> a few pages before an existing <span class=\"ui\">Start hidden flow</"
"span>, that existing one is no longer involved. This overlapping or obsolete "
"tags are remembered for practical purposes. Again in the previous example, "
"if you end that second hidden flow before the existing-but-no-longer-"
"involved Start hidden flow, this deactive one will be involved again. You "
"can clear all these inactive markers if they interfere with your custom "
"flows, or once you finish making your hidden flows and happy with the "
"results:"
msgstr ""
"Agus tú ag obair ar shreabhadh folaithe a chruthú trí leathanaigh a "
"chlibeáil mar <span class=\"ui\">Tosaigh sreabhadh folaithe</span> nó <span "
"class=\"ui\">Atosaigh sreabhadh rialta</span>, d'fhéadfadh sé nach mbeadh "
"éifeacht ag cuid de na cinn a rinneadh roimhe seo. Mar shampla, i gcás go "
"ndéanann tú <span class=\"ui\">Tosaigh sreabhadh folaithe</span> cúpla "
"leathanach roimh <span class=\"ui\">Tosaigh sreabhadh folaithe</span> atá "
"ann cheana féin, níl an ceann atá ann cheana féin i gceist a thuilleadh. "
"Cuimhnítear ar na clibeanna forluiteacha nó atá as dáta seo chun críocha "
"praiticiúla. Arís san sampla roimhe seo, má chríochnaíonn tú an dara "
"sreabhadh folaithe sin roimh an sreabhadh Tosaigh folaithe atá ann cheana "
"féin ach nach bhfuil i gceist a thuilleadh, beidh an ceann díghníomhach seo "
"i gceist arís. Is féidir leat na marcóirí neamhghníomhacha seo go léir a "
"ghlanadh má chuireann siad isteach ar do shreabhadh saincheaptha, nó nuair a "
"chríochnaíonn tú do shreabhadh folaithe a dhéanamh agus má tá tú sásta leis "
"na torthaí:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2211-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Settings / Custom layout features / Clear inactive "
"marked pages"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Socruithe / Gnéithe leagan amach saincheaptha / "
"Glan leathanaigh mharcáilte neamhghníomhacha"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2217-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L1-customizingappearance"
msgid "CUSTOMIZING TEXT APPEARANCE"
msgstr "AG SAINTÚ DEALRAÍOCHT AN TÉACS"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2219-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-defaultappearance"
msgid "Default appearance settings"
msgstr "Socruithe cuma réamhshocraithe"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2221-5
msgid ""
"In some reader applications, when you change a setting let's say the font "
"used for books, it changes globally. Which means, if you change the default "
"font to <b>Verdana</b>, any books you open next including the ones you are "
"already reading will be shown in this Verdana font."
msgstr ""
"I roinnt feidhmchlár léitheoirí, nuair a athraíonn tú socrú, abair an cló a "
"úsáidtear do leabhair, athraíonn sé go hidirnáisiúnta. Ciallaíonn sé sin, má "
"athraíonn tú an cló réamhshocraithe go <b>Verdana</b>, go dtaispeánfar aon "
"leabhair a osclaíonn tú ina dhiaidh sin, lena n-áirítear na cinn atá á léamh "
"agat cheana féin, sa chló Verdana seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2223-5
msgid ""
"KOReader's approach is different from this. We save appearance settings per "
"book. This gives you the flexibility to change your settings for the current "
"book without affecting others. For example if you have some fantasy books, "
"you can change the font to a medieval looking one just for these books. Or "
"you can set some books to open in <b>landscape orientation</b> or <b>double "
"column</b> mode."
msgstr ""
"Tá cur chuige KOReader difriúil ón méid seo. Sábhálaimid socruithe cuma in "
"aghaidh an leabhair. Tugann sé seo an tsolúbthacht duit do shocruithe a "
"athrú don leabhar reatha gan difear a dhéanamh do leabhair eile. Mar "
"shampla, má tá roinnt leabhar fantaisíochta agat, is féidir leat an cló a "
"athrú go cló meánaoiseach do na leabhair seo amháin. Nó is féidir leat "
"roinnt leabhar a shocrú le hoscailt i mód <b>tírdhreach</b> nó <b>dhá "
"cholún</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2225-5
msgid ""
"To change a setting globally, tap and hold an <b>option</b> or <b>menu item</"
"b> (font weight, line spacing etc.), to set its value as <span "
"class=\"ui\">default</span>. This new value will only be applied to books "
"opened from now on as we said above. Previously opened books will keep their "
"settings. You can identify default values as a <span class=\"ui\">star</"
"span> (★) in the menu or as a <span class=\"ui\">black border</span> around "
"the indicators as seen below:"
msgstr ""
"Chun socrú a athrú go domhanda, tapáil agus coinnigh <b>rogha</b> nó <b>mír "
"roghchláir</b> (meáchan cló, spásáil líne srl.), chun a luach a shocrú mar "
"<span class=\"ui\">réamhshocraithe</span>. Ní chuirfear an luach nua seo i "
"bhfeidhm ach ar leabhair a osclaítear feasta mar a dúirt muid thuas. "
"Coinneoidh leabhair a osclaíodh roimhe seo a socruithe. Is féidir leat "
"luachanna réamhshocraithe a aithint mar <span class=\"ui\">réalta</span> (★) "
"sa roghchlár nó mar <span class=\"ui\">imreán dubh</span> timpeall na "
"dtáscairí mar a fheictear thíos:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2231-1
msgid "Applying current defaults to an already opened book"
msgstr ""
"Réamhshocruithe reatha a chur i bhfeidhm ar leabhar atá oscailte cheana féin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2233-5
msgid ""
"So when you adjust your document defaults like <span class=\"ui\">default "
"line spacing</span> or <span class=\"ui\">default contrast</span>, this new "
"value will only be used for the new documents you open after the change. "
"Your already opened books will not change."
msgstr ""
"Mar sin, nuair a choigeartóidh tú réamhshocruithe do dhoiciméid ar nós <span "
"class=\"ui\">spásáil líne réamhshocraithe</span> nó <span "
"class=\"ui\">codarsnacht réamhshocraithe</span>, ní úsáidfear an luach nua "
"seo ach amháin do na doiciméid nua a osclóidh tú tar éis an athraithe. Ní "
"athróidh do leabhair atá oscailte cheana féin."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2235-5
msgid ""
"But what if you want them to change too? For example, if you change your "
"default <span class=\"ui\">font</span>, you will probably adjust <span "
"class=\"ui\">font weight</span> and <span class=\"ui\">line spacing</span> "
"to more suitable values for this new font. You are satisfied with how the "
"text looks and now you want all your books to look like this. With this "
"feature you don’t need to change these values manually in all your opened "
"books."
msgstr ""
"Ach cad a tharlóidh má theastaíonn uait go n-athródh siad freisin? Mar "
"shampla, má athraíonn tú do <span class=\"ui\">chló</span> réamhshocraithe, "
"is dócha go ndéanfaidh tú <span class=\"ui\">meáchan an chló</span> agus an "
"<span class=\"ui\">spásáil líne</span> a choigeartú go luachanna níos "
"oiriúnaí don chló nua seo. Tá tú sásta leis an gcuma atá ar an téacs agus "
"anois ba mhaith leat go mbeadh cuma mar seo ar do chuid leabhar go léir. "
"Leis an ngné seo ní gá duit na luachanna seo a athrú de láimh i ngach ceann "
"de do leabhair oscailte."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2237-5
msgid ""
"You can easily apply these changes to your already opened books by choosing:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat na hathruithe seo a chur i bhfeidhm go héasca ar do leabhair "
"atá oscailte cheana féin trí na nithe seo a leanas a roghnú:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2239-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Reset document settings to default"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Athshocraigh socruithe an doiciméid go dtí na "
"socruithe réamhshocraithe"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2241-5
msgid ""
"When you tap this option, your current book settings will change to the "
"latest <b>defaults</b> you have set. Don’t worry, this will only change the "
"appearance of the book. Your <b>reading position, highlights, notes and "
"bookmarks</b> will be preserved."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a thapálann tú an rogha seo, athróidh socruithe reatha do leabhair go "
"dtí na <b>réamhshocruithe</b> is déanaí atá socraithe agat. Ná bíodh imní "
"ort, ní athróidh sé seo ach cuma an leabhair. Coinneofar do <b>shuíomh "
"léitheoireachta, buaicphointí, nótaí agus leabharmharcanna</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2244-1
msgid "Saving current book settings as defaults"
msgstr "Ag sábháil socruithe reatha an leabhair mar réamhshocruithe"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2246-5
msgid ""
"When you adjust a book to your liking, for example by changing <span "
"class=\"ui\">line spacing</span>, <span class=\"ui\">font contrast</span> "
"etc. you can save all the changes at once as <span class=\"ui\">defaults</"
"span>. Then you can apply these settings to other books with the <span "
"class=\"ui\">Reset document settings to default</span> option as explained "
"above."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a choigeartaíonn tú leabhar de réir mar is mian leat, mar shampla trí "
"<span class=\"ui\">spásáil líne</span>, <span class=\"ui\">chodarsnacht cló</"
"span> srl. a athrú, is féidir leat na hathruithe go léir a shábháil ag an am "
"céanna mar <span class=\"ui\">réamhshocruithe</span>. Ansin is féidir leat "
"na socruithe seo a chur i bhfeidhm ar leabhair eile leis an rogha <span "
"class=\"ui\">Athshocraigh socruithe doiciméad go réamhshocraithe</span> mar "
"a mhínítear thuas."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2248-5
msgid ""
"You can save your changes as <span class=\"ui\">defaults</span> by choosing:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat do chuid athruithe a shábháil mar <span "
"class=\"ui\">réamhshocruithe</span> trí roghnú:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2250-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Save document settings as default"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Sábháil socruithe an doiciméid mar réamhshocrú"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2254-1
msgid "Creating different groups of settings"
msgstr "Grúpaí socruithe éagsúla a chruthú"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2256-5
msgid ""
"This powerful feature allows you to save all the <span class=\"ui\">BOTTOM "
"MENU</span> settings + font type as a <b>profile</b>. This means you can "
"have different group of settings for different conditions or book types "
"which you can apply at once instead of changing the settings manually every "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Leis an ngné chumhachtach seo is féidir leat na socruithe uile sa <span "
"class=\"ui\">ROGHCHLÁR BUNA</span> + cineál cló a shábháil mar <b>phróifíl</"
"b>. Ciallaíonn sé seo gur féidir leat grúpaí éagsúla socruithe a bheith agat "
"le haghaidh coinníollacha nó cineálacha leabhar éagsúla ar féidir leat a "
"chur i bhfeidhm ag an am céanna seachas na socruithe a athrú de láimh gach "
"uair."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2258-5
msgid "For example you can create:"
msgstr "Mar shampla is féidir leat a chruthú:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2261-9
msgid ""
"<b>Double column</b> profile with <span class=\"ui\">two columns</span> of "
"small sized text, <span class=\"ui\">landscape orientation</span> and "
"minimum <span class=\"ui\">margins</span>"
msgstr ""
"Próifíl <b>Dhá cholún</b> le <span class=\"ui\">dhá cholún</span> de théacs "
"beag, <span class=\"ui\">treoshuíomh tírdhreacha</span> agus <span "
"class=\"ui\"> corrlaigh</span>íosta"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2262-9
msgid ""
"<b>Night reading</b> profile with <span class=\"ui\">bigger sans serif font</"
"span> and higher <span class=\"ui\">contrast</span> for more visible text "
"under low light"
msgstr ""
"Próifíl <b>léitheoireachta oíche</b> le <span class=\"ui\">cló sans serif "
"níos mó</span> agus <span class=\"ui\">codarsnacht níos airde</span> le "
"haghaidh téacs níos infheicthe faoi sholas íseal"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2263-9
msgid ""
"<b>Disabled styles</b> profile with <span class=\"ui\">embedded style</span> "
"and <span class=\"ui\">embedded fonts</span> disabled for badly structured "
"books"
msgstr ""
"Próifíl <b>Stíleanna díchumasaithe</b> le <span class=\"ui\">stíl leabaithe</"
"span> agus <span class=\"ui\">clónna leabaithe</span> díchumasaithe do "
"leabhair a bhfuil drochstruchtúr orthu"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2266-5
msgid ""
"After adjusting your settings to your liking, you can create a profile from "
"them via:"
msgstr ""
"Tar éis duit do shocruithe a choigeartú de réir mar is mian leat, is féidir "
"leat próifíl a chruthú uathu trí:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2268-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_tools.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Profiles / New with current document settings"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_tools.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Próifílí / Nua leis na socruithe doiciméad reatha"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2270-5
msgid ""
"After creating a profile with your settings, you have many options for "
"applying it to another book:"
msgstr ""
"Tar éis próifíl a chruthú le do shocruithe, tá go leor roghanna agat chun í "
"a chur i bhfeidhm ar leabhar eile:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2272-9
msgid ""
"You can apply the profile from the <span class=\"ui\">Profiles menu</span>"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat an phróifíl a chur i bhfeidhm ón <span class=\"ui\">roghchlár "
"Próifílí</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2273-9
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ul.li:2273-9"
msgid "You can assign a gesture to it"
msgstr "Is féidir leat gotha a shannadh dó"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2274-9
msgid "You can show it in your <span class=\"ui\">Quick Menu</span>"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat é a thaispeáint i do <span class=\"ui\">Roghchlár Tapa</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2277-5
msgid ""
"Click here to go to the <a href=\"#L1-qmandprofiles\">QUICK MENU AND "
"PROFILES</a> section of the guide."
msgstr ""
"Cliceáil anseo chun dul go dtí an chuid <a href=\"#L1-"
"qmandprofiles\">ROGHCHLÁR MEAR AGUS PRÓIFÍLÍ</a> den treoir."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2279-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-fonts"
msgid "Using your own fonts"
msgstr "Ag baint úsáide as do chlónna féin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2281-5
msgid ""
"KOReader supports fonts in most widely used TrueType (.ttf) and OpenType "
"formats (.otf). Font files with these extensions can be directly copied to "
"<span class=\"ui\">/koreader/fonts/</span> folder on your device. Check <a "
"href=\"https://github.com/koreader/koreader/wiki/Fonts\">our wiki</a> for "
"more info."
msgstr ""
"Tacaíonn KOReader le clónna sna formáidí TrueType (.ttf) agus OpenType "
"(.otf) is mó a úsáidtear. Is féidir comhaid clónna leis na síntí seo a "
"chóipeáil go díreach chuig an bhfillteán <span class=\"ui\">/koreader/fonts/"
"</span> ar do ghléas. Seiceáil <a href=\"https://github.com/koreader/"
"koreader/wiki/Fonts\">ár vicí</a> le haghaidh tuilleadh eolais."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2283-5
msgid ""
"When starting up, KOReader compiles the available fonts from the <b>font "
"metadata/info</b> and classifies them according to family and weights. This "
"means you can add different weights and variants of a font and KOReader will "
"try to use the most suitable one. <b>Since it takes font family information "
"from metadata, font names are not important when copying to your device. "
"Installed fonts will be available after restarting KOReader.</b>"
msgstr ""
"Agus é á thosú, tiomsaíonn KOReader na clónna atá ar fáil ó na "
"<b>meiteashonraí/eolas cló</b> agus déanann sé iad a aicmiú de réir "
"teaghlaigh agus meáchain. Ciallaíonn sé seo gur féidir leat meáchain agus "
"malairtí éagsúla de chló a chur leis agus déanfaidh KOReader iarracht an "
"ceann is oiriúnaí a úsáid. <b>Ós rud é go nglacann sé faisnéis faoin "
"teaghlach clónna ó mheiteashonraí, níl ainmneacha clónna tábhachtach agus "
"cóipeáil á déanamh chuig do ghléas. Beidh clónna suiteáilte ar fáil tar éis "
"KOReader a atosú.</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2285-5
msgid ""
"Here are some example fonts which look good on an e-ink screen. You can find "
"more of them on the <a href=\"https://fonts.google.com\">Google Fonts</a> "
"website:"
msgstr ""
"Seo roinnt clónna samplacha a bhfuil cuma mhaith orthu ar scáileán dúigh "
"leictreonach. Is féidir leat tuilleadh díobh a fháil ar shuíomh gréasáin <a "
"href=\"https://fonts.google.com\">Google Fonts</a>:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2286-5
msgid "Serif:"
msgstr "Serif:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2288-9
msgid "Spectral"
msgstr "Speictreach"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2289-9
msgid "Vollkorn"
msgstr "Vollkorn"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2290-9
msgid "EB Garamond"
msgstr "EB Garamond"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2293-5
msgid "Sans Serif:"
msgstr "Sans Serif:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2295-9
msgid "Varela Round"
msgstr "Varela Round"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2296-9
msgid "Wix Madefor Text"
msgstr "Téacs Wix Madefor"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2297-9
msgid "Maven Pro (User guide font you are currently reading)"
msgstr "Maven Pro (cló treoir úsáideora atá á léamh agat faoi láthair)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2300-5
msgid "Monospace:"
msgstr "Monospace:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2301-5
msgid ""
"If you are planning to use your own monospace font, probably you already "
"have a favorite one, so we are not offering any examples here. But you can "
"find and compare many monospace fonts at <a href=\"https://"
"www.programmingfonts.org/\">programmingfonts.org</a>"
msgstr ""
"Más mian leat do chló aonspáis féin a úsáid, is dócha go bhfuil ceann is "
"fearr leat agat cheana féin, mar sin níl aon samplaí á dtairiscint againn "
"anseo. Ach is féidir leat go leor clónna aonspáis a fháil agus a chur i "
"gcomparáid ag <a href=\"https://www.programmingfonts.org/"
"\">programmingfonts.org</a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2303-2
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">TIP</span> KOReader can generate a document with "
"sample text rendered with all the fonts installed on your device. This "
"allows you to quickly compare the look and features of the fonts like "
"ligatures and character sets in non-Latin scripts like Greek, Hebrew or "
"Chinese. You can access this feature via:"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">LEID</span> Is féidir le KOReader doiciméad a "
"ghiniúint le téacs samplach a rindreáiltear leis na clónna go léir atá "
"suiteáilte ar do ghléas. Ligeann sé seo duit cuma agus gnéithe na gclónna a "
"chur i gcomparáid go tapa, amhail ligatúir agus tacair charachtar i "
"scripteanna neamh-Laidineacha amhail Gréigis, Eabhrais nó Sínis. Is féidir "
"leat rochtain a fháil ar an ngné seo trí:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div:2305-3
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Font / Font settings / Generate font test document"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Cló / Socruithe cló / Gin doiciméad tástála cló"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2310-1
msgid "Monospace font scale"
msgstr "Scála cló Monospace"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2312-5
msgid ""
"If your book includes parts with <b>Monospace</b> fonts (like in programming "
"books), Monospace text might look disproportional even if it is technically "
"at the same size as the rest of the book. This is caused by differing font "
"metrics. KOReader has an option that allows you to adjust the relative "
"Monospace font size to fix this difference:"
msgstr ""
"Má tá codanna de do leabhar le clónna <b>Monospace</b> (cosúil le leabhair "
"ríomhchlárúcháin), d'fhéadfadh téacs Monospace breathnú neamhréireach fiú má "
"tá sé go teicniúil ar an méid céanna leis an gcuid eile den leabhar. Is é is "
"cúis leis seo ná méadrachtaí clónna éagsúla. Tá rogha ag KOReader a ligeann "
"duit méid coibhneasta an chló Monospace a choigeartú chun an difríocht seo a "
"shocrú:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2314-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Font / Font settings / Monospace fonts scaling"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Cló / Socruithe cló / Scálú clónna aonspáis"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2316-5
msgid ""
"Here you can increase or decrease the size of your Monospace font by "
"adjusting its scaling as a percentage of the default size."
msgstr ""
"Anseo is féidir leat méid do chló Monospace a mhéadú nó a laghdú trína scálú "
"a choigeartú mar chéatadán den mhéid réamhshocraithe."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2320-1
msgid "Using different fonts in one document"
msgstr "Clónna éagsúla a úsáid in aon doiciméad amháin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2322-5
msgid ""
"In HTML/CSS based documents like EPUBs, books can specify to use fonts by "
"family instead of a specific font name. These families can be <b>Serif, Sans-"
"Serif, Monospace, Cursive, Fantasy, Emoji, Fang Song and Math</b>. For "
"example in a book, normal text can be shown in <b>Sans-serif</b> while "
"dialogues are shown in <b>Serif</b> font. KOReader normally uses your "
"default font for all these families except <b>Monospace</b> and <b>Math</b> "
"(which is determined by the style of the text nodes, for example <b>'font-"
"family: serif'</b>). If you want these families to look distinct, you can "
"assign specific fonts for them here:"
msgstr ""
"I ndoiciméid bunaithe ar HTML/CSS cosúil le EPUBanna, is féidir le leabhair "
"clónna a úsáid de réir teaghlaigh seachas ainm cló ar leith. Is féidir na "
"teaghlaigh seo a bheith <b>Serif, Sans-Serif, Monospace, Cursive, Fantasy, "
"Emoji, Fang Song agus Math</b>. Mar shampla, i leabhar, is féidir téacs "
"gnáth a thaispeáint i <b>Sans-serif</b> agus taispeántar dialóga i gcló "
"<b>Serif</b>. De ghnáth, úsáideann KOReader do chló réamhshocraithe do na "
"teaghlaigh seo go léir seachas <b>Monospace</b> agus <b>Math</b> (a "
"chinntear de réir stíl na nóid téacs, mar shampla <b>'font-family: serif'</"
"b>). Más mian leat go mbeadh cuma shainiúil ar na teaghlaigh seo, is féidir "
"leat clónna sonracha a shannadh dóibh anseo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2324-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Font / Font-family fonts"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Cló / Clónna teaghlaigh cló"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2326-5
msgid ""
"To change a family font for the current book just tap on the desired font "
"name. If you want to set this for all your books, long-tap to set it as a "
"<b>default (★)</b>. If a book abuses this font family feature to the point "
"where your default font is hardly used, you can disable that family font for "
"this book by unchecking the association."
msgstr ""
"Chun cló teaghlaigh a athrú don leabhar reatha, níl le déanamh ach sconna ar "
"ainm an chló atá uait. Más mian leat é seo a shocrú do gach cuid leabhar, "
"sconna fada chun é a shocrú mar <b>réamhshocrú (★)</b>. Má bhaineann leabhar "
"mí-úsáid as an ngné teaghlaigh cló seo go dtí an pointe nach n-úsáidtear do "
"chló réamhshocraithe beagnach go minic, is féidir leat an cló teaghlaigh sin "
"a dhíchumasú don leabhar seo tríd an gcomhlachas a dhíthiceáil."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2332-1
msgid "Changing font quickly"
msgstr "Athrú cló go tapa"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2334-2
msgid ""
"If you are switching between fonts frequently (i.e. <b>monospace</b> for "
"programming books and <b>serif</b> for novels) there is a workaround which "
"makes this easier than going into the menu each time. You can create "
"profiles for your fonts and all font related settings like <span "
"class=\"ui\">line spacing, contrast, bold</span> etc. and add these profiles "
"to a <span class=\"ui\">Quick Menu</span>. So with a single gesture you can "
"open your font selection menu and change the font like shown in the image "
"below:"
msgstr ""
"Má bhíonn tú ag athrú idir clónna go minic (m.sh. <b>monospace</b> le "
"haghaidh leabhar ríomhchlárúcháin agus <b>serif</b> le haghaidh úrscéalta) "
"tá réiteach sealadach ann a fhágann go bhfuil sé seo níos éasca ná dul "
"isteach sa roghchlár gach uair. Is féidir leat próifílí a chruthú le do "
"chlónna agus do gach socrú a bhaineann le clónna cosúil le <span "
"class=\"ui\">spásáil líne, codarsnacht, cló trom</span> srl. agus na "
"próifílí seo a chur le <span class=\"ui\">Roghchlár Tapa</span>. Mar sin, le "
"gotha amháin is féidir leat do roghchlár roghnúcháin clónna a oscailt agus "
"an cló a athrú mar a thaispeántar san íomhá thíos:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2338-5
msgid ""
"Check the <a href=\"#qmandprofiles\">QUICK MENU AND PROFILES</a> section of "
"this guide to learn how to do this."
msgstr ""
"Seiceáil an chuid <a href=\"#qmandprofiles\">ROGHCHLÁR MEAR AGUS PRÓIFÍLÍ</"
"a> den treoir seo chun foghlaim conas é seo a dhéanamh."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2343-1
msgid "Style tweaks"
msgstr "Coigeartuithe stíl"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2345-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.p:2345-5"
msgid "!!! ADVANCED"
msgstr "!!! CASTA"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2347-5
msgid ""
"Style tweaks feature of KOReader allows you to modify how your book is "
"rendered by KOReader. We won't go through a full CSS course here. We just "
"want to show you the basics so when you see a style tweak, you will at least "
"have a rough idea what it does."
msgstr ""
"Leis an ngné feabhsúcháin stíl de chuid KOReader, is féidir leat an chaoi a "
"ndéanann KOReader do leabhar a mhodhnú. Ní dhéanfaimid cúrsa iomlán CSS "
"anseo. Níl uainn ach na bunghnéithe a thaispeáint duit ionas go mbeidh "
"tuairim gharbh agat ar a laghad faoi cad a dhéanann sé nuair a fheiceann tú "
"feabhsúchán stíl."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2349-5
msgid "What is a style tweak?"
msgstr "Cad is coigeartú stíl ann?"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2350-5
msgid ""
"We can describe an EPUB document as a <b>HTML file + some CSS rules</b>. "
"These CSS rules determine how different parts of the book (headings, bold "
"text, quotes etc.) will be shown on a reader app. With <span "
"class=\"ui\">style tweaks</span>, you can change how your book will be "
"rendered by adding new rules and/or overriding the rules written by the "
"publisher that is embedded in your book."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir linn doiciméad EPUB a chur síos mar <b>chomhad HTML + roinnt "
"rialacha CSS</b>. Cinneann na rialacha CSS seo conas a thaispeánfar codanna "
"éagsúla den leabhar (ceannteidil, téacs trom, Sleachta srl.) ar aip "
"léitheora. Le <span class=\"ui\">coigeartuithe stíl</span>, is féidir leat "
"athrú a dhéanamh ar an gcaoi a rindreálfar do leabhar trí rialacha nua a "
"chur leis agus/nó na rialacha a scríobh an foilsitheoir atá leabaithe i do "
"leabhar a shárú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2352-5
msgid "Let's see this on an example <span class=\"ui\">style tweak</span>:"
msgstr ""
"Féachaimis air seo ar shampla de <span class=\"ui\">choigeartú stíl</span>:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2354-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.p:2354-5"
msgid "img { width: 10px !important; height: 10px !important }"
msgstr "img { width: 10px !important; height: 10px !important }"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2355-5
msgid ""
"In plain language this rule says: <b>\"Ignore their original size and make "
"all the images in this book 10 pixels wide and 10 pixels high.\"</b> So if "
"you add this style tweak to KOReader, all the images in your book will be "
"shown tiny."
msgstr ""
"I dteanga shimplí, deir an riail seo: <b>\"Déan neamhaird dá méid bunaidh "
"agus déan na híomhánna uile sa leabhar seo 10 picteilín ar leithead agus 10 "
"picteilín ar airde.\"</b> Mar sin, má chuireann tú an tweak stíl seo le "
"KOReader, taispeánfar na híomhánna uile i do leabhar beag bídeach."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2357-5
msgid "Now lets explain this tweak item by item:"
msgstr "Anois, déanaimis an tweak seo a mhíniú mír ar mhír:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2360-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">img</span> - This is a CSS selector that targets all "
"<b>img</b> (image) elements in the book."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">img</span> - Is roghnóir CSS é seo a dhíríonn ar gach "
"eilimint <b>img</b> (íomhá) sa leabhar."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2361-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">{ width: 10px !important; height: 10px !important; }</"
"span> - This is the declaration block. It contains the styles which will be "
"applied to the selected <b>img</b> elements."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">{ width: 10px !important; height: 10px !important; </"
"span> - Seo é an bloc dearbhaithe. Tá na stíleanna ann a chuirfear i "
"bhfeidhm ar na heilimintí <b>img</b> roghnaithe."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2362-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">width: 10px !important;</span> - This first part sets the "
"width of the targeted <b>img</b> elements to 10 pixels. The <b>!important</"
"b> declaration is an override switch which ensures that your width value "
"takes precedence over any other existing <b>width</b> declaration applied to "
"these images."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">leithead: 10px !important;</span> - Socraíonn an chéad "
"chuid seo leithead na n-eilimintí <b>img</b> spriocdhírithe go 10 picteilín. "
"Is lasc sáraithe é an dearbhú <b>!important</b> a chinntíonn go bhfuil "
"tosaíocht ag do luach leithead thar aon dearbhú <b>leithead</b> eile atá ann "
"cheana a chuirtear i bhfeidhm ar na híomhánna seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2363-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">height: 10px !important;</span> - This part sets the "
"height of the targeted <b>img</b> elements to 10 pixels. Again, the <b>!"
"important</b> declaration is an override switch which ensures that your "
"height value takes precedence over any other existing <b>height</b> "
"declaration applied to these images."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">airde: 10px !important;</span> - Socraíonn an chuid seo "
"airde na n-eilimintí <b>img</b> spriocdhírithe go 10 picteilín. Arís, is "
"lasc sáraithe é an dearbhú <b>!important</b> a chinntíonn go dtógfaidh do "
"luach airde tosaíocht thar aon dearbhú <b>airde</b> eile atá ann cheana a "
"chuirtear i bhfeidhm ar na híomhánna seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2366-5
msgid ""
"In summary, this CSS rule is designed to set a <b>fixed width and height of "
"10 pixels</b> for all <b>img</b> elements in your book, <b>ignoring their "
"original style</b>."
msgstr ""
"Mar achoimre, tá an riail CSS seo deartha chun <b>leithead agus airde seasta "
"de 10 picteilín</b> a shocrú do gach eilimint <b>img</b> i do leabhar, ag "
"<b>neamhaird a dhéanamh dá stíl bhunaidh</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2370-5
msgid "Some useful examples of style tweaks"
msgstr "Roinnt samplaí úsáideacha de choigeartuithe stíl"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2372-5
msgid ""
"These are some useful style tweaks that you can use directly or modify "
"according to your liking. Next heading explains how to use them in KOReader."
msgstr ""
"Seo roinnt feabhsuithe stíl úsáideacha ar féidir leat a úsáid go díreach nó "
"a mhodhnú de réir do thaitin. Mínítear sa chéad cheannteideal eile conas iad "
"a úsáid i KOReader."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2375-13
msgid "Add a separator line above each heading in a book:"
msgstr "Cuir líne deighilte os cionn gach ceannteidil i leabhar:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li.p:2376-17
msgid "H1, H2, H3, H4 { border-top: 2px solid black; }"
msgstr "H1, H2, H3, H4 { border-top: 2px solid black; }"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2379-13
msgid "Add some margin above the headings:"
msgstr "Cuir roinnt corrlaigh os cionn na gceannteideal:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li.p:2380-17
msgid "H1, H2, H3, H4 { margin-top: 2em !important; }"
msgstr "H1, H2, H3, H4 { margin-top: 2em !important; }"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2382-13
msgid "Or if the book has too much margin above the headings, remove them:"
msgstr ""
"Nó má tá an iomarca corrlaigh os cionn na gceannteideal sa leabhar, bain iad:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li.p:2383-17
msgid "H1, H2, H3, H4 { margin-top: 0 !important; }"
msgstr "H1, H2, H3, H4 { margin-top: 0 !important; }"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2386-13
msgid "Add a small gap between paragraphs to make the text more readable:"
msgstr ""
"Cuir bearna bheag idir mhíreanna chun an téacs a dhéanamh níos inléite:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li.p:2387-17
msgid ""
"p + p { margin-top: 0.5em !important; margin-bottom: 0.5em !important; }"
msgstr ""
"p + p { margin-top: 0.5em !important; margin-bottom: 0.5em !important; }"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2389-13
msgid "Disable all images in an EPUB:"
msgstr "Díchumasaigh gach íomhá in EPUB:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li.p:2390-17
msgid "img { display: none !important; }"
msgstr "img { display: none !important; }"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2393-13
msgid "Make images very small instead of disabling them:"
msgstr "Déan íomhánna an-bheag in ionad iad a dhíchumasú:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li.p:2395-17
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ul.li.p:2395-17"
msgid "img { width: 10px !important; height: 10px !important }"
msgstr "img { width: 10px !important; height: 10px !important }"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2398-13
msgid ""
"Make the code block sections in computer science books tidier and more "
"readable (<a href=\"https://github.com/koreader/koreader/issues/"
"9261#issuecomment-2508866126\">Here you can see an example</a>):"
msgstr ""
"Déan na codanna bloic cóid i leabhair eolaíochta ríomhaireachta níos "
"slachtmhaire agus níos inléite (<a href=\"https://github.com/koreader/"
"koreader/issues/9261#issuecomment-2508866126\">Feicfidh tú sampla anseo</a>):"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li.p:2400-17
msgid ""
"pre,code { font-size: 0.6em !important; line-height: 1.8em !important; "
"background-color: #eee !important; margin: 1em 0 !important; padding: 1em 0 !"
"important; }"
msgstr ""
"pre,code { font-size: 0.6em !important; line-height: 1.8em !important; "
"background-color: #eee !important; margin: 1em 0 !important; padding: 1em 0 !"
"important; }"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2414-5
msgid "How to add style tweaks"
msgstr "Conas feabhsuithe stíl a chur leis"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2416-5
msgid ""
"Ok, now we have seen what <span class=\"ui\">style tweaks</span> are. But "
"how can we use them? There are three types of <span class=\"ui\">style "
"tweaks</span> in KOReader:"
msgstr ""
"Ceart go leor, anois tá feicthe againn cad iad <span "
"class=\"ui\">coigeartuithe stíl</span>. Ach conas is féidir linn iad a "
"úsáid? Tá trí chineál <span class=\"ui\">coigeartuithe stíl</span> i "
"KOReader:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2420-5
msgid "1. Built-in style tweaks"
msgstr "1. Feabhsuithe stíl ionsuite"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2422-5
msgid ""
"This heading is new, and the screenshot above and below. Anything to add?"
msgstr ""
"Tá an ceannteideal seo nua, agus an scáileán thuas agus thíos. Aon rud le "
"cur leis?"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2425-1
msgid ""
"These tweaks are included in KOReader. They are the easiest to use since you "
"just enable them from the menu to use them. You don't need to write any CSS "
"code:"
msgstr ""
"Tá na coigeartuithe seo san áireamh i KOReader. Is iad is fusa le húsáid ós "
"rud é nach gá ach iad a chumasú ón roghchlár le go n-úsáidfidh tú iad. Ní gá "
"duit aon chód CSS a scríobh:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2427-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Style tweaks"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Coigeartuithe stíle"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2429-5
msgid ""
"They come in many categories. To apply a tweak to the <b>current book only</"
"b>, tick the checkbox. If you want to get more information about this tweak "
"or enable it for <b>all the books</b>, long-press on its name. A dialog will "
"appear:"
msgstr ""
"Tagann siad i mórán catagóirí. Chun coigeartú a chur i bhfeidhm ar an "
"<b>leabhar reatha amháin</b>, cuir tic sa bhosca seiceála. Más mian leat "
"tuilleadh eolais a fháil faoin gcoigeartú seo nó é a chumasú do <b>na "
"leabhair uile</b>, brúigh ar a ainm ar feadh tamaill. Feicfear bosca "
"dialóige:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2434-13
msgid "This area shows the name and description of the tweak"
msgstr "Taispeánann an limistéar seo ainm agus cur síos an tweak"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2435-13
msgid ""
"This box shows the CSS code of the tweak. You can tap on this area to copy "
"the code to the clipboard. Then you can paste and modify this code in your "
"<span class=\"ui\">Book-specific tweak</span> as explained under the next "
"heading."
msgstr ""
"Taispeánann an bosca seo cód CSS an tweak. Is féidir leat tapáil ar an "
"limistéar seo chun an cód a chóipeáil chuig an ghearrthaisce. Ansin is "
"féidir leat an cód seo a ghreamú agus a mhodhnú i do <span "
"class=\"ui\">tweak Leabhar-shonrach</span> mar a mhínítear faoin "
"gceannteideal seo a leanas."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2437-13
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Show in action list</span> button allows you to toggle "
"this tweak with a gesture or add it to a <span class=\"ui\">Quick Menu</"
"span>. See the heading named <b>\"How to use tweaks efficiently\"</b> below "
"for more info."
msgstr ""
"Leis an gcnaipe <span class=\"ui\">Taispeáin sa liosta gníomhartha</span> is "
"féidir leat an tweak seo a athrú le gotha nó é a chur le <span "
"class=\"ui\">Roghchlár Tapa</span>. Féach an ceannteideal dar teideal "
"<b>\"Conas tweaks a úsáid go héifeachtúil\"</b> thíos le haghaidh tuilleadh "
"eolais."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2439-13
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Use on all books</span> button activate this tweak for "
"all your books. A <b>star (★)</b> will appear next to its name in the menu, "
"indicating that this tweak will be applied to all books. You can disable "
"this with the same steps."
msgstr ""
"Cuireann an cnaipe <span class=\"ui\">Úsáid ar gach leabhar</span> an "
"coigeartú seo i ngníomh le do chuid leabhar go léir. Beidh <b>réalta (★)</b> "
"le feiceáil in aice lena ainm sa roghchlár, rud a léiríonn go gcuirfear an "
"coigeartú seo i bhfeidhm ar gach leabhar. Is féidir leat é seo a dhíchumasú "
"leis na céimeanna céanna."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2443-5
msgid "2. Book-specific tweak"
msgstr "2. Coigeartú atá sainiúil don leabhar"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2444-9
msgid ""
"As you can guess from its name, this type of tweaks are only active for the "
"book which you created them in. This feature is more useful for testing your "
"tweaks or if you need to fix something on the current book and you know that "
"you won't need it on other books. After creating this type of tweak, if you "
"decide that you will need it on other books too (i.e. from the same "
"publisher), you can convert it to a <span class=\"ui\">user style tweak</"
"span>, which we will explain next."
msgstr ""
"Mar is féidir leat a thomhas óna ainm, níl an cineál seo coigeartuithe "
"gníomhach ach don leabhar inar chruthaigh tú iad. Tá an ghné seo níos úsáidí "
"chun do choigeartuithe a thástáil nó má theastaíonn uait rud éigin a shocrú "
"ar an leabhar reatha agus má tá a fhios agat nach mbeidh sé de dhíth ort ar "
"leabhair eile. Tar éis duit an cineál seo coigeartuithe a chruthú, má "
"shocraíonn tú go mbeidh sé de dhíth ort ar leabhair eile freisin (i.e. ón "
"bhfoilsitheoir céanna), is féidir leat é a thiontú go <span "
"class=\"ui\">coigeart stíl úsáideora</span>, a mhíneoimid ina dhiaidh seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2446-9
msgid ""
"To create a <span class=\"ui\">book specific tweak</span>, use the "
"integrated editor which you can find here:"
msgstr ""
"Chun <span class=\"ui\">coigeartú leabhar-shonrach</span> a chruthú, bain "
"úsáid as an eagarthóir comhtháite atá le fáil anseo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2448-9
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Style tweaks / Book-specific tweak"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Coigeartuithe stíl / Coigeartuithe sonracha don "
"leabhar"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.p:2450-24
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">TIP</span> In the editor we have a <span "
"class=\"ui\">CSS</span> menu on the bottom toolbar. This menu contains many "
"useful CSS syntax and properties. When you open this menu please first read "
"the <span class=\"ui\">Long-press for info</span> help. Also you can long-"
"press on CSS items in this menu to see a description."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">LEID</span> San eagarthóir tá roghchlár <span "
"class=\"ui\">CSS</span> againn ar an mbarra uirlisí bun. Tá go leor comhréir "
"agus airíonna CSS úsáideacha sa roghchlár seo. Nuair a osclaíonn tú an "
"roghchlár seo, léigh an chabhair <span class=\"ui\">Brúigh go fada le "
"haghaidh eolais</span> ar dtús. Chomh maith leis sin, is féidir leat brúigh "
"go fada ar mhíreanna CSS sa roghchlár seo chun cur síos a fheiceáil."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2453-5
msgid "3. User style tweaks"
msgstr "3. Feabhsuithe ar stíl an úsáideora"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2455-9
msgid ""
"These group of tweaks are different from the previous ones in the way they "
"are created. Also unlike the previous type, they are not limited to a single "
"book. They can be applied globally to all of your books."
msgstr ""
"Tá an grúpa seo de choigeartuithe difriúil ó na cinn roimhe seo sa chaoi a "
"gcruthaítear iad. Chomh maith leis sin, murab ionann agus an cineál roimhe "
"seo, níl siad teoranta do leabhar amháin. Is féidir iad a chur i bhfeidhm go "
"domhanda ar do chuid leabhar go léir."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2457-9
msgid "Procedure is roughly like this, which we will explain in detail:"
msgstr "Tá an nós imeachta mar seo go garbh, agus míneoimid go mion é:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2460-13
msgid "Create your user tweak file"
msgstr "Cruthaigh do chomhad tweak úsáideora"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2461-13
msgid "Transfer it to your device"
msgstr "Aistrigh chuig do ghléas é"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2462-13
msgid "Enable your tweak from the menu"
msgstr "Cumasaigh do choigeartú ón roghchlár"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2466-9
msgid "1. Creating the user tweak file:"
msgstr "1. An comhad tweak úsáideora a chruthú:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2467-9
msgid ""
"A <span class=\"ui\">user style tweak</span> is actually a normal text file "
"with a <b>.css</b> extension. You can create this file:"
msgstr ""
"Is comhad téacs gnáth é <span class=\"ui\">tweak stíl úsáideora</span> le "
"síneadh <b>.css</b> i ndáiríre. Is féidir leat an comhad seo a chruthú:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2470-13
msgid "On your computer"
msgstr "Ar do ríomhaire"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2471-13
msgid "On your device if it has a text editor (like Android OS based devices)"
msgstr ""
"Ar do ghléas má tá eagarthóir téacs air (cosúil le gléasanna atá bunaithe ar "
"chóras oibriúcháin Android)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2472-13
msgid "In KOReader's integrated text editor which you can find in plugins"
msgstr "In eagarthóir téacs comhtháite KOReader atá le fáil i mbreiseáin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2475-9
msgid "You can copy / paste the examples we mentioned above to your file."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat na samplaí a luaigh muid thuas a chóipeáil/a ghreamú chuig do "
"chomhad."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2479-9
msgid "2. Transferring the file to your device:"
msgstr "2. An comhad a aistriú chuig do ghléas:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2480-9
msgid ""
"After creating the file(s) which contain your CSS rules, save or transfer "
"them to the <span class=\"ui\">styletweaks</span> folder under your KOReader "
"installation. Give the files descriptive names because filename will be the "
"title of the tweak in the KOReader menu system. You can use underscores "
"\"<b>_</b>\" in your filenames, they will be treated as spaces in the menu. "
"<b>You need to restart KOReader after transferring your files so it can load "
"them.</b>"
msgstr ""
"Tar éis duit an comhad/na comhaid ina bhfuil do rialacha CSS a chruthú, "
"sábháil nó aistrigh iad chuig an bhfillteán <span class=\"ui\">styletweaks</"
"span> faoi do shuiteáil KOReader. Tabhair ainmneacha tuairisciúla do na "
"comhaid mar is é ainm an chomhaid teideal an tweak i gcóras roghchláir "
"KOReader. Is féidir leat fo-línte \"<b>_</b>\" a úsáid i d'ainmneacha "
"comhad, déileálfar leo mar spásanna sa roghchlár. <b>Ní mór duit KOReader a "
"atosú tar éis duit do chuid comhad a aistriú ionas gur féidir leis iad a "
"luchtú.</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2484-9
msgid "2. Enabling the tweak:"
msgstr "2. An tweak a chumasú:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2485-9
msgid "After the restart, open a book and go to this menu:"
msgstr ""
"Tar éis an atosaithe, oscail leabhar agus téigh go dtí an roghchlár seo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2487-9
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.div:2487-9"
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Style tweaks / User style tweaks"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Coigeartuithe stíl / Coigeartuithe stíl úsáideora"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2489-9
msgid ""
"Now you should see your tweak in the list with a checkbox next to it. To "
"apply your tweak to the <b>current book only</b>, tick the checkbox. If you "
"want this tweak to be enabled for <b>all the books</b>, long-press on its "
"name. A dialog will appear. Tap the menu item <span class=\"ui\">Use on all "
"books</span>. A <b>star (★)</b> will appear next to its name in the menu, "
"indicating that this tweak will be applied to all books. You can disable "
"this with the same steps. See below for an example:"
msgstr ""
"Anois ba chóir duit do choigeartú a fheiceáil sa liosta agus bosca seiceála "
"in aice leis. Chun do choigeartú a chur i bhfeidhm ar an <b>leabhar reatha "
"amháin</b>, cuir tic sa bhosca seiceála. Más mian leat an coigeartú seo a "
"chumasú do <b>na leabhair uile</b>, brúigh ar a ainm ar feadh tamaill. "
"Feicfear bosca dialóige. Beartaíonn an mhír roghchláir <span "
"class=\"ui\">Úsáid ar gach leabhar</span>. Feicfear <b>réalta (★)</b> in "
"aice lena ainm sa roghchlár, rud a léiríonn go gcuirfear an coigeartú seo i "
"bhfeidhm ar gach leabhar. Is féidir leat é seo a dhíchumasú leis na "
"céimeanna céanna. Féach thíos le haghaidh sampla:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2493-9
msgid ""
"In the image above, I have 3 style tweak files in the <span "
"class=\"ui\">styletweaks</span> folder under my KOReader installation. First "
"one is disabled because checkbox is empty. Second one is enabled for this "
"book only since checkbox is marked but there is no star. Third one is "
"enabled for all the books <b>(★)</b>."
msgstr ""
"San íomhá thuas, tá 3 chomhad tweak stíl agam sa bhfillteán <span "
"class=\"ui\">styletweaks</span> faoi mo shuiteáil KOReader. Tá an chéad "
"cheann díchumasaithe mar go bhfuil an bosca seiceála folamh. Tá an dara "
"ceann cumasaithe don leabhar seo amháin mar go bhfuil an bosca seiceála "
"marcáilte ach nach bhfuil réalta ann. Tá an tríú ceann cumasaithe do na "
"leabhair uile <b>(★)</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2495-9
msgid ""
"You might notice that there is also a <span class=\"ui\">right triangle "
"icon</span> next to the first tweak. This means that this tweak can be "
"activated using gestures. This will explained in the next heading."
msgstr ""
"B’fhéidir go dtabharfá faoi deara go bhfuil deilbhín <span "
"class=\"ui\">triantáin dheis</span> in aice leis an gcéad choigeartú "
"freisin. Ciallaíonn sé seo gur féidir an coigeartú seo a ghníomhachtú trí "
"úsáid a bhaint as gothaí. Míneofar é seo sa chéad cheannteideal eile."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2497-9
msgid "How to use tweaks efficiently"
msgstr "Conas tweaks a úsáid go héifeachtach"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2499-9
msgid ""
"When creating your <span class=\"ui\">user style tweaks</span> you can make "
"multiple tweak files, each modifying some part of the book like in the "
"example image above. You can have one file for the <b>headings</b>, others "
"to modify <b>paragraphs</b>, <b>links</b> etc. This modular system allows "
"you to enable tweaks depending on your document."
msgstr ""
"Agus tú ag cruthú do <span class=\"ui\">choigeartuithe stíl úsáideora</span> "
"is féidir leat roinnt comhad coigeartuithe a chruthú, agus gach ceann acu ag "
"modhnú cuid den leabhar mar atá san íomhá shamplach thuas. Is féidir leat "
"comhad amháin a bheith agat do na <b>ceannteidil</b>, agus cinn eile chun "
"<b>míreanna</b>, <b>naisc</b> srl. a mhodhnú. Ligeann an córas modúlach seo "
"duit coigeartuithe a chumasú ag brath ar do dhoiciméad."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2501-9
msgid ""
"As we said above, you can toggle <span class=\"ui\">user style tweaks</span> "
"from this menu location:"
msgstr ""
"Mar a dúirt muid thuas, is féidir leat <span class=\"ui\">coigeartuithe stíl "
"úsáideora</span> a athrú ón suíomh roghchláir seo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2503-9
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.div:2503-9"
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Style tweaks / User style tweaks"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Coigeartuithe stíl / Coigeartuithe stíl úsáideora"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2507-9
msgid ""
"Also we have easier ways to toggle your style tweaks than going to the menu "
"every time."
msgstr ""
"Chomh maith leis sin, tá bealaí níos éasca againn chun do stíl a choigeartú "
"ná dul chuig an roghchlár gach uair."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2509-9
msgid "1. You can assign a gesture to a tweak"
msgstr "1. Is féidir leat gotha a shannadh do choigeartú"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2510-9
msgid ""
"To do this, first we have to add our <span class=\"ui\">user style tweak</"
"span> to the list of gesture actions:"
msgstr ""
"Chun seo a dhéanamh, ní mór dúinn ár <span class=\"ui\">coigeartú stíl "
"úsáideora</span> a chur leis an liosta gníomhartha gothaí ar dtús:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2513-17
msgid ""
"Go to the <span class=\"ui\">user style tweaks</span> menu and long-press on "
"your style tweak"
msgstr ""
"Téigh go dtí an roghchlár <span class=\"ui\">coigeartuithe stíl úsáideora</"
"span> agus brúigh ar do choigeartú stíl ar feadh i bhfad"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2514-17
msgid ""
"In the dialog press the button <span class=\"ui\">Show in action list</span>"
msgstr ""
"Sa dialóg brúigh an cnaipe <span class=\"ui\">Taispeáin sa liosta "
"gníomhartha</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2515-17
msgid ""
"A <span class=\"ui\">right triangle icon</span> will appear next to your "
"style tweak in the menu"
msgstr ""
"Beidh deilbhín <span class=\"ui\">triantáin dheis</span> le feiceáil in aice "
"le do choigeartú stíl sa roghchlár"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2518-13
msgid ""
"You can see it in the example image above, next to the <b>Adjust margins</b> "
"style tweak. Now this style tweak is added to the actions list. You can find "
"it under <span class=\"ui\">Gesture Manager > Reflowable documents</span> "
"category. It will be at the end of the list."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat é a fheiceáil san íomhá shamplach thuas, in aice leis an "
"tweak stíl <b>Coigeartaigh imeall</b>. Anois tá an tweak stíl seo curtha "
"leis an liosta gníomhartha. Is féidir leat é a fháil faoin gcatagóir <span "
"class=\"ui\">Bainisteoir Gothaí > Doiciméid Athshreabhtha</span>. Beidh sé "
"ag deireadh an liosta."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2522-9
msgid "2. You can add a tweak to your Quick Menu"
msgstr "2. Is féidir leat mionchoigeartú a chur le do Roghchlár Tapa"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2524-9
msgid ""
"To add a tweak to your <span class=\"ui\">Quick Menu</span>, first it has to "
"be added to the actions list as described in the heading above. Then you can "
"follow the instructions under the <a href=\"#quickmenu\">Quick Menu</a> "
"section of this guide."
msgstr ""
"Chun coigeartú a chur le do <span class=\"ui\">Roghchlár Tapa</span>, ní mór "
"é a chur leis an liosta gníomhartha ar dtús mar a thuairiscítear sa "
"cheannteideal thuas. Ansin is féidir leat na treoracha faoin rannán <a "
"href=\"#quickmenu\">Roghchlár Tapa</a> den treoir seo a leanúint."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2526-9
msgid ""
"You can even combine both methods and create a special <span "
"class=\"ui\">Quick Menu</span> for your style tweaks and then assign it to a "
"gesture. This way, with a simple gesture you can access all your style "
"tweaks and activate them as needed."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat an dá mhodh a chomhcheangal fiú agus <span "
"class=\"ui\">Roghchlár Tapa</span> speisialta a chruthú le do chuid "
"feabhsuithe stíl agus ansin é a shannadh do ghluaiseacht. Ar an mbealach "
"seo, le gluaiseacht shimplí is féidir leat rochtain a fháil ar do chuid "
"feabhsuithe stíl go léir agus iad a ghníomhachtú de réir mar is gá."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2529-5
msgid "Finding elements for modifying"
msgstr "Eilimintí a aimsiú le haghaidh modhnú"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2531-5
msgid ""
"Note that in some books, titles might not be in <b>&lt;H1&gt; or &lt;H2&gt;</"
"b> elements, but in something like <b>&lt;p class=\"tit123\"&gt;</b>. You "
"can find which selectors are used for a part of text by checking the source. "
"To achieve this, select the text around the element which you are interested "
"in, and choose <span class=\"ui\">View HTML</span> from the dialog. In the "
"example above, your style tweak would look like this:"
msgstr ""
"Tabhair faoi deara nach mbíonn teidil i roinnt leabhar i ngnéithe "
"<b>&lt;H1&gt; nó &lt;H2&gt;</b>, ach i rud éigin cosúil le <b>&lt;p "
"class=\"tit123\"&gt;</b>. Is féidir leat a fháil amach cé na roghnóirí a "
"úsáidtear le haghaidh cuid den téacs tríd an bhfoinse a sheiceáil. Chun seo "
"a bhaint amach, roghnaigh an téacs timpeall an eilimint a bhfuil suim agat "
"inti, agus roghnaigh <span class=\"ui\">Féach HTML</span> ón dialóg. Sa "
"sampla thuas, bheadh do choigeartú stíl mar seo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2533-5
msgid "P.tit123 { border-top: 2px solid black; }"
msgstr "P.tit123 { border-top: 2px solid black; }"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2535-5
msgid "instead of this:"
msgstr "in ionad seo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2537-5
msgid "H1 { border-top: 2px solid black; }"
msgstr "H1 { border-top: 2px solid black; }"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2548-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L1-bookmarks"
msgid "BOOKMARKS, HIGHLIGHTS AND NOTES"
msgstr "LEABHARMHARCANNA, BUAICPHOINTÍ AGUS NÓTAÍ"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2550-5
msgid ""
"KOReader gives you options to interact with your book like you can do with a "
"real book. Many settings of the bookmark window can be changed here:"
msgstr ""
"Tugann KOReader roghanna duit chun idirghníomhú le do leabhar díreach mar is "
"féidir leat a dhéanamh le fíorleabhar. Is féidir go leor socruithe den "
"fhuinneog leabharmharcanna a athrú anseo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2554-6
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Settings / Bookmarks"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Socruithe / Leabharmharcanna"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2559-5
msgid "BOOKMARKS:"
msgstr "LEABHARMHARCANNA:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2561-5
msgid ""
"You can add (and remove) a bookmark by pressing the upper right corner. This "
"is the equivalent of folding the corner of a page on a real book and shows a "
"similar icon when you enable it."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat leabharmharc a chur leis (agus a bhaint) trí bhrú ar an "
"gcúinne uachtarach ar dheis. Is ionann é seo agus cúinne leathanaigh a "
"fhilleadh ar leabhar fíor agus taispeánann sé deilbhín cosúil nuair a "
"chuireann tú ar chumas é."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2565-5
msgid "HIGHLIGHTS:"
msgstr "BUAICPHOINTÍ:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2567-5
msgid ""
"You can highlight text in 4 different styles. In the image below, you can "
"see a normal paragraph followed by different styles of highlights. <span "
"class=\"ui\">Lighten</span> (with gray background), <span "
"class=\"ui\">Underline, Strikeout</span> and <span class=\"ui\">Invert</"
"span>."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat téacs a aibhsiú i gceithre stíl éagsúla. San íomhá thíos, "
"feiceann tú mír gnáth agus stíleanna éagsúla aibhsithe ina diaidh. <span "
"class=\"ui\">Éadromaigh</span> (le cúlra liath), <span class=\"ui\">Fo-líne, "
"Stróic Amach</span> agus <span class=\"ui\">Inbhéartaigh</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2572-5
msgid ""
"You can use all these styles at the same time, like they are different "
"colored highlight markers. Or you can decide your favorite style and set it "
"as default from this menu by long pressing:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat na stíleanna seo go léir a úsáid ag an am céanna, amhail is "
"dá mba marcóirí aibhsithe de dhathanna difriúla iad. Nó is féidir leat do "
"stíl is fearr leat a roghnú agus í a shocrú mar réamhshocrú ón roghchlár seo "
"trí bhrú fada:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2574-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.div:2574-5"
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Highlight style"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Stíl Aibhsithe"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2578-5
msgid ""
"Also if you have a device with a color screen, you can create highlights in "
"different colors:"
msgstr ""
"Chomh maith leis sin, má tá gléas agat le scáileán daite, is féidir leat "
"buaicphointí a chruthú i ndathanna éagsúla:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2580-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Highlights / Highlight color"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Buaicphointí / Dath na mbuaicphointí"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2584-5
msgid "Some tips for color highlights:"
msgstr "Roinnt leideanna maidir le buaicphointí datha:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2587-9
msgid ""
"You can change the color of an existing highlight by tapping on it and "
"choosing <span class=\"ui\">Color</span> from the popup menu."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat dath aird atá ann cheana a athrú trí thapáil air agus <span "
"class=\"ui\">Dath</span> a roghnú ón roghchlár aníos."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2589-9
msgid ""
"You can combine the colors with different highlight styles like "
"<b>Underline</b> and <b>Strikethrough</b> to create a powerful highlighting "
"system. For example you can use a <span style=\"text-decoration: line-"
"through; font-weight: bold; color: red;\">red strikethrough</span> style for "
"removals or <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-weight: bold; "
"color: orange;\">orange underline</span> style for important points etc."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat na dathanna a chomhcheangal le stíleanna aibhsithe éagsúla "
"cosúil le <b>Fo-líne</b> agus <b>Líne Trí</b> chun córas aibhsithe "
"cumhachtach a chruthú. Mar shampla, is féidir leat stíl <span style=\"text-"
"decoration: line-through; font-weight: bold; color: red;\">líne dhearg tríd</"
"span> a úsáid le haghaidh bainte nó stíl <span style=\"text-decoration: "
"underline; font-weight: bold; color: orange;\">fo-líne oráiste</span> le "
"haghaidh pointí tábhachtacha srl."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2592-1
msgid "Setting the defaults for highlights"
msgstr "Socrú na réamhshocruithe le haghaidh buaicphointí"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2598-9
msgid ""
"In the highlights menu you can long-press on a highlight type to set it as "
"default (★)"
msgstr ""
"Sa roghchlár buaicphointí is féidir leat brú fada a choinneáil ar chineál "
"buaicphointí chun é a shocrú mar réamhshocrú (★)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2599-9
msgid ""
"<b>After selecting a color</b>, you can long-press on the color name in this "
"menu to set that color as default (★)"
msgstr ""
"<b>Tar éis dath a roghnú</b>, is féidir leat brúigh fhada ar ainm an datha "
"sa roghchlár seo chun an dath sin a shocrú mar réamhshocrú (★)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2600-9
msgid ""
"You can press the <span class=\"ui\">Apply current style and color to all "
"highlights</span> option to make all the highlights in the current book "
"same. <b>Be careful, there is no undo!</b>"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat an rogha <span class=\"ui\">Cuir an stíl agus an dath reatha "
"i bhfeidhm ar na buaicphointí go léir</span> a bhrú chun na buaicphointí go "
"léir sa leabhar reatha a dhéanamh mar an gcéanna. <b>Bí cúramach, níl aon "
"chealú ann!</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2605-5
msgid "NOTES:"
msgstr "NÓTAÍ:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2607-5
msgid ""
"You can also add notes to your highlights. Just tap on a highlight and "
"choose <span class=\"ui\">Add note</span> from the popup menu. You can also "
"choose a <span class=\"ui\">Note marker</span> that shows which highlights "
"contain a note. There are three styles: <span class=\"ui\">Underline, Side "
"line</span> and <span class=\"ui\">Side mark</span> (which is the pencil "
"icon shown on the right side of the picture below):"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat nótaí a chur le do bhuaicphointí freisin. Níl le déanamh ach "
"sconna ar bhuaicphointe agus <span class=\"ui\">Cuir nóta leis</span> a "
"roghnú ón roghchlár aníos. Is féidir leat <span class=\"ui\">marcóir nóta</"
"span> a roghnú freisin a thaispeánann cé na buaicphointí ina bhfuil nóta. Tá "
"trí stíl ann: <span class=\"ui\">Fo-líne, Líne taobh</span> agus <span "
"class=\"ui\">Marc taobh</span> (is é sin an deilbhín peann luaidhe a "
"thaispeántar ar thaobh na láimhe deise den phictiúr thíos):"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2613-5
msgid ""
"To enable this feature and choose a <span class=\"ui\">Note marker</span> "
"style, go to:"
msgstr ""
"Chun an ghné seo a chumasú agus stíl <span class=\"ui\">marcóir nótaí</span> "
"a roghnú, téigh chuig:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2615-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Highlight style / Note marker"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Stíl aibhsithe / Marcóir nótaí"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2619-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-howtohighlight"
msgid "Highlight modes of KOReader"
msgstr "Aibhsigh modhanna KOReader"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2621-5
msgid "KOReader has two highlighting modes for different use cases:"
msgstr "Tá dhá mhodh aibhsithe ag KOReader le haghaidh cásanna úsáide éagsúla:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2626-1
msgid "Normal mode"
msgstr "Mód gnáth"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2628-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Normal mode</span> is similar to selecting a text with "
"your finger on a phone/tablet and more suitable if your highlights are "
"shorter than one page."
msgstr ""
"Tá an modh <span class=\"ui\">Gnáthmhód</span> cosúil le téacs a roghnú le "
"do mhéar ar ghuthán/táibléad agus tá sé níos oiriúnaí má tá do chuid "
"buaicphointí níos giorra ná leathanach amháin."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2631-9
msgid "Long-press on the starting word"
msgstr "Brúigh go fada ar an bhfocal tosaigh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2632-9
msgid "Move your finger to the end of the passage"
msgstr "Bog do mhéar go dtí deireadh an phasáiste"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2633-9
msgid "Release finger"
msgstr "Scaoil an méar"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2636-5
msgid ""
"When you reach page boundaries, KOReader will turn the page for you to "
"continue highlighting <b>(only in EPUB/HTML documents)</b>. You can disable "
"this feature from:"
msgstr ""
"Nuair a shroicheann tú teorainneacha leathanaigh, casfaidh KOReader an "
"leathanach ionas gur féidir leat leanúint ar aghaidh ag airdiú <b>(i "
"ndoiciméid EPUB/HTML amháin)</b>. Is féidir leat an ghné seo a dhíchumasú ó:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2638-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Taps and gestures / Long-press on text / Auto-"
"scroll when selection reaches a corner"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Tapálacha agus gothaí / Brúigh ar théacs / "
"Scrollaigh go huathoibríoch nuair a shroicheann an rogha cúinne"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2642-1
msgid "Select and highlight mode"
msgstr "Mód roghnaithe agus aibhsithe"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2644-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Select and highlight mode</span> is more suitable for "
"highlighting longer passages which cross page boundaries. It might also work "
"better if you have touch screen sensitivity problems or motor control issues "
"with your hands. Because in this highlight mode you don’t need to drag your "
"finger along the screen."
msgstr ""
"Tá an modh <span class=\"ui\">Roghnaigh agus Aibhsigh</span> níos oiriúnaí "
"chun pasáistí níos faide a sháraíonn teorainneacha leathanaigh a aibhsiú. "
"D’fhéadfadh sé go n-oibreodh sé níos fearr freisin má tá fadhbanna agat le "
"híogaireacht an scáileáin tadhaill nó fadhbanna rialaithe mótair le do "
"lámha. Mar sa mhodh aibhsigh seo ní gá duit do mhéar a tharraingt feadh an "
"scáileáin."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2646-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">INFO</span> If you have dictionary lookup "
"enabled, when you long-press a word, you have to drag your finger to "
"initiate this mode."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">EOLAS</span> Má tá cuardach foclóra cumasaithe "
"agat, nuair a bhrúnn tú focal ar feadh i bhfad, caithfidh tú do mhéar a "
"tharraingt chun an mód seo a thionscnamh."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2648-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Taps and gestures / Long-press on text / Dictionary "
"on single word selection"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Tapálacha agus gothaí / Brúigh fada ar théacs / "
"Foclóir ar roghnú focal aonair"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2652-5
msgid "How to highlight:"
msgstr "Conas aird a tharraingt ar:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2657-5
msgid ""
"Long-press (or drag if dictionary lookup is enabled as described above) on "
"the starting word, popup menu will show up."
msgstr ""
"Brúigh go fada (nó tarraing má tá cuardach foclóra cumasaithe mar a "
"thuairiscítear thuas) ar an bhfocal tosaigh, agus taispeánfar roghchlár "
"aníos."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2658-5
msgid ""
"Tap on <span class=\"ui\">Select</span>, now you are in highlighting mode. "
"When you are in this mode, you will see an indicator at the upper left "
"corner of the screen (which you can tap on it to get more information). You "
"can cancel highlighting by tapping on the beginning of highlight again. You "
"can turn pages with taps/swipes and freely navigate the document (TOC, skim "
"etc) in this mode."
msgstr ""
"Beartaíonn ar <span class=\"ui\">Roghnaigh</span>, tá tú i mód aibhsithe "
"anois. Nuair atá tú sa mhodh seo, feicfidh tú táscaire sa chúinne uachtarach "
"ar chlé den scáileán (ar féidir leat tapáil air chun tuilleadh eolais a "
"fháil). Is féidir leat an aibhsiú a chealú trí thapáil ar thús an aibhsithe "
"arís. Is féidir leat leathanaigh a chasadh le tapálacha/svaipeanna agus "
"nascleanúint a dhéanamh go saor tríd an doiciméad (ábhar ábhair, scimeáil "
"srl.) sa mhodh seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2659-5
msgid ""
"Long-press (or drag if dictionary lookup is enabled as described above) on "
"the ending word for your highlight, menu will show up again."
msgstr ""
"Brúigh go fada (nó tarraing má tá cuardach foclóra cumasaithe mar a "
"thuairiscítear thuas) ar an bhfocal deiridh le haghaidh d’aibhsithe, "
"taispeánfar an roghchlár arís."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2660-5
msgid ""
"Tap <span class=\"ui\">Highlight</span> this time to finish highlighting the "
"passage."
msgstr ""
"Tapáil <span class=\"ui\">Aibhsigh</span> an uair seo chun an sliocht a "
"aibhsiú a chríochnú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2663-5
msgid ""
"This dialog normally opens at the center of the screen. If you want this "
"dialog to open closer to your highlight location, you can change the <span "
"class=\"ui\">center</span> option here to <span class=\"ui\">gesture "
"position</span> (located on the second page of this menu):"
msgstr ""
"De ghnáth, osclaítear an dialóg seo i lár an scáileáin. Más mian leat an "
"dialóg seo a oscailt níos gaire le do shuíomh aibhsithe, is féidir leat an "
"rogha <span class=\"ui\">lár</span> anseo a athrú go <span "
"class=\"ui\">suíomh gotha</span> (atá suite ar an dara leathanach den "
"roghchlár seo):"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2665-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\">/ Taps and Gestures / Long-press on text / Highlight "
"dialog position"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\">/ Tapálacha agus Gothaí / Brúigh ar théacs / Aibhsigh "
"suíomh an dialóige"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2667-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">TIP</span> There is a <b>faster</b> method for "
"this mode if you don’t need <b>long-press menu items</b> shown above. You "
"can disable the popup menu completely so when you long-press on a word you "
"will immediately enter the <span class=\"ui\">Select and highlight</span> "
"mode. This method is much faster and you can highlight any length of text "
"with just two taps. To use this method enable this option:"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">LEID</span> Tá modh <b>níos tapúla</b> ann don "
"mhodh seo mura bhfuil na míreanna roghchláir <b>brúigh fhada</b> atá "
"léirithe thuas uait. Is féidir leat an roghchlár aníos a dhíchumasú go "
"hiomlán ionas go rachaidh tú isteach sa mhodh <span class=\"ui\">Roghnaigh "
"agus aibhsigh</span> láithreach nuair a bhrúnn tú ar fhocal. Tá an modh seo "
"i bhfad níos tapúla agus is féidir leat aon fhad téacs a aibhsiú le dhá "
"sconna amháin. Chun an modh seo a úsáid, cumasaigh an rogha seo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div:2669-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Taps and gestures / Long-press on text / Select and "
"highlight"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Tapálacha agus gothaí / Brúigh ar théacs / "
"Roghnaigh agus aibhsigh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2675-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">TIP</span> KOReader can highlight a passage in "
"different styles. If you use <span class=\"ui\">Lighten</span> option, text "
"background will be gray. Due to e-ink limitations, screens can’t change from "
"white to gray directly, so highlighted part first has to turn black and then "
"gray. If you want to avoid this flashing, you can choose <span "
"class=\"ui\">Inverted</span> as your highlight style. In this mode text "
"background will be black so it can be set without flashing. You can adjust "
"these highlighting options from:"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">LEID</span> Is féidir le KOReader sliocht a "
"aibhsiú i stíleanna éagsúla. Má úsáideann tú an rogha <span "
"class=\"ui\">Éadromaigh</span>, beidh cúlra an téacs liath. Mar gheall ar "
"theorainneacha dúigh leictreonacha, ní féidir le scáileáin athrú ó bhán go "
"liath go díreach, mar sin caithfidh an chuid atá aibhsithe dul dubh ar dtús "
"agus ansin liath. Más mian leat an splancadh seo a sheachaint, is féidir "
"leat <span class=\"ui\">Inbhéartaithe</span> a roghnú mar do stíl aibhsithe. "
"Sa mhodh seo beidh cúlra an téacs dubh ionas gur féidir é a shocrú gan "
"splancadh. Is féidir leat na roghanna aibhsithe seo a choigeartú ó:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div:2677-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.div.div:2677-5"
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Highlight style"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Stíl Aibhsithe"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2682-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">TIP</span> You can add multiple highlights and "
"notes to the same section of text. If they are overlapping, when you tap on "
"a highlight you will be presented with a menu to choose which highlight you "
"want to edit."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">LEID</span> Is féidir leat roinnt buaicphointí "
"agus nótaí a chur leis an gcuid chéanna den téacs. Má tá siad ag forluí, "
"nuair a thapálann tú ar bhuaicphointe cuirfear roghchlár i láthair duit chun "
"a roghnú cén bhuaicphointe is mian leat a chur in eagar."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2686-1
msgid "Selecting punctuation while highlighting"
msgstr "Poncaíocht a roghnú agus aibhsiú á dhéanamh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2688-5
msgid ""
"When you are highlighting, KOReader tries to include the related punctuation "
"marks around your selection. For example if you highlight from the first "
"word to the last word of a sentence, KOReader will automatically include the "
"punctuation marks at the both ends of the sentence to your highlight."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a bhíonn tú ag aibhsiú, déanann KOReader iarracht na marcanna "
"poncaíochta gaolmhara a chur timpeall ar do rogha. Mar shampla, má dhéanann "
"tú aibhsiú ón gcéad fhocal go dtí an focal deireanach d’abairt, cuirfidh "
"KOReader na marcanna poncaíochta ag an dá cheann den abairt san áireamh go "
"huathoibríoch i do aibhsiú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2691-5
msgid ""
"But if you start highlighting from the middle of a sentence, period at the "
"end <b>will not be included</b> because KOReader assumes that you want to "
"make a partial highlight. So if you want the punctuation marks to be added "
"to your highlight, be sure that you select the <b>whole sentence</b>. Also "
"you can add these marks later by long pressing the <span "
"class=\"ui\">Highlight edit</span> buttons."
msgstr ""
"Ach má thosaíonn tú ag aibhsiú ó lár abairte, ní chuirfear ponc ag an "
"deireadh <b>san áireamh</b> mar glacann KOReader leis gur mian leat cuid den "
"aibhsiú a dhéanamh. Mar sin, más mian leat na marcanna poncaíochta a chur le "
"d’aibhsiú, déan cinnte go roghnaíonn tú an <b>abairt iomlán</b>. Chomh maith "
"leis sin, is féidir leat na marcanna seo a chur leis níos déanaí trí bhrú "
"fada a chur ar na cnaipí <span class=\"ui\">Eagarthóireacht Aibhsithe</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2694-1
msgid "Editing highlights"
msgstr "Buaicphointí á n-eagarthóireacht"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2696-5
msgid ""
"When you tap on an already highlighted text <b>(without a note)</b>, you "
"will see this popup menu. <span class=\"ui\">Delete</span> and <span "
"class=\"ui\">Add note</span> items are clear. Bottom row menu items are used "
"to extend or shrink the highlight."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a thapaíonn tú ar théacs atá aibhsithe cheana féin <b>(gan nóta)</b>, "
"feicfidh tú an roghchlár aníos seo. Tá na míreanna <span "
"class=\"ui\">Scrios</span> agus <span class=\"ui\">Cuir nóta leis</span> "
"soiléir. Úsáidtear míreanna roghchláir sa tsraith íochtarach chun an aibhsiú "
"a leathnú nó a chrapadh."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2700-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">INFO</span> This adjustment works only on "
"reflowable documents like EPUBs. If you want to extend or shrink a highlight "
"on PDFs, you have to delete it and highlight again due to the limitations of "
"the PDF format."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">EOLAS</span> Ní oibríonn an coigeartú seo ach ar "
"dhoiciméid in-athshreabhta ar nós EPUBanna. Más mian leat aibhsiú ar PDFanna "
"a leathnú nó a chrapadh, caithfidh tú é a scriosadh agus aibhsiú arís mar "
"gheall ar theorainneacha fhormáid PDF."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2702-5
msgid ""
"When you tap on an already highlighted text <b>with a note added</b>, you "
"will see this popup menu. Tap on <span class=\"ui\">Edit highlight</span> to "
"open the menu above where you can edit both the highlight and the contained "
"note:"
msgstr ""
"Nuair a thapaíonn tú ar théacs atá aibhsithe cheana féin <b>agus nóta curtha "
"leis</b>, feicfidh tú an roghchlár aníos seo. Tapáil ar <span "
"class=\"ui\">Cuir aibhsiú in Eagar</span> chun an roghchlár thuas a oscailt "
"inar féidir leat an aibhsiú agus an nóta atá ann a chur in eagar:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2706-5
msgid ""
"On your <span class=\"ui\">Bookmarks</span> page you can filter the view to "
"see only one type of bookmark by pressing the menu icon ( <img "
"class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_hamburger.svg\" style=\"width:22px;"
"\"> ) You can also filter by highlight style:"
msgstr ""
"Ar do leathanach <span class=\"ui\">Leabharmharcanna</span> is féidir leat "
"an radharc a scagadh chun cineál amháin leabharmharc a fheiceáil trí bhrú ar "
"dheilbhín an roghchláir ( <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/"
"top_hamburger.svg\" style=\"width:22px;\"> ). Is féidir leat scagadh a "
"dhéanamh de réir stíl aibhsithe freisin:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2712-1
msgid "Editing the text of a highlight"
msgstr "Téacs buaicphointe á chur in eagar"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2714-5
msgid ""
"In addition to adding a note, KOReader also allows you to edit the "
"highlighted text itself that is shown in your <span class=\"ui\">Bookmarks "
"list</span>. In some situations this might be more useful than adding a note "
"to a highlight. For example imagine that you are reviewing a text. You want "
"to highlight a sentence which contains many dates and one of the dates is "
"wrong. When you want add a note to point to this mistake, you need to "
"specify in your note, which one is wrong. But if you edit the text of a "
"highlight, you can directly write <b>\"(this date needs to be checked)\"</b> "
"next to the problematic date."
msgstr ""
"Chomh maith le nóta a chur leis, tugann KOReader deis duit an téacs "
"aibhsithe féin a chur in eagar, téacs a thaispeántar i do <span "
"class=\"ui\">liosta Leabharmharcanna</span>. I gcásanna áirithe, d'fhéadfadh "
"sé seo a bheith níos úsáidí ná nóta a chur le haibhsiú. Mar shampla, "
"samhlaigh go bhfuil tú ag athbhreithniú téacs. Ba mhaith leat abairt a "
"aibhsiú ina bhfuil go leor dátaí agus go bhfuil ceann de na dátaí mícheart. "
"Nuair is mian leat nóta a chur leis chun aird a tharraingt ar an earráid "
"seo, ní mór duit a shonrú i do nóta cé acu ceann atá mícheart. Ach má "
"chuireann tú téacs an aibhsithe in eagar, is féidir leat <b>\"(ní mór an "
"dáta seo a sheiceáil)\"</b> a scríobh go díreach in aice leis an dáta "
"fadhbach."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2716-5
msgid ""
"Note that this editing <b>doesn't change</b> the book content or the "
"highlighted passage on the page. You will still see the same highlighted "
"sentence in the reader. Your edit will be visible in the <span "
"class=\"ui\">Bookmarks list</span>. And when you export your highlights "
"later, edited text will be the one that is exported."
msgstr ""
"Tabhair faoi deara <b>nach n-athraíonn</b> an eagarthóireacht seo ábhar an "
"leabhair ná an sliocht atá aibhsithe ar an leathanach. Feicfidh tú an abairt "
"chéanna atá aibhsithe sa léitheoir fós. Beidh d’eagarthóireacht le feiceáil "
"sa <span class=\"ui\">liosta Leabharmharcanna</span>. Agus nuair a dhéanann "
"tú d’aibhsithe a onnmhairiú níos déanaí, is é an téacs eagraithe a bheidh á "
"onnmhairiú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2718-5
msgid "To edit a highlight text, you can:"
msgstr "Chun téacs aibhsithe a chur in eagar, is féidir leat:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2720-13
msgid "Tap on the highlight"
msgstr "Tapáil ar an airdmharc"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2721-13
msgid "Tap <span class=\"ui\">Details</span> from the popup menu"
msgstr "Beartaíonn <span class=\"ui\">Sonraí</span> ón roghchlár aníos"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2722-13
msgid "Tap <span class=\"ui\">Edit text</span> from the details dialog"
msgstr "Tapáil <span class=\"ui\">Cuir téacs in Eagar</span> ón dialóg sonraí"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2726-9
msgid "Also you can do it from the Bookmarks window:"
msgstr "Is féidir leat é a dhéanamh ón bhfuinneog Leabharmharcanna freisin:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2729-9
msgid "Go to the <span class=\"ui\">Bookmarks list</span> via menu or gesture"
msgstr ""
"Téigh go dtí an <span class=\"ui\">liosta Leabharmharcanna</span> tríd an "
"roghchlár nó trí ghluaiseacht"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2730-9
msgid "Long press on the highlight you want to edit"
msgstr "Brúigh go fada ar an airdphointe is mian leat a chur in eagar"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2731-9
msgid "Press <span class=\"ui\">Edit text</span> in the menu"
msgstr "Brúigh <span class=\"ui\">Cuir téacs in eagar</span> sa roghchlár"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2732-9
msgid ""
"Change the text in the dialog and press the <span class=\"ui\">Save</span> "
"button"
msgstr ""
"Athraigh an téacs sa dialóg agus brúigh an cnaipe <span "
"class=\"ui\">Sábháil</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2735-5
msgid ""
"If you want to <b>revert</b> an edited text to the original highlight, "
"follow the steps above and at the step <b>3</b>, instead of <span "
"class=\"ui\">Edit text</span>, press the <span class=\"ui\">Reset text</"
"span> button."
msgstr ""
"Más mian leat téacs eagraithe a <b>fhilleadh</b> ar an aird bhunaidh, lean "
"na céimeanna thuas agus ag céim <b>3</b>, in ionad <span class=\"ui\">Téacs "
"a chur in eagar</span>, brúigh an cnaipe <span class=\"ui\">Téacs a "
"athshocrú</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2738-1
msgid "Changing how the added notes are shown in the Bookmarks List"
msgstr ""
"Athrú ar an gcaoi a léirítear na nótaí breise sa Liosta Leabharmharcanna"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2740-5
msgid ""
"Normally when you open the Bookmarks list, only the content of your "
"highlights are shown. If you added a note to a highlight, you will only see "
"a pencil icon in the Bookmarks list. You can long-press on an item in this "
"list to show (and edit) the added note. If you want to see the note text too "
"in your <span class=\"ui\">Bookmarks list</span> you can set it from here:"
msgstr ""
"De ghnáth nuair a osclaíonn tú an liosta Leabharmharcanna, ní thaispeántar "
"ach ábhar do bhuaicphointí. Má chuir tú nóta le buaicphointe, ní fheicfidh "
"tú ach deilbhín peann luaidhe sa liosta Leabharmharcanna. Is féidir leat brú "
"fada a chur ar mhír sa liosta seo chun an nóta breise a thaispeáint (agus a "
"chur in eagar). Más mian leat téacs an nóta a fheiceáil i do <span "
"class=\"ui\">liosta Leabharmharcanna</span> freisin, is féidir leat é a "
"shocrú as seo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2742-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Settings / Bookmarks / Show in items"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Socruithe / Leabharmharcanna / Taispeáin i míreanna"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2744-5
msgid "You can choose to show:"
msgstr "Is féidir leat rogha a dhéanamh na nithe seo a thaispeáint:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2746-9
msgid "<b>Only</b> highlight text (default behavior)"
msgstr "Aibhsigh téacs <b>Amháin</b> (iompar réamhshocraithe)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2747-9
msgid "<b>Both</b> highlight text and the note"
msgstr "Aibhsíonn an téacs <b>agus</b> an nóta araon"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2748-9
msgid "<b>Note if there is one</b>, otherwise highlight text"
msgstr "<b>Tabhair faoi deara má tá ceann ann</b>, nó cuir béim ar an téacs"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2751-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">TIP</span> Normally number of items in the "
"bookmarks window is static and divided equally. If you want a more flexible "
"layout, you can change the <span class=\"ui\">Max lines per bookmark</span> "
"setting from here:"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">LEID</span> De ghnáth bíonn líon na míreanna sa "
"fhuinneog leabharmharcanna statach agus roinnte go cothrom. Más mian leat "
"leagan amach níos solúbtha, is féidir leat an socrú <span "
"class=\"ui\">Uasmhéid línte in aghaidh an leabharmharc</span> a athrú anseo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div:2753-6
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Settings / Bookmarks / Max lines per bookmark"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_bookmark.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Socruithe / Leabharmharcanna / Uasmhéid línte in "
"aghaidh an leabharmhairc"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2757-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-exportinghighlights"
msgid "Exporting highlights"
msgstr "Ag easpórtáil buaicphointí"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2759-5
msgid ""
"After finishing a book, you can move it to a specific folder for archiving "
"or processing purposes. Enable <span class=\"ui\">Move to archive</span> "
"plugin and set your target directory in the plugin’s settings (<span "
"class=\"ui\">Set archive folder</span>). After this, you can move a book to "
"your archive folder using:"
msgstr ""
"Tar éis duit leabhar a chríochnú, is féidir leat é a bhogadh chuig fillteán "
"ar leith chun críocha cartlannúcháin nó próiseála. Cumasaigh an breiseán "
"<span class=\"ui\">Bog chuig cartlann</span> agus socraigh d'eolaire sprice "
"i socruithe an bhreiseáin (<span class=\"ui\">Socraigh fillteán cartlainne</"
"span>). Ina dhiaidh sin, is féidir leat leabhar a bhogadh chuig d'fhillteán "
"cartlainne ag baint úsáide as:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2763-9
msgid "<span class=\"ui\">Move to archive</span> plugin menu"
msgstr "Roghchlár breiseáin <span class=\"ui\">Bog go dtí an chartlann</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2764-9
msgid "With a gesture or"
msgstr "Le gotha nó"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2765-9
msgid "With a <span class=\"ui\">Quick Menu</span> entry"
msgstr "Le hiontráil <span class=\"ui\">Roghchlár Tapa</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2768-5
msgid ""
"KOReader provides different ways of exporting your highlights and notes from "
"your reader device:"
msgstr ""
"Cuireann KOReader bealaí éagsúla ar fáil chun do bhuaicphointí agus nótaí a "
"easpórtáil ó do ghléas léitheoirí:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2771-1
msgid "1. Export Highlights plugin"
msgstr "1. Breiseán Easpórtála Buaicphointí"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2773-5
msgid ""
"This versatile plugin can export your highlights to <b>local files</b> or "
"<b>online services</b>."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leis an mbreiseán ildánach seo do bhuaicphointí a onnmhairiú chuig "
"<b>comhaid áitiúla</b> nó chuig <b>seirbhísí ar líne</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2778-5
msgid "Local export"
msgstr "Easpórtáil áitiúil"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2780-5
msgid "You can export your highlights to your device in these file formats:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat do bhuaicphointí a onnmhairiú chuig do ghléas sna formáidí "
"comhaid seo a leanas:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2782-9
msgid "Text (.txt)"
msgstr "Téacs (.txt)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2783-9
msgid "HTML (.html)"
msgstr "HTML (.html)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2784-9
msgid "Markdown (.md)"
msgstr "Marcáil síos (.md)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2785-9
msgid "Kindle Clippings (.txt)"
msgstr "Gearrthóga Kindle (.txt)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2786-9
msgid "JSON (.json)"
msgstr "JSON (.json)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2789-5
msgid "You can choose your preferred export formats from:"
msgstr "Is féidir leat do fhormáidí easpórtála is fearr leat a roghnú as:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2791-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_tools.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Export Highlights / Choose formats and services"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_tools.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Easpórtáil Buaicphointí / Roghnaigh formáidí agus "
"seirbhísí"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2793-5
msgid "You can see the export location (and also change it if you want):"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat an suíomh onnmhairithe a fheiceáil (agus é a athrú freisin "
"más mian leat):"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2795-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_tools.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Export Highlights / Choose export folder"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_tools.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Easpórtáil Buaicphointí / Roghnaigh fillteán "
"easpórtála"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2799-5
msgid "Online services"
msgstr "Seirbhísí ar líne"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2801-5
msgid "You can also export to these services over the network:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat onnmhairiú chuig na seirbhísí seo thar an líonra freisin:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2804-9
msgid ""
"<a href=\"https://joplinapp.org/\">Joplin</a> - a note taking application"
msgstr ""
"<a href=\"https://joplinapp.org/\">Joplin</a> - feidhmchlár chun nótaí a "
"thógáil"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2805-9
msgid ""
"<a href=\"https://readwise.io/\">Readwise</a> - an online bookmarks/"
"highlights application"
msgstr ""
"<a href=\"https://readwise.io/\">Readwise</a> - feidhmchlár leabharmharcanna/"
"buaicphointí ar líne"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2806-9
msgid ""
"<a href=\"https://github.com/usememos/memos\">Memos</a> - a self-hosted open "
"source memo hub"
msgstr ""
"<a href=\"https://github.com/usememos/memos\">Memos</a> - mol meamram foinse "
"oscailte féinóstáilte"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2807-9
msgid ""
"<a href=\"https://flomoapp.com\">Flomo</a> - an online note taking service"
msgstr "<a href=\"https://flomoapp.com\">Flomo</a> - seirbhís nótaí ar líne"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2809-9
msgid ""
"<a href=\"https://www.xmnote.com/\">XMNote</a> - an Android bookmark "
"organizer in Chinese language"
msgstr ""
"<a href=\"https://www.xmnote.com/\">XMNote</a> - eagraí leabharmharcanna "
"Android i Sínis"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2816-5
msgid ""
"You can find detailed setup instructions for these services on our related "
"<a href=\"https://github.com/koreader/koreader/wiki/Highlight-export\">wiki "
"page</a>."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat treoracha mionsonraithe maidir le socrú na seirbhísí seo a "
"fháil ar ár <a href=\"https://github.com/koreader/koreader/wiki/Highlight-"
"export\">leathanach vicí</a> gaolmhar."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2820-5
msgid ""
"After selecting your formats, you can export the notes for the <b>current "
"book</b> or <b>all the books in your library</b> from the same plugin menu."
msgstr ""
"Tar éis duit do fhormáidí a roghnú, is féidir leat na nótaí don <b>leabhar "
"reatha</b> nó do <b>na leabhair uile i do leabharlann</b> a onnmhairiú ón "
"roghchlár breiseán céanna."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2821-5
msgid ""
"If you want to export only some of the books in your library, you can do "
"this from the <span class=\"ui\">File Browser</span>:"
msgstr ""
"Más mian leat cuid de na leabhair i do leabharlann amháin a easpórtáil, is "
"féidir leat é seo a dhéanamh ón <span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span>:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2823-9
msgid "Select multiple books in the <span class=\"ui\">File Browser</span>"
msgstr "Roghnaigh il-leabhair sa <span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2824-9
msgid "Tap on the menu button (shown as a check mark) at the top right corner"
msgstr ""
"Beartaigh ar an gcnaipe roghchláir (a thaispeántar mar mharc seiceála) sa "
"chúinne uachtarach ar dheis"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:2825-9
msgid "Select <span class=\"ui\">Export highlights</span> from the menu shown"
msgstr ""
"Roghnaigh <span class=\"ui\">Easpórtáil buaicphointí</span> ón roghchlár a "
"thaispeántar"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2828-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">TIP</span> You can also export only some of "
"these highlight styles: <b>lighten, underline, strikeout, invert</b>. "
"Normally KOReader exports all of them. You can choose from:"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">LEID</span> Is féidir leat cuid de na stíleanna "
"aibhsithe seo a easpórtáil freisin: <b>éadromú, folíne, stríocadh amach, "
"inbhéartú</b>. De ghnáth easpórtálann KOReader iad uile. Is féidir leat "
"rogha a dhéanamh as:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div:2830-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_tools.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Export Highlights / Choose highlight styles"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_tools.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Easpórtáil Buaicphointí / Roghnaigh stíleanna "
"buaicphointí"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2834-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">TIP</span> You can assign export actions to "
"gestures for quicker access. You can find these under the <span "
"class=\"ui\">Reader</span> category of the <span class=\"ui\">Gesture "
"Manager</span>."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">LEID</span> Is féidir leat gníomhartha "
"easpórtála a shannadh do ghluaiseachtaí le haghaidh rochtain níos tapúla. Is "
"féidir leat iad seo a fháil faoin gcatagóir <span class=\"ui\">Léitheoir</"
"span> den <span class=\"ui\">Bainisteoir Gluaiseachtaí</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2839-1
msgid "2. Using KoHighlights"
msgstr "2. Ag Úsáid KoHighlights"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2841-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"external\">KoHighlights</span> is an external program that you "
"can install on your computer. It can access your book notes and highlights "
"when you plug your reader to your computer. Check the <a href=\"https://"
"github.com/noembryo/KoHighlights\">GitHub project page</a> for download and "
"instructions."
msgstr ""
"Is clár seachtrach é <span class=\"external\">KoHighlights</span> is féidir "
"leat a shuiteáil ar do ríomhaire. Is féidir leis rochtain a fháil ar nótaí "
"agus ar bhuaicphointí do leabhair nuair a nascann tú do léitheoir le do "
"ríomhaire. Seiceáil <a href=\"https://github.com/noembryo/"
"KoHighlights\">leathanach tionscadail GitHub</a> le haghaidh íoslódáil agus "
"treoracha."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2846-1
msgid "3. Using Calibre"
msgstr "3. Ag Úsáid Calibre"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2848-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"external\">Calibre</span> is an external program that you can "
"install on your computer. You can import highlights into your <span "
"class=\"external\">Calibre</span> database with its <span "
"class=\"external\">KOReader Sync</span> plugin. You can install the "
"mentioned plugin within the <span class=\"external\">Calibre</span> "
"application. Check the <a href=\"https://calibre-ebook.com/\">project page</"
"a> for download and instructions."
msgstr ""
"Is clár seachtrach é <span class=\"external\">Calibre</span> ar féidir leat "
"a shuiteáil ar do ríomhaire. Is féidir leat buaicphointí a allmhairiú "
"isteach i do bhunachar sonraí <span class=\"external\">Calibre</span> lena "
"bhreiseán <span class=\"external\">KOReader Sync</span>. Is féidir leat an "
"breiseán luaite a shuiteáil laistigh den fheidhmchlár <span "
"class=\"external\">Calibre</span>. Seiceáil an <a href=\"https://calibre-"
"ebook.com/\">leathanach tionscadail</a> le haghaidh íoslódáil agus treoracha."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2852-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">INFO</span> When you open a document in KOReader, "
"it creates a directory alongside the document with same name as the "
"document. This directory contains a .LUA file which includes all the "
"highlights, notes and user options (formatting properties etc.) related to "
"that document. You can manually backup/restore these directories."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">EOLAS</span> Nuair a osclaíonn tú doiciméad i "
"KOReader, cruthaítear eolaire taobh leis an doiciméad leis an ainm céanna "
"air. Tá comhad .LUA san eolaire seo ina bhfuil na buaicphointí, na nótaí "
"agus na roghanna úsáideora go léir (airíonna formáidithe srl.) a bhaineann "
"leis an doiciméad sin. Is féidir leat cúltaca/athchóiriú de láimh a dhéanamh "
"de na heolairí seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2859-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L1-pdfs"
msgid "READING PDFS"
msgstr "AG LÉAMH PDFANNA"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2861-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-readingpdfs"
msgid "Reading large PDFs on a small screen"
msgstr "Léamh PDFanna móra ar scáileán beag"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2862-5
msgid ""
"KOReader provides you many ways to read a PDF/DJVU document which is "
"optimized for bigger page sizes (generally A4 or Letter) on your smaller "
"screen device:"
msgstr ""
"Cuireann KOReader go leor bealaí ar fáil duit chun doiciméad PDF/DJVU a "
"léamh atá optamaithe do mhéideanna leathanaigh níos mó (A4 nó Letter de "
"ghnáth) ar do ghléas scáileáin níos lú:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2867-5
msgid "<b>1. You can enable </b><span class=\"ui\">Reflow</span>"
msgstr ""
"<b>1. Is féidir leat </b><span class=\"ui\">Athshreabhadh</span> a chumasú"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2869-5
msgid ""
"BOTTOM MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/bottom_font.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Reflow"
msgstr ""
"AN ROCHLÁR BUNA / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/bottom_font.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Athshreabhadh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2871-5
msgid ""
"Reflow tries to extract the text portion from your document (if it is "
"available) and format it as a single column. Results are generally "
"satisfactory. You can also set this as a <b>default</b> by tapping and "
"holding on it."
msgstr ""
"Déanann Reflow iarracht an chuid téacs a bhaint as do dhoiciméad (más ann "
"dó) agus é a fhormáidiú mar cholún aonair. Bíonn na torthaí sásúil i "
"gcoitinne. Is féidir leat é seo a shocrú mar <b>réamhshocrú</b> freisin trí "
"thapáil agus coinneáil air."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2875-2
msgid "<b>2. You can enable</b> <span class=\"ui\">Zoom To Content</span>"
msgstr ""
"<b>2. Is féidir leat a chumasú</b><span class=\"ui\">Zúmáil go dtí an t-"
"ábhar</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2877-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.div:2877-5"
msgid ""
"BOTTOM MENU / <img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/"
"bottom_fit.svg\" style=\"width:22px;\"> /"
msgstr ""
"AN ROCHLÁR BUNA / <img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/"
"bottom_fit.svg\" style=\"width:22px;\"> /"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2882-5
msgid ""
"With this option KOReader tries to crop margins from your document so text "
"can look bigger on your screen. You can set <span class=\"ui\">fit</span> to "
"<span class=\"ui\">width</span> in the same menu which will try to fit only "
"page width instead of whole page, so your text will look bigger."
msgstr ""
"Leis an rogha seo, déanann KOReader iarracht imill do dhoiciméid a bhearradh "
"ionas go mbeidh cuma níos mó ar an téacs ar do scáileán. Is féidir leat "
"<span class=\"ui\">oiriúnú</span> a shocrú go <span class=\"ui\">leithead</"
"span> sa roghchlár céanna a dhéanfaidh iarracht leithead an leathanaigh "
"amháin a fheistiú seachas an leathanach ar fad, ionas go mbeidh cuma níos mó "
"ar do théacs."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2886-5
msgid ""
"<b>3. You can try to use your device in </b><span class=\"ui\">Landscape "
"orientation</span>"
msgstr ""
"<b>3. Is féidir leat iarracht a dhéanamh do ghléas a úsáid i </b><span "
"class=\"ui\">treoshuíomh tírdhreacha</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2888-5
msgid ""
"This will make your screen wider so your document may look big enough to "
"read comfortably."
msgstr ""
"Déanfaidh sé seo do scáileán níos leithne ionas go mbeidh cuma mhór go leor "
"ar do dhoiciméad le léamh go compordach."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2890-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.div:2890-5"
msgid "BOTTOM MENU /"
msgstr "AN ROGHCHLÁR BUNA /"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2894-2
msgid ""
"4. You can zoom to 100 percent size and instead scroll the screen to read "
"different parts"
msgstr ""
"4. Is féidir leat súmáil isteach go méid 100 faoin gcéad agus ina ionad sin "
"scrollaigh an scáileán chun codanna éagsúla a léamh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2897-5
msgid ""
"This is especially helpful with comic books. First enable <span "
"class=\"ui\">column mode</span> from this menu item:"
msgstr ""
"Tá sé seo an-chabhrach go háirithe le leabhair ghrinn. Ar dtús, cumasaigh "
"<span class=\"ui\">mód colún</span> ón mír roghchláir seo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2899-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.div:2899-5"
msgid ""
"BOTTOM MENU / <img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/"
"bottom_fit.svg\" style=\"width:22px;\"> /"
msgstr ""
"AN ROCHLÁR BUNA / <img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/"
"bottom_fit.svg\" style=\"width:22px;\"> /"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2901-5
msgid ""
"Then select an appropriate flow direction for your document from the same "
"menu:"
msgstr "Ansin roghnaigh treo sreafa cuí le do dhoiciméad ón roghchlár céanna:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2907-9
msgid ""
"For example if you are reading an article which has two columns, you will "
"scroll down until the end of page reading left column then go to right upper "
"side to continue reading right column:"
msgstr ""
"Mar shampla, má tá tú ag léamh alt ina bhfuil dhá cholún, scrollaigh síos go "
"dtí deireadh an leathanaigh ag léamh an cholúin chlé agus ansin téigh go dtí "
"an taobh uachtarach ar dheis chun leanúint ar aghaidh ag léamh an cholúin "
"dheis:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2910-9
msgid ""
"Or if you are reading a comic book, you will want to go <b>“right / down "
"left / right”</b> in a zigzag pattern:"
msgstr ""
"Nó má tá tú ag léamh leabhar grinn, beidh tú ag iarraidh dul <b>“ar dheis / "
"síos ar chlé / ar dheis”</b> i bpatrún zigzag:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:2913-9
msgid ""
"For a Japanese comic book (right-to-left panel order) this might be the "
"reverse:"
msgstr ""
"I gcás leabhar grinn Seapánach (ord painéil ó dheis go clé) d'fhéadfadh sé "
"seo a bheith ina mhalairt:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2917-5
msgid ""
"In this mode you can also adjust <span class=\"ui\">Horizontal/Vertical "
"Overlap</span> and <span class=\"ui\">Number of Columns</span> from the same "
"menu to fit the text on your screen better. Feel free to experiment with "
"these settings."
msgstr ""
"Sa mhodh seo is féidir leat <span class=\"ui\">Forluí Cothrománach/"
"Ingearach</span> agus <span class=\"ui\">Líon na gColún</span> a choigeartú "
"ón roghchlár céanna chun go n-oirfidh an téacs níos fearr ar do scáileán. Ná "
"bíodh drogall ort triail a bhaint as na socruithe seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2919-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">TIP</span> When reading a PDF document, if you "
"are in a zoomed in view other than 100% (column, row or manual) or in the "
"<span class=\"ui\">reflow mode</span>, you can tap the top left corner of "
"screen to enter <span class=\"ui\">flip mode</span>. This mode temporarily "
"displays the full page without cropping, scaled to fit your screen. You can "
"turn the pages in this mode. To exit, tap on this icon."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">LEID</span> Agus doiciméad PDF á léamh agat, má "
"tá tú i radharc súmáilte isteach seachas 100% (colún, sraith nó lámhleabhar) "
"nó sa <span class=\"ui\">mód athshreafa</span>, is féidir leat tapáil ar "
"chúinne uachtarach na láimhe clé den scáileán chun dul isteach i <span "
"class=\"ui\">mód smeach</span>. Taispeánann an mód seo an leathanach iomlán "
"go sealadach gan bhearradh, scálaithe chun freastal ar do scáileán. Is "
"féidir leat na leathanaigh a chasadh sa mhodh seo. Chun imeacht, tapáil ar "
"an deilbhín seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2921-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-pdfbottom"
msgid "PDF Specific Bottom Menu Items"
msgstr "Míreanna Bun-Roghchláir Sainmhínithe PDF"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2926-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Contrast</span> setting adjusts black levels in your "
"document. Be aware that same contrast value applies to both text and images "
"in your document. If you set it very high, your images may become too dark."
msgstr ""
"Coigeartaíonn an socrú <span class=\"ui\">Codarsnacht</span> leibhéil dhubha "
"i do dhoiciméad. Bíodh a fhios agat go mbaineann an luach codarsnachta "
"céanna le téacs agus íomhánna i do dhoiciméad. Má shocraíonn tú an-ard é, "
"d'fhéadfadh do íomhánna a bheith ró-dhorcha."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2928-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Dewatermark</span> removes watermarks from the rendered "
"document. It can also be used to remove gray backgrounds. This feature can "
"convert a grayscale or color document to black & white to produce more "
"contrast for easier reading."
msgstr ""
"Baintear uiscemharcanna as an doiciméad rindreáilte le <span "
"class=\"ui\">Dewatermark</span>. Is féidir é a úsáid freisin chun cúlraí "
"liatha a bhaint. Is féidir leis an ngné seo doiciméad liathscála nó daite a "
"thiontú go dubh agus bán chun codarsnacht níos fearr a tháirgeadh le "
"haghaidh léitheoireachta níos éasca."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2930-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Render quality</span> <b>(only active in Reflow mode)</b> "
"sets the quality of text and image extraction processing and output. <span "
"class=\"ui\">High</span> is more pleasing but it can be much slower (several "
"seconds for page turn) than <span class=\"ui\">default</span> depending on "
"your document. If your PDF/DJVU files are slow, this is the first setting "
"you should check."
msgstr ""
"Socraíonn <span class=\"ui\">Cáilíocht rindreála</span> <b>(gníomhach i mód "
"Athshreabhadh amháin)</b> cáilíocht phróiseáil agus aschuir eastósctha téacs "
"agus íomhá. Tá <span class=\"ui\">Ard</span> níos taitneamhaí ach is féidir "
"leis a bheith i bhfad níos moille (roinnt soicind le haghaidh casadh "
"leathanaigh) ná an <span class=\"ui\">réamhshocrú</span> ag brath ar do "
"dhoiciméad. Má tá do chuid comhad PDF/DJVU mall, seo an chéad socrú ba chóir "
"duit a sheiceáil."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2936-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Document language</span> sets the language that will be "
"used by the OCR engine."
msgstr ""
"Socraíonn <span class=\"ui\">Teanga an doiciméid</span> an teanga a "
"úsáidfidh an t-inneall OCR."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2938-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Forced OCR</span> as the name says, forces the use of OCR "
"even if the document has a text layer."
msgstr ""
"Cuireann <span class=\"ui\">OCR Éigeantach</span>, mar a deir an t-ainm, "
"iallach ar OCR a úsáid fiú má tá ciseal téacs sa doiciméad."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2940-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Writing direction</span> <b>(only active in Reflow mode)</"
"b> sets the direction of original document. Set this to <b>RTL</b> for "
"languages like Arabic and Hebrew."
msgstr ""
"Socraíonn <span class=\"ui\">Treo na scríbhneoireachta</span> <b>(gníomhach "
"i mód Athshreabhadh amháin)</b> treo an doiciméid bhunaidh. Socraigh é seo "
"go <b>RTL</b> do theangacha cosúil le Araibis agus Eabhrais."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2942-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Document columns</span> <b>(only active in Reflow mode)</"
"b> sets the number of text columns in the original document."
msgstr ""
"Socraíonn <span class=\"ui\">Colúin an doiciméid</span> <b>(gníomhach i mód "
"Athshreabhadh amháin)</b> líon na gcolún téacs sa bhun-dhoiciméad."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2948-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Auto straighten</span> feature can straighten the pages "
"of a problematic document, for example pages of a PDF which are scanned with "
"an angle. It is available in <b>PDF, DJVU, CBZ/CBT</b> documents and "
"<b>image</b> files. To enable, choose the maximum tilt angle which KOReader "
"will try to correct. If it doesn’t correct you might have to choose a bigger "
"angle. Note that this feature <b>might slow down your reader</b> depending "
"on several factors."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leis an ngné <span class=\"ui\">Uathdhíreach</span> leathanaigh "
"doiciméad fadhbach a dhíriú, mar shampla leathanaigh PDF atá scanta le "
"huillinn. Tá sé ar fáil i ndoiciméid <b>PDF, DJVU, CBZ/CBT</b> agus i "
"gcomhaid <b>íomhá</b>. Chun é a chumasú, roghnaigh an uillinn chlaonta uasta "
"a dhéanfaidh KOReader iarracht a cheartú. Mura gceartaíonn sé, b'fhéidir go "
"mbeidh ort uillinn níos mó a roghnú. Tabhair faoi deara go bhféadfadh an "
"ghné seo <b>do léitheoir a mhoilliú</b> ag brath ar roinnt fachtóirí."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2953-1
msgid "Saving highlights into PDF"
msgstr "Sábháil buaicphointí i bhformáid PDF"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2955-5
msgid ""
"For saving your highlights, you can use the <span class=\"ui\">Export "
"highlights</span> feature of KOReader which is explained in a previous "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Chun do bhuaicphointí a shábháil, is féidir leat an ghné <span "
"class=\"ui\">Easpórtáil buaicphointí</span> de KOReader a úsáid, rud a "
"mhínítear i roinn roimhe seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2956-5
msgid ""
"If you are making your highlights on a PDF document, KOReader can also save "
"them directly to the PDF file. This can be useful in certain situations "
"because with this method, your highlights become a part of the PDF file. "
"This means you can see them on other applications or platforms without "
"installing KOReader. For example if you are sending a file with highlights "
"to another user, they don't have to install KOReader to see your highlights. "
"You can just send the PDF file with your highlights saved into it and they "
"can open and see them with a <b>compatible</b> PDF reader."
msgstr ""
"Má tá tú ag déanamh do bhuaicphointí ar dhoiciméad PDF, is féidir le "
"KOReader iad a shábháil go díreach chuig an gcomhad PDF freisin. Is féidir "
"leis seo a bheith úsáideach i gcásanna áirithe mar leis an modh seo, bíonn "
"do bhuaicphointí mar chuid den chomhad PDF. Ciallaíonn sé seo gur féidir "
"leat iad a fheiceáil ar fheidhmchláir nó ardáin eile gan KOReader a "
"shuiteáil. Mar shampla, má tá tú ag seoladh comhad le buaicphointí chuig "
"úsáideoir eile, ní gá dóibh KOReader a shuiteáil chun do bhuaicphointí a "
"fheiceáil. Is féidir leat an comhad PDF le do bhuaicphointí sábháilte ann a "
"sheoladh agus is féidir leo iad a oscailt agus a fheiceáil le léitheoir PDF "
"<b>comhoiriúnach</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.p:2958-24
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_red\">WARNING</span> If you are using the <span "
"class=\"ui\">Progress Sync</span> plugin, saving PDF highlights will change "
"your file so your synchronization will fail. If you are planning to use both "
"features, in the <span class=\"ui\">Progress Sync</span> plugin's settings, "
"change the <span class=\"ui\">Document matching method</span> to <span "
"class=\"ui\">Filename</span> instead of the default <span "
"class=\"ui\">Binary</span> matching:"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_red\">RABHADH</span> Má tá tú ag úsáid an bhreiseáin "
"<span class=\"ui\">Progress Sync</span>, athróidh sábháil buaicphointí PDF "
"do chomhad agus mar sin teipfidh ar do shioncrónú. Má tá sé beartaithe agat "
"an dá ghné a úsáid, i socruithe an bhreiseáin <span class=\"ui\">Progress "
"Sync</span>, athraigh an <span class=\"ui\">modh meaitseála doiciméad</span> "
"go <span class=\"ui\">Ainm comhaid</span> in ionad an mheaitseála "
"réamhshocraithe <span class=\"ui\">Dénártha</span>:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.p.div:2959-9
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_tools.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Progress sync / Document matching method"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_tools.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Sioncrónú dul chun cinn / Modh meaitseála doiciméad"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2964-5
msgid "Which PDF readers can show these highlights?"
msgstr "Cé na léitheoirí PDF ar féidir leo na buaicphointí seo a thaispeáint?"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2965-5
msgid ""
"PDF readers generally depend on some standard libraries to render PDF files. "
"Two of the most known PDF libraries are <b>MuPDF</b> and <b>Poppler</b> "
"libraries. KOReader uses the <b>MuPDF</b> library, so the highlights written "
"to PDFs in KOReader are not currently visible on PDF readers which uses the "
"<b>Poppler</b> library. You can find a compatibility list below. ✅ means "
"you can see your KOReader highlights in this application, ❌ means you can't "
"see them. And ⚠️ means the application needs some plugin to show them. List "
"is ordered alphabetically within categories."
msgstr ""
"Go ginearálta, bíonn léitheoirí PDF ag brath ar roinnt leabharlanna "
"caighdeánacha chun comhaid PDF a rindreáil. Is iad dhá cheann de na "
"leabharlanna PDF is cáiliúla ná leabharlanna <b>MuPDF</b> agus <b>Poppler</"
"b>. Úsáideann KOReader an leabharlann <b>MuPDF</b>, mar sin níl na "
"buaicphointí a scríobhtar chuig PDFanna i KOReader le feiceáil faoi láthair "
"ar léitheoirí PDF a úsáideann an leabharlann <b>Poppler</b>. Is féidir leat "
"liosta comhoiriúnachta a fháil thíos. Ciallaíonn ✅ gur féidir leat do "
"bhuaicphointí KOReader a fheiceáil san fheidhmchlár seo, ciallaíonn ❌ nach "
"féidir leat iad a fheiceáil. Agus ciallaíonn ⚠️ go bhfuil breiseán éigin ag "
"teastáil ón bhfeidhmchlár chun iad a thaispeáint. Tá an liosta ordaithe go "
"haibítreach laistigh de na catagóirí."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.p:2967-32
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_red\">WARNING</span> This list is not complete and might "
"not be up to date. So we suggest you to test the compatibility yourself. "
"Simply make a highlight in KOReader, write it into the PDF file and try "
"opening the file on your intended reader to check if the highlight is "
"visible."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_red\">RABHADH</span> Níl an liosta seo iomlán agus "
"b'fhéidir nach bhfuil sé cothrom le dáta. Mar sin molaimid duit an "
"comhoiriúnacht a thástáil tú féin. Níl le déanamh ach aird a tharraingt i "
"KOReader, é a scríobh isteach sa chomhad PDF agus déan iarracht an comhad a "
"oscailt ar an léitheoir atá beartaithe agat chun a sheiceáil an bhfuil an "
"aird le feiceáil."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.ul.li:2971-13
msgid "✅ Chrome Browser (All platforms)"
msgstr "✅ Brabhsálaí Chrome (Gach ardán)"

