#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:2989-9
msgid "Important information about saving PDF highlights feature"
msgstr "Faisnéis thábhachtach faoi ghné buaicphointí PDF a shábháil"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2990-9
msgid ""
"Since making highlights for later usage can involve significant effort, if "
"you are planning to use this feature, you should understand how it works in "
"order to avoid frustrating situations."
msgstr ""
"Ós rud é gur féidir go mbeadh iarracht mhór i gceist le haibhsithe a chruthú "
"le húsáid níos déanaí, má tá sé ar intinn agat an ghné seo a úsáid, ba "
"cheart duit tuiscint a fháil ar an gcaoi a n-oibríonn sí chun cásanna "
"frustracha a sheachaint."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2992-9
msgid ""
"<b>QUICK SUMMARY:</b> If you want to be able to delete or export your PDF "
"highlights later, you have to copy the <span class=\"ui\">.sdr folder</span> "
"associated with your book when you backup or copy your book to other "
"devices. Without this folder, KOReader can still show the saved highlights "
"but it can't know where they are in the file, so it can't modify them. "
"Please continue reading for more information about this."
msgstr ""
"<b>ACHOIMRE THAPA:</b> Más mian leat a bheith in ann do bhuaicphointí PDF a "
"scriosadh nó a easpórtáil níos déanaí, ní mór duit an fillteán <span "
"class=\"ui\">.sdr</span> a bhaineann le do leabhar a chóipeáil nuair a "
"dhéanann tú cúltaca de do leabhar nó nuair a chóipeálann tú é chuig "
"gléasanna eile. Gan an fillteán seo, is féidir le KOReader na buaicphointí "
"sábháilte a thaispeáint fós ach ní féidir leis a fháil amach cá bhfuil siad "
"sa chomhad, mar sin ní féidir leis iad a mhodhnú. Lean ort ag léamh le "
"haghaidh tuilleadh eolais faoi seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2996-9
msgid "How normal highlights work in KOReader"
msgstr "Conas a oibríonn gnáth-aibhsithe i KOReader"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:2998-9
msgid ""
"When you make a highlight in KOReader, whether the document is an EPUB or "
"PDF, this highlight is written into a settings file. For example if you are "
"reading <b>Alice in Wonderland.epub</b> you will have a folder named <span "
"class=\"ui\">Alice in Wonderland.sdr</span> in the same folder as your book. "
"Your highlights will be kept in a file under this <span class=\"ui\">.sdr "
"folder</span>. Which means, if you delete this <span class=\"ui\">.sdr "
"folder</span> which is associated with your book, you will lose your "
"highlights."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a dhéanann tú aibhsiú i KOReader, bíodh an doiciméad ina EPUB nó ina "
"PDF, scríobhtar an aibhsiú seo i gcomhad socruithe. Mar shampla, má tá tú ag "
"léamh <b>Alice in Wonderland.epub</b> beidh fillteán agat darb ainm <span "
"class=\"ui\">Alice in Wonderland.sdr</span> san fhillteán céanna le do "
"leabhar. Coinneofar do aibhsiú i gcomhad faoin bhfillteán <span "
"class=\"ui\">.sdr</span> seo. Ciallaíonn sé sin, má scriosann tú an fillteán "
"<span class=\"ui\">.sdr</span> seo atá bainteach le do leabhar, caillfidh tú "
"do aibhsiú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3002-9
msgid "How PDF highlights work in KOReader"
msgstr "Conas a oibríonn buaicphointí PDF i KOReader"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3003-9
msgid ""
"PDF highlights feature works a bit different than the description above. As "
"we mentioned before, when you save your PDF highlights, they will be "
"directly written into the PDF file, which means they become a part of the "
"file itself. That's why you can send this PDF to another user and they can "
"see the highlights with a compatible PDF reader. They won't need your <span "
"class=\"ui\">.sdr folder</span> which contains a record of your highlights "
"because now the highlights are embedded directly into the PDF file."
msgstr ""
"Oibríonn gné buaicphointí PDF beagán difriúil ón tuairisc thuas. Mar a luadh "
"cheana, nuair a shábhálann tú do bhuaicphointí PDF, scríobhfar iad go "
"díreach isteach sa chomhad PDF, rud a chiallaíonn go n-éiríonn siad mar "
"chuid den chomhad féin. Sin é an fáth gur féidir leat an PDF seo a sheoladh "
"chuig úsáideoir eile agus is féidir leo na buaicphointí a fheiceáil le "
"léitheoir PDF comhoiriúnach. Ní bheidh do fhillteán <span class=\"ui\">.sdr</"
"span> ina bhfuil taifead de do bhuaicphointí ag teastáil uathu mar anois tá "
"na buaicphointí leabaithe go díreach isteach sa chomhad PDF."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3005-9
msgid ""
"Let's explain the problem which can arise when you are using this feature, "
"on an example. Imagine that you are reading a PDF book on your <b>e-reader</"
"b> with KOReader:"
msgstr ""
"Mínímis an fhadhb a d'fhéadfadh teacht chun cinn agus an ghné seo á húsáid "
"agat, le sampla. Samhlaigh go bhfuil tú ag léamh leabhar PDF ar do "
"<b>léitheoir leictreonach</b> le KOReader:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3008-13
msgid ""
"You are making highlights and <span class=\"ui\">Save highlights to PDF</"
"span> option is enabled, so as you make these highlights, KOReader saves "
"them to your PDF file."
msgstr ""
"Tá tú ag déanamh buaicphointí agus tá an rogha <span class=\"ui\">Sábháil "
"buaicphointí go PDF</span> cumasaithe, mar sin de réir mar a dhéanann tú na "
"buaicphointí seo, sábhálann KOReader iad chuig do chomhad PDF."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3009-13
msgid ""
"You want to continue reading the book on your <b>phone</b> with KOReader, so "
"you copy this PDF file from your <b>e-reader</b> to your <b>phone</b> (but "
"you didn't copy the <span class=\"ui\">.sdr folder</span>, only the PDF "
"file)."
msgstr ""
"Ba mhaith leat leanúint ar aghaidh ag léamh an leabhair ar do <b>ghuthán</b> "
"le KOReader, mar sin cóipeálann tú an comhad PDF seo ó do <b>léitheoir "
"leictreonach</b> chuig do <b>ghuthán</b> (ach níor chóipeáil tú an fillteán "
"<span class=\"ui\">.sdr</span>, ach an comhad PDF amháin)."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3010-13
msgid ""
"When you open the book on your <b>phone</b> with KOReader, you will see that "
"your highlights are still there."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a osclaíonn tú an leabhar ar do <b>fhón</b> le KOReader, feicfidh tú "
"go bhfuil do chuid buaicphointí fós ann."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3013-9
msgid ""
"Now the situation on both of your devices looks identical. Both your <b>e-"
"reader</b> and <b>phone</b> KOReader shows the PDF file with the same "
"highlights. But it only <b>looks</b> identical, actually there is a big "
"difference."
msgstr ""
"Anois tá cuma chéanna ar an scéal ar an dá ghléas. Taispeánann KOReader do "
"<b>léitheoir leictreonach</b> agus do <b>fhón</b> an comhad PDF leis na "
"haibhsithe céanna. Ach níl ann ach <b>cuma</b> chéanna, i ndáiríre tá "
"difríocht mhór ann."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3015-9
msgid ""
"KOReader on your <b>e-reader</b> has the knowledge of which highlights in "
"this PDF file are made by KOReader because it has the <span "
"class=\"ui\">.sdr folder</span>. But KOReader on your phone doesn't have "
"this knowledge. It only has the PDF file."
msgstr ""
"Tá a fhios ag KOReader ar do <b>léitheoir leictreonach</b> cé na "
"buaicphointí sa chomhad PDF seo a rinne KOReader toisc go bhfuil an fillteán "
"<span class=\"ui\">.sdr</span> ann. Ach níl an t-eolas seo ag KOReader ar do "
"ghuthán. Níl ann ach an comhad PDF."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3017-9
msgid ""
"Difference arises when you try to delete the pdf highlights or export them. "
"Your <b>e-reader</b> can both delete these PDF highlights and export them. "
"But your <b>phone</b> KOReader can't, because as we said, it doesn't have "
"the <span class=\"ui\">.sdr folder</span> of your book so the highlights in "
"the book look like a part of the original book from its point of view."
msgstr ""
"Éiríonn difríocht nuair a dhéanann tú iarracht na buaicphointí pdf a "
"scriosadh nó iad a easpórtáil. Is féidir le do <b>léitheoir leictreonach</b> "
"na buaicphointí PDF seo a scriosadh agus iad a easpórtáil araon. Ach ní "
"féidir le do <b>fhón</b> KOReader é sin a dhéanamh, mar a dúirt muid, níl an "
"fillteán <span class=\"ui\">.sdr</span> de do leabhar aige, mar sin tá cuma "
"cuid den leabhar bunaidh ar na buaicphointí sa leabhar óna dhearcadh féin."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3019-9
msgid ""
"So in short, if you want to be able to delete or export your PDF highlights "
"later, you have to copy the <span class=\"ui\">.sdr folder</span> associated "
"with your book when you backup or copy your book to other devices."
msgstr ""
"Mar sin, i mbeagán focal, más mian leat a bheith in ann do bhuaicphointí PDF "
"a scriosadh nó a easpórtáil níos déanaí, ní mór duit an fillteán <span "
"class=\"ui\">.sdr</span> a bhaineann le do leabhar a chóipeáil nuair a "
"dhéanann tú cúltaca de do leabhar nó nuair a chóipeálann tú é chuig "
"gléasanna eile."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3023-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-ocr"
msgid "OCR (Optical Character Recognition)"
msgstr "OCR (Aithint Optúil Carachtar)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3024-5
msgid ""
"<b>OCR (Optical Character Recognition)</b> is the process of extracting text "
"from images. In KOReader context, it is generally used for extracting text "
"from scanned book pages in PDF files. KOReader relies on <a href=\"https://"
"github.com/tesseract-ocr/tessdoc\">Tesseract Open Source OCR Engine</a> for "
"this task."
msgstr ""
"Is éard atá i gceist le <b>OCR (Aithint Optúil Carachtar)</b> ná próiseas "
"chun téacs a bhaint as íomhánna. I gcomhthéacs KOReader, úsáidtear é go "
"ginearálta chun téacs a bhaint as leathanaigh leabhar scanta i gcomhaid PDF. "
"Braitheann KOReader ar <a href=\"https://github.com/tesseract-ocr/"
"tessdoc\">Inneall OCR Foinse Oscailte Tesseract</a> don tasc seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3027-5
msgid "To use this feature you need to:"
msgstr "Chun an ghné seo a úsáid ní mór duit:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3029-9
msgid ""
"Install <span class=\"external\">Tesseract</span> language data to your "
"KOReader"
msgstr ""
"Suiteáil sonraí teanga <span class=\"external\">Tesseract</span> ar do "
"KOReader"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3030-9
msgid ""
"Add newly installed languages to koreader/defaults.lua configuration file "
"(necessary only if your language is other than English or Chinese)"
msgstr ""
"Cuir teangacha nua-shuiteáilte leis an gcomhad cumraíochta koreader/"
"defaults.lua (riachtanach ach amháin má tá teanga eile agat seachas Béarla "
"nó Sínis)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3034-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">INFO</span> Buttons on OCR menu <b>will not "
"function</b> until you install the necessary Tesseract files. Details of "
"this process can be read in our <a href=\"https://github.com/koreader/"
"koreader/wiki/Dictionary-support#dictionary-lookups-in-scanned-"
"pages\">related wiki page</a>."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">EOLAS</span> <b>Ní fheidhmeoidh</b> na cnaipí ar "
"an roghchlár OCR go dtí go suiteálfaidh tú na comhaid Tesseract "
"riachtanacha.. Is féidir sonraí an phróisis seo a léamh ar ár <a "
"href=\"https://github.com/koreader/koreader/wiki/Dictionary-"
"support#dictionary-lookups-in-scanned-pages\">leathanach vicí gaolmhar</a>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3042-1
msgid "READING COMICS AND MANGA"
msgstr "AG LÉAMH GREANNÁIN AGUS MANGA"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3044-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-mangarefresh"
msgid "Adjusting the page refresh interval"
msgstr "Ag coigeartú an eatramh athnuachana leathanaigh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3046-5
msgid ""
"Comic books generally need more frequent page refreshes than the pure text "
"content. For normal text, you can set your page refresh interval to high "
"numbers without problem. But images can leave more residue and cause "
"ghosting, especially depending on the panel of your e-reader."
msgstr ""
"Go ginearálta bíonn gá le hathnuachan leathanaigh níos minice i leabhair "
"ghrinn ná mar a bhíonn i leabhair théacs íon. I gcás gnáththéacs, is féidir "
"leat eatramh athnuachana leathanaigh a shocrú go huimhreacha arda gan fadhb. "
"Ach is féidir le híomhánna níos mó iarmhair a fhágáil agus taibhsí a chur "
"faoi deara, go háirithe ag brath ar phainéal do léitheora r-phoist."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3048-5
msgid ""
"KOReader allows you to assign any gesture to switch to different refresh "
"rates. For example you can set <b>swipe up left edge</b> for <span "
"class=\"ui\">every page</span> refresh when reading comics and set <b>swipe "
"down left edge</b> for <span class=\"ui\">every x page</span> refresh for "
"text only books. So when you open a comic, you can switch to more frequent "
"refresh with a simple tap or swipe (or vice versa)."
msgstr ""
"Le KOReader is féidir leat aon ghluaiseacht a shannadh chun athrú go rátaí "
"athnuachana difriúla. Mar shampla, is féidir leat <b>swipeáil suas ar an "
"imeall clé</b> a shocrú le haghaidh athnuachan <span class=\"ui\">gach "
"leathanaigh</span> agus greannáin á léamh agat agus <b>swipeáil síos ar an "
"imeall clé</b> a shocrú le haghaidh athnuachan <span class=\"ui\">gach x "
"leathanach</span> le haghaidh leabhar téacs amháin. Mar sin, nuair a "
"osclaíonn tú greannán, is féidir leat athrú go hathnuachan níos minice le "
"sconna nó swipeáil shimplí (nó a mhalairt)."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3050-5
msgid "This action is under:"
msgstr "Tá an gníomh seo faoi:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3052-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Taps and Gestures / Gesture manager / Screen and "
"lights section / Full screen refresh rate"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Tapálacha agus Gothaí / Bainisteoir Gothaí / Rannóg "
"Scáileáin agus Soilse / Ráta Athnuachana Lánscáileáin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3056-1
msgid "Panel zoom feature"
msgstr "Gné súmáil painéil"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3058-5
msgid ""
"This feature makes reading comic books easier on smaller screens. You can "
"enable it while you are reading a <b>PDF, DJVU, CBZ or CBT</b> document via:"
msgstr ""
"Déanann an ghné seo léamh greannán níos éasca ar scáileáin níos lú. Is "
"féidir leat é a chumasú agus tú ag léamh doiciméad <b>PDF, DJVU, CBZ nó CBT</"
"b> trí:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3060-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Panel Zoom (manga/comic)"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Zúmáil Painéil (manga/greannán)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3062-5
msgid ""
"When this option is enabled, KOReader tries to find the boundaries of "
"rectangular panels on the screen. If you long-press on a panel, KOReader "
"zooms in and shows just that panel."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a bhíonn an rogha seo cumasaithe, déanann KOReader iarracht "
"teorainneacha painéal dronuilleogach a aimsiú ar an scáileán. Má bhrúnn tú "
"ar phainéal ar feadh tamaill fhada, zúmálann KOReader isteach agus "
"taispeánann sé an painéal sin amháin."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3064-5
msgid ""
"As you can guess, this feature works best with comics that has clean panel "
"boundaries. Also there is no <b>page turn</b> in this mode to jump to the "
"next panel due to this boundary problem. You have to close the zoomed in "
"panel and long-press on the next one. To do this, just <span "
"class=\"ui\">swipe down</span> this zoomed in panel. Also you can use any "
"<span class=\"ui\">multiswipe gesture</span> (any combination of up, down, "
"left, right) to exit this view."
msgstr ""
"Mar is féidir leat a thomhas, oibríonn an ghné seo is fearr le greannáin a "
"bhfuil teorainneacha glana painéil acu. Chomh maith leis sin, níl aon "
"<b>chasadh leathanaigh</b> sa mhodh seo chun léim go dtí an chéad phainéal "
"eile mar gheall ar an bhfadhb teorann seo. Caithfidh tú an painéal súmáilte "
"isteach a dhúnadh agus brúigh ar an gcéad cheann eile ar feadh tamaill. Chun "
"seo a dhéanamh, níl le déanamh ach <span class=\"ui\">swipeáil síos</span> "
"an painéal súmáilte isteach seo. Chomh maith leis sin, is féidir leat aon "
"<span class=\"ui\">ghluaiseacht il-swipe</span> (aon teaglaim de suas, síos, "
"ar chlé, ar dheis) a úsáid chun an radharc seo a fhágáil."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3066-5
msgid "Procedure can be seen below:"
msgstr "Is féidir an nós imeachta a fheiceáil thíos:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3070-5
msgid ""
"If you want to use this feature with other file types like EPUB, FB2, HTML "
"or image files, you should open the file with a different engine: In the "
"<span class=\"ui\">File Browser</span> long-tap on the file name, tap <span "
"class=\"ui\">Open with…</span> and select <span class=\"ui\">MuPDF</span>."
msgstr ""
"Más mian leat an ghné seo a úsáid le cineálacha comhaid eile cosúil le EPUB, "
"FB2, HTML nó comhaid íomhá, ba cheart duit an comhad a oscailt le hinneall "
"difriúil: Sa <span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span>, tapáil go fada ar "
"ainm an chomhaid, tapáil <span class=\"ui\">Oscail le…</span> agus roghnaigh "
"<span class=\"ui\">MuPDF</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3074-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-manganextfile"
msgid "Jump to the next file"
msgstr "Léim go dtí an chéad chomhad eile"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3076-5
msgid ""
"When you reach the last page of a book, KOReader shows you a dialog. In this "
"dialog there is an <span class=\"ui\">Open next file</span> action which "
"will open the next file in the same directory as the current book. So you "
"can put your series in separate directories and read them one after another "
"without going back to the <span class=\"ui\">File Browser</span>."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a shroicheann tú an leathanach deireanach de leabhar, taispeánann "
"KOReader dialóg duit. Sa dialóg seo tá gníomh <span class=\"ui\">Oscail an "
"chéad chomhad eile</span> a osclóidh an chéad chomhad eile san eolaire "
"céanna leis an leabhar reatha. Mar sin, is féidir leat do shraith a chur in "
"eolairí ar leithligh agus iad a léamh ceann i ndiaidh a chéile gan dul ar "
"ais chuig an <span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3080-5
msgid ""
"When opening this next file, KOReader skips the files that you have marked "
"as <b>finished</b>. This feature is useful for example when you have a "
"folder of manga files and you have already read some of them. You can mark a "
"file as finished from the end of book dialog shown above. Also you can mark "
"it from the <span class=\"ui\">File Browser</span> by long-pressing on the "
"file. After copying them to your device, you can:"
msgstr ""
"Agus an chéad chomhad eile á oscailt agat, scipeálann KOReader na comhaid "
"atá marcáilte agat mar <b>críochnaithe</b>. Tá an ghné seo úsáideach mar "
"shampla nuair a bhíonn fillteán de chomhaid manga agat agus má tá cuid acu "
"léite agat cheana féin. Is féidir leat comhad a mharcáil mar chríochnaithe "
"ón dialóg deireadh leabhair a thaispeántar thuas. Chomh maith leis sin, is "
"féidir leat é a mharcáil ón <span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span> trí "
"bhrú fada a choinneáil ar an gcomhad. Tar éis iad a chóipeáil chuig do "
"ghléas, is féidir leat:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3083-5
msgid "Open the <span class=\"ui\">File Browser</span> in KOReader"
msgstr "Oscail an <span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span> i KOReader"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3084-5
msgid ""
"Long press on the ones you already finished and tap <span class=\"ui\">Mark "
"as finished</span>"
msgstr ""
"Brúigh ar na cinn atá críochnaithe agat cheana féin agus tapáil <span "
"class=\"ui\">Marcáil mar chríochnaithe</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3087-5
msgid ""
"Now you can read all the files by just tapping <span class=\"ui\">Open next "
"file</span> at the end of the book. KOReader will skip the ones you have "
"already read."
msgstr ""
"Anois is féidir leat na comhaid go léir a léamh trí <span "
"class=\"ui\">Oscail an chéad chomhad eile</span> a thapáil ag deireadh an "
"leabhair. Scipeálfaidh KOReader na cinn atá léite agat cheana féin."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3090-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-mangaprepare"
msgid "Optimizing manga for reader"
msgstr "Manga a bharrfheabhsú don léitheoir"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3092-5
msgid ""
"If you like reading manga books on your e-ink device there are some tips "
"that can make your experience better. Preparing your own manga files is the "
"best solution if you're not satisfied with how comics look on your device."
msgstr ""
"Más maith leat leabhair manga a léamh ar do ghléas dúigh leictreonach, tá "
"roinnt leideanna anseo a d’fhéadfadh feabhas a chur ar do thaithí. Is é "
"ullmhú do chuid comhad manga féin an réiteach is fearr mura bhfuil tú sásta "
"leis an gcuma atá ar ghreannáin ar do ghléas."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3095-1
msgid "Which file type to use"
msgstr "Cén cineál comhaid le húsáid"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3096-5
msgid ""
"File types like MOBI and EPUB are not suitable for handling primarily image "
"content (e.g., manga/comics). <b>MOBI</b> support in KOReader is minimal to "
"nonexistent, and <b>EPUB’s</b> text rendering priorities can cause problems "
"when showing full-page images. For further technical details, please visit "
"this <a href=\"https://github.com/koreader/koreader/issues/"
"9163#issuecomment-1146637205\">GitHub issue</a>."
msgstr ""
"Níl cineálacha comhaid cosúil le MOBI agus EPUB oiriúnach chun ábhar íomhá a "
"láimhseáil go príomha (e.g., manga/greannáin). Tá tacaíocht <b>MOBI</b> i "
"KOReader íosta nó neamhiomlán, agus is féidir le tosaíochtaí rindreála téacs "
"<b>EPUB</b> fadhbanna a chruthú agus íomhánna lánleathanaigh á dtaispeáint. "
"Le haghaidh tuilleadh sonraí teicniúla, tabhair cuairt ar an <a "
"href=\"https://github.com/koreader/koreader/issues/"
"9163#issuecomment-1146637205\">saincheist GitHub</a> seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3098-5
msgid ""
"Your best option is building a <b>CBZ</b> file which works better in "
"KOReader. A file with <b>.cbz</b> extension is a zip file (with no "
"compression) that is a collection of images. It saves multiple images, "
"commonly <b>.png</b> or <b>.jpeg</b> files, organized into pages of the "
"comic. KOReader can also open <b>CBT</b> files, which are similar to <b>CBZ</"
"b> files but use <b>TAR</b> archive format."
msgstr ""
"Is é an rogha is fearr atá agat ná comhad <b>CBZ</b> a thógáil a oibríonn "
"níos fearr i KOReader. Is comhad zip (gan aon chomhbhrú) é comhad leis an "
"síneadh <b>.cbz</b> arb é atá ann bailiúchán d'íomhánna. Sábhálann sé "
"ilíomhánna, comhaid <b>.png</b> nó <b>.jpeg</b> de ghnáth, eagraithe i "
"leathanaigh an ghrinnleabhair. Is féidir le KOReader comhaid <b>CBT</b> a "
"oscailt freisin, atá cosúil le comhaid <b>CBZ</b> ach a úsáideann formáid "
"cartlainne <b>TAR</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3100-5
msgid ""
"Easiest way to convert a manga to <b>CBZ</b> is to get the manga as images "
"from various websites, then convert them using <span "
"class=\"external\">Kindle Comic Converter</span> (<a href=\"https://"
"github.com/ciromattia/kcc\">https://github.com/ciromattia/kcc</a>). There "
"are some useful settings like <b>auto-rotating two-page splits to landscape "
"and applying dithering</b> so that eink-rendered gradients are smoothly "
"dithered without jagged layers."
msgstr ""
"Is é an bealach is fusa chun manga a thiontú go <b>CBZ</b> ná an manga a "
"fháil mar íomhánna ó shuíomhanna gréasáin éagsúla, agus ansin iad a thiontú "
"ag baint úsáide as <span class=\"external\">Kindle Comic Converter</span> "
"(<a href=\"https://github.com/ciromattia/kcc\">https://github.com/ciromattia/"
"kcc</a>). Tá roinnt socruithe úsáideacha ann cosúil le <b>roinnt dhá "
"leathanach a rothlú go huathoibríoch go tírdhreach agus díodrú a chur i "
"bhfeidhm</b> ionas go ndéantar grádáin rindreáilte le ein-dúch a dhíodrú go "
"réidh gan sraitheanna garbha."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3102-1
msgid "Which resolution to use"
msgstr "Cén rún atá le húsáid"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3103-5
msgid ""
"The best results can be achieved by resizing your images to exactly your e-"
"reader screen size. A screen-specific <b>CBZ</b> which targets the exact "
"screen size of the device, prevents rescaling during reading. KOReader "
"downscales your images to your screen size while reading but this is not "
"recommended because KOReader adds a dithering pass before scaling and this "
"causes loss of quality."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir na torthaí is fearr a bhaint amach trí mhéid d’íomhánna a athrú go "
"díreach go méid scáileáin do léitheora ríomhleabhair. Cuireann <b>CBZ</b> "
"atá sainiúil don scáileán agus a dhíríonn ar mhéid cruinn scáileáin an "
"fheiste cosc ar athscálú le linn léitheoireachta. Laghdaíonn KOReader "
"d’íomhánna go méid do scáileáin agus iad ag léamh ach ní mholtar é seo mar "
"go gcuireann KOReader pas dídithe leis roimh an scálú agus caillfidh sé seo "
"cáilíocht."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3105-5
msgid ""
"But if you want to use your hand made <b>CBZ</b> on more than one device or "
"you want to preserve high resolution for future proofing, your best option "
"might be to make the <b>CBZ</b> for your highest resolution device. Or pick "
"an arbitrary \"high\" resolution, possibly one that matches the source. "
"<b>300 PPI</b> or better (up to <b>450</b> or even <b>600</b>), unless the "
"source is lower of course. If we assume a screen size of <b>8\", 1500×2000</"
"b> is a good target resolution. For bigger images, you should try it on your "
"device and see whether it can deal with it. Especially old Kindles with low "
"memory can struggle with sizes like <b>3000×4000</b> for example. If you're "
"automating the process, it might be worth considering creating both a lower "
"and higher quality version (e.g., at <b>200/400</b> or <b>300/600</b> DPI)."
msgstr ""
"Ach más mian leat do <b>CBZ</b> lámhdhéanta a úsáid ar níos mó ná gléas "
"amháin nó más mian leat ardtaifeach a chaomhnú le haghaidh ullmhúcháin sa "
"todhchaí, b'fhéidir gurb é an rogha is fearr duit an <b>CBZ</b> a chruthú "
"don ghléas is airde taifeach atá agat. Nó roghnaigh \"ardtaifeach\" "
"treallach, b'fhéidir ceann a mheaitseálann an fhoinse. <b>300 PPI</b> nó "
"níos fearr (suas le <b>450</b> nó fiú <b>600</b>), mura bhfuil an fhoinse "
"níos ísle ar ndóigh. Má ghlacaimid leis go bhfuil méid scáileáin de <b>8\", "
"1500 × 2000</b> ina réiteach sprice maith. I gcás íomhánna níos mó, ba "
"cheart duit é a thriail ar do ghléas agus a fheiceáil an féidir leis "
"déileáil leis. Go háirithe, is féidir le Kindles seanchaite a bhfuil cuimhne "
"íseal acu streachailt le méideanna cosúil le <b>3000 × 4000</b> mar shampla. "
"Má tá tú ag uathoibriú an phróisis, b'fhéidir go mbeadh sé fiúntach "
"smaoineamh ar leagan níos ísle agus níos airde cáilíochta a chruthú (e.g., "
"ag <b>200/400</b> nó <b>300/600</b> DPI)."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3107-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">INFO</span> KOReader doesn't parse <b>spine page-"
"progression-direction=\"rtl\"</b> attribute of the books. So it doesn’t "
"change page turning direction even though the file was created with right-to-"
"left reading. Users can switch this via:"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">EOLAS</span> Ní dhéanann KOReader parsáil ar an "
"tréith <b>spine page-progression-direction=\"rtl\"</b> de na leabhair. Mar "
"sin ní athraíonn sé treo casadh leathanaigh fiú má cruthaíodh an comhad le "
"léamh ó dheis go clé. Is féidir le húsáideoirí é seo a athrú trí:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div:3109-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Taps and gestures / Page turns / Invert page turn "
"tap and swipes / buttons"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Tapálacha agus gothaí / Casadh leathanaigh / "
"Inbhéartaigh casadh leathanaigh, tapáil agus svaidhpeáil / cnaipí"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3112-1
msgid "Advanced preparation of manga"
msgstr "Ullmhúchán ardleibhéil manga"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3114-5
msgid "The following is an example procedure to process one manga file:"
msgstr ""
"Seo a leanas nós imeachta samplach chun comhad manga amháin a phróiseáil:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3117-9
msgid ""
"Download <span class=\"external\">Kindle Comic Converter (KCC)</span> from "
"<a href=\"https://github.com/ciromattia/kcc\">https://github.com/ciromattia/"
"kcc</a>"
msgstr ""
"Íoslódáil <span class=\"external\">Tiontaire Greannáin Kindle (KCC)</span> ó "
"<a href=\"https://github.com/ciromattia/kcc\">https://github.com/ciromattia/"
"kcc</a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3118-9
msgid ""
"Download your manga from the source of your choosing (i.e. <span "
"class=\"external\">HakuNeko</span>)"
msgstr ""
"Íoslódáil do manga ón bhfoinse is rogha leat (i.e. <span "
"class=\"external\">HakuNeko</span>)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3119-9
msgid ""
"Unpack the manga file. Now you should have a directory that contains only "
"images (or subdirectories with images, no archives)"
msgstr ""
"Díphacáil an comhad manga. Anois ba chóir go mbeadh eolaire agat nach bhfuil "
"ach íomhánna ann (nó fo-eolaire le híomhánna, gan aon chartlanna)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3120-9
msgid ""
"Process this directory with <span class=\"external\">KCC</span>. Each "
"directory will produce a single <b>CBZ</b> file, so if you want to make "
"several volumes at once, select multiple directories at once"
msgstr ""
"Próiseáil an t-eolaire seo le <span class=\"external\">KCC</span>. Cruthóidh "
"gach eolaire comhad <b>CBZ</b> aonair, mar sin más mian leat roinnt "
"imleabhair a chruthú ag an am céanna, roghnaigh il-eolaire ag an am céanna"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3123-5
msgid "Some useful settings of <span class=\"external\">KCC</span>:"
msgstr "Roinnt socruithe úsáideacha de <span class=\"external\">KCC</span>:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3125-5
msgid ""
"<b>Spread splitter:</b> This feature detects double pages and allows you to "
"rotate or cut them in two."
msgstr ""
"<b>Scoilteoir leathanaigh:</b> Braitheann an ghné seo leathanaigh dhúbailte "
"agus ligeann sí duit iad a rothlú nó a ghearradh ina dhá leath."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3127-5
msgid ""
"<b>Upscaling:</b> Enlarge images that is smaller than your target resolution."
msgstr "<b>Uas-scálú:</b> Méadaigh íomhánna atá níos lú ná do rún."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3133-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-mangatips"
msgid "Other manga tips"
msgstr "Leideanna eile maidir le manga"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3137-1
msgid "Immersive mode in KOReader"
msgstr "Mód tumoideachais i KOReader"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3139-5
msgid ""
"If you would like to enjoy your manga in a more immersive way, make sure "
"that you selected the exact same resolution as your device’s screen "
"resolution in <b>KCC</b> when creating your <b>CBZ</b> file. Also you can "
"hide the bottom progress bar while reading your manga in KOReader. So you "
"will have an immersive full screen view of your manga without obstructions."
msgstr ""
"Más mian leat taitneamh a bhaint as do manga ar bhealach níos tumtha, déan "
"cinnte gur roghnaigh tú an taifeach céanna le taifeach scáileáin do ghléis i "
"<b>KCC</b> agus do chomhad <b>CBZ</b> á chruthú agat. Chomh maith leis sin, "
"is féidir leat an barra dul chun cinn bun a cheilt agus tú ag léamh do manga "
"i KOReader. Mar sin, beidh radharc lánscáileáin tumtha agat ar do manga gan "
"bhacainní."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3143-1
msgid "Extra step for smooth gradients"
msgstr "Céim bhreise le haghaidh grádáin réidh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3145-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.p:3145-5"
msgid "!!! ADVANCED"
msgstr "!!! CASTA"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3147-5
msgid ""
"After using <span class=\"external\">KCC</span> to create a <b>CBZ</b> file, "
"you can apply additional <b>dithering</b> to the images. This way, eink-"
"rendered gradients will be smoothly dithered without jagged layers. This "
"step will produce fine-tuned manga volumes which look better in KOReader."
msgstr ""
"Tar éis duit <span class=\"external\">KCC</span> a úsáid chun comhad <b>CBZ</"
"b> a chruthú, is féidir leat <b>dithering</b> breise a chur i bhfeidhm ar na "
"híomhánna. Ar an mbealach seo, déanfar grádáin rindreáilte le einc a "
"dhithering go réidh gan sraitheanna garbha. Ginfidh an chéim seo imleabhair "
"manga mínchoigeartaithe a bheidh níos fearr i KOReader."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3150-5
msgid ""
"You can use <span class=\"external\">ImageMagick</span> to process your "
"images. <span class=\"external\">ImageMagick</span>, is a powerful open-"
"source software suite for displaying, creating, converting, modifying, and "
"editing raster images. You can download <span "
"class=\"external\">ImageMagick</span> and use it from the command line to "
"process many images at once."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat <span class=\"external\">ImageMagick</span> a úsáid chun do "
"chuid íomhánna a phróiseáil. Is sraith bogearraí foinse oscailte "
"chumhachtach é <span class=\"external\">ImageMagick</span> chun íomhánna "
"rastair a thaispeáint, a chruthú, a thiontú, a mhodhnú agus a chur in eagar. "
"Is féidir leat <span class=\"external\">ImageMagick</span> a íoslódáil agus "
"é a úsáid ón líne ordaithe chun go leor íomhánna a phróiseáil ag an am "
"céanna."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3153-9
msgid ""
"Unpack the prepared <b>CBZ</b> file that you created with <span "
"class=\"external\">KCC</span>,"
msgstr ""
"Díphacáil an comhad <b>CBZ</b> ullmhaithe a chruthaigh tú le <span "
"class=\"external\">KCC</span>,"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3154-9
msgid ""
"Download the following file <a href=\"https://disk.yandex.com/d/"
"glEebjmPYYp7og\">dither_pack.zip</a> (located on <span "
"class=\"external\">Yandex Disk</span>) which contains two <b>batch files "
"(.BAT)</b> and a <b>GIF</b> color template."
msgstr ""
"Íoslódáil an comhad seo a leanas <a href=\"https://disk.yandex.com/d/"
"glEebjmPYYp7og\">dither_pack.zip</a> (atá suite ar <span "
"class=\"external\">Diosca Yandex</span>) ina bhfuil dhá <b>chomhad bhaisce "
"(.BAT)</b> agus teimpléad datha <b>GIF</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3155-9
msgid "Extract these three files next to your images that will be processed"
msgstr ""
"Bain na trí chomhad seo amach in aice le do chuid íomhánna a phróiseálfar"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3156-9
msgid ""
"Edit the <b>_magick_manga_ditherN_resize.bat</b> and change the resolution "
"to your device resolution (in both places in the <b>BAT</b> file)."
msgstr ""
"Cuir an comhad <b>_magick_manga_ditherN_resize.bat</b> in eagar agus "
"athraigh an taifeach go dtí taifeach do ghléis (sa dá áit sa chomhad <b>BAT</"
"b>)."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li.p:3157-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_red\">WARNING</span> Next step will replace all the "
"images in the directory with the processed ones. So make sure that you have "
"a copy of them in some other directory if you want to keep the originals."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_red\">RABHADH</span> Sa chéad chéim eile, cuirfear na "
"híomhánna próiseáilte in ionad na n-íomhánna uile san eolaire. Mar sin, déan "
"cinnte go bhfuil cóip díobh agat in eolaire éigin eile más mian leat na "
"bunchóipeanna a choinneáil."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3159-9
msgid ""
"Run <b>_magick_manga_ditherN_resize.bat</b> to resize and dither the images."
msgstr ""
"Rith <b>_magick_manga_ditherN_resize.bat</b> chun na híomhánna a athrú agus "
"a dhíthriú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3160-9
msgid ""
"Assuming you have <b>7-Zip</b> installed, run <b>_batch_archive.bat</b> to "
"pack all the processed images into a <b>CBZ</b> archive."
msgstr ""
"Ag glacadh leis go bhfuil <b>7-Zip</b> suiteáilte agat, rith "
"<b>_batch_archive.bat</b> chun na híomhánna próiseáilte go léir a phacáil i "
"gcartlann <b>CBZ</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3165-1
msgid "Reversing the page turn direction for authentic Japanese manga"
msgstr ""
"Ag aisiompú treo casadh leathanaigh le haghaidh manga Seapánach barántúil"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3167-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.p:3167-5"
msgid "!!! ADVANCED"
msgstr "!!! CASTA"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3169-5
msgid ""
"You can make KOReader turn pages from <b>Left to Right</b>, so that swipes "
"and tap zones are swapped. To enable this, add the following lines:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat KOReader a chur ag casadh leathanaigh ó <b>Chlé go Deas</b>, "
"ionas go ndéantar na criosanna svaidhpeála agus tapála a mhalartú. Chun seo "
"a chumasú, cuir na línte seo a leanas leis:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3173-5
msgid ""
"[\"/storage/emulated/0/Books/manga\"] = {<br> [\"inverse_reading_order\"] = "
"true,<br> [\"kopt_zoom_direction\"] = 0,<br> },"
msgstr ""
"[\"/storage/emulated/0/Books/manga\"] = {<br> [\"inverse_reading_order\"] = "
"true,<br> [\"kopt_zoom_direction\"] = 0,<br> },"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3182-5
msgid "to this file:"
msgstr "chuig an gcomhad seo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div:3182-21
msgid "/koreader/settings/directory_defaults.lua"
msgstr "/koreader/settings/directory_defaults.lua"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3186-5
msgid ""
"where <b>/storage/emulated/0/Books/manga</b> is the absolute path to the "
"directory containing your mangas. After this change, when you open a file "
"from the mentioned directory, your swipes and tap zones will be swapped."
msgstr ""
"áit a bhfuil <b>/storage/emulated/0/Books/manga</b> an cosán iomlán chuig an "
"eolaire ina bhfuil do mhangaí. Tar éis an athraithe seo, nuair a osclaíonn "
"tú comhad ón eolaire luaite, malartófar do chriosanna svaidhpeála agus "
"tapála."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3191-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L1-managinglibrary"
msgid "MANAGING YOUR LIBRARY"
msgstr "AG BAINISTÍOCHT DO LEABHARLANN"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3195-1
msgid "File Browser Usage"
msgstr "Úsáid Brabhsálaí Comhad"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3197-5
msgid ""
"You will see the <span class=\"ui\">file browser</span> interface when you "
"run KOReader for the first time. It is one of the two main interfaces of "
"KOReader. You will do all your file and folder operations here. You can "
"access it from the reading screen by:"
msgstr ""
"Feicfidh tú comhéadan an <span class=\"ui\">bhrabhsálaí comhad</span> nuair "
"a ritheann tú KOReader den chéad uair. Tá sé ar cheann de dhá phríomh-"
"chomhéadan KOReader. Déanfaidh tú do chuid oibríochtaí comhad agus fillteán "
"go léir anseo. Is féidir leat rochtain a fháil air ón scáileán "
"léitheoireachta trí:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3199-5
msgid "TOP MENU /"
msgstr "BARR-ROGHCHLÁR /"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3205-5
msgid ""
"By default, <span class=\"ui\">file browser</span> shows your <span "
"class=\"ui\">HOME</span> folder, which is your main library folder. You can "
"change this by <b>long-pressing on any folder</b>. You can change <span "
"class=\"ui\">file browser</span>s many options like how books are displayed "
"or sorted via the <span class=\"ui\">TOP MENU</span> by swiping down from "
"the top part of the screen."
msgstr ""
"De réir réamhshocraithe, taispeánann an <span class=\"ui\">brabhsálaí "
"comhad</span> d'fhillteán <span class=\"ui\">BAILE</span>, arb é "
"príomhfhillteán do leabharlainne é. Is féidir leat é seo a athrú trí <b>bhrú "
"fada ar aon fhillteán</b>. Is féidir leat roghanna iomadúla an <span "
"class=\"ui\">bhrabhsálaí comhad</span> a athrú, amhail an chaoi a "
"dtaispeántar nó a shórtáiltear leabhair tríd an <span class=\"ui\">ROGHCHLÁR "
"BARR</span> trí svaidhpeáil síos ón gcuid uachtarach den scáileán."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3207-5
msgid "Circled items in the image are explained below:"
msgstr "Mínítear na míreanna atá ciorclaithe san íomhá thíos:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3209-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">RESET:</span> This option allows you to reset some "
"properties of your document like <b>reading progress, bookmarks, custom "
"cover image</b> etc. which you can choose in a following dialog."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">ATHSHOCRAITH:</span> Ligeann an rogha seo duit roinnt "
"airíonna de do dhoiciméad a athshocrú amhail <b>dul chun cinn "
"léitheoireachta, leabharmharcanna, íomhá chlúdaigh saincheaptha</b> srl. ar "
"féidir leat a roghnú i ndialóg ina dhiaidh sin."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3211-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_red\">WARNING</span> Be very careful when using the "
"<span class=\"ui\">reset</span> dialog and double check which items are "
"marked, otherwise you can reset everything related to your book accidentally."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_red\">RABHADH</span> Bí an-chúramach agus an dialóg "
"<span class=\"ui\">athshocraithe</span> á húsáid agat agus déan seiceáil "
"faoi dhó cé na míreanna atá marcáilte, nó is féidir leat gach rud a "
"bhaineann le do leabhar a athshocrú de thaisme."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3213-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">OPEN WITH:</span> KOReader has different engines for "
"rendering different file types. In some cases you can open a file in a "
"different engine to get some other features. See <b>Viewing archive files</"
"b> and <b>Viewing image files</b> sections just below."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">OSCAIL LE:</span> Tá innill éagsúla ag KOReader chun "
"cineálacha éagsúla comhad a rindreáil. I gcásanna áirithe is féidir leat "
"comhad a oscailt in inneall difriúil chun gnéithe eile a fháil. Féach na "
"rannóga <b>Ag féachaint ar chomhaid chartlainne</b> agus <b>Ag féachaint ar "
"chomhaid íomhá</b> thíos."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3215-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">IGNORE COVER:</span> If for some reason you want to "
"disable the cover for this book (it may have wrong cover or cover is not "
"very readable on the e-ink screen) you can select this."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">NÍ CUIR NEAMH AR AN gCLÚDACH:</span> Más mian leat "
"clúdach an leabhair seo a dhíchumasú ar chúis éigin (b’fhéidir go bhfuil "
"clúdach mícheart air nó nach bhfuil an clúdach an-léite ar an scáileán dúigh "
"leictreonach) is féidir leat é seo a roghnú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3217-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">IGNORE METADATA:</span> If your book metadata is not "
"correct, name field may show useless information. Select this option to show "
"the file name instead of metadata."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">NÍ DO MHEATASHONAITHE:</span> Mura bhfuil meiteashonraí "
"do leabhair ceart, d'fhéadfadh faisnéis neamhúsáideach a bheith le feiceáil "
"sa réimse ainm. Roghnaigh an rogha seo chun ainm an chomhaid a thaispeáint "
"in ionad na meiteashonraí."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3219-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">REFRESH CACHED BOOK INFORMATION:</span> KOReader caches a "
"book's metadata and book cover when you add it to your library. If you make "
"some changes to the book after copying to your device, this information "
"might need to be updated. If you see wrong cover or metadata, you can "
"refresh the book information with this menu item."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">ATHNUACHAN EOLAS FAOI LEABHAIR ATÁ I dTAISCEÁIL:</span> "
"Cuireann KOReader meiteashonraí agus clúdach leabhair i dtaisce nuair a "
"chuireann tú le do leabharlann é. Má dhéanann tú roinnt athruithe ar an "
"leabhar tar éis é a chóipeáil chuig do ghléas, b'fhéidir go mbeadh ort an "
"fhaisnéis seo a nuashonrú. Má fheiceann tú clúdach nó meiteashonraí "
"míchearta, is féidir leat an fhaisnéis leabhair a athnuachan leis an mír "
"roghchláir seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3223-1
msgid "Working on multiple files"
msgstr "Ag obair ar ilchomhaid"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3225-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">File browser</span> allows you to perform some operations "
"(like copying, moving, deleting, exporting highlights) on many files at the "
"same time. For this procedure, first you have to select the files. Currently "
"there are three different ways of selecting files for bulk operations in the "
"<span class=\"ui\">file browser</span>:"
msgstr ""
"Ligeann an <span class=\"ui\">brabhsálaí comhad</span> duit roinnt "
"oibríochtaí a dhéanamh (cosúil le cóipeáil, bogadh, scriosadh, agus "
"buaicphointí a onnmhairiú) ar go leor comhad ag an am céanna. Chun an nós "
"imeachta seo a dhéanamh, ní mór duit na comhaid a roghnú ar dtús. Faoi "
"láthair tá trí bhealach éagsúla ann chun comhaid a roghnú le haghaidh "
"oibríochtaí mórchóir sa <span class=\"ui\">brabhsálaí comhad</span>:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3227-5
msgid ""
"<b>- In the first method</b>, long press on a file name and choose <span "
"class=\"ui\">Select</span> from the popup dialog. This will activate the "
"<span class=\"ui\">Selection mode</span>. Now you can tap on other files to "
"add them to the selection. When you finish selecting your files, tap on the "
"<span class=\"ui\">checkmark icon</span> at the <b>top right corner</b> of "
"your screen. You can choose what to do with these files from the dialog. Or "
"exit the selection mode from the same dialog."
msgstr ""
"<b>- Sa chéad mhodh</b>, brúigh fada ar ainm comhaid agus roghnaigh <span "
"class=\"ui\">Roghnaigh</span> ón dialóg aníos. Cuirfidh sé seo an <span "
"class=\"ui\">mód roghnúcháin</span> i ngníomh. Anois is féidir leat tapáil "
"ar chomhaid eile chun iad a chur leis an roghnú. Nuair a bheidh tú "
"críochnaithe le do chuid comhad a roghnú, tapáil ar an deilbhín <span "
"class=\"ui\">seiceála</span> ag <b>cúinne uachtarach ar dheis</b> do "
"scáileáin. Is féidir leat a roghnú cad atá le déanamh leis na comhaid seo ón "
"dialóg. Nó imeacht as an mód roghnúcháin ón dialóg chéanna."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3229-5
msgid ""
"<b>- In the second method</b>, press the <span class=\"ui\">+ (plus) icon</"
"span> at the <b>top right corner</b> and choose <span class=\"ui\">Select "
"files</span> from the dialog. This will activate the <span "
"class=\"ui\">Selection mode</span> and rest is the same as the first method "
"above."
msgstr ""
"<b>- Sa dara modh</b>, brúigh an deilbhín <span class=\"ui\">+ (móide)</"
"span> ag an <b>chúinne uachtarach ar dheis</b> agus roghnaigh <span "
"class=\"ui\">Roghnaigh comhaid</span> ón dialóg. Cuirfidh sé seo an <span "
"class=\"ui\">mód roghnúcháin</span> i ngníomh agus tá an chuid eile mar an "
"gcéanna leis an gcéad mhodh thuas."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3231-5
msgid ""
"<b>- In the third method</b>, you can choose your files based on a <span "
"class=\"ui\"> File search</span>. This is useful if you need to perform an "
"operation on many files distributed in different folders. For example you "
"want to move all files in your collection authored by Tolkien, to a new "
"folder. Steps for this action will be:"
msgstr ""
"<b>- Sa tríú modh</b>, is féidir leat do chuid comhad a roghnú bunaithe ar "
"<span class=\"ui\">chuardach comhad</span>. Tá sé seo úsáideach má bhíonn "
"ort oibríocht a dhéanamh ar go leor comhad atá scaipthe i bhfillteáin "
"éagsúla. Mar shampla, más mian leat na comhaid go léir i do bhailiúchán, "
"arna scríobh ag Tolkien, a bhogadh chuig fillteán nua. Seo a leanas na "
"céimeanna don ghníomh seo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3234-9
msgid ""
"From the <span class=\"ui\">Top menu</span> press on the <span "
"class=\"ui\">Search tab</span> (with the magnifier icon) and choose <span "
"class=\"ui\">File search</span>."
msgstr ""
"Ón <span class=\"ui\">roghchlár barr</span> brúigh ar an táb <span "
"class=\"ui\">Cuardaigh</span> (leis an deilbhín formhéadaitheora) agus "
"roghnaigh <span class=\"ui\">Cuardaigh comhad</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3235-9
msgid ""
"Check <span class=\"ui\">Include subfolders</span> option if you want to "
"search inside the folders too. You can check <span class=\"ui\">Also search "
"in book metadata</span> if you want KOReader to look in book's metadata. "
"Otherwise KOReader will only look at the file names for the word you entered."
msgstr ""
"Seiceáil an rogha <span class=\"ui\">Cuir fo-fhillteáin san áireamh</span> "
"más mian leat cuardach a dhéanamh laistigh de na fillteáin freisin. Is "
"féidir leat seiceáil a dhéanamh ar <span class=\"ui\">Cuardaigh i "
"meiteashonraí leabhar freisin</span> más mian leat go bhféachfadh KOReader i "
"meiteashonraí an leabhair. Seachas sin, ní fhéachfaidh KOReader ach ar "
"ainmneacha na gcomhad don fhocal a chuir tú isteach."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3236-9
msgid ""
"You can start the search from your library <span class=\"ui\">Home folder</"
"span> or your <span class=\"ui\">Current folder</span> by pressing on the "
"respective button."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat an cuardach a thosú ó do <span class=\"ui\">fhillteán baile</"
"span> leabharlainne nó ó do <span class=\"ui\">fhillteán reatha</span> trí "
"bhrú ar an gcnaipe faoi seach."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3237-9
msgid ""
"After search is finished, you will see a file list (if your search term is "
"found of course). Now you can tap on the <span class=\"ui\">Hamburger icon</"
"span> at the <b>top left corner</b> of the screen to enter the <span "
"class=\"ui\">Selection mode</span>."
msgstr ""
"Tar éis don chuardach a bheith críochnaithe, feicfidh tú liosta comhad (má "
"aimsítear do théarma cuardaigh ar ndóigh). Anois is féidir leat tapáil ar "
"dheilbhín an <span class=\"ui\">Hamburger</span> ag an <b>cúinne uachtarach "
"ar chlé</b> den scáileán chun dul isteach sa <span class=\"ui\">mód "
"roghnúcháin</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3238-9
msgid ""
"Tap on all the files you want to perform operations on and tap on the <span "
"class=\"ui\">Checkmark icon</span> at the <b>top left corner</b> of your "
"screen. You will see a dialog which contains <span class=\"ui\">Select in "
"file browser</span>. Select this option."
msgstr ""
"Tar éis don bhaile a bheith críochnaithe, feicfidh tú liosta comhad (má tá "
"sé mar aidhm ag an bhfocal cuardaigh ar ndóigh). Anois is féidir leat tapáil "
"ar dheilbhín an <span class=\"ui\">Hamburger</span> ag an <b>cúinne "
"uachtarach ar chlé</b> den scáileán chun dul isteach sa <span "
"class=\"ui\">mód roghnúcháin</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3239-9
msgid ""
"Now you will be back at the <span class=\"ui\">File browser</span> and the "
"files you selected in the <span class=\"ui\">Search dialog</span> will also "
"be selected here."
msgstr ""
"Anois beidh tú ar ais sa <span class=\"ui\">bhrabhsálaí comhad</span> agus "
"roghnófar na comhaid a roghnaigh tú sa <span class=\"ui\">dhialóg cuardaigh</"
"span> anseo freisin."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3240-9
msgid ""
"Tap on the <span class=\"ui\">Checkmark icon</span> at the <b>top right "
"corner</b> of your screen. Now you can choose what to do with these files "
"from the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Beartaigh ar dheilbhín an <span class=\"ui\">mharc seiceála</span> ag "
"<b>cúinne uachtarach ar dheis</b> do scáileáin. Anois is féidir leat a "
"roghnú cad atá le déanamh leis na comhaid seo ón dialóg."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3247-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.div:3247-1"
msgid "Folder shortcuts"
msgstr "Aicearraí fillteán"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3249-5
msgid ""
"KOReader allows you to add your favorite folders to a quickly accessible "
"Folder shortcuts menu. For example if you have an <b>Archive</b> folder in "
"your library that is under <b>Home>Articles>Scientific>Archived</b>, you can "
"assign a folder shortcut to this <b>Archived</b> folder and access it "
"quickly even while reading a book."
msgstr ""
"Le KOReader, is féidir leat do fhillteáin is fearr leat a chur le roghchlár "
"aicearraí fillteán atá inrochtana go tapa. Mar shampla, má tá fillteán "
"<b>Cartlann</b> agat i do leabharlann atá faoi "
"<b>Baile>Ailt>Eolaíoch>Cartlannaithe</b>, is féidir leat aicearra fillteáin "
"a shannadh don fhillteán <b>Cartlannaithe</b> seo agus rochtain thapa a "
"fháil air fiú agus leabhar á léamh agat."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3251-5
msgid "Adding a folder shortcut:"
msgstr "Ag cur aicearra fillteáin leis:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3252-5
msgid ""
"There are two ways of adding a folder to your <span class=\"ui\">Folder "
"shortcuts</span> list:"
msgstr ""
"Tá dhá bhealach ann chun fillteán a chur le do liosta <span "
"class=\"ui\">aicearraí fillteán</span>:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3254-9
msgid ""
"When you are in the File Browser, tap right corner <span class=\"ui\">+ "
"(plus) menu</span> button then tap <span class=\"ui\">Add to folder "
"shortcuts</span> item and enter a descriptive name for this shortcut. "
"<b>This will add the folder you are currently in.</b>"
msgstr ""
"Nuair atá tú sa Bhrabhsálaí Comhad, tapáil an cnaipe <span class=\"ui\">+ "
"(móide) roghchláir</span> sa chúinne ar dheis agus ansin tapáil an mhír "
"<span class=\"ui\">Cuir le haicearraí fillteáin</span> agus cuir isteach "
"ainm tuairisciúil don aicearra seo. <b>Cuirfidh sé seo an fillteán ina "
"bhfuil tú faoi láthair leis.</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3255-9
msgid ""
"When you are in the File Browser, long-press on a folder name to open the "
"context menu. Tap <span class=\"ui\">Add to folder shortcuts</span> item and "
"enter a descriptive name for this shortcut. <b>This will add the folder you "
"pressed on.</b>"
msgstr ""
"Nuair atá tú sa Bhrabhsálaí Comhad, brúigh ar ainm fillteáin go fada chun an "
"roghchlár comhthéacs a oscailt. Tapáil an mhír <span class=\"ui\">Cuir le "
"haicearraí fillteáin</span> agus cuir isteach ainm tuairisciúil don aicearra "
"seo. <b>Cuirfidh sé seo an fillteán ar bhrúigh tú leis.</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3258-5
msgid ""
"Folders which are in your <span class=\"ui\">Folder shortcuts</span> list "
"will have a <b>star (★)</b> in the <span class=\"ui\">File Browser</span>."
msgstr ""
"Beidh <span class=\"ui\">aicearraí fillteán</span> i do liosta ag fillteáin "
"a mbeidh <b>réalta (★)</b> acu sa <span class=\"ui\">Bhrabhsálaí Comhad</"
"span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3260-5
msgid ""
"You can remove a folder from the shortcuts in the same way, by long-pressing "
"on it and selecting <span class=\"ui\">Remove from folder shortcuts</span>."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat fillteán a bhaint de na haicearraí ar an mbealach céanna, trí "
"bhrú fada air agus <span class=\"ui\">Bain as aicearraí fillteáin</span> a "
"roghnú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3263-5
msgid "Viewing your folder shortcuts:"
msgstr "Ag féachaint ar aicearraí do fhillteáin:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3264-5
msgid ""
"You can open your <span class=\"ui\">Folder shortcuts</span> from the <span "
"class=\"ui\">File Browser</span> or <span class=\"ui\">Reading screen</span> "
"while reading a book."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat do <span class=\"ui\">aicearraí fillteáin</span> a oscailt ón "
"<span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span> nó ón <span "
"class=\"ui\">scáileán Léitheoireachta</span> agus leabhar á léamh agat."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3266-9
msgid ""
"<b>From the File browser:</b> Top right corner <span class=\"ui\">+ (plus) "
"menu</span> then choosing <span class=\"ui\">Folder shortcuts</span> or "
"assigning a gesture."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ón mbrabhsálaí comhad:</b> Sa chúinne uachtarach ar dheis <span "
"class=\"ui\">+ (móide) roghchlár</span> ansin roghnaigh <span "
"class=\"ui\">Aicearraí fillteáin</span> nó sannadh gotha."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3267-9
msgid "<b>From the reading screen:</b> By assigning a gesture to it."
msgstr "<b>Ón scáileán léitheoireachta:</b> Trí ghluaiseacht a shannadh dó."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3270-5
msgid ""
"It is under the <span class=\"ui\">File browser</span> section of the <span "
"class=\"ui\">Gesture manager</span>. You can learn how to set gestures in "
"the relevant section of this guide."
msgstr ""
"Tá sé faoin rannán <span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span> den <span "
"class=\"ui\">Bainisteoir Gothaí</span>. Is féidir leat foghlaim conas gothaí "
"a shocrú sa rannán ábhartha den treoir seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3276-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-viewingfiletypes"
msgid "Viewing other file types"
msgstr "Ag féachaint ar chineálacha comhad eile"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3280-1
msgid "Viewing text files"
msgstr "Ag féachaint ar chomhaid téacs"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3282-5
msgid ""
"If you have books in <b>.txt</b> format (which is more common in <b>Chinese</"
"b> and <b>Cyrillic</b> languages), you can try enabling the <span "
"class=\"ui\">Auto-detect TXT files layout</span> feature. In some cases it "
"can improve the rendering and make the text more \"book like\". When "
"enabled, the rendering engine will use heuristics (text wrapped under some "
"max line length, single or double blank lines marking paragraphs, "
"indentation or centered text considered heading...) to guess how to better "
"render the text and will try to create a <b>table of contents</b>."
msgstr ""
"Má tá leabhair agat i bhformáid <b>.txt</b> (rud atá níos coitianta i "
"dteangacha <b>Sínise</b> agus <b>Coireallach</b>), is féidir leat iarracht a "
"dhéanamh an ghné <span class=\"ui\">Leagan amach comhaid TXT a bhrath go "
"huathoibríoch</span> a chumasú. I gcásanna áirithe, is féidir leis an "
"rindreáil a fheabhsú agus an téacs a dhéanamh níos \"cosúla le leabhar\". "
"Nuair a bhíonn sé cumasaithe, úsáidfidh an t-inneall rindreála heorasticí "
"(téacs fillte faoi uasfhad líne, línte bána aonair nó dúbailte ag marcáil "
"míreanna, téacs istigh nó lárnaithe a mheastar a bheith ina "
"cheannteideal...) chun buille faoi thuairim a thabhairt ar conas an téacs a "
"rindreáil níos fearr agus déanfaidh sé iarracht <b>clár ábhair</b> a chruthú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3284-5
msgid ""
"You can enable this feature here (which is visible only if you are reading "
"a .txt file):"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat an ghné seo a chumasú anseo (nach bhfuil le feiceáil ach "
"amháin má tá comhad .txt á léamh agat):"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3286-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Style / Auto-detect TXT files layout"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_document.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Stíl / Leagan amach comhaid TXT a bhrath go "
"huathoibríoch"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3288-5
msgid ""
"Note that this feature might mess up ASCII art drawings and space character "
"based formatting. If your book has these kind of features, it might be "
"better to use the default mode in which, the text file is rendered <b>as is</"
"b> in a monospace font."
msgstr ""
"Tabhair faoi deara go bhféadfadh an ghné seo cur isteach ar líníochtaí "
"ealaíne ASCII agus ar fhormáidiú bunaithe ar charachtair spáis. Má tá na "
"cineálacha gnéithe seo i do leabhar, b'fhéidir gurbh fhearr an modh "
"réamhshocraithe a úsáid ina ndéantar an comhad téacs a rindreáil <b>mar atá</"
"b> i gcló aonspáis."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3292-1
msgid "Viewing archive files"
msgstr "Ag féachaint ar chomhaid chartlainne"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3294-5
msgid ""
"KOReader can read files stored/compressed in <b>ZIP</b> files. You can open "
"<b>ZIP</b>, <b>CBZ</b> and <b>EPUB</b> (as they are <b>ZIP</b> archives too) "
"files with the archive viewer to have a look at the contained files:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le KOReader comhaid atá stóráilte/comhbhrúite i gcomhaid <b>ZIP</"
"b> a léamh. Is féidir leat comhaid <b>ZIP</b>, <b>CBZ</b> agus <b>EPUB</b> "
"(ós rud é gur cartlanna <b>ZIP</b> iad freisin) a oscailt leis an amharcóir "
"cartlainne chun breathnú ar na comhaid atá iontu:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3297-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ol.li:3297-5"
msgid "In <span class=\"ui\">File Browser</span> long-press the file name"
msgstr ""
"I <span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span>, brúigh ainm an chomhaid ar "
"feadh i bhfad"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3298-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ol.li:3298-5"
msgid "Tap <span class=\"ui\">Open with…</span>"
msgstr "Tapáil <span class=\"ui\">Oscail le…</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3299-5
msgid "Tap <span class=\"ui\">Archive viewer</span>"
msgstr "Tapáil <span class=\"ui\">Amharcóir cartlainne</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3302-5
msgid ""
"A ZIP file can contain many types of documents like html, txt or images. "
"KOReader can open your ZIP file properly <b>only if you give it a hint for "
"the type of file in the ZIP archive</b>. If you give your file only a "
"<b>.zip</b> extension, KOReader will assume that this archive contains "
"images and try to open it like a <b>CBZ</b> file."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir go leor cineálacha doiciméad a bheith i gcomhad ZIP, ar nós html, "
"txt nó íomhánna. Ní féidir le KOReader do chomhad ZIP a oscailt i gceart "
"<b>ach amháin má thugann tú leid dó faoin gcineál comhaid atá sa chartlann "
"ZIP</b>. Má thugann tú síneadh <b>.zip</b> amháin le do chomhad, glacfaidh "
"KOReader leis go bhfuil íomhánna sa chartlann seo agus déanfaidh sé iarracht "
"é a oscailt mar chomhad <b>CBZ</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3304-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">DEFAULT CASE:</span> yourfilename<b>.zip</b> - Assumed to "
"be a zip file of images (and opened by <span class=\"ui\">MuPDF engine</"
"span>)"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">CÁS RÉAMHCHÓIRIÚCHÁIN:</span> d'ainm comhaid<b>.zip</b> - "
"Glactar leis gur comhad zip d'íomhánna é (agus oscailte ag <span "
"class=\"ui\">inneall MuPDF</span>)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3306-5
msgid ""
"If your zip file contains one of these types (instead of just images), "
"please name it accordingly:"
msgstr ""
"Más rud é go bhfuil ceann de na cineálacha seo i do chomhad zip (in ionad "
"íomhánna amháin), tabhair ainm dá réir air:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3309-9
msgid "<b>FictionBook</b> - yourfilename.<b>fb2.zip</b>"
msgstr "<b>Leabhar Ficsean</b> - d'ainm comhaid.<b>fb2.zip</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3310-9
msgid "<b>HTML</b> - yourfilename.htm.zip / yourfilename.<b>html.zip</b>"
msgstr "<b>HTML</b> - d'ainmchomhaid.htm.zip / d'ainmchomhaid.<b>html.zip</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3311-9
msgid "<b>Text log files</b> - yourfilename.<b>log.zip</b>"
msgstr "<b>Comhaid loga téacs</b> - d'ainm comhaid.<b>log.zip</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3312-9
msgid "<b>Markdown</b> - yourfilename.<b>md.zip</b>"
msgstr "<b>Markdown</b> - d'ainm comhaid.<b>md.zip</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3313-9
msgid "<b>Rich Text Format</b> - yourfilename.<b>rtf.zip</b>"
msgstr "<b>Formáid Téacs Saibhir</b> - d'ainm comhaid.<b>rtf.zip</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3314-9
msgid "<b>Plain text</b> - yourfilename.<b>txt.zip</b>"
msgstr "<b>Téacs simplí</b> - d'ainm comhaid.<b>txt.zip</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3317-5
msgid ""
"If the documents are not named like this, the wrong reader/format engine is "
"likely to be used and you will see the <span class=\"ui\">No reader engine "
"for this file or invalid file</span> message. You can rename this file as "
"explained above or long-press the filename and then choose <span "
"class=\"ui\">Open with...</span> to select the correct engine."
msgstr ""
"Mura bhfuil na doiciméid ainmnithe mar seo, is dócha go bhfuil an t-inneall "
"léitheoireachta/formáide mícheart in úsáid agus feicfidh tú an "
"teachtaireacht <span class=\"ui\">Gan inneall léitheoireachta don chomhad "
"seo nó comhad neamhbhailí</span>. Is féidir leat an comhad seo a athainmniú "
"mar a mhínítear thuas nó brúigh ar ainm an chomhaid agus ansin roghnaigh "
"<span class=\"ui\">Oscail le...</span> chun an t-inneall ceart a roghnú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3319-2
msgid "Viewing images"
msgstr "Ag féachaint ar íomhánna"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3321-5
msgid ""
"You can open image files with the image viewer instead of opening as a book. "
"Files opened like this don’t show up in your history and have better scaling "
"and rotation support."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat comhaid íomhá a oscailt leis an amharcóir íomhá in ionad iad "
"a oscailt mar leabhar. Ní thaispeántar comhaid a osclaítear mar seo i do "
"stair agus tá tacaíocht níos fearr acu maidir le scálú agus rothlú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3324-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ol.li:3324-5"
msgid "In <span class=\"ui\">File Browser</span> long-press the file name"
msgstr ""
"I <span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span>, brúigh ainm an chomhaid ar "
"feadh i bhfad"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3325-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ol.li:3325-5"
msgid "Tap <span class=\"ui\">Open with…</span>"
msgstr "Tapáil <span class=\"ui\">Oscail le…</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3326-5
msgid "Tap <span class=\"ui\">Image viewer</span>"
msgstr "Tapáil <span class=\"ui\">Breathnóir íomhánna</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3329-2
msgid "Viewing Markdown files"
msgstr "Ag féachaint ar chomhaid Markdown"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3331-5
msgid "KOReader provides two options for reading Markdown documents."
msgstr "Cuireann KOReader dhá rogha ar fáil chun doiciméid Markdown a léamh."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3333-9
msgid ""
"You can open the document directly like a book by tapping on it. This mode "
"doesn't provide formatting. So your <b>.md</b> file will look like as it is "
"opened in a text editor."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat an doiciméad a oscailt go díreach cosúil le leabhar trí "
"thapáil air. Ní sholáthraíonn an modh seo formáidiú. Mar sin, beidh cuma ar "
"do chomhad <b>.md</b> mar a osclaítear é in eagarthóir téacs."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3334-9
msgid ""
"You can convert your Markdown document to HTML. This action will render a "
"HTML file from your Markdown document with the correct formatting and a "
"<b>Table of Contents</b> created from the headings."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat do dhoiciméad Markdown a thiontú go HTML. Leis an ngníomh "
"seo, cruthófar comhad HTML ó do dhoiciméad Markdown leis an bhformáidiú "
"ceart agus <b>Clár Ábhair</b> cruthaithe ó na ceannteidil."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3337-5
msgid ""
"To convert a <b>.md</b> file, long press on it in the <span "
"class=\"ui\">File Browser</span> and tap <span class=\"ui\">Convert</span> "
"from the popup menu. A new file with the same name but HTML extension will "
"be created in the same directory. Be aware that conversion might take a "
"while depending on your Markdown file and device speed."
msgstr ""
"Chun comhad <b>.md</b> a thiontú, brúigh air go fada sa <span "
"class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span> agus tapáil <span "
"class=\"ui\">Tiontaigh</span> ón roghchlár aníos. Cruthófar comhad nua leis "
"an ainm céanna ach leis an síneadh HTML san eolaire céanna. Bíodh a fhios "
"agat go bhféadfadh tamall a bheith ag teastáil chun an tiontú a dhéanamh ag "
"brath ar do chomhad Markdown agus luas do ghléis."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3340-2
msgid "Setting file associations"
msgstr "Cumainn chomhad a shocrú"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3342-5
msgid ""
"You can also set file associations for file types which KOReader doesn’t "
"automatically recognize. To associate a file with one of the KOReader "
"providers, first long tap on your file in the <span class=\"ui\">File "
"Browser</span> then choose a provider engine to handle this file. You can "
"check:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat comhlachais comhad a shocrú freisin do chineálacha comhad "
"nach n-aithníonn KOReader go huathoibríoch. Chun comhad a cheangal le ceann "
"de sholáthraithe KOReader, tapáil ar dtús ar do chomhad sa <span "
"class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span> agus ansin roghnaigh inneall soláthraí "
"chun an comhad seo a láimhseáil. Is féidir leat seiceáil:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3345-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Always use this engine for this file</span> to associate "
"this provider with this particular file only"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Úsáid an t-inneall seo i gcónaí don chomhad seo</span> "
"chun an soláthraí seo a cheangal leis an gcomhad seo amháin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3347-9
msgid ""
"Or check <span class=\"ui\">Always use this engine for file type</span> to "
"associate this provider with all the files that has same extension as this "
"one"
msgstr ""
"Nó seiceáil <span class=\"ui\">Úsáid an t-inneall seo i gcónaí le haghaidh "
"cineál comhaid</span> chun an soláthraí seo a cheangal leis na comhaid uile "
"a bhfuil an síneadh céanna acu leis an gceann seo"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3349-9
msgid ""
"From the same dialog, you can see the associations you made by tapping on "
"<span class=\"ui\">View defaults for file types</span>"
msgstr ""
"Ón dialóg chéanna, is féidir leat na comhlachais a rinne tú a fheiceáil trí "
"thapáil ar <span class=\"ui\">Féach ar réamhshocruithe do chineálacha "
"comhad</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3358-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-collections"
msgid "Collections"
msgstr "Bailiúcháin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3360-5
msgid ""
"KOReader's <span class=\"ui\">Collections</span> feature can help you with "
"arranging your library more efficiently. As a very simple definition, "
"collections are user created lists of your books. For example you can create "
"two collections named <b>Fiction</b> and <b>Non-Fiction</b> to arrange your "
"books accordingly. Of course you can also use folders to do this but using "
"collections gives you more flexibility."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le gné <span class=\"ui\">Bailiúcháin</span> KOReader cabhrú leat "
"do leabharlann a eagrú ar bhealach níos éifeachtaí. Mar shainmhíniú an-"
"simplí, is liostaí de do leabhair iad bailiúcháin a chruthaíonn an t-"
"úsáideoir. Mar shampla, is féidir leat dhá bhailiúchán darb ainm <b>Ficsean</"
"b> agus <b>Neamhfhicsean</b> a chruthú chun do leabhair a eagrú dá réir. Ar "
"ndóigh, is féidir leat fillteáin a úsáid freisin chun seo a dhéanamh ach "
"tugann bailiúcháin níos mó solúbthachta duit."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3361-5
msgid ""
"Some advantages of collections compared to the folder based organization:"
msgstr ""
"Seo roinnt buntáistí a bhaineann le bailiúcháin i gcomparáid leis an eagrú "
"atá bunaithe ar fhillteáin:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3363-9
msgid ""
"Adding a book to a collection doesn't move the book file. So your books can "
"be located in different folders but they can appear in the same collection."
msgstr ""
"Ní bhogtar comhad an leabhair nuair a chuirtear leabhar le bailiúchán. Mar "
"sin, is féidir do leabhair a bheith suite i bhfillteáin éagsúla ach is "
"féidir leo a bheith le feiceáil sa bhailiúchán céanna."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3364-9
msgid ""
"One book can be in many collections, which is not possible with folders. For "
"example you can have a <b>Science Fiction</b> collection and <b>War Fiction</"
"b> collection. A book can be added to both of these collections at the same "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leabhar amháin a bheith i mbailiúcháin éagsúla, rud nach féidir le "
"fillteáin. Mar shampla, is féidir bailiúchán <b>Ficsean Eolaíochta</b> agus "
"bailiúchán <b>Ficsean Cogaidh</b> a bheith agat. Is féidir leabhar a chur "
"leis an dá bhailiúchán seo ag an am céanna."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3365-9
msgid ""
"You can trigger <span class=\"ui\">profiles</span> with <span "
"class=\"ui\">collections</span>. This will be explained below if you are not "
"familiar with the <span class=\"ui\">profiles</span> feature of KOReader. "
"(Of course you can trigger <span class=\"ui\">profiles</span> with folders "
"too but <span class=\"ui\">collections</span> doesn't require you to move "
"your books in order to use temporary <span class=\"ui\">profiles</span> for "
"example.)"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat <span class=\"ui\">próifílí</span> a spreagadh le <span "
"class=\"ui\">bailiúcháin</span>. Míneofar é seo thíos mura bhfuil tú eolach "
"ar ghné <span class=\"ui\">próifílí</span> KOReader. (Ar ndóigh, is féidir "
"leat <span class=\"ui\">próifílí</span> a spreagadh le fillteáin freisin ach "
"ní gá duit do leabhair a bhogadh chun <span class=\"ui\">próifílí</span> "
"sealadacha a úsáid mar shampla le haghaidh <span class=\"ui\">bailiúcháin</"
"span>.)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3368-5
msgid ""
"You can create collections to mirror any kind of categorization. Some "
"example ideas:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat bailiúcháin a chruthú chun aon chineál catagóirithe a léiriú. "
"Seo roinnt smaointe samplacha:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3370-9
msgid "<b>Genres:</b> Fiction, non-fiction, memoir..."
msgstr "<b>Seánraí:</b> Ficsean, neamhfhicsin, cuimhní cinn..."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3371-9
msgid ""
"<b>Book status:</b> Currently reading, want to read, next, did not finish..."
msgstr ""
"<b>Stádas an leabhair:</b> Ag léamh faoi láthair, ba mhaith liom é a léamh, "
"seo chugainn, níor chríochnaigh sé..."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3372-9
msgid "<b>Series:</b> Lord of the Rings, Harry Potter..."
msgstr "<b>Sraith:</b> Tiarna na bhFáinní, Harry Potter..."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3373-9
msgid "<b>Document type:</b> Books, scientific articles, web articles..."
msgstr "<b>Cineál doiciméid:</b> Leabhair, ailt eolaíochta, ailt ghréasáin..."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3378-1
msgid "Creating and modifying collections"
msgstr "Bailiúcháin a chruthú agus a mhodhnú"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3379-5
msgid ""
"You can create collections from the <span class=\"ui\">Collections</span> "
"dialog located here:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat bailiúcháin a chruthú ón dialóg <span "
"class=\"ui\">Bailiúcháin</span> atá le fáil anseo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3381-2
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_hamburger.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Collections"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/"
"top_hamburger.svg\" style=\"width:26px;\"> / Bailiúcháin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3383-2
msgid ""
"You can access this dialog from the reader view or from the <span "
"class=\"ui\">File Browser</span>. When you open this menu, it will show you "
"a list of your collections. By default you will see <span "
"class=\"ui\">Favorites</span> there as a collection item which includes the "
"books you have already added to your <span class=\"ui\">Favorites</span> "
"list."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat rochtain a fháil ar an dialóg seo ón radharc léitheora nó ón "
"<span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span>. Nuair a osclaíonn tú an "
"roghchlár seo, taispeánfar liosta de do bhailiúcháin duit. De réir "
"réamhshocraithe feicfidh tú <span class=\"ui\">Is Fearr Liom</span> ann mar "
"mhír bhailiúcháin lena n-áirítear na leabhair atá curtha agat le do liosta "
"<span class=\"ui\">Is Fearr Liom</span> cheana féin."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3386-3
msgid ""
"<b>Adding a new collection:</b> Use the hamburger menu <img "
"class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_hamburger.svg\" style=\"width:26px;"
"\"> located at the top left corner of this screen > <span class=\"ui\">New "
"collection</span>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Ag cur bailiúchán nua leis:</b> Úsáid an roghchlár hamburger <img "
"class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_hamburger.svg\" style=\"width:26px;"
"\"> atá suite sa chúinne uachtarach ar chlé den scáileán seo > <span "
"class=\"ui\">Bailiúchán nua</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3388-3
msgid ""
"<b>Removing a collection:</b> Long tap on the collection name > <span "
"class=\"ui\">Remove collection</span>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Bailiúchán a bhaint:</b> Tapáil fada ar ainm an bhailiúcháin > <span "
"class=\"ui\">Bain bailiúchán</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3390-3
msgid ""
"<b>Renaming a collection:</b> Long tap on the collection name > <span "
"class=\"ui\">Rename collection</span>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Athainmniú bailiúcháin:</b> Tapáil fada ar ainm an bhailiúcháin > <span "
"class=\"ui\">Athainmnigh bailiúchán</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3392-3
msgid ""
"<b>Changing the order of your collections:</b> Use the hamburger menu <img "
"class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_hamburger.svg\" style=\"width:26px;"
"\"> located at the top left corner of this screen > <span "
"class=\"ui\">Arrange collection</span>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Ag athrú ord do bhailiúchán:</b> Úsáid an roghchlár hamburger <img "
"class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_hamburger.svg\" style=\"width:26px;"
"\"> atá suite sa chúinne uachtarach ar chlé den scáileán seo > <span "
"class=\"ui\">Socraigh bailiúchán</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3397-1
msgid "Adding books to your collections"
msgstr "Leabhair á gcur le do bhailiúcháin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3399-2
msgid ""
"There are three different places in KOReader where you can add books to your "
"collections:"
msgstr ""
"Tá trí áit éagsúla i KOReader inar féidir leat leabhair a chur le do "
"bhailiúcháin:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3403-2
msgid "1. From the File Browser and History screen"
msgstr "1. Ón scáileán Brabhsálaí Comhad agus Stair"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3404-2
msgid ""
"You can add a book to your collections from the <span class=\"ui\">File "
"browser</span> or <span class=\"ui\">History</span> screen. From the <span "
"class=\"ui\">History</span> screen you can add books <b>one at a time</b>. "
"Long press on the book and choose <span class=\"ui\">Collections...</span>. "
"Then you can choose which collection(s) you want to add this book to."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat leabhar a chur le do bhailiúcháin ón scáileán <span "
"class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span> nó ón scáileán <span "
"class=\"ui\">Stair</span>. Ón scáileán <span class=\"ui\">Stair</span> is "
"féidir leat leabhair a chur leis <b>ceann ag an am</b>. Brúigh ar an leabhar "
"agus roghnaigh <span class=\"ui\">Bailiúcháin...</span>. Ansin is féidir "
"leat a roghnú cé acu bailiúchán/bailiúcháin ar mhaith leat an leabhar seo a "
"chur leo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3406-2
msgid ""
"If you are adding several books, you can do this from the <span "
"class=\"ui\">File browser</span>. For multiple books this is the procedure:"
msgstr ""
"Más rud é go bhfuil tú ag cur roinnt leabhar leis, is féidir leat é seo a "
"dhéanamh ón <span class=\"ui\">bhrabhsálaí comhad</span>. I gcás roinnt "
"leabhar, seo an nós imeachta:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3408-3
msgid "Long press on a book"
msgstr "Brúigh fada ar leabhar"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3409-3
msgid "Choose <span class=\"ui\">Select</span> from the popup menu"
msgstr "Roghnaigh <span class=\"ui\">Roghnaigh</span> ón roghchlár aníos"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3410-3
msgid "Select other books"
msgstr "Roghnaigh leabhair eile"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3411-3
msgid ""
"Tap the <span class=\"ui\">checkmark</span> (✔️) icon at the top-right corner"
msgstr ""
"Tapáil an deilbhín <span class=\"ui\">seicmharc</span> (✔️) sa chúinne "
"uachtarach ar dheis"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3412-3
msgid "Tap <span class=\"ui\">Collections</span>"
msgstr "Tapáil <span class=\"ui\">Bailiúcháin</span>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3415-2
msgid ""
"For adding a single book, just long-press on it in the <span "
"class=\"ui\">File browser</span> and choose <span class=\"ui\">Collections</"
"span> from the popup menu."
msgstr ""
"Chun leabhar amháin a chur leis, brúigh air ar feadh i bhfad sa <span "
"class=\"ui\">bhrabhsálaí comhad</span> agus roghnaigh <span "
"class=\"ui\">Bailiúcháin</span> ón roghchlár aníos."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3419-2
msgid "2. From the Collections menu"
msgstr "2. Ón roghchlár Bailiúcháin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3420-2
msgid ""
"This method allows you to add single and multiple books to your <span "
"class=\"ui\">Collections</span>. Biggest difference from the <span "
"class=\"ui\">File browser</span> method is that you can add <b>whole folders "
"and their subfolders</b> to your collections at once. This is very useful if "
"your books are already arranged in folders. For example if all your "
"<b>science fiction</b> books are in a single folder, you can create a "
"collection named <b>Science fiction</b> and add this folder at once."
msgstr ""
"Leis an modh seo is féidir leat leabhair aonair agus leabhair iolracha a "
"chur le do <span class=\"ui\">Bailiúcháin</span>. Is é an difríocht is mó ón "
"modh <span class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span> ná gur féidir leat "
"<b>fillteáin iomlána agus a bhfo-fhillteáin</b> a chur le do bhailiúcháin ag "
"an am céanna. Tá sé seo an-úsáideach má tá do leabhair eagraithe i "
"bhfillteáin cheana féin. Mar shampla, má tá do chuid <b>ficsean eolaíochta</"
"b> go léir i bhfillteán amháin, is féidir leat bailiúchán darb ainm "
"<b>Ficsean eolaíochta</b> a chruthú agus an fillteán seo a chur leis ag an "
"am céanna."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3425-2
msgid ""
"In the image above, <b>Box 1</b> shows the book adding options. You can "
"reach this menu from the collections screen's hamburger menu:"
msgstr ""
"Sa íomhá thuas, taispeánann <b>Bosca 1</b> na roghanna chun leabhair a chur "
"leis. Is féidir leat an roghchlár seo a bhaint amach ó roghchlár hamburger "
"an scáileáin bhailiúcháin:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3427-2
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_hamburger.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Collections / Your collection name /"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/"
"top_hamburger.svg\" style=\"width:26px;\"> / Bailiúcháin / Ainm do "
"bhailiúcháin /"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3430-3
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Add all books from a folder:</span> As its name says, "
"this options allows you to select a folder to add all the books in it to "
"this collection. Note that this option <b>doesn't add the books in "
"subfolders</b> of the chosen folder. For example if you select your "
"<b>Fiction</b> folder and you have folders named <b>Science Fiction</b> and "
"<b>War Fiction</b> under it, they won't be added with this option."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Cuir gach leabhar ó fhillteán leis:</span> Mar a deir a "
"ainm, tugann an rogha seo deis duit fillteán a roghnú chun na leabhair go "
"léir ann a chur leis an mbailiúchán seo. Tabhair faoi deara <b>nach "
"gcuireann an rogha seo na leabhair i bhfo-fhillteáin</b> den fhillteán "
"roghnaithe leis. Mar shampla, má roghnaíonn tú d'fhillteán <b>Ficsean</b> "
"agus má tá fillteáin darb ainm <b>Ficsean Eolaíochta</b> agus <b>Ficsean "
"Cogaidh</b> faoi, ní chuirfear leis an rogha seo iad."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3431-3
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Add all books from a folder and its subfolders:</span> "
"This is the option that will <b>add all the subfolders</b> of your chosen "
"folder. Be careful with this option because it will go down all the way "
"while adding the books. So if you have many levels of nested folders, there "
"might be too many books than you thought."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Cuir gach leabhar ó fhillteán agus a fho-fhillteáin leis:"
"</span> Seo an rogha a <b>chuirfidh gach fo-fhillteán leis</b> den fhillteán "
"roghnaithe agat. Bí cúramach leis an rogha seo mar go rachaidh sé síos an "
"bealach ar fad agus na leabhair á gcur leis. Mar sin, má tá go leor leibhéil "
"de fhillteáin neadaithe agat, d'fhéadfadh go mbeadh an iomarca leabhar ann "
"ná mar a cheap tú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3432-3
msgid ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Add a book to collection</span>: This is the basic option "
"that will allow you to add a single book."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"ui\">Cuir leabhar leis an mbailiúchán</span>: Seo an rogha "
"bhunúsach a ligfidh duit leabhar amháin a chur leis."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3437-1
msgid "Removing books from your collections"
msgstr "Leabhair á mbaint as do bhailiúcháin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3439-9
msgid ""
"You can remove a book from collections from the <span class=\"ui\">File "
"browser</span>, <span class=\"ui\">History</span> screen or the <span "
"class=\"ui\">Collections</span> screen. In the <span class=\"ui\">File "
"browser</span> and <span class=\"ui\">History</span> screens, long press on "
"the book and choose <span class=\"ui\">Collections...</span>. You will see a "
"checkmark next to the collections that you added this book to. Uncheck the "
"ones by tapping on it to remove the book from that collection. Also from the "
"<span class=\"ui\">Collections</span> screen, you can long press on a book "
"and choose <span class=\"ui\">Remove from collection</span>."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat leabhar a bhaint as bailiúcháin ón scáileán <span "
"class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span>, <span class=\"ui\">Stair</span> nó ón "
"scáileán <span class=\"ui\">Bailiúcháin</span>. Sna scáileáin <span "
"class=\"ui\">Brabhsálaí Comhad</span> agus <span class=\"ui\">Stair</span>, "
"brúigh fada ar an leabhar agus roghnaigh <span class=\"ui\">Bailiúcháin...</"
"span>. Feicfidh tú marc seiceála in aice leis na bailiúcháin ar chuir tú an "
"leabhar seo leo. Díthiceáil na cinn trí thapáil orthu chun an leabhar a "
"bhaint as an mbailiúchán sin. Chomh maith leis sin ón scáileán <span "
"class=\"ui\">Bailiúcháin</span>, is féidir leat brú fada ar leabhar agus "
"<span class=\"ui\">Bain as bailiúchán</span> a roghnú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3443-1
msgid "Arranging the books in your collections"
msgstr "Ag socrú na leabhar i do bhailiúcháin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3445-9
msgid ""
"Collections can be very crowded but KOReader allows you to find your books "
"easily by providing many filtering options. If you look at the image above, "
"you can see the filtering options in <b>Box 2</b> and <b>Box 3</b>. <b>Box "
"2</b> allows you to filter by book status (new, reading, finished, on hold) "
"and <b>Box 3</b> allows you to filter by book metadata (author, series, "
"language, keywords). And also you can combine these two groups of filters "
"like this example: <b>\"Show me the new books in this collection which are "
"written by Isaac Asimov <span class=\"ui\">(Filter by authors -> Isaac "
"Asimov)</span> that I haven't started yet <span class=\"ui\">(Filter by "
"status -> New)</span>.\"</b>"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le bailiúcháin a bheith an-phlódaithe ach ligeann KOReader duit do "
"leabhair a aimsiú go héasca trí roghanna scagtha iomadúla a sholáthar. Má "
"fhéachann tú ar an íomhá thuas, is féidir leat na roghanna scagtha a "
"fheiceáil i <b>Bosca 2</b> agus <b>Bosca 3</b>. Ligeann <b>Bosca 2</b> duit "
"scagadh a dhéanamh de réir stádas an leabhair (nua, á léamh, críochnaithe, "
"ar feitheamh) agus ligeann <b>Bosca 3</b> duit scagadh a dhéanamh de réir "
"meiteashonraí an leabhair (údar, sraith, teanga, eochairfhocail). Agus is "
"féidir leat an dá ghrúpa scagairí seo a chomhcheangal freisin mar an sampla "
"seo: <b>\"Taispeáin dom na leabhair nua sa bhailiúchán seo atá scríofa ag "
"Isaac Asimov <span class=\"ui\">(Scag de réir údair -> Isaac Asimov)</span> "
"nach bhfuil tosaithe agam fós <span class=\"ui\">(Scag de réir stádais -> "
"Nua)</span>.\"</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3447-9
msgid ""
"You can update the book metadata by long-pressing on the book in <span "
"class=\"ui\">File browser</span> and choosing <span class=\"ui\">Book "
"information</span> from the menu. In the popup window you can long-press on "
"any field to change the metadata like <b>author</b> or <b>keywords</b>. You "
"can also use <span class=\"external\">Calibre</span> for this task, a third-"
"party application which makes managing your book metadata much easier."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat meiteashonraí an leabhair a nuashonrú trí bhrú fada ar an "
"leabhar sa <span class=\"ui\">bhrabhsálaí comhad</span> agus <span "
"class=\"ui\">Faisnéis faoin leabhar</span> a roghnú ón roghchlár. Sa "
"fhuinneog aníos is féidir leat brú fada ar aon réimse chun na meiteashonraí "
"a athrú cosúil le <b>údar</b> nó <b>eochairfhocail</b>. Is féidir leat <span "
"class=\"external\">Calibre</span> a úsáid don tasc seo freisin, feidhmchlár "
"tríú páirtí a fhágann go bhfuil sé i bhfad níos éasca meiteashonraí do "
"leabhair a bhainistiú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3449-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">INFO</span> Be aware that <span "
"class=\"external\">Calibre</span> changes the metadata within the book "
"itself, so the changed metadata is visible outside of <span "
"class=\"external\">Calibre</span>. But KOReader doesn't change the book "
"file, it only adds custom metadata as a file in the book's <b>.sdr folder</"
"b>, so this metadata is visible in KOReader only."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">EOLAS</span> Tabhair faoi deara go n-athraíonn "
"<span class=\"external\">Calibre</span> na meiteashonraí laistigh den "
"leabhar féin, mar sin tá na meiteashonraí athraithe le feiceáil lasmuigh de "
"<span class=\"external\">Calibre</span>. Ach ní athraíonn KOReader an comhad "
"leabhair, ní chuireann sé ach meiteashonraí saincheaptha leis mar chomhad i "
"bhfillteán <b>.sdr</b> an leabhair, mar sin níl na meiteashonraí seo le "
"feiceáil ach i KOReader."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3453-1
msgid "Searching in collections"
msgstr "Ag cuardach i mbailiúcháin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3455-9
msgid ""
"There are two types of search you can perform in collections: You can search "
"for a phrase <b>in the book titles and metadata</b> or you can also search "
"<b>inside the book texts</b>. You can open the search dialog from:"
msgstr ""
"Tá dhá chineál cuardaigh ann ar féidir leat a dhéanamh i mbailiúcháin: Is "
"féidir leat frása a chuardach <b>i dteidil agus i meiteashonraí na leabhar</"
"b> nó is féidir leat cuardach a dhéanamh <b>laistigh de théacsanna na "
"leabhar</b> freisin. Is féidir leat an dialóg cuardaigh a oscailt ó:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3457-9
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_hamburger.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Collections / <img loading=\"lazy\" "
"class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_hamburger.svg\" style=\"width:26px;"
"\"> / Collections search"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/"
"top_hamburger.svg\" style=\"width:26px;\"> / Bailiúcháin / <img "
"loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/top_hamburger.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Cuardach bailiúcháin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3459-9
msgid ""
"If you want to perform a search <b>in the book texts</b>, please keep these "
"points in mind:"
msgstr ""
"Más mian leat cuardach a dhéanamh <b>i dtéacsanna an leabhair</b>, coinnigh "
"na pointí seo i gcuimhne le do thoil:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3462-13
msgid ""
"This type of search is only available if you open the <span "
"class=\"ui\">collections</span> from the <span class=\"ui\">file browser</"
"span>. It is <b>not available</b> from the reading screen."
msgstr ""
"Níl an cineál cuardaigh seo ar fáil ach amháin má osclaíonn tú na <span "
"class=\"ui\">bailiúcháin</span> ón <span class=\"ui\">bhrabhsálaí comhad</"
"span>. <b>Níl</b> sé ar fáil ón scáileán léitheoireachta."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3463-13
msgid ""
"This search can be slow (around 2 seconds per book in the collection). So if "
"you have a crowded collection, it might take a long time."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir go mbeidh an cuardach seo mall (thart ar 2 shoicind in aghaidh an "
"leabhair sa bhailiúchán). Mar sin, má tá bailiúchán plódaithe agat, "
"d’fhéadfadh sé go dtógfadh sé tamall fada."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3466-9
msgid ""
"Search function depends on where you are in the <span "
"class=\"ui\">collections</span> window. If you are at the root level where "
"you can see all your collections, search will be performed on all "
"collections. If you want to search only in a specific collection, you have "
"to tap and enter the collection. This is especially important if you are "
"also searching in the book texts because it is a slow operation."
msgstr ""
"Braitheann feidhm an chuardaigh ar an áit a bhfuil tú sa fhuinneog <span "
"class=\"ui\">bailiúcháin</span>. Má tá tú ag an leibhéal fréimhe áit ar "
"féidir leat do bhailiúcháin go léir a fheiceáil, déanfar cuardach ar na "
"bailiúcháin go léir. Más mian leat cuardach a dhéanamh i mbailiúchán ar "
"leith amháin, caithfidh tú tapáil agus dul isteach sa bhailiúchán. Tá sé seo "
"thar a bheith tábhachtach má tá tú ag cuardach i dtéacsanna an leabhair "
"freisin mar is oibríocht mhall í."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3468-9
msgid ""
"When you perform a search, results will be automatically saved as a new "
"collection."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a dhéanann tú cuardach, sábhálfar na torthaí go huathoibríoch mar "
"bhailiúchán nua."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3472-1
msgid "Automatically synchronizing collections with folders"
msgstr "Sioncrónú uathoibríoch bailiúcháin le fillteáin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3474-5
msgid ""
"After creating your collections and adding books to them, you will probably "
"want to keep them in sync with some folders. For example imagine that you "
"created a <b>Science Fiction</b> collection. And you also have a <b>SF</b> "
"folder in your library where you put your science fiction books. If you want "
"to make the <span class=\"ui\">science fiction collection</span> update "
"itself when you add a new file to this folder, you can do it with <span "
"class=\"ui\">connected folders</span> feature of the collections."
msgstr ""
"Tar éis duit do bhailiúcháin a chruthú agus leabhair a chur leo, is dócha "
"gur mhaith leat iad a choinneáil sioncrónaithe le roinnt fillteán. Mar "
"shampla, samhlaigh gur chruthaigh tú bailiúchán <b>Ficsean Eolaíochta</b>. "
"Agus tá fillteán <b>SF</b> agat i do leabharlann freisin inar chuireann tú "
"do leabhair ficsean eolaíochta. Más mian leat go ndéanfadh an <span "
"class=\"ui\">bailiúchán ficsean eolaíochta</span> é féin a nuashonrú nuair a "
"chuireann tú comhad nua leis an bhfillteán seo, is féidir leat é sin a "
"dhéanamh le gné <span class=\"ui\">fillteáin nasctha</span> na mbailiúchán."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3476-5
msgid ""
"With this feature you can connect one or more folders to your collection. "
"After that, KOReader will (re)scan the folders to add or remove books from "
"your collections in these conditions:"
msgstr ""
"Leis an ngné seo is féidir leat fillteán amháin nó níos mó a nascadh le do "
"bhailiúchán. Ina dhiaidh sin, déanfaidh KOReader scanadh (ath) ar na "
"fillteáin chun leabhair a chur le do bhailiúcháin nó a bhaint díobh sna "
"coinníollacha seo a leanas:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3479-9
msgid "When connecting a folder to a collection"
msgstr "Agus fillteán á cheangal le bailiúchán"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3480-9
msgid "When including subfolders of a connected folder"
msgstr "Agus fo-fhillteáin de fhillteán ceangailte á gcur san áireamh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3481-9
msgid "When showing the collection"
msgstr "Agus an bailiúchán á thaispeáint"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3482-9
msgid "On program start"
msgstr "Ar thús an chláir"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3486-5
msgid "How to connect a folder to your collection:"
msgstr "Conas fillteán a nascadh le do bhailiúchán:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3491-9
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ol.li:3491-9"
msgid ""
"Go to the <span class=\"ui\">Collections</span> screen that is seen in the "
"image above."
msgstr ""
"Téigh go dtí an scáileán <span class=\"ui\">Bailiúcháin</span> atá le "
"feiceáil san íomhá thuas."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3492-9
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ol.li:3492-9"
msgid ""
"Long-press on the collection name which you want to connect folders <b>(1)</"
"b>."
msgstr ""
"Brúigh go fada ar ainm an bhailiúcháin ar mhaith leat fillteáin a nascadh "
"leis <b>(1)</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3493-9
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ol.li:3493-9"
msgid ""
"Select <span class=\"ui\">Connect folders</span> from the pop-up menu "
"<b>(2)</b>."
msgstr ""
"Roghnaigh <span class=\"ui\">Ceangail fillteáin</span> ón roghchlár aníos "
"<b>(2)</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3494-9
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ol.li:3494-9"
msgid "<span class=\"ui\">List of connected folders screen</span> will open."
msgstr ""
"Osclófar an scáileán <span class=\"ui\">Liosta na bhfillteán ceangailte</"
"span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3495-9
msgid ""
"Add a folder by pressing the <span class=\"ui\">PLUS icon</span> at the top "
"left corner of that screen, which will open the <span class=\"ui\">Folder "
"chooser screen</span>."
msgstr ""
"Cuir fillteán leis trí bhrú ar an deilbhín <span class=\"ui\">PLUS</span> ag "
"an gcúinne uachtarach ar chlé den scáileán sin, rud a osclóidh an <span "
"class=\"ui\">scáileán roghnóir fillteán</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3497-9
msgid "Repeat the last item if you want to connect more folders."
msgstr ""
"Déan an mhír dheireanach arís más mian leat níos mó fillteán a nascadh."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3500-5
msgid ""
"Collections with connected folders will have a <span class=\"ui\">folder "
"icon</span> as you can see from the image above <b>(3)</b>."
msgstr ""
"Beidh deilbhín fillteáin <span class=\"ui\">ag bailiúcháin a bhfuil "
"fillteáin nasctha leo</span> mar is féidir leat a fheiceáil ón íomhá thuas "
"<b>(3)</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3502-5
msgid ""
"You might want to include subfolders of a folder too for synchronization. In "
"the <b>step 4</b> above, when you open the <span class=\"ui\">List of "
"connected folders screen</span>, you can long-press on a folder to <span "
"class=\"ui\">include/exclude subfolders</span> from the popup menu."
msgstr ""
"B’fhéidir gur mhaith leat fo-fhillteáin fillteáin a chur san áireamh freisin "
"le haghaidh sioncrónaithe. I <b>chéim 4</b> thuas, nuair a osclaíonn tú an "
"scáileán <span class=\"ui\">Liosta fillteán ceangailte</span>, is féidir "
"leat brú fada a chur ar fhillteán chun <span class=\"ui\">fo-fhillteáin a "
"chur san áireamh/a eisiamh</span> ón roghchlár aníos."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3505-5
msgid "How to disconnect a folder from your collection:"
msgstr "Conas fillteán a dhícheangal ó do bhailiúchán:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3508-9
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ol.li:3508-9"
msgid ""
"Go to the <span class=\"ui\">Collections</span> screen that is seen in the "
"image above."
msgstr ""
"Téigh go dtí an scáileán <span class=\"ui\">Bailiúcháin</span> atá le "
"feiceáil san íomhá thuas."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3509-9
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ol.li:3509-9"
msgid ""
"Long-press on the collection name which you want to connect folders <b>(1)</"
"b>."
msgstr ""
"Brúigh go fada ar ainm an bhailiúcháin ar mhaith leat fillteáin a nascadh "
"leis <b>(1)</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3510-9
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ol.li:3510-9"
msgid ""
"Select <span class=\"ui\">Connect folders</span> from the pop-up menu "
"<b>(2)</b>."
msgstr ""
"Roghnaigh <span class=\"ui\">Ceangail fillteáin</span> ón roghchlár aníos "
"<b>(2)</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3511-9
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ol.li:3511-9"
msgid "<span class=\"ui\">List of connected folders screen</span> will open."
msgstr ""
"Osclófar an scáileán <span class=\"ui\">Liosta na bhfillteán ceangailte</"
"span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ol.li:3512-9
msgid ""
"Long-press on the folder which you want to disconnect and choose <span "
"class=\"ui\">Disconnect folder</span> from the popup menu."
msgstr ""
"Brúigh go fada ar an bhfillteán ar mhaith leat a dhícheangal agus roghnaigh "
"<span class=\"ui\">Dícheangail fillteán</span> ón roghchlár aníos."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3517-1
msgid "Using Collections with Profiles"
msgstr "Ag Úsáid Bailiúcháin le Próifílí"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3519-5
msgid ""
"Your collections can be used with the <span class=\"ui\">profiles</span> "
"feature of KOReader. If you don't know about <span class=\"ui\">profiles</"
"span> yet, here is a description from our <a href=\"#L2-profiles\">Profiles</"
"a> section:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir do bhailiúcháin a úsáid leis an ngné <span class=\"ui\">próifílí</"
"span> de KOReader. Mura bhfuil a fhios agat faoi <span "
"class=\"ui\">phróifílí</span> fós, seo cur síos ónár rannán <a href=\"#L2-"
"profiles\">Próifílí</a>:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3521-5
msgid ""
"A <span class=\"ui\">profile</span> is basically a set of actions that can "
"be triggered with a single gesture (like a macro)."
msgstr ""
"Is sraith gníomhartha é <span class=\"ui\">próifíl</span> go bunúsach is "
"féidir a spreagadh le gotha amháin (cosúil le macra)."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3524-9
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.p:3524-9"
msgid ""
"As an example, imagine that when reading some type of books, you always:"
msgstr ""
"Mar shampla, samhlaigh agus tú ag léamh cineál éigin leabhar, go ndéanann tú "
"i gcónaí:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3526-13
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ul.li:3526-13"
msgid "Rotate the screen to landscape orientation"
msgstr "Rothlaigh an scáileán go dtí an treoshuíomh tírdhreacha"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3527-13
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ul.li:3527-13"
msgid "Increase the font size and contrast and"
msgstr "Méadaigh méid an chló agus an chodarsnacht agus"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3528-13
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.ul.li:3528-13"
msgid "Turn the screen light on"
msgstr "Cas solas an scáileáin air"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3531-9
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.p:3531-9"
msgid ""
"With the profiles plugin, you can do all these at once with a single action."
msgstr ""
"Leis an mbreiseán próifílí, is féidir leat iad seo go léir a dhéanamh ag an "
"am céanna le gníomh amháin."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3533-9
msgid ""
"You can run a profile manually but real power of profiles can be unleashed "
"with its <span class=\"ui\">auto-execute</span> feature. Using this feature, "
"you can trigger a profile depending on some conditions. Here is the link to "
"the relevant section of the guide: <a href=\"#L2-profileautoexec\">Profile "
"auto-execution</a>. For now we will just explain one trigger condition here: "
"<span class=\"ui\">Collections</span>."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat próifíl a rith de láimh ach is féidir fíorchumhacht próifílí "
"a scaoileadh saor lena ghné <span class=\"ui\">uath-fhorghníomhaithe</span>. "
"Agus an ghné seo á húsáid, is féidir leat próifíl a spreagadh ag brath ar "
"choinníollacha áirithe. Seo an nasc chuig an gcuid ábhartha den treoir: <a "
"href=\"#L2-profileautoexec\">Uath-fhorghníomhú próifíle</a>. Faoi láthair, "
"ní dhéanfaimid ach coinníoll spreagtha amháin a mhíniú anseo: <span "
"class=\"ui\">Bailiúcháin</span>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3535-9
msgid ""
"Basically you can create some profiles and set them to auto-execute if an "
"opened book is in some specific collection. Some useful examples:"
msgstr ""
"Go bunúsach is féidir leat roinnt próifílí a chruthú agus iad a shocrú le go "
"n-athrófar iad go huathoibríoch má tá leabhar oscailte i mbailiúchán ar "
"leith. Seo roinnt samplaí úsáideacha:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3538-13
msgid ""
"You can add all your manga to a <b>Manga</b> collection and make a profile "
"to switch the page turn direction to <b>Right-To-Left</b> and to invert page "
"turn taps and swipes when you open a manga book from this collection."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat do manga go léir a chur le bailiúchán <b>Manga</b> agus "
"próifíl a chruthú chun treo casadh an leathanaigh a athrú go <b>Deas go Clé</"
"b> agus chun sconnaí agus svaidhpeálacha casadh leathanaigh a aisiompú nuair "
"a osclaíonn tú leabhar manga ón mbailiúchán seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3539-13
msgid ""
"You can add your comic books to a collection, which can trigger a profile to "
"decrease the screen refresh interval to <span class=\"ui\">every page</span> "
"to avoid ghosting."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat do leabhair ghrinn a chur le bailiúchán, rud a fhéadfaidh "
"próifíl a spreagadh chun an t-eatramh athnuachana scáileáin a laghdú go "
"<span class=\"ui\">gach leathanach</span> chun taibhsí a sheachaint."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3540-13
msgid ""
"You can add your problematic PDFs to a collection, so when you open them "
"<span class=\"ui\">Auto OCR</span> or <span class=\"ui\">Reflow mode</span> "
"is activated with a profile."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat do PDFanna fadhbacha a chur le bailiúchán, ionas go "
"ngníomhófar <span class=\"ui\">Auto OCR</span> nó <span class=\"ui\">mód "
"Athshreafa</span> le próifíl nuair a osclaíonn tú iad."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3545-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-optimizing"
msgid "Optimizing EPUB/PDF documents for your reader"
msgstr "Doiciméid EPUB/PDF a bharrfheabhsú don léitheoir"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3547-5
msgid ""
"KOReader can reflow PDF documents (this option can be found in the bottom "
"menu while reading a fixed-layout document like PDF) to make them suitable "
"for the small screens of e-readers. But for best results, you may want to "
"convert your documents into more flexible EPUB format."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le KOReader doiciméid PDF a athshreabhadh (is féidir an rogha seo "
"a fháil sa roghchlár bun agus doiciméad le leagan amach seasta cosúil le PDF "
"á léamh) chun iad a dhéanamh oiriúnach do scáileáin bheaga léitheoirí "
"leictreonacha. Ach chun na torthaí is fearr a fháil, b'fhéidir gur mhaith "
"leat do dhoiciméid a thiontú go formáid EPUB níos solúbtha."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3549-5
msgid ""
"Most widely used applications for converting or optimizing your document for "
"your mobile reading device are <span class=\"external\">Calibre</span> "
"(<b>EPUB, Kindle</b> focused) and <span class=\"external\">K2pdfopt</span> "
"(<b>PDF</b> focused)."
msgstr ""
"Is iad na feidhmchláir is mó a úsáidtear chun do dhoiciméad a thiontú nó a "
"bharrfheabhsú le haghaidh do ghléas léitheoireachta soghluaiste ná <span "
"class=\"external\">Calibre</span> (dírithe ar <b>EPUB, Kindle</b>) agus "
"<span class=\"external\">K2pdfopt</span> (dírithe ar <b>PDF</b>)."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3551-5
msgid ""
"<a href=\"https://calibre-ebook.com/\">Calibre</a> can convert your "
"documents between many formats. It also has a built-in editor that allows "
"you to edit e-books (and fix problems) in the most popular e-book formats, "
"EPUB and Kindle."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le <a href=\"https://calibre-ebook.com/\">Calibre</a> do "
"dhoiciméid a thiontú idir go leor formáidí. Tá eagarthóir ionsuite ann "
"freisin a ligeann duit ríomhleabhair a chur in eagar (agus fadhbanna a "
"réiteach) sna formáidí ríomhleabhar is mó tóir, EPUB agus Kindle."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3553-5
msgid ""
"<a href=\"https://www.willus.com/k2pdfopt/\">K2pdfopt</a> optimizes PDF/DJVU "
"files for mobile e-readers and smartphones. It works well on multi-column "
"PDF/DJVU files and can re-flow text even on scanned PDF files. It can also "
"be used as a general PDF copying/cropping/re-sizing/OCR-ing manipulation "
"tool."
msgstr ""
"Déanann <a href=\"https://www.willus.com/k2pdfopt/\">K2pdfopt</a> comhaid "
"PDF/DJVU a bharrfheabhsú do léitheoirí ríomhleabhar soghluaiste agus do "
"fhóin chliste. Oibríonn sé go maith ar chomhaid PDF/DJVU ilcholún agus is "
"féidir leis téacs a athshreabhadh fiú ar chomhaid PDF scanta. Is féidir é a "
"úsáid freisin mar uirlis ghinearálta cóipeála/bearrtha/athmhéadaithe/"
"ionramhála OCR PDF."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3555-5
msgid ""
"<a href=\"https://github.com/ocrmypdf/OCRmyPDF\">OCRmyPDF</a> is a command "
"line application which can add an OCR text layer to scanned PDF files "
"(containing only images without text), allowing them to be searched or copy-"
"pasted. It can especially be useful for reading old scanned books. It can "
"also optimize the images for a smaller file size."
msgstr ""
"Is feidhmchlár líne ordaithe é <a href=\"https://github.com/ocrmypdf/"
"OCRmyPDF\">OCRmyPDF</a> ar féidir leis sraith téacs OCR a chur le comhaid "
"PDF scanta (ina bhfuil íomhánna gan téacs amháin), rud a ligeann dóibh a "
"bheith cuardaithe nó cóipeáilte agus greamaithe. Is féidir leis a bheith "
"úsáideach go háirithe chun seanleabhair scanta a léamh. Is féidir leis na "
"híomhánna a bharrfheabhsú freisin le haghaidh méid comhaid níos lú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3557-5
msgid ""
"<a href=\"https://github.com/gildas-lormeau/SingleFile#install\">SingleFile</"
"a> is a browser extension for <b>Mozilla Firefox, Google Chrome</b> and "
"<b>Microsoft Edge</b>. This extension allows saving a web page as a "
"<b>single .html file</b> with all the resources (images, stylesheets, "
"scripts) embedded."
msgstr ""
"Is síneadh brabhsálaí é <a href=\"https://github.com/gildas-lormeau/"
"SingleFile#install\">SingleFile</a> do <b>Mozilla Firefox, Google Chrome</b> "
"agus <b>Microsoft Edge</b>. Ligeann an síneadh seo leathanach gréasáin a "
"shábháil mar <b>chomhad .html aonair</b> leis na hacmhainní go léir "
"(íomhánna, bileoga stíle, scripteanna) leabaithe ann."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3561-1
msgid "Book metadata storage options"
msgstr "Roghanna stórála meiteashonraí leabhar"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3563-2
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.p:3563-2"
msgid "!!! ADVANCED"
msgstr "!!! CASTA"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3565-2
msgid ""
"KOReader stores settings and extra information related to your books in the "
"same directory as your book file. We call this <b>metadata</b> and it "
"includes:"
msgstr ""
"Stórálann KOReader socruithe agus faisnéis bhreise a bhaineann le do "
"leabhair san eolaire céanna le do chomhad leabhair. Tugtar <b>meiteashonraí</"
"b> air seo agus áirítear leis:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3567-3
msgid "Visual settings for the book"
msgstr "Socruithe amhairc don leabhar"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3568-3
msgid "Book reading progress"
msgstr "Dul chun cinn léitheoireachta leabhar"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3569-3
msgid "Highlights, bookmarks and notes"
msgstr "Buaicphointí, leabharmharcanna agus nótaí"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3572-2
msgid ""
"In a recent change, we added new ways of storing this metadata to solve "
"certain problems related to synchronization between devices. Currently there "
"are three different methods to store the metadata and each method has its "
"own benefits/negatives."
msgstr ""
"I n-athrú le déanaí, chuireamar bealaí nua leis chun na meiteashonraí seo a "
"stóráil chun fadhbanna áirithe a bhaineann le sioncrónú idir gléasanna a "
"réiteach. Faoi láthair tá trí mhodh éagsúla ann chun na meiteashonraí a "
"stóráil agus tá a buntáistí/míbhuntáistí féin ag baint le gach modh."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3574-2
msgid "You can change this setting from this menu:"
msgstr "Is féidir leat an socrú seo a athrú ón roghchlár seo:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3576-2
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Document / Book metadata location"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Doiciméad / Suíomh meiteashonraí an leabhair"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.p:3579-21
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_red\">WARNING</span> We strongly advise reading the "
"section below to understand the differences and how each method works before "
"making any changes. Otherwise there is a risk of losing your book settings, "
"progress and annotations."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_red\">RABHADH</span> Molaimid go láidir duit an chuid "
"thíos a léamh chun na difríochtaí agus conas a oibríonn gach modh a "
"thuiscint sula ndéanann tú aon athruithe. Seachas sin, tá baol ann go "
"gcaillfidh tú socruithe do leabhair, do dhul chun cinn agus do nótaí."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3583-1
msgid "1. Individual metadata folders next to the book files - DEFAULT SETTING"
msgstr ""
"1. Fillteáin meiteashonraí aonair in aice le comhaid an leabhair - SOCRÚ "
"RÉAMHSHOCRAITHE"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3585-3
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Document / Book metadata location: book folder"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Doiciméad / Suíomh meiteashonraí an leabhair: "
"fillteán an leabhair"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3587-2
msgid ""
"This is the <b>default</b> method used on a new installation of KOReader. In "
"this method, when you copy <b>Alice in Wonderland.epub</b> to your device "
"and open it for the first time, a folder named <span class=\"ui\">Alice in "
"Wonderland.sdr</span> will be created in the same directory. This directory "
"contains the files for your settings, annotations and book progress for this "
"book."
msgstr ""
"Seo an modh <b>réamhshocraithe</b> a úsáidtear ar shuiteáil nua de KOReader. "
"Sa mhodh seo, nuair a chóipeálann tú <b>Alice in Wonderland.epub</b> chuig "
"do ghléas agus é a oscailt den chéad uair, cruthófar fillteán darb ainm "
"<span class=\"ui\">Alice in Wonderland.sdr</span> san eolaire céanna. Tá na "
"comhaid le haghaidh do shocruithe, do nótaí agus do dhul chun cinn don "
"leabhar seo san eolaire seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3589-2
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.p:3589-2"
msgid "Benefits"
msgstr "Sochair"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3591-4
msgid "You can manually backup and restore the settings for each book."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat socruithe gach leabhair a chúltaca de láimh agus a athchóiriú."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3592-4
msgid ""
"When you perform directory synchronization or backups with a system like "
"<b>Syncthing</b> or <b>Dropbox</b>, your settings will be synchronized "
"alongside your books."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a dhéanann tú sioncrónú eolaire nó cúltacaí le córas cosúil le "
"<b>Syncthing</b> nó <b>Dropbox</b>, déanfar do shocruithe a sioncrónú in "
"éineacht le do leabhair."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3593-4
msgid ""
"You can rename the parent directories where your book resides, this doesn't "
"confuse KOReader."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat na heolairí tuismitheora ina bhfuil do leabhar a athainmniú, "
"ní chuireann sé seo mearbhall ar KOReader."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3596-2
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.p:3596-2"
msgid "Negatives"
msgstr "Diúltacha"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3598-4
msgid ""
"If you reorganize your library by moving/renaming the book files or their "
"accompanying .sdr folder outside of KOReader file browser, you will lose "
"metadata of those books without any warning."
msgstr ""
"Má atheagraíonn tú do leabharlann trí na comhaid leabhar nó an fillteán .sdr "
"a ghabhann leo a bhogadh/a athainmniú lasmuigh de bhrabhsálaí comhad "
"KOReader, caillfidh tú meiteashonraí na leabhar sin gan aon rabhadh."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3599-4
msgid ""
"These <b>.sdr</b> folders will be visible when you browse your library "
"directories with another file browser or from your computer, which may "
"clutter your view."
msgstr ""
"Beidh na fillteáin <b>.sdr</b> seo le feiceáil nuair a bhrabhsálann tú "
"eolairí do leabharlainne le brabhsálaí comhad eile nó ó do ríomhaire, rud a "
"d'fhéadfadh cur isteach ar d'amharc."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3604-1
msgid "2. Metadata directories under a single KOReader directory"
msgstr "2. Eolairí meiteashonraí faoi eolaire KOReader amháin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3606-2
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Document / Book metadata location: .../koreader/"
"docsettings"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Doiciméad / Suíomh meiteashonraí an leabhair: .../"
"koreader/docsettings"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3608-1
msgid ""
"This method is essentially same as the default one above. The difference is, "
"in this method, all <b>.sdr</b> folders of your books will be under a single "
"directory <b>which is under the KOReader main directory structure</b>, "
"instead of your library directory, next to the book files."
msgstr ""
"Tá an modh seo mar an gcéanna go bunúsach leis an gceann réamhshocraithe "
"thuas. Is é an difríocht ná, sa mhodh seo, go mbeidh gach fillteán <b>.sdr</"
"b> de do chuid leabhar faoi eolaire amháin <b>atá faoi phríomhstruchtúr "
"eolaire KOReader</b>, seachas d'eolaire leabharlainne, in aice leis na "
"comhaid leabhar."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3610-2
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.p:3610-2"
msgid "Benefits"
msgstr "Sochair"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3612-3
msgid ""
"Book <b>.sdr</b> folders will only be visible to and used by KOReader. They "
"won't clutter your view of your library directories when you browse your "
"library with another file browser or from your computer."
msgstr ""
"Ní bheidh fillteáin leabhar <b>.sdr</b> le feiceáil agus in úsáid ach ag "
"KOReader. Ní chuirfidh siad isteach ar d’eolairí leabharlainne nuair a "
"bhrabhsálann tú do leabharlann le brabhsálaí comhad eile nó ó do ríomhaire."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3615-2
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.p:3615-2"
msgid "Negatives"
msgstr "Diúltacha"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3617-3
msgid ""
"If you reorganize your library by moving/renaming the moving/renaming "
"library directories, book files or their accompanying .sdr folder outside of "
"KOReader file browser, you will lose metadata of those books without any "
"warning."
msgstr ""
"Má atheagraíonn tú do leabharlann trí na heolairí leabharlainne, na comhaid "
"leabhar nó an fillteán .sdr a ghabhann leo a bhogadh/a athainmniú lasmuigh "
"de bhrabhsálaí comhad KOReader, caillfidh tú meiteashonraí na leabhar sin "
"gan aon rabhadh."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3619-3
msgid ""
"Since your book metadata will not be in your library folders, any "
"synchronization or backups of your library will not include them."
msgstr ""
"Ós rud é nach mbeidh meiteashonraí do leabhair i bhfillteáin do "
"leabharlainne, ní bheidh siad san áireamh in aon sioncrónú ná cúltacaí de do "
"leabharlann."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3624-1
msgid ""
"3. Individual HASHED metadata directories under a single KOReader directory"
msgstr "3. Eolairí meiteashonraí HASHED aonair faoi eolaire KOReader aonair"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3626-2
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Document / Book metadata location: .../koreader/"
"hashdocsettings"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:26px;\"> / Doiciméad / Suíomh meiteashonraí an leabhair: .../"
"koreader/hashdocsettings"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3628-2
msgid ""
"This method is similar to the previous one as the <b>.sdr</b> folders will "
"be under an internal directory. But this method is developed to address the "
"shortcomings of the previous method. Because, normally if you rename a book "
"outside KOReader (with the native file manager/reader of the device or from "
"a connected computer), its <b>.sdr</b> folder name will no longer match and "
"your metadata for that book will be lost. <b>If you are only using the "
"KOReader File Browser for file operations, this is automatically handled so "
"there are no repercussions.</b>"
msgstr ""
"Tá an modh seo cosúil leis an gceann roimhe seo mar go mbeidh na fillteáin "
"<b>.sdr</b> faoi eolaire inmheánach. Ach tá an modh seo forbartha chun "
"aghaidh a thabhairt ar easnaimh an mhodha roimhe seo. Mar, de ghnáth má "
"athraíonn tú ainm leabhair lasmuigh de KOReader (leis an mbainisteoir/"
"léitheoir comhad dúchasach den fheiste nó ó ríomhaire ceangailte), ní bheidh "
"ainm a fhillteáin <b>.sdr</b> ag teacht leis an méid céanna a thuilleadh "
"agus caillfear do mheiteashonraí don leabhar sin. <b>Mura bhfuil tú ag úsáid "
"ach Brabhsálaí Comhad KOReader le haghaidh oibríochtaí comhad, déantar é seo "
"a láimhseáil go huathoibríoch agus mar sin níl aon iarmhairtí ann.</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3630-2
msgid ""
"In this <b>HASHED</b> method, <b>.sdr</b> folders are not identified by the "
"filepath/filename of the book. Instead, a partial <b>MD5 hash</b> will be "
"used to link the books to their settings. This hash is used as a unique ID "
"for the book and it is calculated based on the <b>contents of the book file</"
"b>. Also same hash is used for naming its .sdr folder."
msgstr ""
"Sa mhodh <b>HAISITHE</b> seo, ní aithnítear fillteáin <b>.sdr</b> de réir "
"chonair/ainm comhaid an leabhair. Ina áit sin, úsáidfear <b>hais MD5</b> "
"páirteach chun na leabhair a nascadh lena socruithe. Úsáidtear an hais seo "
"mar aitheantas uathúil don leabhar agus ríomhtar é bunaithe ar <b>ábhar "
"chomhad an leabhair</b>. Úsáidtear an hais chéanna freisin chun ainm a "
"thabhairt ar a fhillteán .sdr."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3633-2
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.p:3633-2"
msgid "Benefits"
msgstr "Sochair"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3635-4
msgid ""
"Book <b>.sdr</b> folders will only be visible to and used by KOReader. They "
"won't clutter your view of your library directories when you browse your "
"library directories with another file browser or from your computer."
msgstr ""
"Ní bheidh fillteáin <b>.sdr</b> leabhar le feiceáil agus ní úsáidfidh ach "
"KOReader iad. Ní chuirfidh siad isteach ar d'eolairí leabharlainne nuair a "
"bhrabhsálann tú d'eolairí leabharlainne le brabhsálaí comhad eile nó ó do "
"ríomhaire."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3637-4
msgid ""
"You can rename, move, and copy your books with another file browser or from "
"your computer. KOReader will still recognize the books after these "
"operations."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat d’leabhair a athainmniú, a bhogadh agus a chóipeáil le "
"brabhsálaí comhad eile nó ó do ríomhaire. Aithneoidh KOReader na leabhair "
"fós i ndiaidh na n-oibríochtaí seo."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3639-4
msgid ""
"In this method, KOReader associates the same <b>.sdr</b> folder with all "
"copies of the book, even if these copies are on different devices. For "
"example if you are using <b>Syncthing</b>, this method enables you to sync "
"your <span class=\"ui\">/hashdocsettings</span> folder alongside your book "
"files, across many devices that all have KOReader installed. Despite the "
"different relative paths of those books on each device, you can still get "
"your annotations and progress synchronized across your devices. This isn't "
"possible with other methods."
msgstr ""
"Sa mhodh seo, ceanglaíonn KOReader an fillteán <b>.sdr</b> céanna le gach "
"cóip den leabhar, fiú má tá na cóipeanna seo ar fheistí éagsúla. Mar "
"shampla, má tá <b>Syncthing</b> in úsáid agat, cuireann an modh seo ar do "
"chumas d’fhillteán <span class=\"ui\">/hashdocsettings</span> a shioncronú "
"in éineacht le comhaid do leabhair, trasna go leor feistí a bhfuil KOReader "
"suiteáilte orthu go léir. In ainneoin na gcosán coibhneasta éagsúla atá ag "
"na leabhair sin ar gach feiste, is féidir leat do nótaí agus do dhul chun "
"cinn a shioncronú fós trasna do fheistí. Ní féidir é seo a dhéanamh le "
"modhanna eile."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3642-3
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.p:3642-3"
msgid "Negatives"
msgstr "Diúltacha"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3644-4
msgid ""
"Any operations that modify the file directly (such as writing highlights "
"into PDFs or downloading from <b>Calibre</b>) will change the file so its "
"<b>MD5 ID will change</b> (unlike renaming or moving which is safe with this "
"method). In this case KOReader wouldn't be able to recognize the book so "
"these books will lose their metadata."
msgstr ""
"Aon oibríocht a mhodhnaíonn an comhad go díreach (amhail buaicphointí a "
"scríobh i gcomhaid PDF nó é a íoslódáil ó <b>Calibre</b>) athróidh sé an "
"comhad ionas go n-athróidh a <b>ID MD5</b> (murab ionann agus athainmniú nó "
"bogadh atá sábháilte leis an modh seo). Sa chás seo ní bheadh KOReader in "
"ann an leabhar a aithint agus mar sin caillfidh na leabhair seo a "
"meiteashonraí."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:3646-4
msgid ""
"Calculating file IDs may slow down <span class=\"ui\">File browser</span> "
"navigation when browsing larger directories."
msgstr ""
"D’fhéadfadh sé go gcuirfeadh ríomh aitheantóirí comhad moill ar nascleanúint "
"an <span class=\"ui\">bhrabhsálaí comhad</span> agus tú ag brabhsáil eolairí "
"níos mó."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3655-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L1-gestures"
msgid "GESTURES AND KEYBOARD SHORTCUTS"
msgstr "GOSANNA AGUS AICÉIRÍ MÉARCHLÁIR"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3657-5
msgid ""
"There are many types of gestures you can use to control KOReader. Some "
"gestures have limitations regarding where on the screen they can be used and "
"which directions are supported. These limitations are indicated below."
msgstr ""
"Tá go leor cineálacha gothaí ann ar féidir leat a úsáid chun KOReader a "
"rialú. Tá teorainneacha ag baint le roinnt gothaí maidir leis an áit ar an "
"scáileán ar féidir iad a úsáid agus na treoracha a dtacaítear leo. Léirítear "
"na teorainneacha seo thíos."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3660-5
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-gesturetypes"
msgid "Gesture Types"
msgstr "Cineálacha Gothaí"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3662-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">INFO</span> Some devices support only single "
"touch so multi-finger gestures <b>are not available</b> on them."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">EOLAS</span> Ní thacaíonn roinnt gléasanna ach le "
"teagmháil aonair agus mar sin <b>níl</b> gothaí ilmhéar ar fáil orthu."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3671-17
msgid "TAP / DOUBLE TAP"
msgstr "TAPÁIL / TAPÁIL FAOI DHÓ"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3672-17
msgid "Single or double tap with <b>ONE</b> finger"
msgstr "Tapáil aonair nó faoi dhó le <b>AON mhéar</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3673-17
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3673-17"
msgid "<b>WORKS:</b> Anywhere on the screen"
msgstr "<b>OIBRÍONN:</b> Áit ar bith ar an scáileán"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3680-17
msgid "TAP AND HOLD"
msgstr "TAPÁIL AGUS COINNIGH"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3681-17
msgid "Single tap and hold with <b>ONE</b> finger"
msgstr "Tapáil agus coinnigh le <b>AON mhéar</b> amháin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3682-17
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3682-17"
msgid "<b>WORKS:</b> Only on four corners"
msgstr "<b>OIBREACHA:</b> Ar cheithre choirnéal amháin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3688-17
msgid "TWO FINGER TAP"
msgstr "TAPÁIL LE DÁ MHÉAR"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3689-9
msgid "Single tap with <b>TWO</b> fingers at the same time"
msgstr "Tapáil amháin le <b>DHÁ</b> mhéar ag an am céanna"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3690-9
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3690-9"
msgid "<b>WORKS:</b> Only on four corners"
msgstr "<b>OIBREACHA:</b> Ar cheithre choirnéal amháin"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3696-17
msgid "SPREAD AND PINCH"
msgstr "LEATHNAIGH AGUS PINSE"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3697-9
msgid "Same as zooming in and out on a phone or tablet."
msgstr "Mar an gcéanna le zúmáil isteach agus amach ar ghuthán nó táibléad."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3698-9
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3698-9"
msgid "<b>WORKS:</b> Anywhere on the screen"
msgstr "<b>OIBRÍONN:</b> Áit ar bith ar an scáileán"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.div:3699-9
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">INFO</span> This gesture may work less reliably "
"depending on your device. If that’s the case please choose another gesture "
"type."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">EOLAS</span> B’fhéidir nach n-oibreoidh an "
"ghluaiseacht seo chomh hiontaofa ag brath ar do ghléas. Más amhlaidh atá, "
"roghnaigh cineál gluaiseachta eile le do thoil."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3703-17
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3703-17"
msgid "ONE FINGER SWIPE"
msgstr "SVAIDHPEÁIL MÉAR AMHÁIN"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3704-9
msgid "Swiping motion with <b>ONE</b> finger"
msgstr "Gluaiseacht svaidhpeála le <b>AON mhéar</b>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3705-9
msgid ""
"<b>WORKS:</b> Screen edges (HORIZONTAL and VERTICAL) Anywhere except edges "
"(DIAGONAL)"
msgstr ""
"<b>OIBRÍONN:</b> Imill an scáileáin (COTHROMÁNACH agus INGEARACH) Áit ar "
"bith seachas imill (TRASNÁNACH)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3709-17
msgid "TWO FINGER SWIPE"
msgstr "SVAIDHPEÁIL DÁ MHÉAR"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3710-9
msgid "Swiping motion with <b>TWO</b> fingers at the same time"
msgstr "Gluaiseacht svaidhpeála le <b>DHÁ</b> mhéar ag an am céanna"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3711-9
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3711-9"
msgid "<b>WORKS:</b> Anywhere on the screen"
msgstr "<b>OIBRÍONN:</b> Áit ar bith ar an scáileán"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3715-17
msgid "MULTISWIPE"
msgstr "IL-SVAIDHPEÁIL"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3716-9
msgid ""
"More than one swipe done after each other without lifting your finger. For "
"example like drawing the letter <b>U</b> (DOWN-RIGHT-UP)"
msgstr ""
"Níos mó ná svaidhpeáil amháin déanta i ndiaidh a chéile gan do mhéar a ardú. "
"Mar shampla, cosúil le tarraingt an litir <b>U</b> (SÍOS-DEAS-SUAS)"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3718-9
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html+html.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3718-9"
msgid "<b>WORKS:</b> Anywhere on the screen"
msgstr "<b>OIBRÍONN:</b> Áit ar bith ar an scáileán"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.table.tr.td.p:3722-17
msgid ""
"Icons by <b>Econceptive</b> from the <a href=\"https://thenounproject.com/"
"econceptive/collection/touch-gesture/\">Noun Project</a>"
msgstr ""
"Deilbhíní le <b>Econceptive</b> ón <a href=\"https://thenounproject.com/"
"econceptive/collection/touch-gesture/\">Tionscadal Noun</a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3728-1
msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-predefinedgestures"
msgid "Predefined Gestures"
msgstr "Gothaí Réamhshainithe"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3729-5
msgid ""
"This table shows the gestures that comes with KOReader. You can change these "
"gestures according to your preferences via:"
msgstr ""
"Taispeánann an tábla seo na gothaí a thagann le KOReader. Is féidir leat na "
"gothaí seo a athrú de réir do chuid sainroghanna trí:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3733-5
msgid ""
"TOP MENU / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Gesture Manager"
msgstr ""
"BARR-ROGHCHLÁR / <img class=\"img_inline\" src=\"pictures/gear.svg\" "
"style=\"width:22px;\"> / Bainisteoir Gothaí"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.div:3740-5
msgid "CORNER TAP"
msgstr "TAP CÚINNE"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.p:3742-5
msgid "<b>Top Left Corner</b> > Toggle page flipping"
msgstr "<b>Cúinne Barr ar Chlé</b> > Scoraigh an leathanach a fhilleadh"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.p:3743-5
msgid "<b>Top Right Corner</b> > Toggle bookmark"
