msgctxt "user_guide/en.html:L2-gesturecategories"
msgid "Gesture Categories"
msgstr "Catagóirí Gothaí"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:3783-5
msgid ""
"This is a list of every action that you can assign to a gesture using the "
"<span class=\"ui\">Gesture Manager</span> menu. You can use the search "
"function of your browser (generally <b>Ctrl+F</b>) to search for an action "
"here. These actions can also be used in your own <span class=\"ui\">Quick "
"Menu</span>. Please check the relevant section in the guide for more info."
msgstr ""
"Seo liosta de gach gníomh is féidir leat a shannadh do ghluaisne ag baint "
"úsáide as roghchlár <span class=\"ui\">Bainisteoir Gluaisne</span>. Is "
"féidir leat feidhm chuardaigh do bhrabhsálaí (de ghnáth <b>Ctrl+F</b>) a "
"úsáid chun gníomh a chuardach anseo. Is féidir na gníomhartha seo a úsáid i "
"do <span class=\"ui\">Roghchlár Tapa</span> féin freisin. Seiceáil an chuid "
"ábhartha sa treoir le haghaidh tuilleadh eolais."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:3786-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">INFO</span> When chooosing an action for a "
"gesture, you will see a special item in the list named <span "
"class=\"ui\">pass through</span>. This action is used to keep the default "
"behavior of that gesture, like text selection when long pressing near the "
"corners. If you want to disable a gesture to avoid accidental actions, "
"choose <span class=\"ui\">nothing</span> as the action. In other words <span "
"class=\"ui\">pass through</span>=<b>another handler might act on it</b>, "
"<span class=\"ui\">nothing</span>=<b>swallow the action</b>."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">EOLAS</span> Agus gníomh á roghnú agat le "
"haghaidh gotha, feicfidh tú mír speisialta sa liosta darb ainm <span "
"class=\"ui\">pas tríd</span>. Úsáidtear an gníomh seo chun iompar "
"réamhshocraithe an ghotha sin a choinneáil, amhail roghnú téacs nuair a "
"bhrúnn tú go fada in aice leis na coirnéil. Más mian leat gotha a dhíchumasú "
"chun gníomhartha de thaisme a sheachaint, roghnaigh <span class=\"ui\">dada</"
"span> mar an ngníomh. I bhfocail eile, <span class=\"ui\">pas tríd</"
"span>=<b>d’fhéadfadh láimhseálaí eile gníomhú air</b>, <span "
"class=\"ui\">dada</span>=<b>an gníomh a shlogadh</b>."

